===== BEGIN FILE: munart_mvp\backend\app\core\config.py (text) =====
from pydantic_settings import BaseSettings

class Settings(BaseSettings):
    POSTGRES_HOST: str
    POSTGRES_PORT: int
    POSTGRES_DB: str
    POSTGRES_USER: str
    POSTGRES_PASSWORD: str

    @property
    def database_url(self) -> str:
        return (
            f"postgresql+psycopg2://"
            f"{self.POSTGRES_USER}:{self.POSTGRES_PASSWORD}"
            f"@{self.POSTGRES_HOST}:{self.POSTGRES_PORT}/{self.POSTGRES_DB}"
        )

    class Config:
        env_file = ".env"

settings = Settings()
===== END FILE: munart_mvp\backend\app\core\config.py =====

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_mvp\backend\app\core\database.py (text) =====
from sqlalchemy import create_engine
from sqlalchemy.orm import sessionmaker
from .config import settings

engine = create_engine(
    settings.database_url,
    pool_pre_ping=True,
    future=True,
)

SessionLocal = sessionmaker(
    bind=engine,
    autocommit=False,
    autoflush=False,
)

def get_db():
    db = SessionLocal()
    try:
        yield db
    finally:
        db.close()
===== END FILE: munart_mvp\backend\app\core\database.py =====

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_mvp\backend\app\models\activity.py (text) =====
from datetime import date
from sqlalchemy import ForeignKey
from sqlalchemy.orm import Mapped, mapped_column, relationship
from .base import Base
from .enums import ActivityType

class Activity(Base):
    __tablename__ = "activities"

    id: Mapped[int] = mapped_column(primary_key=True)
    project_id: Mapped[int] = mapped_column(ForeignKey("projects.id"), nullable=False)

    name: Mapped[str]
    type: Mapped[ActivityType]

    planned_budget: Mapped[float]
    start_date: Mapped[date]
    end_date: Mapped[date]

    project = relationship("Project", back_populates="activities")
    budgets = relationship("Budget", back_populates="activity")
    contracts = relationship("Contract", back_populates="activity")
===== END FILE: munart_mvp\backend\app\models\activity.py =====

from sqlalchemy import ForeignKey
from sqlalchemy.orm import Mapped, mapped_column, relationship
from .base import Base

class Budget(Base):
    __tablename__ = "budgets"

    id: Mapped[int] = mapped_column(primary_key=True)
    activity_id: Mapped[int] = mapped_column(ForeignKey("activities.id"), nullable=False)

    year: Mapped[int]
    planned_amount: Mapped[float]
    approved_amount: Mapped[float]

    activity = relationship("Activity", back_populates="budgets")

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_mvp\backend\app\models\contract.py (text) =====
from datetime import date
from sqlalchemy import ForeignKey
from sqlalchemy.orm import Mapped, mapped_column, relationship
from .base import Base
from .enums import ContractStatus

class Contract(Base):
    __tablename__ = "contracts"

    id: Mapped[int] = mapped_column(primary_key=True)
    activity_id: Mapped[int] = mapped_column(ForeignKey("activities.id"), nullable=False)

    number: Mapped[str]
    signed_at: Mapped[date]
    amount: Mapped[float]
    status: Mapped[ContractStatus]

    activity = relationship("Activity", back_populates="contracts")
    payments = relationship("Payment", back_populates="contract")

import enum

class ProjectStatus(str, enum.Enum):
    draft = "draft"
    active = "active"
    completed = "completed"
    cancelled = "cancelled"


class ActivityType(str, enum.Enum):
    research = "research"
    production = "production"
    marketing = "marketing"


class ContractStatus(str, enum.Enum):
    planned = "planned"
    signed = "signed"
    closed = "closed"


class UserRole(str, enum.Enum):
    admin = "admin"
    manager = "manager"
    viewer = "viewer"


class ProjectRole(str, enum.Enum):
    owner = "owner"
    editor = "editor"
    viewer = "viewer"

from sqlalchemy.orm import Mapped, mapped_column
from sqlalchemy import Integer, Float
from .base import Base

class ProjectFinancialSummary(Base):
    __tablename__ = "project_financial_summary"
    __table_args__ = {"info": {"is_view": True}}

    project_id: Mapped[int] = mapped_column(Integer, primary_key=True)
    total_planned: Mapped[float] = mapped_column(Float)
    total_approved: Mapped[float] = mapped_column(Float)
    total_paid: Mapped[float] = mapped_column(Float)

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_mvp\backend\app\routers\projects.py (text) =====
from fastapi import APIRouter, Depends
from sqlalchemy.orm import Session
from app.core.database import get_db
from app.models.project import Project
from app.models.project_financial_summary import ProjectFinancialSummary

router = APIRouter()

@router.get("/")
def list_projects(db: Session = Depends(get_db)):
    rows = (
        db.query(Project, ProjectFinancialSummary)
        .outerjoin(
            ProjectFinancialSummary,
            Project.id == ProjectFinancialSummary.project_id
        )
        .all()
    )

    result = []
    for project, fin in rows:
        result.append({
            "id": project.id,
            "code": project.code,
            "name": project.name,
            "status": project.status,
            "financials": {
                "planned": fin.total_planned if fin else 0,
                "approved": fin.total_approved if fin else 0,
                "paid": fin.total_paid if fin else 0,
            }
        })

    return result
===== END FILE: munart_mvp\backend\app\routers\projects.py =====

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_mvp\backend\app\schemas\project.py (text) =====
from pydantic import BaseModel
from decimal import Decimal
from typing import List

class ProjectFinancials(BaseModel):
    approved_budget: Decimal
    contracted_amount: Decimal
    paid_amount: Decimal


class ProjectOut(BaseModel):
    id: int
    name: str
    code: str
    status: str
    financials: ProjectFinancials

    class Config:
        from_attributes = True
===== END FILE: munart_mvp\backend\app\schemas\project.py =====

WORKDIR /app

ENV MEDIA_ROOT=/data/media

EXPOSE 8000

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_mvp\db\schema.sql (text) =====
BEGIN;

CREATE TYPE project_status AS ENUM (
    'planned',
    'in_progress',
    'on_hold',
    'done',
    'cancelled'
);

CREATE TYPE activity_type AS ENUM (
    'construction',
    'equipment',
    'service',
    'other'
);

CREATE TYPE contract_status AS ENUM (
    'draft',
    'signed',
    'closed',
    'cancelled'
);

CREATE TYPE user_role AS ENUM (
    'admin',
    'manager',
    'viewer'
);

CREATE TYPE project_role AS ENUM (
    'owner',
    'editor',
    'viewer'
);

CREATE TABLE directions (
    id              SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    code            VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    name            VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description     TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE projects (
    id              SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    direction_id    INTEGER NOT NULL REFERENCES directions(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    code            VARCHAR(50) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    name            VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    status          project_status NOT NULL,
    start_date      DATE,
    end_date        DATE,
    created_at      TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
);

CREATE TABLE activities (
    id              SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id      INTEGER NOT NULL REFERENCES projects(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    name            VARCHAR(500) NOT NULL,
    type            activity_type NOT NULL,
    planned_budget  NUMERIC(15,2),
    start_date      DATE,
    end_date        DATE
);

CREATE TABLE budgets (
    id              SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    activity_id     INTEGER NOT NULL REFERENCES activities(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    year            INTEGER NOT NULL,
    planned_amount  NUMERIC(15,2) NOT NULL,
    approved_amount NUMERIC(15,2),

    UNIQUE(activity_id, year)
);

CREATE TABLE contracts (
    id              SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    activity_id     INTEGER NOT NULL REFERENCES activities(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    number          VARCHAR(100),
    signed_at       DATE,
    amount          NUMERIC(15,2) NOT NULL,
    status          contract_status NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE payments (
    id              SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    contract_id     INTEGER NOT NULL REFERENCES contracts(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    paid_at         DATE NOT NULL,
    amount          NUMERIC(15,2) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE users (
    id              SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    email           VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    password_hash   VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    role            user_role NOT NULL,
    is_active       BOOLEAN NOT NULL DEFAULT TRUE,
    created_at      TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT now()
);

CREATE TABLE project_users (
    id              SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    project_id      INTEGER NOT NULL REFERENCES projects(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    user_id         INTEGER NOT NULL REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    role            project_role NOT NULL,

    UNIQUE(project_id, user_id)
);

CREATE INDEX idx_projects_direction ON projects(direction_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_activities_project ON activities(project_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_budgets_activity ON budgets(activity_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_contracts_activity ON contracts(activity_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_payments_contract ON payments(contract_id);

CREATE VIEW project_financial_summary AS
SELECT
    p.id AS project_id,
    SUM(b.approved_amount)        AS approved_budget,
    SUM(c.amount)                 AS contracted_amount,
    SUM(pay.amount)               AS paid_amount
FROM projects p
JOIN activities a ON a.project_id = p.id
LEFT JOIN budgets b ON b.activity_id = a.id
LEFT JOIN contracts c ON c.activity_id = a.id
LEFT JOIN payments pay ON pay.contract_id = c.id
GROUP BY p.id;

COMMIT;
===== END FILE: munart_mvp\db\schema.sql =====

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_mvp\README.md (text) =====
# MunArt (betta) — MVP

## Quick start
1) Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and edit secrets.
2) `docker compose build && docker compose up -d`
3) Open `http://<server>:8080/health` → `{"status":"ok"}`
4) Seed admin:
   ```bash
   curl -X POST "http://<server>:8080/users/seed_admin?email=admin@example.com&password=StrongPass"
   ```
5) Open Swagger: `http://<server>:8080/docs` and create Project/Task.

## Notes
- Use VPN for external access if possible (WireGuard/Tailscale).
- If exposing a port to Internet: enforce HTTPS via Caddy and restrict IPs/rate-limit.
===== END FILE: munart_mvp\README.md =====

      <button class="btn" id="scan">Сканировать</button>
      <span class="muted">Оффлайн: загрузите CSV (Excel → «Сохранить как…» CSV UTF‑8). Ожидаются 2 колонки: «№ п/п», «Данные».</span>
    </div>
    <div id="sliceResult" class="muted" style="margin-top:8px">Файл не загружен</div>
    <a id="download" class="download badge" download="slice_result.csv">Скачать результат (CSV)</a>
  </div>

  <div class="card" id="panel-deep" style="display:none">
    <h3>Глубокий анализ</h3>
    <div class="stack">
      <label>Период: <input id="from" type="date">–<input id="to" type="date"></label>
      <select id="chartType">
        <option value="times">Time series + autocorr</option>
        <option value="surface">Псевдо‑3D поверхность</option>
        <option value="radar">Радар/паук</option>
        <option value="box">Box‑proxy</option>
        <option value="donuts">Мульти‑донаты</option>
      </select>
      <span class="badge">Зависимости:</span>
      <button class="badge" data-dep="proj">Провал проекта</button>
      <button class="badge" data-dep="task">Провал поручения</button>
      <button class="btn" id="build">Создать график</button>
    </div>
    <svg id="deep" class="chart" viewBox="0 0 900 340" preserveAspectRatio="none"></svg>
    <div class="legend" id="deepLegend"></div>
    <div class="muted" id="explain"></div>
  </div>

    <h3>Аномалии (тепловая матрица z‑score)</h3>
    <svg id="heat" class="chart" viewBox="0 0 900 340" preserveAspectRatio="none"></svg>
    <div class="muted">Источник: локальные проекты/поручения (localStorage).</div>
  </div>
</div>



<script>
(function () {
  const IDS = ['report','slice','deep','anoms'];

  function show(tab) {
    if (!IDS.includes(tab)) return;
    IDS.forEach(p => {
      const panel = document.getElementById('panel-' + p);
      if (panel) panel.style.display = (p === tab ? 'block' : 'none');
    });
    document.querySelectorAll('.tab').forEach(x =>
      x.classList.toggle('active', x.dataset.tab === tab)
    );
  }

  // 1) Инициализация из URL (?tab=...)
  const m = location.search.match(/[?&]tab=(report|slice|deep|anoms)/);
  if (m) show(m[1]);

  // 2) Слушатель из родителя (React-вкладки)
  window.addEventListener('message', (e) => {
    if (e.origin !== location.origin) return; // важно: тот же origin
    const d = e.data || {};
    if (d.type === 'analytics:setTab' && d.tab) show(d.tab);
  }, false);
})();
</script>





<script>
document.querySelectorAll('.tab').forEach(t=>t.onclick=()=>{
  document.querySelectorAll('.tab').forEach(x=>x.classList.toggle('active', x===t));
  const id = t.dataset.tab;
  ['report','slice','deep','anoms'].forEach(p=> document.getElementById('panel-'+p).style.display = (p===id?'block':'none'));
});
function parseCSV(text){
  const rows=[]; let cur='', row=[], inQ=false;
  for(let i=0;i<text.length;i++){
    const c=text[i];
    if(c==='"'){ if(inQ && text[i+1]==='"'){ cur+='"'; i++; } else { inQ=!inQ; } }
    else if(c===',' && !inQ){ row.push(cur); cur=''; }
    else if((c==='\n' || c==='\r') && !inQ){ if(cur!=='' || row.length){ row.push(cur); rows.push(row); row=[]; cur=''; } }
    else { cur+=c; }
  }
  if(cur!=='' || row.length) { row.push(cur); rows.push(row); }
  return rows.filter(r=>r.some(x=>x!==''));
}
const $ = (id)=>document.getElementById(id);
$('scan').onclick = async () => {
  const kw = $('kw').value?.trim().toLowerCase();
  const f = $('file').files?.[0];
  if(!f){ $('sliceResult').textContent='Нет файла'; return; }
  const text = await f.text();
  const rows = parseCSV(text);
  const head = rows[0]||[];
  const dataCol = head.findIndex(h => /данн/i.test(h));
  const noCol = head.findIndex(h => /№/i.test(h) || /n/i.test(h));
  const out = [ ['№ п/п','Данные'] ];
  rows.slice(1).forEach(r=>{
     const s = (r[dataCol]||'')+'';
     if(!kw || s.toLowerCase().includes(kw)) out.push([r[noCol]||'', r[dataCol]||'']);
  });
  $('sliceResult').textContent = `Строк найдено: ${out.length-1}`;
  const csv = out.map(r=>r.map(x=>(''+(x??'')).replace(/"/g,'""')).map(x=>`"${x}"`).join(',')).join('\n');
  const blob = new Blob([csv], {type:'text/csv;charset=utf-8'});
  const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
  const a=$('download'); a.href=url; a.style.display='inline-flex';
};
function clear(el){ while(el.firstChild) el.removeChild(el.firstChild); }
function line(svg,x1,y1,x2,y2,attr={}){ const e=document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','line'); e.setAttribute('x1',x1);e.setAttribute('y1',y1);e.setAttribute('x2',x2);e.setAttribute('y2',y2); Object.entries(attr).forEach(([k,v])=>e.setAttribute(k,v)); svg.appendChild(e); return e;}
function rect(svg,x,y,w,h,attr={}){ const e=document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','rect'); e.setAttribute('x',x);e.setAttribute('y',y);e.setAttribute('width',w);e.setAttribute('height',h); Object.entries(attr).forEach(([k,v])=>e.setAttribute(k,v)); svg.appendChild(e); return e;}
function path(svg,d,attr={}){ const e=document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','path'); e.setAttribute('d',d); Object.entries(attr).forEach(([k,v])=>e.setAttribute(k,v)); svg.appendChild(e); return e;}
function text(svg,x,y,t,attr={}){ const e=document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','text'); e.setAttribute('x',x); e.setAttribute('y',y); e.textContent=t; Object.entries(attr).forEach(([k,v])=>e.setAttribute(k,v)); svg.appendChild(e); return e;}
let deps = {proj:false, task:false};
document.querySelectorAll('[data-dep]').forEach(b=>b.onclick=()=>{
  const k=b.dataset.dep; deps[k]=!deps[k]; b.style.outline = deps[k]?'2px solid #60a5fa':'';
});
const projects = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_projects_v1')||'[]');
const tasks    = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_tasks_v1')||'[]');
function calcRisks(){
  const in7 = new Date(Date.now()+7*864e5);
  const riskyProj = projects.filter(p=>{
    const due = p.due? new Date(p.due): null;
    const progress = +p.progress||0;
    const fullyPaid = ((+(p.budget_spent||0) >= +(p.budget_plan||0)) || +(p.budget_plan||0)===0);
    const late = due && due < in7 && progress < 95;
    const overspend = (+(p.budget_plan||0)>0) && (+(p.budget_spent||0) > +(p.budget_plan||0)) && progress < 100;
    return (late && fullyPaid) || overspend;
  });
  const riskyTasks = tasks.filter(t=>{
    const due = t.due? new Date(t.due): null;
    const progress = +t.progress||0;
    return (due && due < in7 && progress < 95);
  });
  return { riskyProj, riskyTasks };
}
function buildDeep(){
  const type = document.getElementById('chartType').value;
  const svg = document.getElementById('deep');
  while(svg.firstChild) svg.removeChild(svg.firstChild);

  const W=900,H=340,pad=40, area={x:pad,y:pad,w:W-2*pad,h:H-2*pad};
  const ns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg';
  const defs=document.createElementNS(ns,'defs');
  defs.innerHTML = `
    <linearGradient id="g-blue" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0" stop-color="#60a5fa"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#3b82f6"/></linearGradient>
    <linearGradient id="g-red"  x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0" stop-color="#f87171"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#ef4444"/></linearGradient>
    <linearGradient id="g-green"x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0" stop-color="#34d399"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#22c55e"/></linearGradient>
    <filter id="glow"><feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="3" result="b"/><feMerge><feMergeNode in="b"/><feMergeNode in="SourceGraphic"/></feMerge></filter>
  `;
  svg.appendChild(defs);

  // рамка
  const rect=(x,y,w,h,a={})=>{const e=document.createElementNS(ns,'rect'); e.setAttribute('x',x); e.setAttribute('y',y); e.setAttribute('width',w); e.setAttribute('height',h); for(const k in a)e.setAttribute(k,a[k]); svg.appendChild(e); return e;}
  const path=(d,a={})=>{const e=document.createElementNS(ns,'path'); e.setAttribute('d',d); for(const k in a)e.setAttribute(k,a[k]); svg.appendChild(e); return e;}
  const line=(x1,y1,x2,y2,a={})=>{const e=document.createElementNS(ns,'line'); e.setAttribute('x1',x1);e.setAttribute('y1',y1);e.setAttribute('x2',x2);e.setAttribute('y2',y2); for(const k in a)e.setAttribute(k,a[k]); svg.appendChild(e); return e;}

  rect(area.x, area.y, area.w, area.h, {fill:'url(#panelGrad)', opacity:.04, stroke:'#334155', 'stroke-width':1});

  // пояснение рисков (останется как было)
  const {riskyProj, riskyTasks} = calcRisks();
  const explain=[];
  if(deps.proj) explain.push(`«Провал проекта»: дедлайн < 7дн и прогресс <95% (или перерасход). Найдено: ${riskyProj.length}`);
  if(deps.task) explain.push(`«Провал поручения»: дедлайн < 7дн и прогресс <95%. Найдено: ${riskyTasks.length}`);
  document.getElementById('explain').textContent = explain.join(' • ') || '—';

  /* ---------- красивые режимы ---------- */
  if (type === 'times') {
    // Time-series с подсветкой и полупрозрачной заливкой
    const n=100, ys1=Array.from({length:n},()=>Math.random()*2-1), ys2=Array.from({length:n},()=>Math.random()*2-1);
    const sx=i=>area.x+i*(area.w/(n-1)), sy=v=>area.y+area.h-(v+1)/2*area.h;
    const poly=(ys,grad,alpha)=>{let d='M '+sx(0)+' '+sy(ys[0]); for(let i=1;i<n;i++) d+=' L '+sx(i)+' '+sy(ys[i]); path(d,{fill:'none',stroke:`url(#${grad})`,'stroke-width':2,filter:'url(#glow)'});};
    // сетка
    for(let i=0;i<=5;i++) line(area.x, area.y+i*(area.h/5), area.x+area.w, area.y+i*(area.h/5), {stroke:'#334155','stroke-dasharray':'2 4',opacity:.6});
    poly(ys1,'g-blue'); poly(ys2,'g-red');
  }
  else if (type === 'surface') {
    // псевдо-3D решётка с «барханами»
    const cols=26, rows=16, cx=area.x+area.w/2, cy=area.y+area.h*0.75;
    const sx=(i,j)=>cx + (i-cols/2)*14 + (j-rows/2)*-6;
    const sy=(i,j,v)=>cy - (j-rows/2)*10 - v*22;
    for(let j=0;j<rows;j++){
      for(let i=0;i<cols;i++){
        const r = Math.hypot(i-cols/2, j-rows/2)/Math.hypot(cols/2,rows/2);
        const v = Math.max(0, 1 - r*r) + 0.15*Math.random();
        const x=sx(i,j), y=sy(i,j,v);
        rect(x-3, y-2, 6, 2+v*18, {fill:'url(#g-green)', opacity:.85, rx:2, ry:2});
      }
    }
  }
  else if (type === 'radar') {
    // паук с мягкой заливкой и свечением
    const axes=6, r=area.h*0.42, cx=area.x+area.w/2, cy=area.y+area.h/2;
    for(let k=1;k<=4;k++) path([...Array(axes)].map((_,a)=>{const ang=a*2*Math.PI/axes; const rr=r*k/4; const x=cx+rr*Math.cos(ang), y=cy+rr*Math.sin(ang); return (a?' L ':'M ')+x+' '+y;}).join('')+' Z',{fill:'none',stroke:'#334155','stroke-dasharray':'2 6'});
    const A=[.6,.9,.5,.7,.4,.8], B=[.3,.5,.8,.4,.9,.6];
    const poly=(vals,col)=>{let d=''; for(let a=0;a<axes;a++){const ang=a*2*Math.PI/axes; const rr=r*(0.35+0.65*vals[a]); const x=cx+rr*Math.cos(ang), y=cy+rr*Math.sin(ang); d+=(a?' L ':'M ')+x+' '+y;} d+=' Z'; path(d,{fill:col,opacity:.28,stroke:col,filter:'url(#glow)'});};
    poly(A,'#60a5fa'); poly(B,'#f87171');
  }
  else if (type === 'box') {
    // упрощённый box-proxy с яркой палитрой
    const cats=6; const w=(area.w/cats)*0.6; const base=Array.from({length:cats},()=>Math.random()*100);
    for(let i=0;i<cats;i++){
      const v=base[i]; const x=area.x + (i+0.2)*(area.w/cats); const h=v/100*area.h;
      rect(x,area.y+area.h-h,w,h,{fill:'url(#g-blue)',opacity:.9,rx:4,ry:4});
    }
  }
  else { // donuts
    const cx=area.x+area.w/2, cy=area.y+area.h/2, r=area.h*0.36;
    const vals=[12,7,3,8], sum=vals.reduce((a,b)=>a+b,0); let a0=-Math.PI/2;
    const colors=['url(#g-green)','url(#g-blue)','url(#g-red)','#f59e0b'];
    vals.forEach((v,i)=>{const a1=a0+2*Math.PI*v/sum; const x0=cx+r*Math.cos(a0),y0=cy+r*Math.sin(a0),x1=cx+r*Math.cos(a1),y1=cy+r*Math.sin(a1),lg=(a1-a0)>Math.PI?1:0; path(`M ${x0} ${y0} A ${r} ${r} 0 ${lg} 1 ${x1} ${y1} L ${cx} ${cy} Z`,{fill:colors[i],opacity:.95,filter:'url(#glow)'}); a0=a1;});
  }
}

document.getElementById('build').onclick = buildDeep;
(function(){
  const svg=document.getElementById('heat'); clear(svg);
  const W=900,H=340,pad=40; const area={x:pad,y:pad,w:W-2*pad,h:H-2*pad};
  rect(svg,area.x,area.y,area.w,area.h,{fill:'rgba(255,255,255,0.02)',stroke:'#334155','stroke-width':1});
  const fields=['budget_plan','budget_spent','progress','risk'];
  const items=(JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_projects_v1')||'[]')).concat(
    (JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_tasks_v1')||'[]')).map(t=>({budget_plan:0,budget_spent:0,progress:+t.progress||0,risk:10})) );
  const arrs=fields.map(f=>items.map(x=>+x[f]||0)); const zs=arrs.map(a=>{const m=a.reduce((s,v)=>s+v,0)/Math.max(1,a.length); const sd=Math.sqrt(a.reduce((s,v)=>s+(v-m)*(v-m),0)/Math.max(1,a.length))||1; return a.map(v=>(v-m)/sd);});
  const nx=fields.length, ny=Math.max(1,items.length); const cw=area.w/nx, ch=area.h/ny;
  for(let i=0;i<nx;i++){ for(let j=0;j<ny;j++){ const v=zs[i][j]||0; const r=v>0?240:0, b=v<0?240:0, a=Math.min(0.95, Math.abs(v)/2); rect(svg,area.x+i*cw, area.y+j*ch, cw-2, ch-2, {fill:`rgba(${r},100,${b},${a})`}); } text(svg, area.x+i*cw+4, area.y-8, fields[i], {fill:'#94a3b8','font-size':12}); }
})();
</script>

</html>

/* Dark-friendly soft glows (so the dark theme on the page doesn't look "blown out") */
@media (prefers-color-scheme: dark){
  #nearestCard.qa--ok{
    background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(34,197,94,.12), transparent);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(34,197,94,.18), inset 0 0 0 2px rgba(34,197,94,.18);

<script>
// ===== MunArt DOM-defer shim (v2): минимально-инвазивный =====
// 1) Не трогаем jQuery ($) вообще.
// 2) Никогда не подменяем элементы, связанные с темой ('theme','dark','mode','scheme','color').
// 3) Прокси выдаём только для отсутствующих узлов, чтобы не падали ранние ".onclick = ..." и т.п.
(function(){
  if (window.__munartDeferShimV2) return; window.__munartDeferShimV2 = true;
  const EXCEPT_RE = /(theme|dark|mode|scheme|color)/i;

  const pending = new Map(); // id -> {props:{}, listeners:[]}
  function ensure(id){
    if (!pending.has(id)) pending.set(id, {props:{}, listeners:[]});
    return pending.get(id);
  }
  function flush(id){
    const data = pending.get(id);
    const el = _get(id);
    if (!el || !data) return;
    // применяем сохранённые присваивания/листенеры
    for (const [k,v] of Object.entries(data.props)){
      try{ el[k] = v; }catch(_){}
    }
    for (const [type,fn,opts] of data.listeners){
      try{ el.addEventListener(type, fn, opts||false); }catch(_){}
    }
    pending.delete(id);
  }
  function proxyFor(id){
    const data = ensure(id);
    return new Proxy({}, {
      get(_, prop){
        if (prop === 'addEventListener') return function(type, fn, opts){ data.listeners.push([type,fn,opts]); };
        if (prop === 'style') return new Proxy({}, { set(_s, k, v){ (data.props.style||(data.props.style={}))[k]=v; return true; }, get(){ return {}; } });
        if (prop === 'classList') return { add(){}, remove(){}, toggle(){} };
        if (prop === 'dataset') return {};
        return function(){ /* заглушки методов */ };
      },
      set(_, prop, value){ data.props[prop] = value; return true; }
    });
  }
  const _get = Document.prototype.getElementById.bind(document);
  function safeGet(id){
    // для сущностей, влияющих на тему — никогда не подменяем: возвращаем реальный результат (вплоть до null)
    if (EXCEPT_RE.test(String(id))) return _get(id);
    const el = _get(id);
    return el || proxyFor(id);
  }
  Document.prototype.getElementById = function(id){ return safeGet(id); };

  function tryFlushAll(){ for (const id of Array.from(pending.keys())) flush(id); }
  new MutationObserver(tryFlushAll).observe(document.documentElement, {subtree:true, childList:true});
  window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', tryFlushAll);
  window.addEventListener('load', tryFlushAll);
})();
</script>

  <script>
    (function () {
      var q = new URLSearchParams(location.search);
      var embed = q.get('embed') === '1' || localStorage.getItem('munart_embed') === '1';
      if (embed) {
        document.documentElement.classList.add('embedded');
        var s = document.getElementById('for-embed');
        if (s) s.disabled = false;
      }
    })();
  </script>

                <button type="button" class="multi-select-toggle" id="fResponsibleToggle">
                  <span id="fResponsibleSummary">Не выбраны</span>
                </button>
                <div class="multi-select-menu" id="fResponsibleMenu">
                  <div id="fResponsible" class="multi-flags"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid g2">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="fType">Тип поручения</label>
            <select id="fType">
              <option value="hardware">Аппаратные</option>
              <option value="field">Выездные</option>

          </div>

  </div>

  <!-- JS -->
  <script>
    // THEME
    const root = document.body;
    function setTheme(mode){ root.classList.toggle('theme-dark', mode==='dark'); }
    function toggleTheme(){ root.classList.toggle('theme-dark'); localStorage.setItem('munart_theme', root.classList.contains('theme-dark')?'dark':'light'); }
    setTheme(localStorage.getItem('munart_theme')||'light');

    // AUTH
    const curtain = document.getElementById('curtain');
    function getUser(){ try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_auth')) }catch(e){ return null } }
    function setUser(u){ localStorage.setItem('munart_auth', JSON.stringify(u)); }
    function logout(){ localStorage.removeItem('munart_auth'); location.reload(); }
    function ensureAuth(){ const u = getUser(); if(!u){ curtain.classList.add('show'); } else { hydrateProfile(u); } }
    ensureAuth();
    document.getElementById('btnLogin').onclick = ()=>{
      const e = document.getElementById('authEmail').value.trim();
      const p = document.getElementById('authPass').value.trim();
      const err = document.getElementById('authErr');
      if(!e || p.length < 4){ err.style.display='block'; return; }
      const u = { email:e, name: e.split('@')[0], role:'Менеджер проектов', org:'MunArt LLC', lang:'ru', session: Math.random().toString(36).slice(2,10) };
      setUser(u); curtain.classList.remove('show'); hydrateProfile(u);
    };
    document.getElementById('toggleThemeLogin').onclick = toggleTheme;

    // PROFILE
    const drawer = document.getElementById('drawer');
    document.getElementById('btnProfile').onclick = ()=> drawer.classList.add('show');
    document.getElementById('btnCloseDrawer').onclick = ()=> drawer.classList.remove('show');
    document.getElementById('btnLogout').onclick = logout;
    document.getElementById('btnTheme').onclick = toggleTheme;
    document.getElementById('btnSaveProfile').onclick = ()=>{
      const u = getUser(); if(!u) return;
      u.org = document.getElementById('profOrg').value;
      u.lang = document.getElementById('profLang').value;
      u.name = document.getElementById('profName').textContent || u.name;
      setUser(u); alert('Сохранено');
    };
    function hydrateProfile(u){
      document.getElementById('profName').textContent = u.name || 'User';
      document.getElementById('profRole').textContent = u.role || '—';
      document.getElementById('profEmail').textContent = u.email || '—';
      document.getElementById('profOrg').value = u.org || '';
      document.getElementById('profLang').value = u.lang || 'ru';
      document.getElementById('profSession').textContent = u.session || '—';
      document.getElementById('profAvatar').textContent = (u.name||'U').slice(0,1).toUpperCase();
    }

    // NAV
    const menu = document.getElementById('menu');
    menu.querySelectorAll('button').forEach(btn=> btn.onclick = ()=> {
      if(btn.dataset.page==='tasks') return;
      alert('В этом офлайн-файле реализована страница «Поручения». Проекты — в предыдущем файле.');
    });

    // SIDEBAR
    const side = document.getElementById('sidebar');
    document.getElementById('btnCollapse').onclick = ()=> side.classList.toggle('collapsed');

    // UTIL
    function spark(n, base, spread){ const arr=[]; for(let i=0;i<n;i++){ arr.push(base + Math.round((Math.random()-.5)*spread)); } return arr; }
    function escapeHtml(s){ return s.replace(/[&<>"]/g, c=>({ '&':'&amp;','<':'&lt;','>':'&gt;','"':'&quot;' }[c])); }
	function debounce(fn, wait=120){ let t; return (...a)=>{ clearTimeout(t); t=setTimeout(()=>fn(...a), wait); }; }
	function cssrgb(name){ return `rgb(var(${name}))`; }

	const STATUS_ORDER = ['todo','in_progress','review','done'];
	const STATUS_TITLE = { todo:'К созданию', in_progress:'В работе', review:'На проверке', done:'Готово' };

    const PRIORITY_TITLE = { low:'Низкий', med:'Средний', high:'Высокий' };
    const TASK_TYPE_TITLE = { hardware:'Аппаратные', other:'Прочие' };

    function formatResponsibles(list, fallback){
      const arr = Array.isArray(list) ? list.filter(Boolean) : [];
      if (arr.length === 0) return fallback || '—';
      if (arr.length === 1) return arr[0];
      return `${arr[0]} (и ещё ${arr.length-1})`;
    }

    function getColCollapsed(key){
      try{ return localStorage.getItem('munart_tasks_col_collapsed_'+key) === '1'; }catch(_){ return false; }
    }
    function setColCollapsed(key, val){
      try{ localStorage.setItem('munart_tasks_col_collapsed_'+key, val ? '1' : '0'); }catch(_){}
    }

    function getOverdueExpanded(){
      try{ return localStorage.getItem('munart_tasks_overdue_expanded') === '1'; }catch(_){ return false; }
    }
    function setOverdueExpanded(val){
      try{ localStorage.setItem('munart_tasks_overdue_expanded', val ? '1' : '0'); }catch(_){}
      const sel = document.getElementById('overdueSelect');
      const cur = document.getElementById('overdueCurrent');
      const tog = document.getElementById('overdueToggle');
      if (sel) sel.style.display = val ? 'block' : 'none';
      if (cur) cur.style.display = val ? 'none' : 'block';
      if (tog) tog.textContent = val ? '▾' : '▸';
    }

    // ---- summary to parent (React shell)
    function readTasksForSummary(){
      try{
        const arr = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_tasks_v1')||'[]');
        if (Array.isArray(arr) && arr.length) return arr;
      }catch(_){}
      const dom = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('[data-status]'));
      if (dom.length) return dom.map(el => ({ status: String(el.getAttribute('data-status')||'todo') }));
      return [];
    }
    function sendTasksSummary(){
      try{
        const items = readTasksForSummary();
        const sum = { todo:0, inprogress:0, done:0 };
        items.forEach(t => {
          const key = t.status === 'in_progress' ? 'inprogress'
                   : t.status === 'done'        ? 'done'
                   : 'todo';
          sum[key]++;
        });
        if (window.parent && window.parent !== window) {
          window.parent.postMessage({ type:'munart:tasks-summary', payload: sum }, location.origin);
        }
      }catch(_){}
    }
    (function(){
      sendTasksSummary();
      window.addEventListener('storage', (e)=>{ if (e.key === 'munart_tasks_v1') sendTasksSummary(); });
      const mo = new MutationObserver(()=> sendTasksSummary());
      mo.observe(document.documentElement, { childList:true, subtree:true, attributes:true });
    })();

    /* ==== ГРАФИКИ (определены ДО render) ==== */
    function areaChart(el, data, color){
      const w = el.clientWidth || 300, h = el.clientHeight || 96, p=8;
      const max = Math.max(...data), min = Math.min(...data);
      const sx = (i)=> p + i*( (w-2*p)/(data.length-1) );
      const sy = (v)=> h - p - ( (v-min) / (max-min || 1) )*(h-2*p);
      let d = `M ${p} ${h-p} `; data.forEach((v,i)=> d += `L ${sx(i)} ${sy(v)} `); d += `L ${w-p} ${h-p} Z`;
      el.innerHTML = `<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="${d}" fill="rgba(34,197,94,.18)" stroke="${color}" stroke-width="2"/></svg>`;
    }
    function donutChart(el, values, colors){
      const w = el.clientWidth || 300, h = el.clientHeight || 180, r = Math.min(w,h)/2 - 10, cx=w/2, cy=h/2;
      const total = values.reduce((s,x)=>s+x,0) || 1; let start = 0, html='';
      values.forEach((v,i)=>{ const a=(v/total)*Math.PI*2, end = start+a;
        const x1=cx+r*Math.cos(start), y1=cy+r*Math.sin(start), x2=cx+r*Math.cos(end), y2=cy+r*Math.sin(end), large=a>Math.PI?1:0;
        html += `<path d="M${cx} ${cy} L ${x1} ${y1} A ${r} ${r} 0 ${large} 1 ${x2} ${y2} Z" fill="${colors[i]}"/>`; start=end; });
      el.innerHTML = `<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none">${html}<circle cx="${cx}" cy="${cy}" r="${r*0.6}" fill="var(--panel)" stroke="var(--brd)"/></svg>`;
    }
    function lineChart(el, data, color){
      const w=el.clientWidth||300,h=el.clientHeight||96,p=8;
      const max=Math.max(...data),min=Math.min(...data);
      const sx=i=>p+i*((w-2*p)/(data.length-1));
      const sy=v=>h-p-((v-min)/(max-min||1))*(h-2*p);
      let d=`M ${sx(0)} ${sy(data[0])}`;
      for(let i=1;i<data.length;i++) d+=` L ${sx(i)} ${sy(data[i])}`;
      el.innerHTML=`<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="${d}" fill="none" stroke="${color}" stroke-width="2"/></svg>`;
    }
    function barChart(el, data, color){
      const w=el.clientWidth||300,h=el.clientHeight||96,p=8;
      const max=Math.max(...data),min=Math.min(...data);
      const bw=(w-2*p)/data.length*0.7, gap=(w-2*p)/data.length;
      const sy=v=>h-p-((v-min)/(max-min||1))*(h-2*p);
      let rects='';
      data.forEach((v,i)=>{
        const x=p+i*gap+(gap-bw)/2, y=sy(v), rh=h-p-y;
        rects+=`<rect x="${x}" y="${y}" width="${bw}" height="${Math.max(1,rh)}" fill="${color}" opacity=".6"/>`;
      });
      el.innerHTML=`<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none">${rects}</svg>`;
    }
    function stepChart(el, data, color){
      const w=el.clientWidth||300,h=el.clientHeight||96,p=8;
      const max=Math.max(...data),min=Math.min(...data);
      const sx=i=>p+i*((w-2*p)/(data.length-1));
      const sy=v=>h-p-((v-min)/(max-min||1))*(h-2*p);
      let d=`M ${sx(0)} ${sy(data[0])}`;
      for(let i=1;i<data.length;i++){ d+=` H ${sx(i)} V ${sy(data[i])}`; }
      el.innerHTML=`<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="${d}" fill="none" stroke="${color}" stroke-width="2"/></svg>`;
    }
    function dotsChart(el, data, color){
      const w=el.clientWidth||300,h=el.clientHeight||96,p=8,r=3;
      const max=Math.max(...data),min=Math.min(...data);
      const sx=i=>p+i*((w-2*p)/(data.length-1));
      const sy=v=>h-p-((v-min)/(max-min||1))*(h-2*p);
      let pts=''; data.forEach((v,i)=> pts+=`<circle cx="${sx(i)}" cy="${sy(v)}" r="${r}" fill="${color}"/>`);
      el.innerHTML=`<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none">${pts}</svg>`;
    }
    function pieChart(el, values, colors){
      const w=el.clientWidth||300,h=el.clientHeight||180,cx=w/2,cy=h/2,r=Math.min(w,h)/2-10;
      const total=values.reduce((s,x)=>s+x,0)||1; let start=0,html='';
      values.forEach((v,i)=>{const a=(v/total)*Math.PI*2,end=start+a;
        const x1=cx+r*Math.cos(start),y1=cy+r*Math.sin(start),x2=cx+r*Math.cos(end),y2=cy+r*Math.sin(end),large=a>Math.PI?1:0;
        html+=`<path d="M${cx} ${cy} L ${x1} ${y1} A ${r} ${r} 0 ${large} 1 ${x2} ${y2} Z" fill="${colors[i]}"/>`; start=end;});
      el.innerHTML=`<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none">${html}</svg>`;
    }
    function gaugeChart(el, valuePct){
      const w=el.clientWidth||300,h=el.clientHeight||180,cx=w/2,cy=h-10,r=Math.min(w,h)-30;
      const bg=`M ${cx-r/2} ${cy} A ${r/2} ${r/2} 0 1 1 ${cx+r/2} ${cy}`;
      const end=Math.PI*(1 - valuePct);
      const x=cx+(r/2)*Math.cos(end),y=cy+(r/2)*Math.sin(end);
      const fg=`M ${cx-r/2} ${cy} A ${r/2} ${r/2} 0 ${valuePct>.5?1:0} 1 ${x} ${y}`;
      el.innerHTML=`<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <path d="${bg}" stroke="var(--brd)" stroke-width="14" fill="none"/>
        <path d="${fg}" stroke="var(--brand2)" stroke-width="14" fill="none" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <text x="${cx}" y="${cy-8}" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18" fill="var(--text)">${Math.round(valuePct*100)}%</text>
      </svg>`;
    }
    function stackedBarChart(el, values, colors){
      const w=el.clientWidth||300,h=el.clientHeight||180,barH=22,cx=10,cy=h/2-barH/2;
      const total=values.reduce((s,x)=>s+x,0)||1; let x=cx,html='';
      values.forEach((v,i)=>{ const wv=(v/total)*(w-20); html+=`<rect x="${x}" y="${cy}" width="${wv}" height="${barH}" fill="${colors[i]}"/>`; x+=wv; });
      el.innerHTML=`<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none"><rect x="10" y="${cy}" width="${w-20}" height="${barH}" fill="none" stroke="var(--brd)"/>${html}</svg>`;
    }
    function radialProgress(el, value, total){
      total = total||1; const pct=(value/total)||0;
      const w=el.clientWidth||300,h=el.clientHeight||180,r=Math.min(w,h)/2-14,cx=w/2,cy=h/2;
      const c=2*Math.PI*r, off=c*(1-pct);
      el.innerHTML=`<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <circle cx="${cx}" cy="${cy}" r="${r}" stroke="var(--brd)" stroke-width="12" fill="none"/>
        <circle cx="${cx}" cy="${cy}" r="${r}" stroke="var(--brand2)" stroke-width="12" fill="none"
                stroke-dasharray="${c}" stroke-dashoffset="${off}" transform="rotate(-90 ${cx} ${cy})" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <text x="${cx}" y="${cy+6}" text-anchor="middle" font-size="18" fill="var(--text)">${Math.round(pct*100)}%</text>
      </svg>`;
    }
    function drawKpiChart(el, data, color){
      switch(localStorage.getItem('chart_type')||'area'){
        case 'line':  return lineChart(el, data, color);
        case 'bars':  return barChart(el, data, color);
        case 'step':  return stepChart(el, data, color);
        case 'dots':  return dotsChart(el, data, color);
        default:      return areaChart(el, data, color);
      }
    }
    function drawProgressChart(el, k){
      const colors=[cssrgb('--done-rgb'), cssrgb('--inprog-rgb'), cssrgb('--review-rgb')];
      const pt = localStorage.getItem('progress_type')||'donut';
      if(pt==='pie')   return pieChart(el, [k.done,k.inprog,k.review+k.todo], colors);
      if(pt==='gauge') return gaugeChart(el, (k.done/(k.total||1)));
      if(pt==='stack') return stackedBarChart(el, [k.done,k.inprog,k.review+k.todo], colors);
      if(pt==='radial')return radialProgress(el, k.done, k.total);
      return donutChart(el, [k.done,k.inprog,k.review+k.todo], colors);
    }

    // ---- Периоды/диапазоны и серии
    const DAY = 24*60*60*1000;
    function atMidnight(ts){ const d=new Date(ts); d.setHours(0,0,0,0); return d.getTime(); }
    function kpiSeriesRange(items, fromTS, toTS){
      const from = atMidnight(fromTS), to = atMidnight(toTS);
      const days = Math.max(1, Math.round((to - from)/DAY) + 1);
      const dates = Array.from({length:days}, (_,i)=> new Date(from + i*DAY));
      const build = status => dates.map(d=>{
        const key = d.getTime();
        return items.filter(t => t.status===status && atMidnight(t.due)===key).length;
      });
      return { dates, done: build('done'), inprog: build('in_progress'), review: build('review') };
    }

    // STORE
    const PRIMARY_KEY='munart_tasks_v1';
    const LEGACY_KEYS=['munart_tasks_store','munart_assignments_v1','assignments_v1','tasks_v1','tasks','munart_tasks_backup'];
    const uid = ()=> Math.random().toString(36).slice(2,9);
    function normalizeTasks(arr){
      const known = new Set(['todo','in_progress','review','done']);
      return arr.map(t => ({ ...t, status: known.has(t.status) ? t.status : 'todo' }));
    }
    const taskLoad = () => {
      try{ const arr = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(PRIMARY_KEY)) || []; return normalizeTasks(arr); }
      catch(e){ return []; }
    };
    const taskSave = (arr) => localStorage.setItem(PRIMARY_KEY, JSON.stringify(normalizeTasks(arr)));

        (function migrateOrSeed(){
      if(taskLoad().length) return;
      for (const k of LEGACY_KEYS){
        try{
          const raw = localStorage.getItem(k); if(!raw) continue;
          const data = JSON.parse(raw);
          if (Array.isArray(data) && data.length){
            localStorage.setItem(PRIMARY_KEY, JSON.stringify(data));
            return;
          }
        }catch(e){}
      }
      // демо-записи не создаём — только живые пользовательские данные
      localStorage.setItem(PRIMARY_KEY, JSON.stringify([]));
    })();
;

    const $tSearch = document.getElementById('tSearch');

    $fOverdue.onclick = ()=>{ filterOverdue=!filterOverdue; $fOverdue.classList.toggle('pill'); render(); };

    let editId = null;
    const $modal = document.getElementById('taskModal');

    const $fDesc = document.getElementById('fDesc');
