    function buildOptionsFromTasks(dictKey, taskProp){
      try{
        const dictItems = loadDict(dictKey);
        const fromDict = Array.isArray(dictItems) ? dictItems.map(x => x && x.name).filter(Boolean) : [];
        const fromTasks = taskLoad().flatMap(t => {
          if (!t || !t[taskProp]) return [];
          const v = t[taskProp];
          return Array.isArray(v) ? v : [v];
        }).filter(Boolean);
        return Array.from(new Set([...fromDict, ...fromTasks])).sort((a,b)=>a.localeCompare(b,'ru'));
      }catch(_){
        return [];
      }
    }

    
    function buildExecutorOptions(){
      try{
        const dictItems = loadDict(DICT_KEYS.exec);
        const fromDict = Array.isArray(dictItems) ? dictItems.map(x => x && x.name).filter(Boolean) : [];
        const fromTasks = taskLoad().flatMap(t => {
          if (!t) return [];
          const vals = [];
          if (Array.isArray(t.executors)) vals.push(...t.executors);
          else if (t.executors) vals.push(t.executors);
          if (t.assignee) vals.push(t.assignee);
          return vals;
        }).filter(Boolean);
        return Array.from(new Set([...fromDict, ...fromTasks])).sort((a,b)=>a.localeCompare(b,'ru'));
      }catch(_){
        return [];
      }
    }

function populateSphereSelect(currentValue){
      if (!$fSphere) return;
      const list = buildOptionsFromTasks(DICT_KEYS.cats, 'sphere');
      const cur = (currentValue || '').trim();
      let html = '<option value="">Не выбрана</option>';
      html += list.map(v => `<option value="${escapeHtml(v)}">${escapeHtml(v)}</option>`).join('');
      $fSphere.innerHTML = html;
      if (cur){
        $fSphere.value = cur;
        if ($fSphere.value !== cur){
          const opt = document.createElement('option');
          opt.value = cur;
          opt.textContent = cur;
          $fSphere.appendChild(opt);
          $fSphere.value = cur;
        }
      }
    }

    function populateTerritorySelect(currentValue){
      if (!$fTerritory) return;
      const list = buildOptionsFromTasks(DICT_KEYS.terr, 'territory');
      const cur = (currentValue || '').trim();
      let html = '<option value="">Не выбрана</option>';
      html += list.map(v => `<option value="${escapeHtml(v)}">${escapeHtml(v)}</option>`).join('');
      $fTerritory.innerHTML = html;
      if (cur){
        $fTerritory.value = cur;
        if ($fTerritory.value !== cur){
          const opt = document.createElement('option');
          opt.value = cur;
          opt.textContent = cur;
          $fTerritory.appendChild(opt);
          $fTerritory.value = cur;
        }
      }
    }

    function getSelectedResponsibles(){
      if (!$fResponsible) return [];
      return Array.from($fResponsible.querySelectorAll('input[type="checkbox"]:checked'))
        .map(el => el.value.trim())
        .filter(Boolean);
    }

    function updateResponsibleSummary(){
      if (!$fResponsibleSummary) return;
      const selected = getSelectedResponsibles();
      if (!selected.length){
        $fResponsibleSummary.textContent = 'Не выбраны';
      }else if (selected.length <= 2){
        $fResponsibleSummary.textContent = selected.join(', ');
      }else{
        $fResponsibleSummary.textContent = selected.slice(0,2).join(', ') + ` + ещё ${selected.length-2}`;
      }
    }

    function populateResponsibleFlags(currentValues){
      if (!$fResponsible) return;
      const list = buildOptionsFromTasks(DICT_KEYS.resp, 'responsibles');
      const selected = Array.isArray(currentValues) ? currentValues : (currentValues ? [currentValues] : []);
      const set = new Set(selected.map(v => String(v)));
      const labels = list.map(v => {
        const safe = escapeHtml(v);
        const checked = set.has(v) ? ' checked' : '';
        return `<label><input type="checkbox" value="${safe}"${checked}><span>${safe}</span></label>`;
      });
      $fResponsible.innerHTML = labels.join('') || '<span class="muted">Нет ответственных в справочнике</span>';
      $fResponsible.querySelectorAll('input[type="checkbox"]').forEach(ch=>{
        ch.addEventListener('change', updateResponsibleSummary);
      });
      updateResponsibleSummary();
    }

    
    function getSelectedExecutors(){
      if (!$fExecutors) return [];
      return Array.from($fExecutors.querySelectorAll('input[type="checkbox"]:checked'))
        .map(el => el.value.trim())
        .filter(Boolean);
    }

    function updateExecutorsSummary(){
      if (!$fExecutorsSummary) return;
      const selected = getSelectedExecutors();
      if (!selected.length){
        $fExecutorsSummary.textContent = 'Не выбраны';
      }else if (selected.length <= 2){
        $fExecutorsSummary.textContent = selected.join(', ');
      }else{
        $fExecutorsSummary.textContent = selected.slice(0,2).join(', ') + ` + ещё ${selected.length-2}`;
      }
    }

    function populateExecutorFlags(currentValues){
      if (!$fExecutors) return;
      const list = buildExecutorOptions();
      const selected = Array.isArray(currentValues) ? currentValues : (currentValues ? [currentValues] : []);
      const set = new Set(selected.map(v => String(v)));
      const labels = list.map(v => {
        const safe = escapeHtml(v);
        const checked = set.has(v) ? ' checked' : '';
        return `<label><input type="checkbox" value="${safe}"${checked}><span>${safe}</span></label>`;
      });
      $fExecutors.innerHTML = labels.join('') || '<span class="muted">Нет исполнителей в справочнике</span>';
      $fExecutors.querySelectorAll('input[type="checkbox"]').forEach(ch=>{
        ch.addEventListener('change', updateExecutorsSummary);
      });
      updateExecutorsSummary();
    }

function ensureExtraOpen(task){
      if (!$taskExtraBody || !$taskExtraToggle) return;
      const hasExtra = task && (task.sphere || task.territory || (task.responsibles && task.responsibles.length) || (task.executors && task.executors.length));
      if (hasExtra){
        $taskExtraBody.classList.add('show');
        $taskExtraToggle.classList.add('open');
      }else{
        $taskExtraBody.classList.remove('show');
        $taskExtraToggle.classList.remove('open');
      }
    }

    function openTaskForm(task){
      editId = task?.id || null;
      $taskFormTitle.textContent = editId ? 'Редактирование поручения' : 'Новое поручение';
      $fTitle.value = task?.title || '';
      $fAssignee.value = task?.assignee || (getUser()?.name||'User');

      if ($fStartDate){
        const createdMs = task?.startDate || task?.createdAt || Date.now();
        const ds = new Date(createdMs);
        $fStartDate.value = ds.toISOString().slice(0,10);
      }

      const d = new Date(task?.due || Date.now());
      $fDue.value = d.toISOString().slice(0,10);
      $fStatus.value = task?.status || 'todo';
      $fPriority.value = task?.priority || 'med';

      const sphere = task?.sphere || '';
      populateSphereSelect(sphere);

      const territory = task?.territory || '';
      populateTerritorySelect(territory);

      const executors = (Array.isArray(task?.executors) && task.executors.length)
        ? task.executors
        : (task?.assignee && task.assignee !== '—' ? [task.assignee] : []);
      populateExecutorFlags(executors);

      const responsibles = task?.responsibles || [];
      populateResponsibleFlags(responsibles);

      const ttype = task?.taskType || 'other';
      if ($fType) $fType.value = ttype;
      if ($fProtocol) $fProtocol.value = task?.protocol || '';
      if ($fTaskText) $fTaskText.value = task?.taskText || '';
      $fDesc.value = task?.description || '';

      ensureExtraOpen(task);

      if ($fResponsibleMenu && $fResponsibleToggle){
        $fResponsibleMenu.classList.remove('show');
        $fResponsibleToggle.classList.remove('open');
      }
      if ($fExecutorsMenu && $fExecutorsToggle){
        $fExecutorsMenu.classList.remove('show');
        $fExecutorsToggle.classList.remove('open');
      }

      $modal.classList.add('show');
    }

    function closeTaskForm(){
      $modal.classList.remove('show');
      if ($fResponsibleMenu && $fResponsibleToggle){
        $fResponsibleMenu.classList.remove('show');
        $fResponsibleToggle.classList.remove('open');
      }
      if ($fExecutorsMenu && $fExecutorsToggle){
        $fExecutorsMenu.classList.remove('show');
        $fExecutorsToggle.classList.remove('open');
      }
    }

    document.getElementById('taskClose').onclick = closeTaskForm;
    document.getElementById('taskCancel').onclick = closeTaskForm;

    if ($fResponsibleToggle && $fResponsibleMenu){
      $fResponsibleToggle.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
        const isOpen = !$fResponsibleMenu.classList.contains('show');
        $fResponsibleMenu.classList.toggle('show', isOpen);
        $fResponsibleToggle.classList.toggle('open', isOpen);
      });
    }

    if ($fResponsibleWrapper && $fResponsibleMenu && $fResponsibleToggle){
      document.addEventListener('click', (ev)=>{
        if (!$fResponsibleWrapper.contains(ev.target)){
          $fResponsibleMenu.classList.remove('show');
          $fResponsibleToggle.classList.remove('open');
        }
      });
    }

    if ($fExecutorsToggle && $fExecutorsMenu){
      $fExecutorsToggle.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
        const isOpen = !$fExecutorsMenu.classList.contains('show');
        $fExecutorsMenu.classList.toggle('show', isOpen);
        $fExecutorsToggle.classList.toggle('open', isOpen);
      });
    }

    if ($fExecutorsWrapper && $fExecutorsMenu && $fExecutorsToggle){
      document.addEventListener('click', (ev)=>{
        if (!$fExecutorsWrapper.contains(ev.target)){
          $fExecutorsMenu.classList.remove('show');
          $fExecutorsToggle.classList.remove('open');
        }
      });
    }

    if ($taskExtraToggle && $taskExtraBody){
      $taskExtraToggle.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
        const isOpen = !$taskExtraBody.classList.contains('show');
        $taskExtraBody.classList.toggle('show', isOpen);
        $taskExtraToggle.classList.toggle('open', isOpen);
      });
    }

    document.getElementById('taskSave').onclick = ()=>{
      const selectedExecutors = getSelectedExecutors();
      const assigneePrimary = $fAssignee.value.trim() || (selectedExecutors[0] || '—');

      const payload = {
        title: $fTitle.value.trim(),
        assignee: assigneePrimary,
        executors: selectedExecutors,
        startDate: ($fStartDate && $fStartDate.value ? Date.parse($fStartDate.value) : Date.now()),
        due: Date.parse($fDue.value),
        status: $fStatus.value,
        priority: $fPriority.value,
        sphere: ($fSphere && $fSphere.value ? $fSphere.value.trim() : ''),
        territory: ($fTerritory && $fTerritory.value ? $fTerritory.value.trim() : ''),
        responsibles: getSelectedResponsibles(),
        taskType: ($fType || {value:'other'}).value,
        protocol: $fProtocol ? $fProtocol.value.trim() : '',
        taskText: $fTaskText ? $fTaskText.value.trim() : '',
        description: $fDesc.value.trim() || ''
      };
      if(!payload.title){ alert('Укажите название'); return; }
      const arr = taskLoad();
      const next = editId ? arr.map(x=> x.id===editId ? {...x, ...payload} : x)
                          : [{ id: uid(), ...payload }, ...arr];
      taskSave(next);
      closeTaskForm();
      render();
      const calendarEl = document.getElementById('tasksCalendar');
      if (calendarEl && calendarEl.style.display === 'block') renderCalendar();
    };

    // кнопки создания
    document.getElementById('btnTaskNew').onclick = ()=> openTaskForm({ due: Date.now()+3*86400000, status:'todo', priority:'med' });
    document.getElementById('btnCreateTask').onclick = ()=> openTaskForm({ due: Date.now()+24*3600*1000, status:'todo', priority:'med' });

    // выпадающее меню для кнопки "Создать"
    (function(){
      var btn = document.getElementById('btnCreateTask');
      var menu = document.getElementById('createMenu');
      if (!btn || !menu) return;

      var newItem    = document.getElementById('createNewTask');
      var sphereItem = document.getElementById('createSphere');
      var terrItem   = document.getElementById('createTerritory');
      var respItem   = document.getElementById('createResponsible');
      var execItem   = document.getElementById('createExecutor');

      function closeMenu(){ menu.classList.remove('show'); }

      // отменяем прямой handler создания, заменяем на открытие меню
      btn.onclick = null;
      btn.addEventListener('click', function(e){
        e.stopPropagation();
        menu.classList.toggle('show');
      });

      document.addEventListener('click', function(){
        closeMenu();
      });

      if (newItem){
        newItem.addEventListener('click', function(e){
          e.stopPropagation();
          closeMenu();
          openTaskForm({ due: Date.now()+24*3600*1000, status:'todo', priority:'med' });
        });
      }

      if (sphereItem){
        sphereItem.addEventListener('click', function(e){
          e.stopPropagation();
          closeMenu();
          // открыть справочник сфер поручений (как "Категории" в проектах)
          if (typeof openDict === 'function') {
            openDict('cats');
          }
        });
      }

      if (terrItem){
        terrItem.addEventListener('click', function(e){
          e.stopPropagation();
          closeMenu();
          // справочник территорий
          if (typeof openDict === 'function') {
            openDict('terr');
          }
        });
      }

      if (respItem){
        respItem.addEventListener('click', function(e){
          e.stopPropagation();
          closeMenu();
          // справочник ответственных
          if (typeof openDict === 'function') {
            openDict('resp');
          }
        });
      }

      if (execItem){
        execItem.addEventListener('click', function(e){
          e.stopPropagation();
          closeMenu();
          // справочник исполнителей
          if (typeof openDict === 'function') {
            openDict('exec');
          }
        });
      }
    })();

    // VIEW SWITCH + DENSITY
    const $tasksBoard = document.getElementById('tasksBoard');
    const $tasksCalendar = document.getElementById('tasksCalendar');
    document.getElementById('btnViewBoard').onclick = ()=>{ $tasksBoard.style.display='block'; $tasksCalendar.style.display='none'; localStorage.setItem('tasks_view','board'); };
    document.getElementById('btnViewCalendar').onclick = ()=>{ $tasksBoard.style.display='none'; $tasksCalendar.style.display='block'; localStorage.setItem('tasks_view','calendar'); renderCalendar(); };
    document.getElementById('btnDensity').onclick = ()=>{ document.body.classList.toggle('dense'); };

    // Chart selectors — обработчики выпадающих списков
    (function(){
      const ct = document.getElementById('chartType');
      const pt = document.getElementById('progressType');
      if (ct){ const v=localStorage.getItem('chart_type')||'area'; ct.value=v; ct.onchange = ()=>{ localStorage.setItem('chart_type',ct.value); render(); }; }
      if (pt){ const v=localStorage.getItem('progress_type')||'donut'; pt.value=v; pt.onchange = ()=>{ localStorage.setItem('progress_type',pt.value); render(); }; }

      const rp = document.getElementById('rangePreset');
      const rf = document.getElementById('rangeFrom');
      const rt = document.getElementById('rangeTo');
      let rangePreset   = localStorage.getItem('chart_range') || 'f7';
      let customFrom    = localStorage.getItem('chart_from')  || '';
      let customTo      = localStorage.getItem('chart_to')    || '';

      function getRange(){
        const today = atMidnight(Date.now());
        if(rangePreset==='custom'){
          const f = customFrom ? Date.parse(customFrom) : today;
          const t = customTo   ? Date.parse(customTo)   : f;
          return { from: atMidnight(f), to: atMidnight(t) };
        }
        const map = { f7:[0,6], f14:[0,13], f30:[0,29], p7:[-6,0], p30:[-29,0] };
        const [a,b] = map[rangePreset] || [0,6];
        return { from: today + a*DAY, to: today + b*DAY };
      }
      window.getRange = getRange; // чтобы использовать в render()

      if(rp){
        rp.value = rangePreset;
        const sync = ()=>{ const custom = rp.value==='custom'; rf.style.display = custom?'inline-block':'none'; rt.style.display = custom?'inline-block':'none'; };
        sync();
        rp.onchange = ()=>{ rangePreset = rp.value; localStorage.setItem('chart_range',rangePreset); sync(); render(); };
      }
      if(rf){ rf.value = customFrom || new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10); rf.onchange = ()=>{ customFrom = rf.value; localStorage.setItem('chart_from',customFrom); render(); }; }
      if(rt){ rt.value = customTo   || new Date(Date.now()+7*DAY).toISOString().slice(0,10); rt.onchange = ()=>{ customTo   = rt.value; localStorage.setItem('chart_to',customTo);   render(); }; }
    })();

    // KPIs + BOARD + CALENDAR
    function tasksFiltered(){
      const u = getUser();
      const items = taskLoad();
      const q=($tSearch.value||'').toLowerCase();
      const byName = t => (t.title+t.assignee).toLowerCase().includes(q);
      const byAssignee = t => $tAssignee.value==='all' ? true : t.assignee===$tAssignee.value;
      const byPriority = t => $tPriority.value==='all' ? true : t.priority===$tPriority.value;
      const byType = t => !$tType || $tType.value==='all'
            ? true
            : (t.taskType || 'other') === $tType.value;
      const byMine = t => !filterMine ? true : (u && t.assignee===(u.name||'User'));
      const byOverdue = t => !filterOverdue ? true : (t.status!=='done' && t.due < Date.now());
      return items.filter(t=> byName(t) && byAssignee(t) && byPriority(t) && byType(t) && byMine(t) && byOverdue(t));
    }

    function render(){
      const itemsAll = taskLoad();
      const items = (typeof tasksFiltered==='function') ? tasksFiltered() : itemsAll;

      // наполняем фильтр по исполнителю
      const uniq = [...new Set(itemsAll.map(t=>t.assignee))];
      $tAssignee.innerHTML =
        '<option value="all">Все ответственные</option>' +
        uniq.map(n=>`<option value="${n}">${n}</option>`).join('');

      const known = ['todo','in_progress','review','done'];
      const itemsKnown = items.filter(t => known.includes(t.status));

      const k = {
        total:  itemsKnown.length,
        done:   itemsKnown.filter(x => x.status==='done').length,
        inprog: itemsKnown.filter(x => x.status==='in_progress').length,
        review: itemsKnown.filter(x => x.status==='review').length,
        todo:   itemsKnown.filter(x => x.status==='todo').length,
      };
      k.pending = k.review + k.todo;

      document.getElementById('kpiTTotal').textContent  = k.total;
      document.getElementById('kpiTDone').textContent   = k.done;
      document.getElementById('kpiTInProg').textContent = k.inprog;
      document.getElementById('kpiTPending').textContent = k.review;
      document.getElementById('kpiTdelta').textContent = '+' + Math.floor(Math.random()*5);

      // диапазон
      const {from, to} = window.getRange();
      const seriesAll = kpiSeriesRange(itemsKnown, from, to);
      const zeroes = len => Array.from({length: len}, ()=>0);

      const chartStatuses = new Set(JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('chart_statuses')||'["todo","in_progress","review","done"]'));
      const sDone   = chartStatuses.has('done')        ? seriesAll.done   : zeroes(seriesAll.done.length);
      const sInprog = chartStatuses.has('in_progress') ? seriesAll.inprog : zeroes(seriesAll.inprog.length);
      const sReview = chartStatuses.has('review')      ? seriesAll.review : zeroes(seriesAll.review.length);

      const fmt = d => d.toLocaleDateString('ru-RU', {day:'2-digit', month:'2-digit'});
      ['tChartDone','tChartInProg','tChartPending'].forEach(id=>{
        const el = document.getElementById(id);
        if (el) el.title = `Диапазон: ${fmt(seriesAll.dates[0])} — ${fmt(seriesAll.dates.at(-1))}`;
      });

      drawKpiChart(document.getElementById('tChartDone'),    sDone,   '#22c55e');
      drawKpiChart(document.getElementById('tChartInProg'),  sInprog, '#10b981');
      drawKpiChart(document.getElementById('tChartPending'), sReview, '#f59e0b');

      const inRange = t => { const d=atMidnight(t.due); return d>=from && d<=to; };
      const kRange = {
        total:  itemsKnown.filter(t => inRange(t)).length,
        done:   itemsKnown.filter(t => inRange(t) && t.status==='done').length,
        inprog: itemsKnown.filter(t => inRange(t) && t.status==='in_progress').length,
        review: itemsKnown.filter(t => inRange(t) && t.status==='review').length,
        todo:   itemsKnown.filter(t => inRange(t) && t.status==='todo').length,
      };
      drawProgressChart(document.getElementById('tDonut'), kRange);

      renderBoard();
	  
	let listSortKey='due', listSortDir='asc', listSearch='';
	function tasksForList(){
	  const q=listSearch.toLowerCase().trim();
	  return taskLoad().filter(t => !q || (t.title+t.assignee+(t.description||'')).toLowerCase().includes(q));
	}
	function compare(a,b,k){
	  let va=a[k], vb=b[k];
	  if(k==='due'){ va=+a.due||0; vb=+b.due||0; }
	  if(k==='status'){ va=STATUS_ORDER.indexOf(a.status); vb=STATUS_ORDER.indexOf(b.status); }
	  if(k==='priority'){ const order=['low','med','high']; va=order.indexOf(a.priority); vb=order.indexOf(b.priority); }
	  if(k==='assignee'){ va=(Array.isArray(a.responsibles)&&a.responsibles[0])?a.responsibles[0]:(a.assignee||''); vb=(Array.isArray(b.responsibles)&&b.responsibles[0])?b.responsibles[0]:(b.assignee||''); }
	  if(typeof va==='string') va=va.toLowerCase(); if(typeof vb==='string') vb=vb.toLowerCase();
	  return va>vb?1:va<vb?-1:0;
	}
	function renderList(){
	  const tbl=document.getElementById('tasksTable'); if(!tbl) return;
	  const rows=[...tasksForList()].sort((a,b)=> (listSortDir==='asc'?1:-1)*compare(a,b,listSortKey));

	  const head=`<thead><tr>
		<th style="width:36px"><input type="checkbox" id="chkAll"></th>
		<th>Название</th><th>Ответственные</th><th>Срок</th><th>Статус</th><th>Приоритет</th>
	  </tr></thead>`;

	  const body= rows.map(t=>{
		const d = new Date(t.due||Date.now()).toLocaleDateString('ru-RU');
		return `<tbody data-id="${t.id}">
		  <tr class="row">
			<td><input type="checkbox" class="chk" data-id="${t.id}"></td>
			<td><button class="btn-ghost" data-expand="${t.id}" style="padding:2px 6px">${escapeHtml(t.title)}</button></td>
			<td>${escapeHtml(formatResponsibles(t.responsibles, t.assignee))}</td>
			<td>${d}</td>
			<td><span class="st ${t.status}">${STATUS_TITLE[t.status]||t.status}</span></td>
			<td><span class="pill" style="border-color:${priorityColor(t.priority)}; color:${priorityColor(t.priority)}">${PRIORITY_TITLE[t.priority]||t.priority}</span></td>
		  </tr>
		  <tr class="details" style="display:none"><td></td>
			<td colspan="5">
			  <div class="muted">${escapeHtml(t.description||'Нет описания')}</div>
			  <div class="right mt">
				<select data-set-status="${t.id}" class="chip">
				  <option value="todo" ${t.status==='todo'?'selected':''}>К созданию</option>
				  <option value="in_progress" ${t.status==='in_progress'?'selected':''}>В работе</option>
				  <option value="review" ${t.status==='review'?'selected':''}>На проверке</option>
				  <option value="done" ${t.status==='done'?'selected':''}>Готово</option>
				</select>
				<select data-set-priority="${t.id}" class="chip">
				  <option value="low" ${t.priority==='low'?'selected':''}>Низкий</option>
				  <option value="med" ${t.priority==='med'?'selected':''}>Средний</option>
				  <option value="high" ${t.priority==='high'?'selected':''}>Высокий</option>
				</select>
				<button class="btn-ghost" data-edit="${t.id}">Изм.</button>
				<button class="btn-ghost" data-del="${t.id}">Удалить</button>
			  </div>
			</td>
		  </tr>
		</tbody>`;
	  }).join('');

	  tbl.innerHTML = head + body;

	  // select all
	  const chkAll = document.getElementById('chkAll');
	  if(chkAll){ chkAll.onchange = ()=> tbl.querySelectorAll('.chk').forEach(c=> c.checked = chkAll.checked); }

	  // expand
	  tbl.querySelectorAll('[data-expand]').forEach(btn=>{
		btn.onclick = ()=>{
		  const tb = btn.closest('tbody'); const det = tb.querySelector('.details');
		  det.style.display = det.style.display==='none' ? 'table-row' : 'none';
		};
	  });

	  // inline set status/priority
	  tbl.querySelectorAll('[data-set-status]').forEach(s=>{
		s.onchange = ()=>{
		  const id=s.getAttribute('data-set-status');
		  const arr=taskLoad().map(x=> x.id===id ? {...x, status:s.value} : x); taskSave(arr); render();
		};
	  });
	  tbl.querySelectorAll('[data-set-priority]').forEach(s=>{
		s.onchange = ()=>{
		  const id=s.getAttribute('data-set-priority');
		  const arr=taskLoad().map(x=> x.id===id ? {...x, priority:s.value} : x); taskSave(arr); render();
		};
	  });

	  // reuse edit/del
	  tbl.querySelectorAll('[data-edit]').forEach(b=> b.onclick = e=> editTask(e.target.getAttribute('data-edit')));
	  tbl.querySelectorAll('[data-del]').forEach(b=> b.onclick = e=>{
		const id=e.target.getAttribute('data-del');
		taskSave(taskLoad().filter(x=>x.id!==id)); render();
	  });
	}	  

      if (localStorage.getItem('tasks_view') === 'calendar') renderCalendar();
    }

    function priorityColor(p){ return p==='high' ? 'var(--rose)' : p==='med' ? 'var(--amber)' : 'var(--brand2)'; }

    // BOARD with DnD
    const $kb = document.getElementById('kanban');
    function renderBoard(){
      const items = taskLoad();
      const cols=[
        {key:'todo',title:'К созданию'},
        {key:'in_progress',title:'В работе'},
        {key:'review',title:'На проверке'},
        {key:'done',title:'Готово'}
      ];
      $kb.innerHTML='';
      cols.forEach(col=>{
        const inCol = items.filter(x=>x.status===col.key);
        const collapsed = getColCollapsed(col.key) && inCol.length > 1;

        const c = document.createElement('div'); c.className='col'; c.dataset.col = col.key;
        if (collapsed) c.classList.add('is-collapsed');

        const head = document.createElement('div'); head.className='col-head';
        head.innerHTML = `
          <div class="left">
            <div class="title">${col.title}</div>
            <span class="pill">${inCol.length}</span>
          </div>
          <button class="btn-mini col-toggle" data-col-toggle="${col.key}" title="Свернуть/развернуть">${collapsed?'▸':'▾'}</button>
        `;
        c.appendChild(head);

        const body = document.createElement('div'); body.className='col-body';
        c.appendChild(body);

        inCol.forEach(t=>{
          const div = document.createElement('div'); div.className='task'; div.draggable=true; div.dataset.id = t.id;
          div.ondragstart = (e)=> e.dataTransfer.setData('text/plain', t.id);
          const due = t.due ? new Date(t.due).toLocaleDateString('ru-RU') : '—';
          div.innerHTML = `
            <div><b class="t-title" data-id="${t.id}">${escapeHtml(t.title)}</b></div>
            <div class="t-meta">
              <span>👤</span><span>${escapeHtml((t.assignee||'user'))}</span>
              <span>📅</span><span class="${(t.due && t.due<Date.now() && t.status!=='done')?'overdue':''}">${due}</span>
              <span class="pill" style="border-color:${priorityColor(t.priority)}; color:${priorityColor(t.priority)}">${PRIORITY_TITLE[t.priority]||t.priority}</span>
              <span class="pill">${TASK_TYPE_TITLE[t.taskType]||'Прочие'}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="right" style="gap:6px;margin-top:6px">
              <button class="btn-mini" data-dir="-1" data-id="${t.id}">◀</button>
              <button class="btn-mini" data-dir="1" data-id="${t.id}">▶</button>
              <button class="btn-mini" data-edit="${t.id}">Изм.</button>
              <button class="btn-mini" data-del="${t.id}">Удалить</button>
            </div>
          `;
          body.appendChild(div);
        });

        if (inCol.length>1){
          const more = document.createElement('div');
          more.className = 'col-more';
          more.textContent = `+ ещё ${inCol.length-1}`;
          more.onclick = ()=>{ setColCollapsed(col.key, false); renderBoard(); (window.renderOverdue?window.renderOverdue():null); renderList(); };
          body.appendChild(more);
        }

        c.ondragover = (e)=>{ e.preventDefault(); c.classList.add('drag-over'); };
        c.ondragleave = ()=> c.classList.remove('drag-over');
        c.ondrop = (e)=>{
          e.preventDefault(); c.classList.remove('drag-over');
          const id = e.dataTransfer.getData('text/plain'); if(!id) return;
          const next = taskLoad().map(x=> x.id===id ? {...x, status: col.key} : x);
          taskSave(next); render();
        };

        $kb.appendChild(c);
      });

      document.querySelectorAll('[data-col-toggle]').forEach(b=> b.onclick = e=>{
        const key = e.currentTarget.getAttribute('data-col-toggle');
        const now = getColCollapsed(key);
        setColCollapsed(key, !now);
        renderBoard();
      });

      document.querySelectorAll('[data-dir]').forEach(b=> b.onclick = e=>{
        const id=e.currentTarget.getAttribute('data-id'); const dir=parseInt(e.currentTarget.getAttribute('data-dir'),10);
        const order=['todo','in_progress','review','done'];
        const arr=taskLoad().map(x=>{
          if(x.id!==id) return x;
          const idx=order.indexOf(x.status);
          const next=Math.min(order.length-1, Math.max(0, idx+dir));
          return {...x, status:order[next]};
        });
        taskSave(arr); render();
      });

      document.querySelectorAll('[data-del]').forEach(b=> b.onclick = e=>{ const id=e.currentTarget.getAttribute('data-del'); taskSave(taskLoad().filter(x=>x.id!==id)); render(); });
      document.querySelectorAll('[data-edit]').forEach(b=> b.onclick = e=> editTask(e.currentTarget.getAttribute('data-edit')));
      document.querySelectorAll('.t-title').forEach(span=>{
        span.ondblclick = ()=>{ const id=span.getAttribute('data-id'); const t=taskLoad().find(x=>x.id===id); if(!t) return; openTaskForm(t); };
      });
    }
    
	
	function editTask(id){ const t = taskLoad().find(x=>x.id===id); if(!t) return; openTaskForm(t); }

    // CALENDAR
    let calRef = new Date();
    const $calGrid = document.getElementById('calGrid'); const $calLabel = document.getElementById('calLabel');
    document.getElementById('calPrev').onclick = ()=>{ calRef.setMonth(calRef.getMonth()-1); renderCalendar(); };
    document.getElementById('calNext').onclick = ()=>{ calRef.setMonth(calRef.getMonth()+1); renderCalendar(); };
    document.getElementById('calToday').onclick = ()=>{ calRef = new Date(); renderCalendar(); };

    function renderCalendar(){
      const base = new Date(calRef.getFullYear(), calRef.getMonth(), 1);
      const firstWeekday = (base.getDay()+6)%7; // Mon=0
      const total = 42; // 6 weeks grid
      $calLabel.textContent = base.toLocaleString('ru-RU', {month:'long', year:'numeric'});
      $calGrid.innerHTML='';
      for(let i=0;i<total;i++){
        const date = new Date(base); date.setDate(date.getDate() - firstWeekday + i);
        const inMonth = date.getMonth()===calRef.getMonth();
        const cell = document.createElement('div'); cell.className='cal-day'+(inMonth?'':' out');
        const isToday = new Date().toDateString()===date.toDateString(); if(isToday) cell.classList.add('today');
        const head = document.createElement('div'); head.className='date'; head.innerHTML = `${date.toLocaleDateString('ru-RU', {day:'2-digit'})}`; cell.appendChild(head);

        const list = tasksFiltered().filter(t=> new Date(t.due).toDateString()===date.toDateString());
        list.slice(0,4).forEach(t=>{
          const b = document.createElement('span'); b.className='task-badge';
          const col = priorityColor(t.priority);
          b.style.borderColor = col; b.style.color = col;
          const overdue = t.status!=='done' && t.due < Date.now(); if(overdue) b.style.borderColor = 'var(--rose)';
          b.textContent = `${t.title}`;
          b.title = `👤 ${t.assignee} • ${t.priority} • ${t.status}`;
          b.onclick = ()=> editTask(t.id);
          cell.appendChild(b);
        });
        if(list.length>4){
          const more = document.createElement('span'); more.className='task-badge'; more.textContent = `+${list.length-4} ещё`; more.style.background='transparent'; more.style.color='var(--muted)'; cell.appendChild(more);
        }
        cell.onclick = (e)=>{ if(e.target!==cell) return; openTaskForm({ due: date.getTime(), status:'todo', priority:'med' }); };
        $calGrid.appendChild(cell);
      }
    }

    // TIMER
    let tInt=null, tSec=0; const $time = document.getElementById('tTimer');
    function fmt(s){ const h=String(Math.floor(s/3600)).padStart(2,'0'); const m=String(Math.floor(s%3600/60)).padStart(2,'0'); const ss=String(s%60).padStart(2,'0'); return `${h}:${m}:${ss}`; }
    function tick(){ tSec++; $time && ($time.textContent = fmt(tSec)); }
    document.getElementById('tStart').onclick = ()=>{ if(tInt) return; tInt=setInterval(tick,1000); };
    document.getElementById('tPause').onclick = ()=>{ clearInterval(tInt); tInt=null; };
    document.getElementById('tReset').onclick = ()=>{ clearInterval(tInt); tInt=null; tSec=0; $time && ($time.textContent=fmt(0)); };

    // INIT
    render();
    if(localStorage.getItem('tasks_view')==='calendar'){ document.getElementById('btnViewCalendar').click(); }
  </script>
  
  
  
<!-- MunArt List Booster v2.1 (guarded) -->
  <script>
	if (window.__munart_list_booster__) {
	  console.info('ListBooster: already loaded, skipping');
	} else {
	  window.__munart_list_booster__ = true;
	  (function(){
		const STORE_KEY = window.KEY_MAIN || 'munart_tasks_v1';
		const $ = (s)=> document.querySelector(s);
		const esc = (s)=> String(s).replace(/[&<>"]/g, c => ({'&':'&amp;','<':'&lt;','>':'&gt;','"':'&quot;'}[c]) );
		const label = (st)=>({todo:'к выполнению', in_progress:'в работе', inprogress:'в работе', review:'на проверке', done:'готово'})[String(st||'').toLowerCase()]||st;
		const norm = (st)=>{ st=String(st||'').toLowerCase();
		  if(st==='inprogress') st='in_progress';
		  if(st==='на проверке'||st==='проверке') st='review';
		  if(st==='в работе') st='in_progress';
		  if(st==='готово') st='done';
		  if(st==='к созданию'||st==='к выполнению') st='todo';
		  return st;
		};

		function load(){ try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(STORE_KEY))||[] }catch(_){ return [] } }
		function save(arr){
		  if (typeof window.taskSave === 'function'){ window.taskSave(arr); } else { localStorage.setItem(STORE_KEY, JSON.stringify(arr)); }
		  renderList();
		}
		function src(){
		  try{ if (typeof window.tasksFiltered === 'function') return window.tasksFiltered(); }catch(_){}
		  return load();
		}

		let filterStatus = ''; // todo|in_progress|review|done
		function rowsFiltered(){
		  const q = ($('#listSearch')?.value || '').toLowerCase().trim();
		  const typeSel = $('#listTypeFilter');
		  const typeVal = typeSel ? typeSel.value : 'all';
		  let list = src();
		  if (filterStatus) list = list.filter(t => String(t.status||'').toLowerCase() === filterStatus);
		  if (typeVal && typeVal !== 'all') list = list.filter(t => (t.taskType || 'other') === typeVal);
		  if (!q) return list;
		  return list.filter(t=>{
			const hay = (t.title||'')+' '+(t.assignee||'')+' '+(t.description||'');
			return hay.toLowerCase().includes(q);
		  });
		}

		function cmp(a,b,k){
		  const va = (a?.[k] ?? ''), vb = (b?.[k] ?? '');
		  if (k==='due') return (Number(va)||0)-(Number(vb)||0);
		  if (k==='priority'){ const w={high:3,med:2,medium:2,low:1}; return (w[va]||0)-(w[vb]||0); }
		  return String(va).localeCompare(String(vb),'ru',{numeric:true});
		}

		function renderList(){
		  const tbl = $('#tasksTable'); if(!tbl) return;
		  const k = $('#listSortKey')?.value || 'due';
		  const dir = $('#listSortDir')?.value || 'asc';
		  const items = [...rowsFiltered()].sort((a,b)=> (dir==='asc'?1:-1)*cmp(a,b,k));
		  const head = `<thead><tr>
			<th style="width:28px"></th><th>Название</th><th>Исполнитель</th><th>Срок</th><th>Статус</th><th>Приоритет</th><th></th>
		  </tr></thead>`;
		  const body = `<tbody>${
			items.map(t=>{
			  const d = new Date(Number(t.due)||Date.now()).toISOString().slice(0,10);
			  const st = String(t.status||'todo').toLowerCase();
			  const pr = String(t.priority||'med').toLowerCase();
			  return `<tr>
				<td><input type="checkbox" class="chk" data-id="${esc(t.id)}"></td>
				<td>${esc(t.title||'Без названия')}</td>
				<td>${esc(t.assignee||'—')}</td>
				<td><span class="munart-chip">${d}</span></td>
				<td><span class="munart-chip dot status-${st}">${esc(label(st))}</span></td>
				<td><span class="munart-chip">${esc(pr)}</span></td>
				<td class="munart-actions">
				  <button class="munart-btn list-edit" data-id="${esc(t.id)}">Изм.</button>
				  <button class="munart-btn list-del" data-id="${esc(t.id)}">×</button>
				</td>
			  </tr>`;
			}).join('') || `<tr><td colspan="7" style="padding:16px;color:#64748b">Нет данных</td></tr>`}
		  </tbody>`;
		  tbl.classList.add('munart-table');
		  tbl.innerHTML = head + body;

		  tbl.querySelectorAll('.list-edit').forEach(b=> b.onclick = ()=>{
			const id=b.dataset.id; const item = load().find(x=>x.id===id);
			if (item && typeof window.openForm === 'function') window.openForm(item);
		  });
		  tbl.querySelectorAll('.list-del').forEach(b=> b.onclick = ()=>{
			const id=b.dataset.id; if(!confirm('Удалить поручение?')) return;
			const next = load().filter(x=>x.id!==id); save(next);
		  });
		}

		// table styles
		const css = document.createElement('style');
		css.textContent = `
		  .munart-table{width:100%;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:0;font-size:14px}
		  .munart-table thead th{position:sticky;top:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,.9);backdrop-filter:blur(6px);text-align:left;font-weight:600;padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e7eb}
		  .munart-table tbody td{padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid #f1f5f9}
		  .munart-table tbody tr:hover{background:linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(148,163,184,.08), transparent)}
		  .munart-chip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:999px;font-size:12px;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;background:#f8fafc}
		  .munart-chip.dot::before{content:"";width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;background:#94a3b8}
		  .munart-chip.status-todo::before{background:#94a3b8}
		  .munart-chip.status-in_progress::before,.munart-chip.status-inprogress::before{background:#22c55e}
		  .munart-chip.status-review::before{background:#a855f7}
		  .munart-chip.status-done::before{background:#3b82f6}
		  .munart-btn{border:1px solid #e5e7eb;background:#f8fafc;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:10px;font-size:12px;cursor:pointer}
		  .munart-actions button{margin-right:6px}
		  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark){
			.munart-table thead th{background:rgba(15,23,42,.85);border-bottom-color:#1f2937}
			.munart-table tbody td{border-bottom-color:#1f2937}
			.munart-table tbody tr:hover{background:rgba(148,163,184,.08)}
			.munart-chip{border-color:#334155;background:#0b1220;color:#e5e7eb}
			.munart-btn{border-color:#334155;background:#0b1220;color:#e5e7eb}
		  }`;
		document.head.appendChild(css);

		// controls
		['#listSearch','#listTypeFilter','#listSortKey','#listSortDir'].forEach(sel=>{
		  const el=$(sel); if(!el) return; el.addEventListener('input',renderList); el.addEventListener('change',renderList);
		});

		const bulkApply = $('#bulkApply');
		if (bulkApply){
		  bulkApply.onclick = ()=>{
			const stSel = $('#bulkStatus'); const st = norm(stSel?.value || '');
			if (!st) return;
			const tbl = $('#tasksTable');
			const ids = Array.from(tbl?.querySelectorAll('.chk:checked') || []).map(c=>c.dataset.id);
			if (ids.length){
			  const next = load().map(x=> ids.includes(x.id)? {...x, status: st} : x); save(next);
			} else {
			  filterStatus = st; renderList();
			}
		  };
		}

		const listExport = $('#listExport');
		if (listExport){
		  listExport.onclick = ()=>{
			const k=$('#listSortKey')?.value||'due'; const dir=$('#listSortDir')?.value||'asc';
			const items=[...rowsFiltered()].sort((a,b)=> (dir==='asc'?1:-1)*cmp(a,b,k));
			const toCell=s=>String(s).replaceAll(';',',').replaceAll('\n',' ');
			const csv=['id;title;assignee;due;status;priority',
			  ...items.map(t=>[t.id,t.title,t.assignee,new Date(Number(t.due)||Date.now()).toISOString().slice(0,10),t.status,t.priority].map(toCell).join(';'))
			].join('\n');
			const a=document.createElement('a'); a.href=URL.createObjectURL(new Blob([csv],{type:'text/csv;charset=utf-8'}));
			a.download='tasks_list.csv'; a.click();
		  };
		}

		// hooks
		if (typeof window.taskSave === 'function'){
		  const orig=window.taskSave; window.taskSave=function(){ const r=orig.apply(this,arguments); try{renderList();}catch(_){} return r; };
		}
		const _setItem=localStorage.setItem.bind(localStorage);
		localStorage.setItem=function(k,v){ _setItem(k,v); if(k===STORE_KEY) renderList(); };

		addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',renderList);
		addEventListener('load',renderList);
	  })();
	}
  </script>


  

<script>
(function(){
  function $(id){ return document.getElementById(id); }
  function findTimerCard(){
    var cards = document.querySelectorAll('.card');
    for (var c of cards){
      var t = c.querySelector('.title');
      if (t && t.textContent.trim().toLowerCase() === 'таймер') return c;
    }
    return null;
  }
  function normTs(v){ if(v==null) return null; if(typeof v==='number') return v; var t=Date.parse(v); return isNaN(t)?null:t; }
  function loadTasks(){ try{ if(typeof taskLoad==='function') return taskLoad(); return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_tasks_v1')||'[]'); }catch(_){ return []; } }
  function pickNearest(){
    var arr=loadTasks(), now=Date.now();
    var active=(arr||[]).filter(function(t){ return String(t.status||'')!=='done' && normTs(t.due)!=null; });
    if(!active.length) return null;
    active.sort(function(a,b){
      var ad=Math.abs(normTs(a.due)-now), bd=Math.abs(normTs(b.due)-now);
      if(ad===bd){ var af=normTs(a.due)>=now?0:1, bf=normTs(b.due)>=now?0:1; return af-bf; }
      return ad-bd;
    });
    return active[0];
  }
  function mountNearest(host){
    host.innerHTML = '<div class="title">Ближайшее поручение</div>'+
      '<div class="text" id="nearestText">Нет активных поручений со сроком.</div>'+
      '<div class="actions" id="nearestActions" style="display:none">'+
      '  <button class="btn" id="nearestOpen" type="button">Посмотреть</button>'+
      '</div>';
    host.classList.add('qa'); host.id='nearestCard';
  }
  function renderNearest(){
    var card=$('nearestCard'); if(!card) return;
    var txt=$('nearestText'), acts=$('nearestActions');
    var t=pickNearest();
    if(!t){ card.classList.remove('qa--eod'); card.classList.add('qa--ok'); if(txt) txt.textContent='Нет активных поручений со сроком.'; if(acts) acts.style.display='none'; return; }
    var dueTs=normTs(t.due), due=dueTs?new Date(dueTs):null, meta=due?due.toLocaleDateString('ru-RU',{day:'2-digit',month:'2-digit'}):'';
    if(txt) txt.textContent=(t.title||'Поручение')+(meta?' — '+meta:'')+(t.assignee?' · '+t.assignee:'');
    if(acts) acts.style.display='';
    var today0=new Date(); today0.setHours(0,0,0,0); var d0=new Date(dueTs||Date.now()); d0.setHours(0,0,0,0);
    card.classList.remove('qa--eod','qa--ok'); if(d0<=today0){ card.classList.add('qa--eod'); } else { card.classList.add('qa--ok'); }
  }

  function ensureNearest(){
    var timer = findTimerCard();
    if (timer){
      mountNearest(timer);
      timer.addEventListener('click', function(e){
        if (e.target && e.target.id==='nearestOpen'){
          try{ var t=pickNearest(); if(t && typeof openTaskForm==='function') openTaskForm(t); }catch(_){}
        }
      });
      renderNearest();
      window.addEventListener('storage', function(ev){ if(ev.key==='munart_tasks_v1') renderNearest(); });
    }
  }

  if (document.readyState==='loading') document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', ensureNearest);
  else ensureNearest();
})();
</script>


<script>
(function(){
  'use strict';
  const $  = (s,root=document)=>root.querySelector(s);
  const $$ = (s,root=document)=>Array.from(root.querySelectorAll(s));
  const KANBAN = $('#kanban');

  function norm(s){ return String(s||'').toLowerCase(); }
  function toKey(s){
    s = norm(s);
    if (/готов|done/.test(s)) return 'done';
    if (/провер|review/.test(s)) return 'review';
    if (/работ|progress|in[_\s-]*prog/.test(s)) return 'in_progress';
    if (/создан|todo|backlog/.test(s)) return 'todo';
    return null;
  }
  function inferKey(col){
    const attr = toKey(col.getAttribute('data-col'));
    if (attr) return attr;
    const hdr = col.querySelector('.title, .col-title, header, .hdr, b');
    if (hdr) {
      const key = toKey(hdr.textContent);
      if (key) return key;
    }
    return null;
  }
  function getColumns(){
    if (!KANBAN) return [];
    const candidates = $$(
      '#kanban [data-col], #kanban .kanban-col, #kanban .kanban-column, #kanban .column, #kanban > div'
    );
    const cols = [];
    for (const el of candidates){
      const key = inferKey(el);
      if (key && !cols.find(c=>c.key===key)) cols.push({el, key});
    }
    return cols;
  }
  const TASK_SEL_DIRECT = ':scope > .card, :scope > .task, :scope > .task-card, :scope > .kanban-card, :scope > .kanban-item, :scope > [data-task-id]';
  const TASK_SEL_DEEP   = '.card, .task, .task-card, .kanban-card, .kanban-item, [data-task-id]';
  function listTasks(colEl){
    let items = $$(TASK_SEL_DIRECT, colEl);
    if (!items.length) items = $$(TASK_SEL_DEEP, colEl);
    return items.filter(n=>!n.classList.contains('header') && !n.matches('.column'));
  }

  function countsFromBoard(){
    const cols = getColumns();
    const c = {todo:0, in_progress:0, review:0, done:0};
    for (const {el,key} of cols){
      c[key] += listTasks(el).length;
    }
    const total = c.todo + c.in_progress + c.review + c.done;
    return { ...c, total, inprog:c.in_progress };
  }
  function countsFromStore(){
    try{
      const arr = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_tasks_v1')||'[]');
      const c = {todo:0, in_progress:0, review:0, done:0};
      for (const t of arr){
        const k = toKey(t.status);
        if (k) c[k]++;
      }
      const total = c.todo + c.in_progress + c.review + c.done;
      return { ...c, total, inprog:c.in_progress };
    }catch{ return {todo:0,in_progress:0,review:0,done:0,total:0,inprog:0}; }
  }
  function updateProgress(){
    const el = $('#tDonut');
    if (!el || typeof window.drawProgressChart!=='function') return;
    const board = countsFromBoard();
    const data  = (board.total>0) ? board : countsFromStore();
    window.drawProgressChart(el, data);
  }

  const __render = window.render;
  window.render = function(){ try{ __render && __render(); } finally { updateProgress(); } };
  if (KANBAN){
    const mo = new MutationObserver(updateProgress);
    mo.observe(KANBAN, {childList:true, subtree:true});
  }
  window.addEventListener('storage', e=>{ if (e.key==='munart_tasks_v1') updateProgress(); });
  window.addEventListener('load', updateProgress);
  setInterval(updateProgress, 2500);

  function sl(t){ return String(t||'').trim().replace(/\s+/g,' '); }
  function extractDateText(el){
    const m = sl(el.innerText).match(/\\b\\d{2}\\.\\d{2}\\.\\d{4}\\b/);
    return m ? m[0] : '';
  }
  function collectOverdue(){
    const items = [];
    const cols = getColumns();
    for (const {el,key} of cols){
      if (key==='done') continue;
      for (const n of listTasks(el)){
        const title = sl(n.querySelector('.title, .name, b')?.textContent || n.textContent).slice(0,160);
        const date  = extractDateText(n);
        items.push({el:n, title, date});
      }
    }
    return items;
  }
  function renderOverdue(){
    const sel = $('#overdueSelect');
    const meta = $('#overdueMeta');
    const cur = $('#overdueCurrent');
    const tog = $('#overdueToggle');
    if (!sel) return;
    const items = collectOverdue();
    sel.innerHTML = '';

    if (!items.length){
      sel.innerHTML = '<option value="">Нет просроченных</option>';
      if (meta) meta.textContent = '';
      sel._refs = [];
      if (cur) cur.textContent = 'Нет просроченных';
      if (tog) tog.style.display = 'none';
      setOverdueExpanded(false);
      return;
    }

    if (tog) tog.style.display = 'inline-flex';

    items.forEach((it, i)=>{
      const op = document.createElement('option');
      op.value = String(i);
      op.textContent = it.date ? `${it.title} — ${it.date}` : it.title;
      sel.appendChild(op);
    });
    sel._refs = items.map(it=>it.el);
    if (meta) meta.textContent = `Всего: ${items.length}`;

    // выставляем «текущее» (по выбранному, либо первое)
    const idx = Math.max(0, Math.min(items.length-1, parseInt(sel.value||'0',10)||0));
    sel.value = String(idx);
    if (cur){
      cur.textContent = sel.options[idx] ? sel.options[idx].textContent : items[0].title;
    }

    // режим раскрытия (по памяти)
    setOverdueExpanded(getOverdueExpanded());
  }

  function findEditButton(root){
    let btn = root.querySelector('[data-action="edit"], .btn-edit, button.edit, a.edit');
    if (btn) return btn;
    const nodes = root.querySelectorAll('button, a');
    for (const n of nodes){
      const t = (n.textContent||'').trim().toLowerCase();
      if (t === 'изм.' || t === 'изменить' || t.startsWith('изм')) return n;
    }
    return null;
  }
  function openEditForSelected(){
    const sel = $('#overdueSelect');
    if (!sel || !sel._refs) return;
    const i = parseInt(sel.value||'-1',10);
    const el = sel._refs[i];
    if (!el) return;
    el.scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth', block:'center'});
    el.classList.add('pulse');
    setTimeout(()=> el.classList.remove('pulse'), 900);
    const editBtn = findEditButton(el);
    if (editBtn){
      setTimeout(()=> editBtn.click(), 120);
    }
  }

  document.addEventListener('click', e=>{ if (e.target && e.target.id==='overdueOpen') openEditForSelected(); });
  document.addEventListener('click', e=>{
    if (e.target && e.target.id==='overdueToggle'){
      const next = !getOverdueExpanded();
      setOverdueExpanded(next);
      try{ localStorage.setItem('munart_tasks_overdue_expanded', next ? '1' : '0'); }catch(_){}
    }
  });
  document.addEventListener('change', e=>{
    if (e.target && e.target.id==='overdueSelect'){
      const sel = e.target;
      const cur = document.getElementById('overdueCurrent');
      const op = sel.options[sel.selectedIndex];
      if (cur && op) cur.textContent = op.textContent;
    }
  });
  if (KANBAN){
    const mo2 = new MutationObserver(renderOverdue);
    mo2.observe(KANBAN, {childList:true, subtree:true});
  }
  window.addEventListener('storage', e=>{ if (e.key==='munart_tasks_v1') renderOverdue(); });
  window.addEventListener('load', renderOverdue);
  window.renderOverdue = renderOverdue;
  setInterval(renderOverdue, 3000);
})();

// ---- Кнопка "Объезды" рядом с "Создать" ----
(function(){
  var btn = document.getElementById('btnRoundsShortcut');
  if (!btn) return;
  btn.addEventListener('click', function(){
    try{
      if (window.parent && window.parent !== window){
        window.parent.postMessage({ type:'NAVIGATE', payload:'rounds' }, window.location.origin);
      } else {
        window.location.href = '/prototypes/obezdy_offline.html';
      }
    }catch(_){}
  });
})();

  // RESPONSIBILITY shortcut (opens responsibles dictionary)
  (function(){
    const btn = document.getElementById('btnResponsibility');
    if (!btn) return;
    btn.addEventListener('click', function(e){
      e.preventDefault();
      if (typeof openDict === 'function') openDict('resp');
    });
  })();
;

</script>


<div class="mp-modal" id="dictModal" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="mp-modal__content" style="max-width:820px">
      <h2 id="dictTitle">Категории</h2>
      <div class="dict-wrap">
        <div class="dict-form">
          <div class="mp-field"><label id="dictLabelMain">Наименование</label><input id="dict_name" class="mp-input" placeholder="Введите наименование"></div>
          <div class="mp-field"><label>Подразделение</label><input id="dict_dept" class="mp-input" placeholder="Отдел, управление"></div>
          <div class="mp-field" id="dictTypeBlock">
            <label>Тип</label>
            <select id="dict_type" class="mp-input">
              <option value="временная">временная</option>
              <option value="постоянная">постоянная</option>
            </select>
          </div>
          <div class="mp-field">
            <label>Регламент / документ</label>
            <input id="dict_file" type="file" class="mp-input">
          </div>
          <div class="mp-field">
            <label>Комментарии</label>
            <textarea id="dict_comment" class="mp-input" rows="3" placeholder="Дополнительная информация"></textarea>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="dict-list">
          <div class="dict-list-title">Справочник</div>
          <ul id="dictList"></ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mp-toolbar">
        <button type="button" class="mp-btn" id="dictClose">Закрыть</button>
        <button type="button" class="mp-btn primary" id="dictSave">Добавить</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<script>
const DICT_KEYS = {
    cats: 'munart_dict_spheres',
    terr: 'munart_dict_territories',
    owners: 'munart_dict_owners',
    resp: 'munart_dict_responsibles',
    exec: 'munart_dict_executors',
    vendors: 'munart_dict_contractors'
  };
  function loadDict(key){
    try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(key) || '[]'); }catch(e){ return []; }
  }
  function saveDict(key, val){
    try{ localStorage.setItem(key, JSON.stringify(val)); }catch(e){}
  }
  function openDict(kind){
    const modal = document.getElementById('dictModal'); if (!modal) return;
    const title = document.getElementById('dictTitle');
    const labelMain = document.getElementById('dictLabelMain');
    const typeBlock = document.getElementById('dictTypeBlock');
    const listEl = document.getElementById('dictList');
    const nameEl = document.getElementById('dict_name');
    const deptEl = document.getElementById('dict_dept');
    const typeEl = document.getElementById('dict_type');
    const fileEl = document.getElementById('dict_file');
    const commentEl = document.getElementById('dict_comment');
    const key = DICT_KEYS[kind];
    const data = loadDict(key);

    // Заголовки и поле "Наименование" / "ФИО" в зависимости от справочника
    if (kind === 'cats'){
      title.textContent = 'Сферы поручений';
      labelMain.textContent = 'Наименование';
      typeBlock.style.display = '';
    } else if (kind === 'terr'){
      title.textContent = 'Территории поручений';
      labelMain.textContent = 'Территория';
      typeBlock.style.display = 'none';
    } else if (kind === 'owners'){
      title.textContent = 'Руководители';
      labelMain.textContent = 'ФИО';
      typeBlock.style.display = 'none';
    } else if (kind === 'resp'){
      title.textContent = 'Ответственные';
      labelMain.textContent = 'ФИО';
      typeBlock.style.display = 'none';
    } else if (kind === 'exec'){
      title.textContent = 'Исполнители';
      labelMain.textContent = 'ФИО';
      typeBlock.style.display = 'none';
    } else if (kind === 'vendors'){
      title.textContent = 'Подрядчики';
      labelMain.textContent = 'Наименование';
      typeBlock.style.display = 'none';
    } else {
      title.textContent = 'Справочник';
      labelMain.textContent = 'Наименование';
      typeBlock.style.display = 'none';
    }

    listEl.innerHTML = data.length ? data.map((it,idx)=>`
  <li class="dict-item">
    <div class="iavatar">${(it.name||'?').trim().split(/\s+/).slice(0,2).map(s=>s[0]).join('').toUpperCase()}</div>
    <div class="info">
      <div class="row1">
        <b>${escapeHtml(it.name||'')}</b>
        ${ it.kind ? `<span class="pill kind">${escapeHtml(it.kind)}</span>` : '' }
      </div>
      <div class="row2">
        ${ it.dept ? `<span class="pill dept">${escapeHtml(it.dept)}</span>` : '' }
        ${ it.doc ? `<span class="pill doc">📄 ${escapeHtml(it.doc)}</span>` : '' }
      </div>
      ${ it.comment ? `<div class="comment">${escapeHtml(it.comment)}</div>` : '' }
    </div>
    <button type="button" class="del" title="Удалить" data-del="${idx}">×</button>
  </li>
`).join('') : '<li class="dict-empty">пока нет записей</li>';

    listEl.querySelectorAll('[data-del]').forEach(btn=>{
      btn.onclick = ()=>{
        const i = +btn.dataset.del;
        data.splice(i,1);
        saveDict(key,data);
        openDict(kind);
      };
    });

    // Очистка формы
    nameEl.value = '';
    deptEl.value = '';
    if (typeEl) typeEl.value = 'временная';
    try{ fileEl.value = ''; }catch(_){}
    commentEl.value = '';

    modal.classList.add('open');
    modal.setAttribute('aria-hidden','false');

    document.getElementById('dictSave').onclick = ()=>{
      const nm = nameEl.value.trim();
      if (!nm){
        nameEl.focus();
        return;
      }
      const entry = {
        id: 'd_'+Date.now(),
        name: nm,
        dept: deptEl.value.trim(),
        kind: (kind === 'cats') ? (typeEl.value || 'постоянная') : '',
        doc: fileEl.files && fileEl.files[0] ? fileEl.files[0].name : '',
        comment: commentEl.value.trim()
      };
      data.push(entry);
      saveDict(key,data);
      openDict(kind);
    };
    document.getElementById('dictClose').onclick = ()=>{
      modal.classList.remove('open');
      modal.setAttribute('aria-hidden','true');
    };
  }

  function populateLookups(){
  const items = load();
  const catsProj = items.map(x=>x.category).filter(Boolean);
  const ownersProj = items.map(x=>x.owner).filter(Boolean);
  const respProj = items.map(x=>x.responsible).filter(Boolean);
  const vendorsProj = items.map(x=>x.vendor).filter(Boolean);

  const catsAll = Array.from(new Set([...catsProj, ...loadDict(DICT_KEYS.cats).map(x=>x.name)])).filter(Boolean).sort((a,b)=>a.localeCompare(b,'ru'));
  const ownersAll = Array.from(new Set([...ownersProj, ...loadDict(DICT_KEYS.owners).map(x=>x.name)])).filter(Boolean).sort((a,b)=>a.localeCompare(b,'ru'));
  const respAll = Array.from(new Set([...respProj, ...loadDict(DICT_KEYS.resp).map(x=>x.name)])).filter(Boolean).sort((a,b)=>a.localeCompare(b,'ru'));
  const vendorsAll = Array.from(new Set([...vendorsProj, ...loadDict(DICT_KEYS.vendors).map(x=>x.name)])).filter(Boolean).sort((a,b)=>a.localeCompare(b,'ru'));

  const selCat = document.getElementById('mp_category');
  const selOwner = document.getElementById('mp_owner');
  const selResp = document.getElementById('mp_responsible');
  const selVendor = document.getElementById('mp_vendor');

  if (selCat) selCat.innerHTML = '<option value=""></option>' + catsAll.map(v=>`<option value="${v}">${v}</option>`).join('');
  if (selOwner) selOwner.innerHTML = '<option value=""></option>' + ownersAll.map(v=>`<option value="${v}">${v}</option>`).join('');
  if (selResp) selResp.innerHTML = '<option value=""></option>' + respAll.map(v=>`<option value="${v}">${v}</option>`).join('');
  if (selVendor) selVendor.innerHTML = '<option value=""></option>' + vendorsAll.map(v=>`<option value="${v}">${v}</option>`).join('');
}
  
</script>

  <script>
    (function(){
      var splash = document.getElementById('tasksSplash');
      if (!splash) return;
      function hideSplash(){
        splash.classList.add('splash-hidden');
        setTimeout(function(){
          if (splash && splash.parentNode){
            splash.parentNode.removeChild(splash);
          }
        }, 450);
      }
      var delay = 3000;
      if (document.readyState === 'complete' || document.readyState === 'interactive'){
        setTimeout(hideSplash, delay);
      } else {
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function(){
          setTimeout(hideSplash, delay);
        });
      }
    })();
  </script>

</body>
</html>

    .btn-ghost{display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; padding:10px 12px; border-radius:12px; border:1px dashed var(--br); background:transparent; color:var(--text); cursor:pointer}
    input[type="file"]{display:none}
    .tpl-list{display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(220px,1fr)); gap:10px}

  <div class="wrap">

            Если форматирование «разорвало» текст — используйте в шаблоне обычный текст без стилизации вокруг плейсхолдера.
          </div>

              <option value="Поручение по маршруту №1">Поручение по маршруту №1</option>

  <script>
  (function(){
    // --- State & storage
    const LS_KEY = 'munart_tpls_v1';
    const tplListEl = document.getElementById('tplList');
    const tplEmptyEl = document.getElementById('tplEmpty');
    const chosenNameEl = document.getElementById('chosenName');
    const statusEl = document.getElementById('status');
    const assignSel = document.getElementById('assignSel');
    const assignTxt = document.getElementById('assignTxt');
    const dlLink = document.getElementById('dlLink');
    const btnCreate = document.getElementById('btnCreate');
    const depDot = document.getElementById('depDot');
    const depStatus = document.getElementById('depStatus');

    let templates = loadTpls();
    let chosen = null;

    // dependency check
    if (!window.JSZip){ depDot.className='err'; depStatus.title = 'CDN не загрузился'; }

    function loadTpls(){
      try{
        const arr = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(LS_KEY) || '[]');
        return Array.isArray(arr) ? arr : [];
      }catch(_){ return []; }
    }
    function saveTpls(){ localStorage.setItem(LS_KEY, JSON.stringify(templates)); }

    function sizeFmt(bytes){
      if(!bytes && bytes !== 0) return '';
      const u=['Б','КБ','МБ','ГБ']; let i=0; let n=bytes;
      while(n>=1024 && i<u.length-1){ n/=1024; i++; }
      return n.toFixed(n<10?1:0)+' '+u[i];
    }

    function renderList(){
      tplListEl.innerHTML = '';
      if (!templates.length){
        tplEmptyEl.style.display = '';
        return;
      }
      tplEmptyEl.style.display = 'none';
      templates.forEach(t => {
        const card = document.createElement('div');
        card.className = 'tpl';
        card.innerHTML = '<div class="nm"></div><div class="sz"></div><div class="ctl"><button class="btn">Выбрать</button><button class="btn-ghost">Удалить</button></div>';
        card.querySelector('.nm').textContent = t.name;
        card.querySelector('.sz').textContent = sizeFmt(t.size);
        const [btnPick, btnDel] = card.querySelectorAll('button');
        btnPick.onclick = () => { chosen = t; chosenNameEl.textContent = t.name; status('Шаблон выбран'); };
        btnDel.onclick = () => { templates = templates.filter(x => x.id !== t.id); saveTpls(); if(chosen && chosen.id===t.id){ chosen=null; chosenNameEl.textContent='—'; } renderList(); };
        tplListEl.appendChild(card);
      });
    }

    // upload
    document.getElementById('tplFile').addEventListener('change', async (e) => {
      const f = e.target.files && e.target.files[0];
      if(!f) return;
      const buf = await f.arrayBuffer();
      const b64 = arrayBufferToBase64(buf);
      templates.unshift({ id: String(Date.now()), name: f.name, size: f.size, data: b64 });
      if (templates.length > 50) templates = templates.slice(0,50);
      saveTpls();
      renderList();
      status('Шаблон добавлен');
      e.target.value = '';
    });

    document.getElementById('clearTpls').onclick = () => {
      if (confirm('Очистить коллекцию шаблонов?')){
        localStorage.removeItem(LS_KEY);
        templates = [];
        chosen = null; chosenNameEl.textContent='—';
        renderList();
      }
    };

    function pickTitle(){
      const v = (assignTxt.value || assignSel.value || '').trim();
      return v || 'Поручение';
    }

    btnCreate.onclick = async () => {
      const title = pickTitle();
      if(!chosen){ err('Сначала выберите шаблон'); return; }
      try{
        status('Готовим документ…');
        const zip = await JSZip.loadAsync(base64ToArrayBuffer(chosen.data));
        let xml = await zip.file('word/document.xml').async('string');
        // Replace <name> and &lt;name&gt;
        const esc = escapeXml(title);
        xml = xml.replace(/<name>/g, esc).replace(/&lt;name&gt;/g, esc);
        zip.file('word/document.xml', xml);
        const blob = await zip.generateAsync({ type:'blob' });
        const outName = (title.replace(/[\\/:*?"<>|]+/g,'_').slice(0,80) || 'document') + '.docx';
        dlLink.href = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
        dlLink.download = outName;
        dlLink.style.display = 'inline-flex';
        dlLink.textContent = 'Скачать: ' + outName;
        status('Готово. Можно скачивать.');
      }catch(ex){
        console.error(ex);
        err('Не удалось обработать .docx. Убедитесь, что в документе есть цельный плейсхолдер <name> без разрывов форматирования.');
      }
    };

    // helpers
    function status(t){ statusEl.textContent = t; }
    function err(t){ statusEl.innerHTML = '<span class="err">Ошибка:</span> ' + t; }
    function escapeXml(s){ return s.replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;'); }
    function arrayBufferToBase64(buffer) {
      let binary = ''; const bytes = new Uint8Array(buffer);
      const len = bytes.byteLength;
      for (let i = 0; i < len; i++) binary += String.fromCharCode(bytes[i]);
      return window.btoa(binary);
    }
    function base64ToArrayBuffer(base64) {
      const binary_string = window.atob(base64);
      const len = binary_string.length; const bytes = new Uint8Array(len);
      for (let i = 0; i < len; i++) bytes[i] = binary_string.charCodeAt(i);
      return bytes.buffer;
    }

    renderList();
  })();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
===== END FILE: munart_ui\public\prototypes\create-from-template.html =====

<td class="num" data-field="cashPct"></td>
<td class="num" data-field="objects"></td>
<td class="num" data-field="events"></td>
<td class="num" data-field="indicators"></td>
</tr>
<tr class="program-row" data-allocated-ratio="0.7" data-contracted-ratio="0.52" data-events-done="0" data-events-total="0" data-financed-ratio="0.4" data-indicators-done="0" data-indicators-total="0" data-objects="1" data-plan="240.0" data-program-id="productivity">

<tr class="summary-row">
<td class="col-project">
<div class="proj-cell">
