</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<div class="hint">
<span>Все цифры — демонстрационные; в реальной версии сюда подгружаются агрегированные данные из MunArt.</span>
<span>Шкала трактовки: контрактация — отношение «законтрактовано / выделено», кассовое освоение — «профинансировано / законтрактовано».</span>
</div>
</section>
</div>

<script>
    (function(){
      const tbody = document.querySelector('.eco-table tbody');
      const programRows = Array.from(tbody.querySelectorAll('tr.program-row'));
      const summaryRow = tbody.querySelector('tr.summary-row');
      const levelFilter = document.getElementById('levelFilter');

      const STORE_KEY = 'munart_projects_offline_light';

      function safeJSON(v, fallback){
        try { return JSON.parse(v); } catch(e){ return fallback; }
      }
      function toNum(v){
        if (v == null) return 0;
        if (typeof v === 'number') return isFinite(v) ? v : 0;
        const s = String(v).replace(/\s+/g,'').replace(',', '.');
        const n = parseFloat(s);
        return isFinite(n) ? n : 0;
      }
      function formatMoney(n){
        n = toNum(n);
        return n.toLocaleString('ru-RU', { maximumFractionDigits: 1, minimumFractionDigits: 1 });
      }

      function formatNumber(n){
        n = toNum(n);
        return n.toLocaleString('ru-RU', { maximumFractionDigits: 2 });
      }
      function formatInt(n){
        n = Math.round(toNum(n));
        return n.toLocaleString('ru-RU');
      }
      function formatPercent(p){
        return Math.round(toNum(p)) + '%';
      }

      function renderPercentCell(cell, value){
        if (!cell) return;
        if (value == null || isNaN(value)){
          cell.textContent = '—';
          return;
        }
        const pct = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, value));
        const pctLabel = formatPercent(pct);

        cell.innerHTML = '';
        const wrapper = document.createElement('div');
        wrapper.className = 'pct-cell';

        const span = document.createElement('span');
        span.className = 'pct-value';
        span.textContent = pctLabel;

        const bar = document.createElement('div');
        bar.className = 'pct-bar';

        const fill = document.createElement('div');
        fill.className = 'pct-bar-fill';
        fill.style.width = pct + '%';

        bar.appendChild(fill);
        wrapper.appendChild(span);
        wrapper.appendChild(bar);
        cell.appendChild(wrapper);
      }

function setKpi(id, text){
  const el = document.getElementById(id);
  if (el) el.textContent = text;
}
function setKpiBar(id, pct){
  const el = document.getElementById(id);
  if (!el) return;
  const v = isFinite(pct) ? Math.max(0, Math.min(100, pct)) : 0;
  el.style.width = v + '%';
}

function updateSummaryCards(totals){
  // 1) Выделено / Необходимо(План)
  const need = toNum(totals.plan);
  const allocated = toNum(totals.allocated);
  const contracted = toNum(totals.contracted);
  const financed = toNum(totals.financed);

  const pctAllocated = need > 0 ? (allocated / need) * 100 : NaN;
  const pctContracted = allocated > 0 ? (contracted / allocated) * 100 : NaN;
  const pctFinanced = contracted > 0 ? (financed / contracted) * 100 : NaN;

  setKpi('kpiAllocatedPct', isFinite(pctAllocated) ? (Math.round(pctAllocated*10)/10).toLocaleString('ru-RU') + '%' : '—');
  setKpiBar('kpiAllocatedBar', pctAllocated);
  setKpi('kpiAllocatedVal', formatMoney(allocated));
  setKpi('kpiNeedVal', formatMoney(need));

  setKpi('kpiContractedPct', isFinite(pctContracted) ? (Math.round(pctContracted*10)/10).toLocaleString('ru-RU') + '%' : '—');
  setKpiBar('kpiContractedBar', pctContracted);
  setKpi('kpiContractedVal', formatMoney(contracted));
  setKpi('kpiAllocatedVal2', formatMoney(allocated));

  setKpi('kpiFinancedPct', isFinite(pctFinanced) ? (Math.round(pctFinanced*10)/10).toLocaleString('ru-RU') + '%' : '—');
  setKpiBar('kpiFinancedBar', pctFinanced);
  setKpi('kpiFinancedVal', formatMoney(financed));
  setKpi('kpiContractedVal2', formatMoney(contracted));
}

      function getProjectsFromStore(){
        const raw = localStorage.getItem(STORE_KEY);
        const arr = safeJSON(raw, []);
        if (!Array.isArray(arr)) return [];
        return arr;
      }

      function isParentProject(p){
        const parentId = (p && (p.parent_id ?? p.parentId ?? p.parent)) ?? '';
        const petType  = (p && (p.pet_type ?? p.petType ?? p.type)) ?? '';
        const parentEmpty = parentId === null || parentId === undefined || String(parentId).trim() === '';
        const petEmpty = petType === null || petType === undefined || String(petType).trim() === '';
        // В вашем прототипе "пет-проект" обычно имеет pet_type, а дочерний — parent_id
        return parentEmpty && petEmpty;
      }

      function getProjectTitle(p){
        return (p.name || p.title || p.project_name || p.projectTitle || 'Без названия').trim();
      }

      function getProjectClassification(p){
        return (p.classification || p.mp_classification || p.direction || p.program || 'Без классификации').trim();
      }

      const SOURCES = [
        { key:'FB', label:'ФБ — Федеральный бюджет' },
        { key:'KB', label:'КБ — Краевой бюджет' },
        { key:'MB', label:'МБ — Муниципальный бюджет' },
        { key:'VB', label:'ВБ — Внебюджетные средства' }
      ];
      const FIELDS = [
        { key:'plan', label:'plan' },
        { key:'allocated', label:'allocated' },
        { key:'contracted', label:'contracted' },
        { key:'financed', label:'financed' }
      ];

      function readField(obj, pathArr){
        let cur = obj;
        for (const k of pathArr){
          if (!cur || typeof cur !== 'object') return undefined;
          cur = cur[k];
        }
        return cur;
      }

      // Пытаемся вытащить "Экономику" проекта в максимально гибком виде
      function getProjectEconomy(p){
        // 1) Нормализованный формат: p.economy.{FB,KB,MB,VB}.{plan,allocated,contracted,financed}
        const e = p.economy || p.economics || p.budgets || p.budget || null;

        function bySourceField(srcKey, fieldKey){
          // nested object
          if (e && typeof e === 'object'){
            // case-insensitive source key
            const variants = [srcKey, srcKey.toLowerCase(), srcKey.toUpperCase()];
            for (const v of variants){
              const sv = e[v];
              if (sv && typeof sv === 'object'){
                const fv = sv[fieldKey] ?? sv[fieldKey.toLowerCase()] ?? sv[fieldKey.toUpperCase()];
                if (fv != null) return toNum(fv);
              }
            }
            // array of rows [{code:'KB', plan:...}]
            if (Array.isArray(e)){
              const row = e.find(r => String(r.code || r.key || r.id || '').toUpperCase() === srcKey);
              if (row){
                const fv = row[fieldKey] ?? row[fieldKey.toLowerCase()] ?? row[fieldKey.toUpperCase()];
                if (fv != null) return toNum(fv);
              }
            }
          }

          // 2) Плоские поля вида eco_kb_plan / economy_KB_contracted / budget_kb_financed и т.п.
          const flatCandidates = [
            `eco_${srcKey.toLowerCase()}_${fieldKey}`,
            `econ_${srcKey.toLowerCase()}_${fieldKey}`,
            `economy_${srcKey.toLowerCase()}_${fieldKey}`,
            `budget_${srcKey.toLowerCase()}_${fieldKey}`,
            `${srcKey.toLowerCase()}_${fieldKey}`,

            `eco_${srcKey}_${fieldKey}`,
            `economy_${srcKey}_${fieldKey}`,
            `budget_${srcKey}_${fieldKey}`,
            `${srcKey}_${fieldKey}`
          ];
          for (const k of flatCandidates){
            if (p[k] != null) return toNum(p[k]);
          }

          return undefined;
        }

        const out = { FB:{}, KB:{}, MB:{}, VB:{}, _hasBreakdown:false };

        for (const s of SOURCES){
          for (const f of FIELDS){
            const v = bySourceField(s.key, f.key);
            if (v != null){
              out[s.key][f.key] = v;
              if (v !== 0) out._hasBreakdown = true;
            } else {
              out[s.key][f.key] = 0;
            }
          }
        }

        // 3) Fallback: только общий бюджет проекта (если нет детализации)
        const totalPlan = toNum(p.budget_plan ?? p.mp_budget_plan ?? p.plan ?? 0);
        const totalFin  = toNum(p.budget_spent ?? p.mp_budget_spent ?? p.financed ?? p.spent ?? 0);
        const totalAlloc = toNum(p.budget_allocated ?? p.mp_budget_allocated ?? p.allocated ?? totalPlan);
        const totalContr = toNum(p.budget_contracted ?? p.mp_budget_contracted ?? p.contracted ?? 0);

        if (!out._hasBreakdown && (totalPlan || totalFin || totalAlloc || totalContr)){
          // Безопасный вариант: считаем, что это МБ (если источники не разложены)
          out.MB.plan = totalPlan;
          out.MB.allocated = totalAlloc;
          out.MB.contracted = totalContr;
          out.MB.financed = totalFin;
        }

        return out;
      }

      function sumEconomy(econ){
        let plan=0, allocated=0, contracted=0, financed=0;
        for (const s of SOURCES){
          const b = econ[s.key] || {};
          plan += toNum(b.plan);
          allocated += toNum(b.allocated);
          contracted += toNum(b.contracted);
          financed += toNum(b.financed);
        }
        return { plan, allocated, contracted, financed };
      }

      function clearGeneratedRows(){
        Array.from(tbody.querySelectorAll('tr.project-row, tr.budget-row')).forEach(r => r.remove());
        programRows.forEach(r => {
          r.classList.remove('expanded');
          const btn = r.querySelector('.expander');
          if (btn) btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', 'false');
        });
      }

      function render(){
        clearGeneratedRows();

        const projects = getProjectsFromStore().filter(isParentProject);

        // group by classification
        const byClass = new Map();
        projects.forEach(p => {
          const key = getProjectClassification(p);
          if (!byClass.has(key)) byClass.set(key, []);
          byClass.get(key).push(p);
        });

        const totals = { plan:0, allocated:0, contracted:0, financed:0, objects:0, eventsDone:0, eventsTotal:0, indicatorsDone:0, indicatorsTotal:0 };

        programRows.forEach(programRow => {
          const pid = programRow.dataset.programId;
          const dirName = (programRow.querySelector('.proj-name')?.textContent || '').trim();

          // сохранить базовую подпись один раз
          if (!programRow.dataset.baseMeta){
            const metaEl = programRow.querySelector('.proj-meta');
            programRow.dataset.baseMeta = metaEl ? metaEl.textContent.trim() : '';
          }

          const list = byClass.get(dirName) || [];
          const metaEl = programRow.querySelector('.proj-meta');
          if (metaEl){
            const base = programRow.dataset.baseMeta || '';
            const suffix = list.length ? `проектов: ${list.length}` : 'нет проектов';
            metaEl.textContent = base ? `${base} • ${suffix}` : suffix;
          }

          // агрегаты по направлению
          let dirPlan=0, dirAlloc=0, dirContr=0, dirFin=0;

          // вставка проектов (уровень 2) после строки направления
          let lastRow = programRow;

          list.forEach((p, idx) => {
            const projectId = String(p.id || p.project_id || p.uid || (pid + '-p' + idx));

            const econ = getProjectEconomy(p);
            const sums = sumEconomy(econ);

            dirPlan += sums.plan;
            dirAlloc += sums.allocated;
            dirContr += sums.contracted;
            dirFin += sums.financed;

            const pr = document.createElement('tr');
            pr.className = 'project-row';
            pr.dataset.programId = pid;
            pr.dataset.projectId = projectId;

            const title = getProjectTitle(p);

            pr.innerHTML = `
              <td class="col-project">
                <div class="proj-cell">
                  <button class="expander" type="button" aria-label="Раскрыть источники бюджета" aria-expanded="false"></button>
                  <div class="proj-icon icon-project">📁</div>
                  <div>
                    <div class="proj-name">${escapeHtml(title)}</div>
                    <div class="proj-meta">основной проект</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </td>
              <td class="num">${formatNumber(sums.plan)}</td>
              <td class="num">${formatNumber(sums.allocated)}</td>
              <td class="num">${formatNumber(sums.contracted)}</td>
              <td class="num">${formatNumber(sums.financed)}</td>
              <td class="num pct-contract"></td>
              <td class="num pct-cash"></td>
              <td class="num">—</td>
              <td class="num">—</td>
              <td class="num">—</td>
            `;

            const contrPct = sums.allocated > 0 ? (sums.contracted / sums.allocated) * 100 : NaN;
            const cashPct  = sums.contracted > 0 ? (sums.financed / sums.contracted) * 100 : NaN;
            renderPercentCell(pr.querySelector('.pct-contract'), isFinite(contrPct) ? contrPct : NaN);
            renderPercentCell(pr.querySelector('.pct-cash'), isFinite(cashPct) ? cashPct : NaN);

            lastRow.parentNode.insertBefore(pr, lastRow.nextSibling);
            lastRow = pr;

            // строки источников бюджета (уровень 3) — только если есть хоть какая-то детализация (или fallback в МБ)
            const hasAny = SOURCES.some(s => {
              const b = econ[s.key] || {};
              return toNum(b.plan)||toNum(b.allocated)||toNum(b.contracted)||toNum(b.financed);
            });

            if (hasAny){
              SOURCES.forEach(src => {
                const b = econ[src.key] || {};
                const row = document.createElement('tr');
                row.className = 'budget-row';
                row.dataset.programId = pid;
                row.dataset.projectId = projectId;

                row.innerHTML = `
                  <td class="col-project">${src.label}</td>
                  <td class="num">${formatNumber(b.plan)}</td>
                  <td class="num">${formatNumber(b.allocated)}</td>
                  <td class="num">${formatNumber(b.contracted)}</td>
                  <td class="num">${formatNumber(b.financed)}</td>
                  <td class="num pct-contract"></td>
                  <td class="num pct-cash"></td>
                  <td class="num">—</td>
                  <td class="num">—</td>
                  <td class="num">—</td>
                `;

                const cPct = toNum(b.allocated) > 0 ? (toNum(b.contracted) / toNum(b.allocated)) * 100 : NaN;
                const kPct = toNum(b.contracted) > 0 ? (toNum(b.financed) / toNum(b.contracted)) * 100 : NaN;
                renderPercentCell(row.querySelector('.pct-contract'), isFinite(cPct) ? cPct : NaN);
                renderPercentCell(row.querySelector('.pct-cash'), isFinite(kPct) ? kPct : NaN);

                // по умолчанию скрываем — пока не раскрыт проект/направление
                row.style.display = 'none';

                lastRow.parentNode.insertBefore(row, lastRow.nextSibling);
                lastRow = row;
              });
            }

            // проект по умолчанию скрыт, пока не раскрыто направление (или уровень фильтра)
            pr.style.display = 'none';
          });

          // Заполняем строку направления
          const contractPct = dirAlloc > 0 ? (dirContr / dirAlloc) * 100 : NaN;
          const cashPct = dirContr > 0 ? (dirFin / dirContr) * 100 : NaN;

          const setField = (field, val) => {
            const cell = programRow.querySelector('[data-field="'+field+'"]');
            if (cell) cell.textContent = formatNumber(val);
          };

          setField('plan', dirPlan);
          setField('allocated', dirAlloc);
          setField('contracted', dirContr);
          setField('financed', dirFin);
          renderPercentCell(programRow.querySelector('[data-field="contractPct"]'), isFinite(contractPct) ? contractPct : NaN);
          renderPercentCell(programRow.querySelector('[data-field="cashPct"]'), isFinite(cashPct) ? cashPct : NaN);

          // Эти поля пока не считаем (нет данных)
          const objectsCell = programRow.querySelector('[data-field="objects"]');
          const eventsCell = programRow.querySelector('[data-field="events"]');
          const indicatorsCell = programRow.querySelector('[data-field="indicators"]');
          if (objectsCell) objectsCell.textContent = '—';
          if (eventsCell) eventsCell.textContent = '—';
          if (indicatorsCell) indicatorsCell.textContent = '—';

          totals.plan += dirPlan;
          totals.allocated += dirAlloc;
          totals.contracted += dirContr;
          totals.financed += dirFin;
        });

        // Итоги
        if (summaryRow){
          summaryRow.querySelector('[data-field="plan"]').textContent = formatNumber(totals.plan);
          summaryRow.querySelector('[data-field="allocated"]').textContent = formatNumber(totals.allocated);
          summaryRow.querySelector('[data-field="contracted"]').textContent = formatNumber(totals.contracted);
          summaryRow.querySelector('[data-field="financed"]').textContent = formatNumber(totals.financed);

          const contractPct = totals.allocated > 0 ? (totals.contracted / totals.allocated) * 100 : NaN;
          const cashPct = totals.contracted > 0 ? (totals.financed / totals.contracted) * 100 : NaN;
          renderPercentCell(summaryRow.querySelector('[data-field="contractPct"]'), isFinite(contractPct) ? contractPct : NaN);
          renderPercentCell(summaryRow.querySelector('[data-field="cashPct"]'), isFinite(cashPct) ? cashPct : NaN);
        }

        // обновляем KPI-свод (верхняя панель)
        updateSummaryCards(totals);

        // применяем текущий уровень раскрытия
        if (levelFilter){
          applyLevelFilter(levelFilter.value || '1');
        }
      }

      function escapeHtml(s){
        return String(s)
          .replace(/&/g,'&amp;')
          .replace(/</g,'&lt;')
          .replace(/>/g,'&gt;')
          .replace(/"/g,'&quot;')
          .replace(/'/g,'&#039;');
      }

      // --- ОРИГИНАЛЬНАЯ логика уровней раскрытия и ручных раскрытий (оставлена) ---
      function applyLevelFilter(level){
        if (!level) return;
        programRows.forEach(function(programRow){
          const pid = programRow.dataset.programId;
          const projectRows = tbody.querySelectorAll('tr.project-row[data-program-id="'+pid+'"]');
          const budgetRows = tbody.querySelectorAll('tr.budget-row[data-program-id="'+pid+'"]');

          if (level === '1'){
            programRow.classList.remove('expanded');
            programRow.style.display = 'table-row';
            projectRows.forEach(function(r){
              r.style.display = 'none';
              r.classList.remove('expanded');
              const btn = r.querySelector('.expander');
              if (btn) btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded','false');
            });
            budgetRows.forEach(function(r){
              r.style.display = 'none';
            });
          } else if (level === '2'){
            programRow.classList.add('expanded');
            programRow.style.display = 'table-row';
            projectRows.forEach(function(r){
              r.style.display = 'table-row';
              r.classList.remove('expanded');
              const btn = r.querySelector('.expander');
              if (btn) btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded','false');
            });
            budgetRows.forEach(function(r){
              r.style.display = 'none';
            });
          } else if (level === '3'){
            programRow.classList.add('expanded');
            programRow.style.display = 'table-row';
            projectRows.forEach(function(r){
              r.style.display = 'table-row';
              r.classList.add('expanded');
              const btn = r.querySelector('.expander');
              if (btn) btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded','true');
            });
            budgetRows.forEach(function(r){
              r.style.display = 'table-row';
            });
          }
        });
      }

      if (levelFilter){
        levelFilter.addEventListener('change', function(){
          applyLevelFilter(this.value);
        });
      }

      document.querySelector('.eco-table').addEventListener('click', function(evt){
        const btn = evt.target.closest('.expander');
        if (!btn) return;

        const row = btn.closest('tr');
        if (row.classList.contains('program-row')){
          const pid = row.dataset.programId;
          const expanded = !row.classList.contains('expanded');
          row.classList.toggle('expanded', expanded);

          const projectRows = tbody.querySelectorAll('tr.project-row[data-program-id="'+pid+'"]');
          const budgetRows = tbody.querySelectorAll('tr.budget-row[data-program-id="'+pid+'"]');

          projectRows.forEach(function(r){
            r.style.display = expanded ? 'table-row' : 'none';
            if (!expanded){
              r.classList.remove('expanded');
              const b = r.querySelector('.expander');
              if (b) b.setAttribute('aria-expanded','false');
              const projectId = r.dataset.projectId;
              tbody.querySelectorAll('tr.budget-row[data-project-id="'+projectId+'"]').forEach(function(br){
                br.style.display = 'none';
              });
            }
          });
          budgetRows.forEach(function(r){
            r.style.display = 'none';
          });

          btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', expanded ? 'true' : 'false');
        } else if (row.classList.contains('project-row')){
          const projectId = row.dataset.projectId;
          const expanded = !row.classList.contains('expanded');
          row.classList.toggle('expanded', expanded);

          const budgetRows = tbody.querySelectorAll('tr.budget-row[data-project-id="'+projectId+'"]');
          budgetRows.forEach(function(r){
            r.style.display = expanded ? 'table-row' : 'none';
          });

          btn.setAttribute('aria-expanded', expanded ? 'true' : 'false');
        }
      });

      // Перерисовка при загрузке
      render();

      // На случай изменений STORE в другой вкладке
      window.addEventListener('storage', function(e){
        if (e && e.key === STORE_KEY){
          render();
        }
      });

    })();
    </script></body>
</html>
===== END FILE: munart_ui\public\prototypes\economy.html =====

<html lang="ru">

  :root{--bg:#0f172a;--panel:#0b1220;--card:#0b1220;--muted:#94a3b8;--text:#e2e8f0;--accent:#60a5fa;--br:#1f2937;--chip:#111827}

    :root{--bg:#f7f8fb;--panel:#fff;--card:#fff;--muted:#6b7280;--text:#0f172a;--accent:#2563eb;--br:#e5e7eb;--chip:#f1f5f9}

<script>
const LS="munart_audit_log_v1"; const $=id=>document.getElementById(id);
const tbody=document.querySelector("#tbl tbody");
function getLog(){try{return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(LS)||"[]")}catch{return[]}}
function setLog(a){localStorage.setItem(LS,JSON.stringify(a))}
function rowHtml(e){const d=new Date(e.date).toLocaleString();const det=e.details?JSON.stringify(e.details).slice(0,140):"";return `<tr>
<td class="muted">${d}</td>
<td><span class="pill">${e.user||"—"}</span></td>
<td>${e.entity||"—"}</td>
<td><span class="pill ${e.action?.includes("удал")?"danger":e.action?.includes("созд")?"ok":e.action?.includes("блок")?"warn":""}">${e.action||"—"}</span></td>
<td><code class="muted">${det}</code></td></tr>`}
function render(){const q=$("q").value.trim().toLowerCase();const s=$("sort").value;let it=getLog();
 if(q)it=it.filter(x=>[x.user,x.action,x.entity,JSON.stringify(x.details||{})].join(" ").toLowerCase().includes(q));
 const sign=s.startsWith("-")?-1:1,key=s.replace("-","");it.sort((a,b)=>{const va=key==="date"?(a.date||""):(a[key]||"");const vb=key==="date"?(b.date||""):(b[key]||"");return(va>vb?1:va<vb?-1:0)*sign});
 tbody.innerHTML=it.map(rowHtml).join("")}
$("q").oninput=render;$("sort").onchange=render;document.querySelectorAll("th[data-k]").forEach(th=>th.onclick=()=>{$("sort").value=$("sort").value===th.dataset.k?("-"+th.dataset.k):th.dataset.k;render()});
$("gen").onclick=()=>{const users=["Администратор","Менеджер","Сотрудник","Система"],acts=["создал проект","изменил статус","удалил задачу","добавил файл","заблокировал пользователя"],ents=["Проект 404","Поручение SUB-1234","Пользователь ivan.petrov","Смета #2025-02"];const e={id:"ev_"+Date.now(),date:new Date().toISOString(),user:users[Math.random()*users.length|0],action:acts[Math.random()*acts.length|0],entity:ents[Math.random()*ents.length|0],details:{ip:"127.0.0.1",ua:"offline-prototype"}};const a=getLog();a.unshift(e);setLog(a);render()}
$("export").onclick=()=>{const blob=new Blob([localStorage.getItem(LS)||"[]"],{type:"application/json"});const url=URL.createObjectURL(blob);const a=document.createElement("a");a.href=url;a.download="history_export.json";a.click();URL.revokeObjectURL(url)}
$("import").parentElement.onclick=()=>$("import").click()
$("import").onchange=async ev=>{const f=ev.target.files[0];if(!f)return;const txt=await f.text();try{const arr=JSON.parse(txt);setLog(arr);render()}catch{alert("Неверный JSON")}}
render();
</script>
</body></html>

<title>MunArt • Панель управления (offline)</title>
<style>
  :root{--bg:#0f172a;--panel:#0b1220;--card:#0b1220;--muted:#94a3b8;--text:#e2e8f0;--accent:#60a5fa;--br:#1f2937;--chip:#111827}

    :root{--bg:#f7f8fb;--panel:#fff;--card:#fff;--muted:#6b7280;--text:#0f172a;--accent:#2563eb;--br:#e5e7eb;--chip:#f1f5f9}

            <label class="pill"><input type="checkbox" id="p_fin_r"> Финансы: чтение</label>

          <button class="soft" id="del">Удалить</button>

      </div>
      <div class="muted" style="margin-top:6px">Хранится в: <code>localStorage.munart_users_v1</code>. Каждое действие добавляется в <code>munart_audit_log_v1</code>.</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Список -->
    <div class="card">
      <div class="row" style="justify-content:space-between;align-items:center">
        <div class="title" style="font-size:16px">Пользователи</div>
        <div class="row">
          <input id="q" placeholder="Поиск: ФИО/email/роль">
          <select id="sort">
            <option value="name">ФИО ↑</option><option value="-name">ФИО ↓</option>
            <option value="email">Email ↑</option><option value="-email">Email ↓</option>
            <option value="role">Роль ↑</option><option value="-role">Роль ↓</option>
            <option value="-date">По дате ↓</option>
          </select>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="tablewrap" style="margin-top:8px">
        <table id="tbl"><thead>
          <tr><th>ФИО</th><th>Email</th><th>Роль</th><th>Статус</th><th></th></tr>
        </thead><tbody></tbody></table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<script>
const LS_USERS='munart_users_v1', LS_AUDIT='munart_audit_log_v1';
const $=id=>document.getElementById(id), tbody=document.querySelector('#tbl tbody');

function getUsers(){try{return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(LS_USERS)||'[]')}catch{return[]}}
function setUsers(a){localStorage.setItem(LS_USERS,JSON.stringify(a))}
function pushAudit(e){try{const arr=JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(LS_AUDIT)||'[]');arr.unshift({id:'ev_'+Date.now(),date:new Date().toISOString(),...e});localStorage.setItem(LS_AUDIT,JSON.stringify(arr))}catch{}}

let selId='';
function fillForm(u){$('f_name').value=u?.name||'';$('f_email').value=u?.email||'';$('f_role').value=u?.role||'viewer';$('f_active').checked=(u?.active??true);
$('p_projects_r').checked=!!u?.perm?.projects_r;$('p_projects_w').checked=!!u?.perm?.projects_w;$('p_tasks_r').checked=!!u?.perm?.tasks_r;$('p_tasks_w').checked=!!u?.perm?.tasks_w;$('p_fin_r').checked=!!u?.perm?.fin_r;$('p_fin_w').checked=!!u?.perm?.fin_w;$('p_admin').checked=!!u?.perm?.admin}
function readForm(){return{id:selId||'u_'+Date.now(),name:$('f_name').value.trim(),email:$('f_email').value.trim(),role:$('f_role').value,active:$('f_active').checked,perm:{projects_r:$('p_projects_r').checked,projects_w:$('p_projects_w').checked,tasks_r:$('p_tasks_r').checked,tasks_w:$('p_tasks_w').checked,fin_r:$('p_fin_r').checked,fin_w:$('p_fin_w').checked,admin:$('p_admin').checked},createdAt:selId?(getUsers().find(u=>u.id===selId)?.createdAt||new Date().toISOString()):new Date().toISOString()}}
function render(){const q=$('q').value.trim().toLowerCase(),sort=$('sort').value,sign=sort.startsWith('-')?-1:1,key=sort.replace('-','');let items=getUsers();
 if(items.length===0){items=[{id:'u_admin',name:'Администратор',email:'admin@example.com',role:'admin',active:true,perm:{admin:true,projects_r:true,projects_w:true,tasks_r:true,tasks_w:true,fin_r:true,fin_w:true},createdAt:new Date().toISOString()}];setUsers(items)}
 if(q)items=items.filter(u=>[u.name,u.email,u.role,u.active?'active':'blocked'].join(' ').toLowerCase().includes(q));
 items.sort((a,b)=>{const va=key==='date'?(a.createdAt||''):(a[key]||''),vb=key==='date'?(b.createdAt||''):(b[key]||'');return(va>vb?1:va<vb?-1:0)*sign});
 tbody.innerHTML=items.map(u=>`<tr><td>${u.name||'—'}</td><td class="muted">${u.email||'—'}</td><td><span class="role">${u.role}</span></td><td><span class="status ${u.active?'active':'blocked'}">${u.active?'Активен':'Блокирован'}</span></td><td style="white-space:nowrap"><button class="soft" onclick='edit("${u.id}")'>Редактировать</button> <button class="soft" onclick='toggle("${u.id}")'>${u.active?'Блокировать':'Разблокировать'}</button></td></tr>`).join('')}
window.edit=id=>{const u=getUsers().find(x=>x.id===id);selId=id;fillForm(u)}
window.toggle=id=>{const list=getUsers().map(u=>u.id===id?({...u,active:!u.active}):u);setUsers(list);const u=list.find(x=>x.id===id);pushAudit({user:'Администратор',entity:`Пользователь ${u.email}`,action:u.active?'разблокировал пользователя':'заблокировал пользователя'});render()}
$('save').onclick=()=>{const u=readForm();if(!u.name||!u.email)return alert('Заполните ФИО и Email.');const list=getUsers().filter(x=>x.id!==u.id);list.unshift(u);setUsers(list);pushAudit({user:'Администратор',entity:`Пользователь ${u.email}`,action:selId?'изменил пользователя':'создал пользователя',details:{role:u.role,active:u.active}});selId='';fillForm(null);render()}
$('new').onclick=()=>{selId='';fillForm(null)}
$('reset').onclick=()=>{if(!selId)return alert('Выберите пользователя');pushAudit({user:'Администратор',entity:`Пользователь ${selId}`,action:'сбросил пароль'});alert('Сброс пароля: отправка будет реализована позже.')}
$('del').onclick=()=>{if(!selId)return alert('Выберите пользователя');const list=getUsers().filter(u=>u.id!==selId);setUsers(list);pushAudit({user:'Администратор',entity:`Пользователь ${selId}`,action:'удалил пользователя'});selId='';fillForm(null);render()}
$('q').oninput=render;$('sort').onchange=render;
$('export').onclick=()=>{const blob=new Blob([localStorage.getItem(LS_USERS)||'[]'],{type:'application/json'});const url=URL.createObjectURL(blob);const a=document.createElement('a');a.href=url;a.download='users_export.json';a.click();URL.revokeObjectURL(url)}
$('import').parentElement.onclick=()=>$('import').click()
$('import').onchange=async ev=>{const f=ev.target.files[0];if(!f)return;const txt=await f.text();try{const arr=JSON.parse(txt);setUsers(arr);render()}catch{alert('Неверный JSON')}}
render();fillForm(null);
</script>
</body></html>
===== END FILE: munart_ui\public\prototypes\Master_admin.html =====

      <input id="p_from" type="date">
      <span>—</span>
      <input id="p_to" type="date">
      <button id="p_apply" class="btn-ghost">Применить</button>
      <div id="p_info" class="muted" style="margin-left:auto; font-size:12px;"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- === Нижняя сетка из трёх графиков === -->
    <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;">
      <div class="card"><b>Поручения</b><svg id="g_tasks_ts"></svg><div id="g_tasks_legend" class="legend"></div></div>
      <div class="card"><b>Проекты</b><svg id="g_projects_ts"></svg><div id="g_projects_legend" class="legend"></div></div>
      <div class="card"><b>Объезды — распределение статусов</b><svg id="g_rounds_donut"></svg><div id="g_rounds_legend" class="legend"></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Модалка "Событие дня" -->
  <div class="modal" id="eodModal" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="panel" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="eodTitle">
      <div class="flex" style="justify-content:space-between;align-items:center">
        <div class="title" id="eodTitle">Событие дня</div>
        <button class="btn-ghost" id="eodClose" type="button">Закрыть</button>
      </div>
      <div class="form" style="margin-top:6px">
        <div id="eodMeta" class="muted" style="font-size:12px"></div>
        <div id="eodBody" class="text" style="white-space:pre-wrap"></div>
        <div id="eodTags" class="flex" style="gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:8px"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ВЕСЬ JS — В САМОМ КОНЦЕ -->
  <script>
  (function(){
    const $ = (id)=>document.getElementById(id);

	function readDashboardCounters(){
	  // --- кто я ---
	  const me = (function pickMe(){
		const keys = [
		  'munart_auth_user_v1','munart_current_user','munart_user_v1',
		  'munart_profile_v1','munart_user','auth_user'
		];
		for (const k of keys){
		  try{
			const v = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(k) || 'null');
			if (v && typeof v === 'object'){
			  return {
				id: String(v.id ?? v.user_id ?? v.uid ?? ''),
				name: String(v.name ?? v.full_name ?? v.displayName ?? v.username ?? '').toLowerCase(),
				email: String(v.email ?? '').toLowerCase(),
			  };
			}
		  }catch(_){}
		}
		return { id:'', name:'', email:'' };
	  })();

	  // универсальная проверка «назначено на меня»
	  const isMine = (item)=>{
		if (!item || (!me.id && !me.name && !me.email)) return false;

		const fieldsScalar = [
		  'assignee','assigned_to','executor','performer','responsible','owner','doer','user',
		  'assignee_id','assigned_to_id','executor_id','performer_id','responsible_id','owner_id','user_id','manager_id'
		];
		const fieldsArray = [
		  'assignees','executors','performers','responsibles','members','participants'
		];

		const hit = (val)=>{
		  if (val == null) return false;
		  if (Array.isArray(val)) return val.some(hit);
		  if (typeof val === 'object'){
			return hit(val.id) || hit(val.email) || hit(val.name) || hit(val.title);
		  }
		  const s = String(val).toLowerCase();
		  return (me.id && s === String(me.id)) || (!!me.email && s === me.email) || (!!me.name && s === me.name);
		};

		for (const f of fieldsScalar){ if (f in item && hit(item[f])) return true; }
		for (const f of fieldsArray){ if (f in item && hit(item[f])) return true; }

		return false;
	  };

	  const dueTs = (obj)=>{
		const cand = ['due','deadline','due_date','date_due','finish_at','finished_at','end_at','planned_end','expected_end','date_end','dueAt'];
		for (const k of cand){
		  const v = obj?.[k];
		  if (v == null) continue;
		  const t = (typeof v === 'number') ? v : Date.parse(v);
		  if (!isNaN(t)) return t;
		}
		return null;
	  };

	  // источники
	  let projects = [], tasks = [];
	  try{ projects = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_projects_offline_light') || '[]'); }catch(_){}
	  try{ tasks    = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_tasks_v1') || '[]'); }catch(_){}

	  // счётчики
	  const projects_my = projects.filter(p => isMine(p)).length;
	  const tasks_my    = tasks.filter(t => isMine(t)).length;

	  const now   = Date.now();
	  const soon  = now + 7*24*60*60*1000;
	  const expiring = (arr)=> arr.reduce((acc, it)=>{
		const d = dueTs(it);
		if (d != null && d <= soon) acc++;
		return acc;
	  }, 0);

	  const attention = expiring(tasks) + expiring(projects);

	  return { projects_my, tasks_my, attention, plans: 0 };
	}

	function renderCounters(data){
	  $('k_projects').textContent      = data.projects_my || 0;
	  $('k_tasks_new').textContent     = data.tasks_my    || 0;
	  $('k_tasks_inwork').textContent  = data.attention   || 0;
	  $('k_projects_done').textContent = data.plans       || 0;
	}

	function normalizeIncomingCounters(p){
	  const out = {};
	  if (p == null || typeof p !== 'object') return out;
	  if (p.projects_my != null) out.projects_my = p.projects_my;
	  if (p.tasks_my    != null) out.tasks_my    = p.tasks_my;
	  if (p.attention   != null) out.attention   = p.attention;
	  if (p.plans       != null) out.plans       = p.plans;
	  if (p.projects_active != null) out.projects_my = p.projects_active;
	  if (p.tasks_new       != null) out.tasks_my    = p.tasks_new;
	  if (p.tasks_inwork    != null) out.attention   = p.tasks_inwork;
	  if (p.projects_done   != null) out.plans       = p.projects_done;
	  return out;
	}

	// Линейный график
	function drawChart(){
	  const el = $('chart'); const w = el.clientWidth||300, h= el.clientHeight||220, p=28;
	  const DAY = 86400000, days = 14;
	  const end = new Date(); end.setHours(0,0,0,0);
	  const startTs = +end - (days-1)*DAY;

	  const created = new Array(days).fill(0);
	  const closed  = new Array(days).fill(0);
	  const safe = k=>{ try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(k)||'[]'); }catch{ return []; } };
	  const tasks=safe('munart_tasks_v1'), projects=safe('munart_projects_offline_light');

	  const pickTs=(o,fs)=>{ for(const f of fs){ const v=o?.[f]; if(v==null) continue; const t=typeof v==='number'?v:Date.parse(v); if(!isNaN(t)) return t; } return null; };
	  const bucket=(ts)=>{ const i=Math.floor((ts-startTs)/DAY); return (i>=0&&i<days)?i:-1; };

	  for(const t of tasks){
		const c=pickTs(t,['created_at','createdAt','created','added_at']);
		if(c!=null){ const i=bucket(c); if(i>=0) created[i]++; }
		const done=String(t.status||'').toLowerCase();
		if(done.includes('done')||done.includes('close')||done.includes('complete')){
		  const d=pickTs(t,['done_at','closed_at','completed_at','finished_at','updated_at']);
		  if(d!=null){ const i=bucket(d); if(i>=0) closed[i]++; }
		}
	  }
	  for(const p of projects){
		const c=pickTs(p,['created_at','createdAt','created','added_at']);
		if(c!=null){ const i=bucket(c); if(i>=0) created[i]++; }
		if(String(p.status||'').toLowerCase()==='done'){
		  const d=pickTs(p,['done_at','finished_at','completed_at','closed_at','updated_at']);
		  if(d!=null){ const i=bucket(d); if(i>=0) closed[i]++; }
		}
	  }

	  const max = Math.max(1, ...created, ...closed);
	  const sx = (i)=> p + i*((w-2*p)/(days-1));
	  const sy = (v)=> h - p - (v/max)*(h-2*p);
	  const path = (arr)=> 'M '+arr.map((v,i)=> `${sx(i)} ${sy(v)}`).join(' L ');
	  const ticksY = 4; const grid = [];
	  for(let i=0;i<=ticksY;i++){
		const val = Math.round(max*i/ticksY);
		const y = sy(val);
		grid.push(`<line x1="${p}" y1="${y}" x2="${w-p}" y2="${y}" stroke="currentColor" opacity=".08"/>`);
		grid.push(`<text x="${p-6}" y="${y+4}" text-anchor="end" font-size="11" fill="currentColor" opacity=".55">${val}</text>`);
	  }
	  const labelsX = [];
	  for(let i=0;i<days;i+=2){
		const d = new Date(startTs + i*DAY);
		const lbl = d.toLocaleDateString('ru-RU',{day:'2-digit', month:'2-digit'});
		labelsX.push(`<text x="${sx(i)}" y="${h-6}" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="currentColor" opacity=".55">${lbl}</text>`);
	  }

	  el.innerHTML =
	  `<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none">
		 <g fill="none" stroke="currentColor" opacity=".08">
		   <line x1="${p}" y1="${h-p}" x2="${w-p}" y2="${h-p}"/>
		   <line x1="${p}" y1="${p}"   x2="${p}"   y2="${h-p}"/>
		 </g>
		 ${grid.join('')}
		 <path d="${path(created)}" fill="none" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2"/>
		 <path d="${path(closed)}"  fill="none" stroke="#6366f1" stroke-width="2"/>
		 ${labelsX.join('')}
		 <g font-size="12">
		   <rect x="${w-p-170}" y="${p-18}" width="8" height="2" fill="#0ea5e9"/><text x="${w-p-156}" y="${p-14}" fill="currentColor">Создано</text>
		   <rect x="${w-p-92}"  y="${p-18}" width="8" height="2" fill="#6366f1"/><text x="${w-p-78}"  y="${p-14}" fill="currentColor">Завершено</text>
		 </g>
	   </svg>`;
	}

	// Мини-календарь
	(function miniCalendar(){
	  const DAY = 86400000;
	  const $title = $('calTitle');
	  const $prev  = $('calPrev');
	  const $next  = $('calNext');
	  const $grid  = $('miniCal');
	  if (!$title || !$grid) return;

	  const me = (function(){
		const keys = ['munart_auth_user_v1','munart_current_user','munart_user_v1','munart_profile_v1','munart_user','auth_user'];
		for (const k of keys){
		  try{
			const v = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(k)||'null');
			if (v) return {
			  id: String(v.id ?? v.user_id ?? v.uid ?? ''),
			  name: String(v.name ?? v.full_name ?? v.displayName ?? v.username ?? '').toLowerCase(),
			  email: String(v.email ?? '').toLowerCase()
			};
		  }catch(_){}
		}
		return {id:'',name:'',email:''};
	  })();
	  const hit = (val)=>{
		if (val==null) return false;
		if (Array.isArray(val)) return val.some(hit);
		if (typeof val==='object') return hit(val.id)||hit(val.email)||hit(val.name)||hit(val.title);
		const s=String(val).toLowerCase();
		return (me.id && s===String(me.id)) || (me.email && s===me.email) || (me.name && s===me.name);
	  };
	  const isMine = (t)=>{
		const scal=['assignee','assigned_to','executor','performer','responsible','owner','doer','user','assignee_id','assigned_to_id','executor_id','performer_id','responsible_id','owner_id','user_id','manager_id'];
		const arr =['assignees','executors','performers','responsibles','members','participants'];
		for(const f of scal){ if (f in t && hit(t[f])) return true; }
		for(const f of arr){ if (f in t && hit(t[f])) return true; }
		return false;
	  };
	  const pickTs = (obj, fields)=>{
		for(const f of fields){
		  const v = obj?.[f];
		  if (v==null) continue;
		  const t = (typeof v==='number')? v : Date.parse(v);
		  if (!isNaN(t)) return t;
		}
		return null;
	  };
	  const iso = (d)=> new Date(d).toISOString().slice(0,10);

	  let month = new Date(); month.setDate(1);

	  function collectCounts(){
	    const tasks = (()=>{ try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_tasks_v1')||'[]'); }catch{ return []; }})();
	    const counts = Object.create(null);
	    const first = +new Date(month.getFullYear(), month.getMonth(), 1);
	    const last  = +new Date(month.getFullYear(), month.getMonth()+1, 0, 23,59,59,999);
	    const isActive = (s)=>{ const x=String(s||'').toLowerCase(); return !x.includes('done') && !x.includes('close') && !x.includes('cancel'); };
	    const pickDue = (obj)=> pickTs(obj, ['due','deadline','due_date','date_due','finish_at','end_at','planned_end','expected_end','date_end','dueAt']);
	    for(const t of tasks){
		  if (!isActive(t.status)) continue;
		  const due = pickDue(t); if (due==null) continue;
		  if (due < first || due > last) continue;
		  const key = new Date(due).toISOString().slice(0,10);
		  counts[key] = (counts[key]||0) + 1;
		}
	    return counts;
	  }

	  function render(){
		const names=['Пн','Вт','Ср','Чт','Пт','Сб','Вс'];
		$title.textContent = month.toLocaleString('ru-RU',{month:'long', year:'numeric'});

		const firstDay = new Date(month.getFullYear(), month.getMonth(), 1);
		const startOffset = (firstDay.getDay()+6)%7;
		const start = +firstDay - startOffset*DAY;
		const todayIso = iso(Date.now());
		const counts = collectCounts();

		$grid.innerHTML = '';
		for(const n of names){ const el=document.createElement('div'); el.className='dow'; el.textContent=n; $grid.appendChild(el); }

		for(let i=0;i<42;i++){
		  const dts = start + i*DAY;
		  const d = new Date(dts);
		  const cell = document.createElement('div');
		  const inMonth = d.getMonth()===month.getMonth();
		  const keyIso = iso(dts);
		  const count = counts[keyIso]||0;

		  cell.className = 'day' + (inMonth?'':' muted') + (keyIso===todayIso?' today':'') + (count>0 ? ' has-data' : '');
		  const num = document.createElement('div'); num.className='num'; num.textContent = String(d.getDate());
		  cell.appendChild(num);
		  if (count>0){ const b=document.createElement('div'); b.className='count'; b.textContent=String(count); cell.appendChild(b); }
		  $grid.appendChild(cell);
		}
	  }

	  $prev?.addEventListener('click', ()=>{ month.setMonth(month.getMonth()-1); render(); });
	  $next?.addEventListener('click', ()=>{ month.setMonth(month.getMonth()+1); render(); });
	  window.addEventListener('storage', (e)=>{ if (e.key==='munart_tasks_v1') render(); });
	  render();
	})();

    function refresh(){ renderCounters(readDashboardCounters()); drawChart(); }

    /* ---- kpi clicks -> navigate ---- */
    document.querySelectorAll('.kpi[data-go]').forEach(k=> {
      k.addEventListener('click', ()=> {
        try{ parent.postMessage({type:'NAVIGATE', payload:k.dataset.go}, location.origin); }catch(_){}
      });
    });

    /* ---- messages from shell ---- */
	window.addEventListener('message', (e)=>{
	  if (e.origin !== location.origin) return;
	  const d = e.data;
	  if (!d || d.type !== 'munart:dashboard-data') return;
	  const base = readDashboardCounters();
	  const upd  = normalizeIncomingCounters(d.payload || {});
	  renderCounters({ ...base, ...upd });
	});

    /* ---- storage updates ---- */
	window.addEventListener('storage', (e)=>{
	  if (e.key==='munart_projects_offline_light' || 
		  e.key==='munart_dashboard_portfolio_v1' ||
		  e.key==='munart_tasks_v1') {
		refresh();
	  }
	});

    /* ---- "Вопрос дня" / "Событие дня" ---- */
    (function hydrateQuestionOrEventOfDay(){
      const LS_POSTS = 'munart_events_posts_v1';
      const LS_EOD   = 'munart_event_of_day_id_v1';

      const $card   = $('qaCard');
      const $text   = $('qaText');
      const $answer = $('qaAnswer');
      const $skip   = $('qaSkip');
	  const $actions = $('qaActions');
	  $actions.style.display = 'none';
	  
      const openEod = (post)=>{
        $('eodTitle').textContent = post.title || 'Событие дня';
        $('eodMeta').textContent  = (post.createdAt ? new Date(post.createdAt).toLocaleString() : '');
        $('eodBody').textContent  = post.body || '';
        const tagsWrap = $('eodTags'); tagsWrap.innerHTML = '';
        (post.tags || '').split(',').map(t=>t.trim()).filter(Boolean).forEach(t=>{
          const tag = document.createElement('span'); tag.className='pill'; tag.textContent = '#'+t; tagsWrap.appendChild(tag);
        });
        $('eodModal').classList.add('show');
      };
      const closeEod = ()=> $('eodModal').classList.remove('show');
      $('eodClose').addEventListener('click', closeEod);
      $('eodModal').addEventListener('click', (e)=>{ if(e.target.id==='eodModal') closeEod(); });
      window.addEventListener('keydown', (e)=>{ if(e.key==='Escape') closeEod(); });

	  const setQaState = (mode)=>{
		  $card.classList.remove('qa--eod','qa--ok');
		  $card.classList.add(mode === 'eod' ? 'qa--eod' : 'qa--ok');
	  };
	  setQaState('ok');

	  try {
		  const eodId = localStorage.getItem(LS_EOD);
		  const posts = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(LS_POSTS) || '[]');
		  const post  = eodId ? posts.find(p => String(p.id) === String(eodId)) : null;

		  if (post) {
			setQaState('eod');
			$actions.style.display = '';
			$text.textContent = post.title || 'Событие дня';
			if ($answer) $answer.style.display = 'none';
			$skip.textContent = 'Посмотреть';
			$skip.onclick = () => openEod(post);
			window.addEventListener('storage', (e) => { if (e.key === LS_EOD || e.key === LS_POSTS) location.reload(); });
			return;
		  }
	  } catch(_) {}

	  try {
		  const q = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_daily_question') || 'null');
		  if (q && q.text) {
			setQaState('ok');
			$actions.style.display = '';
			$text.textContent = q.text;
			if ($answer) { $answer.style.display = ''; $answer.disabled = false; }
			$skip.textContent = 'Позже';
			if (q.url) {
			  $answer.addEventListener('click', () => {
				try { parent.postMessage({ type:'NAVIGATE', payload:q.url }, location.origin); } catch(_){}
				if (q.url.startsWith('#') || q.url.startsWith('/')) location.href = q.url;
			  });
			}
			$skip.addEventListener('click', () => { $card.style.opacity = .55; });
			window.addEventListener('storage', (e) => { if (e.key === 'munart_daily_question') location.reload(); });
		  } else {
			setQaState('ok');
			$actions.style.display = 'none';
		  }
	  } catch(_) {} 
	})();

    /* ---- Блок трёх графиков нижнего ряда ---- */
    (function(){
      'use strict';
      const LS_TASKS = 'munart_tasks_v1';
      const LS_PROJECTS = 'munart_projects_offline_light';
      const LS_ROUNDS = 'munart_rounds_v1';

      /* DEMO для «Объездов», если хранилище пусто */
      (function ensureRoundsDemo(){
        try{
          const cur = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(LS_ROUNDS) || '[]');
          if (Array.isArray(cur) && cur.length) return;
          const statuses = ['planned','in_progress','done','cancel'];
          const now = Date.now(), rnd=(a,b)=>Math.floor(a+Math.random()*(b-a+1));
          const items = Array.from({length:18},(_,i)=>{
            const d = new Date(now - rnd(0,27)*86400000);
            return { id:'demo-'+(i+1), title:'Объезд №'+(i+1), date:d.toISOString().slice(0,10), status:statuses[rnd(0,3)] };
          });
          localStorage.setItem(LS_ROUNDS, JSON.stringify(items));
        }catch(_){}
      })();

      const parseJSON = k=>{ try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(k)||'[]'); }catch{ return []; } };
      const iso = d=> new Date(d).toISOString().slice(0,10);
      const clampDate = (d)=> isNaN(+new Date(d)) ? null : new Date(d);
      const inPeriod = (d, from, to)=> { const x = clampDate(d); if(!x) return true; return (!from || x>=from) && (!to || x<=to); };

      function aggregateTasks(from,to){
        const arr = parseJSON(LS_TASKS);
        const norm = t=>({ date:+(t.created_at||t.createdAt||t.due||Date.now()), status:String(t.status||'todo').replace('in_progress','inprogress') });
        const items = arr.map(norm).filter(t=> inPeriod(t.date,from,to));
        const by = {placed:0, inprogress:0, done:0};
        items.forEach(t=>{ if(t.status==='done') by.done++; else if(t.status==='inprogress' || t.status==='review') by.inprogress++; else by.placed++; });
        return by;
      }
      function aggregateProjects(from,to){
        const arr = parseJSON(LS_PROJECTS);
        const norm = p=>({date:+(p.created_at||p.updated_at||Date.now()), status:p.status||'planned'});
        const items = arr.map(norm).filter(p=> inPeriod(p.date,from,to));
        const by = {created:0, done:0, open:0};
        items.forEach(p=>{ by.created++; if(p.status==='done') by.done++; else by.open++; });
        return by;
      }
      function aggregateRounds(from,to){
        const arr = parseJSON(LS_ROUNDS).filter(x=> inPeriod(x.date,from,to));
        const order = ['planned','in_progress','done','cancel'];
        const by = Object.fromEntries(order.map(k=>[k,0]));
        arr.forEach(r=>{ by[r.status||'planned'] = (by[r.status||'planned']||0)+1; });
        return {order, by};
      }

      function renderBars(svgId, pairs){
	    const svg = document.getElementById(svgId); const W=svg.clientWidth||380, H=280, pad=24;
	    svg.setAttribute('viewBox',`0 0 ${W} ${H}`); while(svg.firstChild) svg.removeChild(svg.firstChild);
        const defs = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','defs');
        defs.innerHTML = `
          <filter id="glow-red" x="-70%" y="-70%" width="240%" height="240%">
            <feGaussianBlur in="SourceAlpha" stdDeviation="3.5" result="blurOuter"/>
            <feFlood flood-color="#ef4444" flood-opacity=".34" result="floodOuter"/>
            <feComposite in="floodOuter" in2="blurOuter" operator="in" result="outer"/>
            <feFlood flood-color="#ef4444" flood-opacity=".22" result="floodInner"/>
            <feComposite in="floodInner" in2="SourceAlpha" operator="in" result="innerColor"/>
            <feGaussianBlur in="innerColor" stdDeviation="7" result="innerSoft"/>
            <feBlend in="SourceGraphic" in2="innerSoft" mode="screen" result="innerGlow"/>
            <feMerge><feMergeNode in="outer"/><feMergeNode in="innerGlow"/></feMerge>
          </filter>
          <filter id="glow-amber" x="-70%" y="-70%" width="240%" height="240%">
            <feGaussianBlur in="SourceAlpha" stdDeviation="3.5" result="blurOuter"/>
            <feFlood flood-color="#f59e0b" flood-opacity=".34" result="floodOuter"/>
            <feComposite in="floodOuter" in2="blurOuter" operator="in" result="outer"/>
            <feFlood flood-color="#f59e0b" flood-opacity=".22" result="floodInner"/>
            <feComposite in="floodInner" in2="SourceAlpha" operator="in" result="innerColor"/>
            <feGaussianBlur in="innerColor" stdDeviation="7" result="innerSoft"/>
            <feBlend in="SourceGraphic" in2="innerSoft" mode="screen" result="innerGlow"/>
            <feMerge><feMergeNode in="outer"/><feMergeNode in="innerGlow"/></feMerge>
          </filter>
          <filter id="glow-green" x="-70%" y="-70%" width="240%" height="240%">
            <feGaussianBlur in="SourceAlpha" stdDeviation="3.5" result="blurOuter"/>
            <feFlood flood-color="#22c55e" flood-opacity=".34" result="floodOuter"/>
            <feComposite in="floodOuter" in2="blurOuter" operator="in" result="outer"/>
            <feFlood flood-color="#22c55e" flood-opacity=".22" result="floodInner"/>
            <feComposite in="floodInner" in2="SourceAlpha" operator="in" result="innerColor"/>
            <feGaussianBlur in="innerColor" stdDeviation="7" result="innerSoft"/>
            <feBlend in="SourceGraphic" in2="innerSoft" mode="screen" result="innerGlow"/>
            <feMerge><feMergeNode in="outer"/><feMergeNode in="innerGlow"/></feMerge>
          </filter>
          <filter id="inner-soft" x="-30%" y="-30%" width="160%" height="160%">
            <feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="10"/>
          </filter>`;
        svg.appendChild(defs);

	    const max = Math.max(1, ...pairs.map(p=>p[1]||0));
	    const bw = (W-2*pad)/pairs.length*0.7;
	    const cls = ['bar-red','bar-amber','bar-green'];

	    const ax = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','line');
	    ax.setAttribute('x1',pad); ax.setAttribute('y1',H-pad);
	    ax.setAttribute('x2',W-pad); ax.setAttribute('y2',H-pad);
	    ax.setAttribute('stroke','currentColor'); ax.setAttribute('opacity','.08');
	    svg.appendChild(ax);

	    pairs.forEach((p,i)=>{
		  const x = pad+i*(W-2*pad)/pairs.length + ((W-2*pad)/pairs.length-bw)/2;
		  const h = (H-2*pad)*(p[1]||0)/max;
		  const y = H-pad-h;
		  const g = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','g');
		  g.setAttribute('filter', ['url(#glow-red)','url(#glow-amber)','url(#glow-green)'][i%3]);
		  const r = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','rect');
		  r.setAttribute('x',x); r.setAttribute('y',y); r.setAttribute('width',bw); r.setAttribute('height',h);
		  r.setAttribute('rx',6); r.setAttribute('class', cls[i%cls.length]); g.appendChild(r);
		  const clipId = svgId + '-clip-' + i;
		  const cp = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','clipPath'); cp.setAttribute('id', clipId);
		  const rc = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','rect');
		  rc.setAttribute('x',x); rc.setAttribute('y',y); rc.setAttribute('width',bw); rc.setAttribute('height',h);
		  rc.setAttribute('rx',6); cp.appendChild(rc); defs.appendChild(cp);
		  const o = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','rect');
		  o.setAttribute('x',x); o.setAttribute('y',y); o.setAttribute('width',bw); o.setAttribute('height',h);
		  o.setAttribute('rx',6); o.setAttribute('clip-path', 'url(#'+clipId+')');
		  o.setAttribute('fill', ['#ef4444','#f59e0b','#22c55e'][i%3]); o.setAttribute('opacity', '.22');
		  o.setAttribute('filter','url(#inner-soft)'); g.appendChild(o);
		  svg.appendChild(g);

		  const t = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','text');
		  t.setAttribute('x',x+bw/2); t.setAttribute('y',H-pad+12); t.setAttribute('text-anchor','middle'); t.setAttribute('font-size','12');
		  t.setAttribute('fill','currentColor'); t.setAttribute('opacity','.75'); t.textContent = p[0]; svg.appendChild(t);
	    });
      }

      function renderDonut(svgId, entries){
        const svg = document.getElementById(svgId); const W=svg.clientWidth||380, H=280, cx=W/2, cy=H/2, r=60;
        svg.setAttribute('viewBox',`0 0 ${W} ${H}`); while(svg.firstChild) svg.removeChild(svg.firstChild);
        const sum = entries.reduce((s,[,v])=>s+(v||0),0)||1; let a0=-Math.PI/2;
        const colors=['#22c55e','#60a5fa','#f59e0b','#f87171','#a78bfa','#34d399'];
        entries.forEach(([k,v],i)=>{ const a1=a0+2*Math.PI*(v||0)/sum;
          const x0=cx+r*Math.cos(a0), y0=cy+r*Math.sin(a0), x1=cx+r*Math.cos(a1), y1=cy+r*Math.sin(a1);
          const lg=(a1-a0)>Math.PI?1:0; const p=document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','path');
          p.setAttribute('d',`M ${x0} ${y0} A ${r} ${r} 0 ${lg} 1 ${x1} ${y1} L ${cx} ${cy} Z`);
          p.setAttribute('fill',colors[i%colors.length]); p.setAttribute('opacity','0.9'); svg.appendChild(p); a0=a1;
        });
      }
      function legend(elId, entries){
        const el = document.getElementById(elId);
        el.innerHTML = entries.map(([k,v])=>`<span class="badge">${k}: <b>${v||0}</b></span>`).join(' ');
      }

      const $from = $('p_from'), $to = $('p_to'), $info = $('p_info');
      const today = new Date(), from0=new Date(today.getFullYear(), today.getMonth(), 1);
      $from.value = iso(from0); $to.value = iso(today);

      function rerender(){
        const F = clampDate($from.value), T = clampDate($to.value);
        $info.textContent = `с ${$from.value||'—'} по ${$to.value||'—'}`;
        const t = aggregateTasks(F,T);
        renderBars('g_tasks_ts', [['Поставлено',t.placed],['В работе',t.inprogress],['Выполнено',t.done]]);
        legend('g_tasks_legend', [['Поставлено',t.placed],['В работе',t.inprogress],['Выполнено',t.done]]);
        const p = aggregateProjects(F,T);
        renderBars('g_projects_ts', [['Создано',p.created],['Открыто',p.open],['Готово',p.done]]);
        legend('g_projects_legend', [['Создано',p.created],['Открыто',p.open],['Готово',p.done]]);
        const r = aggregateRounds(F,T); const entries = r.order.map(k=> [k, r.by[k]||0]);
        renderDonut('g_rounds_donut', entries); legend('g_rounds_legend', entries);
      }
      $('p_apply').onclick = rerender;
      addEventListener('storage', rerender);
      rerender();
    })();

    refresh(); window.addEventListener('resize', drawChart);
  })();
  </script>

  <!-- Уведомления (к существующему колокольчику) -->
  <script>
(function(){
  const LS_POSTS = 'munart_events_posts_v1';
  const LS_READ  = 'munart_notify_read_v1';

  const byId = (s)=>document.getElementById(s);

  // ищем ваш колокольчик
  const bell = (()=>{
    const sels=['#notifyBell','[data-role="notify-bell"]','[data-notify-bell]','button[aria-label*="ведом"]','button[title*="ведом"]','.notify-bell','.bell','button[id*="bell"]'];
    for (const s of sels){ const el=document.querySelector(s); if(el) return el; }
    return null;
  })();
  if (!bell) return;

  // бейдж
  let badge = bell.querySelector('.notify-badge-host');
  if (!badge){ badge=document.createElement('span'); badge.className='notify-badge-host'; bell.style.position='relative'; bell.appendChild(badge); }

  // панель
  let panel = document.getElementById('notifyPanel');
  if (!panel){
    panel=document.createElement('div'); panel.id='notifyPanel'; panel.className='notify-panel';
    panel.innerHTML = '<div class="hdr"><b>Уведомления</b><div style="display:flex;gap:8px"><button type="button" id="notifyMarkAll" class="btn-ghost">Отметить прочитанными</button><button type="button" id="notifyClose" class="btn-ghost">Закрыть</button></div></div><div id="notifyList" class="list"></div>';
    document.body.appendChild(panel);
  }
  const list   = panel.querySelector('#notifyList');
  const btnAll = panel.querySelector('#notifyMarkAll');
  const btnX   = panel.querySelector('#notifyClose');

  // helpers
  const readSet = new Set(JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(LS_READ)||'[]'));
  const rawSig  = ()=> (localStorage.getItem(LS_POSTS) || '');
  let  lastSig  = rawSig();

  function normalize(posts){
    if (!Array.isArray(posts)) return [];
    return posts.map((p,i)=>{
      const id = String(p.id ?? p.uuid ?? p._id ?? (p.createdAt ?? p.created_at ?? Date.now()+i));
      const ts = Number(p.createdAt)||Number(p.created_at)|| (p.date?Date.parse(p.date):NaN);
      const createdAt = isNaN(ts) ? 0 : ts;
      const tags = Array.isArray(p.tags) ? p.tags : (typeof p.tags==='string' ? p.tags.split(',').map(s=>s.trim()).filter(Boolean) : []);
      return { id, title:(p.title||p.name||'Событие'), body:(p.body||p.text||''), createdAt, author:(p.author||p.user||''), tags };
    });
  }
  function getPosts(){
    try{ return normalize(JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(LS_POSTS)||'[]')); }catch(_){ return []; }
  }

  function render(){
    const posts = getPosts().sort((a,b)=>(b.createdAt||0)-(a.createdAt||0)).slice(0,50);
    list.innerHTML=''; let unread=0;
    for (const p of posts){
      const isUnread = !readSet.has(p.id); if (isUnread) unread++;
      const item = document.createElement('div'); item.className='notify-item'+(isUnread?' unread':'');
      const tg = p.tags.map(t=>`<span class="tag">${t}</span>`).join('');
      item.innerHTML = `<div class="t">${p.title}</div><div class="m">${p.createdAt?new Date(p.createdAt).toLocaleString():''}${p.author?' · '+p.author:''}</div>${tg?'<div class="tags">'+tg+'</div>':''}`;
      item.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
        try{
          byId('eodTitle').textContent = p.title;
          byId('eodMeta').textContent  = p.createdAt? new Date(p.createdAt).toLocaleString() : '';
          byId('eodBody').textContent  = p.body || '';
          const tagsWrap = byId('eodTags'); if (tagsWrap){ tagsWrap.innerHTML=''; p.tags.forEach(x=>{ const s=document.createElement('span'); s.className='pill'; s.textContent='#'+x; tagsWrap.appendChild(s); }); }
          byId('eodModal')?.classList.add('show');
        }catch(_){}
        readSet.add(p.id); localStorage.setItem(LS_READ, JSON.stringify([...readSet])); render();
      });
      list.appendChild(item);
    }
    if (unread>0){ badge.textContent = unread>99?'99+':String(unread); badge.style.display=''; } else { badge.style.display='none'; }
  }

  function anchor(){ const r=bell.getBoundingClientRect(); panel.style.right=`${Math.max(14, innerWidth - r.right)}px`; panel.style.top=`${Math.max(60, r.bottom+8)}px`; }
  function toggle(){ const open=!panel.classList.contains('open'); if(open){ anchor(); panel.classList.add('open'); } else panel.classList.remove('open'); }

  bell.addEventListener('click', toggle);
  btnX.addEventListener('click', ()=> panel.classList.remove('open'));
  btnAll.addEventListener('click', ()=>{ getPosts().forEach(p=> readSet.add(p.id)); localStorage.setItem(LS_READ, JSON.stringify([...readSet])); render(); });
  addEventListener('resize', ()=>{ if(panel.classList.contains('open')) anchor(); });

  // cross-tab
  addEventListener('storage', (e)=>{ if (e.key===LS_POSTS){ lastSig = rawSig(); render(); } });
  // same-tab (возврат на вкладку/страницу)
  addEventListener('visibilitychange', ()=>{ if (document.visibilityState==='visible'){ const s=rawSig(); if (s!==lastSig){ lastSig=s; render(); } }});
  addEventListener('focus', ()=>{ const s=rawSig(); if (s!==lastSig){ lastSig=s; render(); }});
  // лёгкий опрос, пока вкладка активна (на случай SPA-сохранений)
  setInterval(()=>{ if (document.visibilityState!=='visible') return; const s=rawSig(); if (s!==lastSig){ lastSig=s; render(); }}, 1500);

  render();
})();
  </script>


  <script>
    (function(){
      var splash = document.getElementById('tasksSplash');
      if (!splash) return;
      function hideSplash(){
        splash.classList.add('splash-hidden');
        setTimeout(function(){
          if (splash && splash.parentNode){
            splash.parentNode.removeChild(splash);
          }
        }, 450);
      }
      var delay = 2500;
      if (document.readyState === 'complete' || document.readyState === 'interactive'){
        setTimeout(hideSplash, delay);
      } else {
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function(){
          setTimeout(hideSplash, delay);
        });
      }
    })();
  </script>

</body>
</html>

	.chart{

	  position:absolute;
	  left:8px;              /* вместо left:50% + transform */
	  right:8px;             /* даём правую границу, чтобы не вылазило */
