        <div class="mp-field">
          <label>Атрибуты объекта</label>
          <div class="mp-multiselect" id="mp_attr_toggle">Нет атрибутов</div>
          <div class="mp-multiselect-body" id="mp_attr_body">
            <label class="mp-check"><input type="checkbox" id="mp_attr_okc"> Объект является ОКС под контролем Минстроя РФ</label>
            <label class="mp-check"><input type="checkbox" id="mp_attr_critical"> Объект является особо важным</label>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mp-field"><label>Финансовые инструменты</label><select id="mp_fin_tools" class="mp-input"></select></div>

        <div class="mp-field"><label>Бюджет (план / сумма контракта), ₽</label><input id="mp_budget_plan" type="number" min="0" step="1" class="mp-input" placeholder="0"></div>
        <div class="mp-field"><label>Бюджет (факт / оплачено), ₽</label><input id="mp_budget_spent" type="number" min="0" step="1" class="mp-input" value="0"></div>

        <div class="mp-field"><label>Прогресс, %</label><input id="mp_progress" type="number" min="0" max="100" class="mp-input" value="0"></div>
        <div class="mp-field"><label>Риск, %</label><input id="mp_risk" type="number" min="0" max="100" class="mp-input" value="10"></div>

        <div class="mp-field" style="grid-column:1/-1;"><label>Теги (через запятую)</label><input id="mp_tags" class="mp-input" placeholder="ремонт, связь, подрядчики"></div>
        <div class="mp-field" style="grid-column:1/-1;"><label>Описание (комментарии / отставание)</label><textarea id="mp_desc" class="mp-input" style="min-height:80px"></textarea></div>
        <div class="mp-field" style="grid-column:1/-1;"><label>Выполнение, %</label><textarea id="mp_exec" class="mp-input" style="min-height:80px"></textarea></div>

        <div class="mp-row">
          <div class="mp-field"><label>+ точка прогресса</label><input id="mp_addProg" type="number" min="0" max="100" class="mp-input" placeholder="45"></div>
          <div class="mp-field"><label>+ точка затрат, ₽</label><input id="mp_addSpend" type="number" min="0" step="1" class="mp-input" placeholder="150000"></div>
          <div class="mp-field"><label>+ выполнено задач</label><input id="mp_addTasks" type="number" min="0" step="1" class="mp-input" placeholder="3"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mp-toolbar">
        <button class="mp-btn" id="mpCancel">Отмена</button>
        <button class="mp-btn primary" id="mpSave">Сохранить</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

<script>
(()=>{'use strict';
  const $ = (id)=> document.getElementById(id);
  const today = ()=> new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10);
  const nowISO = ()=> new Date().toISOString();

  const STORE='munart_projects_offline_light';
  const VIEW_KEY='munart_projects_view_mode';
  const THREE_KEY='munart_projects_3d'; // отключено в этой версии
  const VIEW_MODES=[
    {id:'std',title:'Стандарт'},
    {id:'bar',title:'Бары'},
    {id:'line',title:'Линии'},
    {id:'area',title:'Площади'},
    {id:'ring',title:'Кольца'}
  ];

  // --- Global helpers for table metrics (available to any renderer) ---
  ;(function(){
    if (typeof window.__descendants !== 'function') {
      window.__descendants = function(all, rootId){
        const res=[]; const stack=all.filter(x=>x.parent_id===rootId);
        while(stack.length){ const n=stack.pop(); res.push(n); stack.push(...all.filter(x=>x.parent_id===n.id)); }
        return res;
      };
    }
    if (typeof window.calcProgressRisk !== 'function') {
      window.calcProgressRisk = function(p, all){
        const desc = window.__descendants(all, p.id);
        const doneCount = desc.filter(x=>x.status==='done').length;
        const plan = +(p.budget_plan||0);
        const fact = +(p.budget_spent||0);
        const cashPct = plan>0 ? (fact/plan*100) : 0;
        const progress0 = desc.length ? (doneCount/Math.max(desc.length,1)*100) : cashPct;
        const progress = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, isFinite(progress0)?progress0:0));
        const undone = (desc.length||0) - doneCount;
        const risk0 = desc.length ? (undone/Math.max(desc.length,1)*100) : (plan>0 ? Math.max(0,(1 - (fact/plan))*100) : 0);
        const risk = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, isFinite(risk0)?risk0:0));
        return {progress, risk};
      };
    }
  })();
  // --- /Global helpers ---
  const load = ()=>{ try { return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(STORE)) || []; } catch(_) { return []; } };
  const persist = (arr)=>{ localStorage.setItem(STORE, JSON.stringify(arr)); render(); sendSummary(); };
  const uid = ()=> 'p'+Math.random().toString(36).slice(2,8);
  const getMode = ()=> VIEW_MODES.find(x=>x.id===localStorage.getItem(VIEW_KEY))?.id || 'std';
  const setMode = (id)=>{ localStorage.setItem(VIEW_KEY,id); $('viewLabel').textContent='Режим: '+(VIEW_MODES.find(x=>x.id===id)?.title||'Стандарт'); render(); };
  const is3D = ()=> false; const toggle3D = ()=>{};

  ;

  // Toolbar wiring
  $('vPrev').onclick = ()=>{ const i=VIEW_MODES.findIndex(x=>x.id===getMode()); setMode(VIEW_MODES[(i-1+VIEW_MODES.length)%VIEW_MODES.length].id); };
  $('vNext').onclick = ()=>{ const i=VIEW_MODES.findIndex(x=>x.id===getMode()); setMode(VIEW_MODES[(i+1)%VIEW_MODES.length].id); };
  $('viewLabel').textContent = 'Режим: '+(VIEW_MODES.find(x=>x.id===getMode())?.title||'Стандарт');
  const btn3d = $('btn3d'); if (btn3d){ btn3d.classList.toggle('active', is3D()); btn3d.onclick = toggle3D; }


  const DICT_KEYS = {
    cats: 'munart_dict_categories',
    owners: 'munart_dict_owners',
    resp: 'munart_dict_responsibles',
    vendors: 'munart_dict_contractors',
    fin: 'munart_dict_fin_tools'
  };
  function loadDict(key){
    try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(key) || '[]'); }catch(e){ return []; }
  }
  function saveDict(key, val){
    try{ localStorage.setItem(key, JSON.stringify(val)); }catch(e){}
  }
  function openDict(kind){
    const modal = document.getElementById('dictModal'); if (!modal) return;
    const title = document.getElementById('dictTitle');
    const labelMain = document.getElementById('dictLabelMain');
    const typeBlock = document.getElementById('dictTypeBlock');
    const listEl = document.getElementById('dictList');
    const nameEl = document.getElementById('dict_name');
    const deptEl = document.getElementById('dict_dept');
    const typeEl = document.getElementById('dict_type');
    const fileEl = document.getElementById('dict_file');
    const commentEl = document.getElementById('dict_comment');
    const key = DICT_KEYS[kind];
    const data = loadDict(key);

    if (kind==='cats'){ title.textContent='Категории'; labelMain.textContent='Наименование'; typeBlock.style.display=''; }
    else if (kind==='owners'){ title.textContent='Руководители'; labelMain.textContent='ФИО'; typeBlock.style.display='none'; }
    else if (kind==='vendors'){ title.textContent='Подрядчики'; labelMain.textContent='Наименование'; typeBlock.style.display='none'; }
    else if (kind==='fin'){ title.textContent='Финансовые инструменты'; labelMain.textContent='Наименование'; typeBlock.style.display='none'; }
    else { title.textContent='Ответственные'; labelMain.textContent='ФИО'; typeBlock.style.display='none'; }

    
listEl.innerHTML = data.length ? data.map((it,idx)=>`
  <li class="dict-item">
    <div class="iavatar">${(it.name||'?').trim().split(/\s+/).slice(0,2).map(s=>s[0]).join('').toUpperCase()}</div>
    <div class="info">
      <div class="row1">
        <b>${escapeHtml(it.name||'')}</b>
        ${ it.kind ? `<span class="pill kind">${escapeHtml(it.kind)}</span>` : '' }
      </div>
      <div class="row2">
        ${ it.dept ? `<span class="pill dept">${escapeHtml(it.dept)}</span>` : '' }
        ${ it.doc ? `<span class="pill doc">📄 ${escapeHtml(it.doc)}</span>` : '' }
      </div>
      ${ it.comment ? `<div class="comment">${escapeHtml(it.comment)}</div>` : '' }
    </div>
    <button type="button" class="del" title="Удалить" data-del="${idx}">×</button>
  </li>
`).join('') : '<li class="dict-empty">пока нет записей</li>';

    listEl.querySelectorAll('[data-del]').forEach(btn=>{
      btn.onclick = ()=>{ const i=+btn.dataset.del; data.splice(i,1); saveDict(key,data); openDict(kind); };
    });

    nameEl.value=''; deptEl.value=''; if (typeEl) typeEl.value='временная'; fileEl.value=''; commentEl.value='';

    modal.classList.add('open'); modal.setAttribute('aria-hidden','false');

    document.getElementById('dictSave').onclick = ()=>{
      const nm = nameEl.value.trim(); if (!nm){ nameEl.focus(); return; }
      const entry = {
        id:'d_'+Date.now(),
        name:nm,
        dept:deptEl.value.trim(),
        kind:(kind==='cats') ? (typeEl.value||'постоянная') : '',
        doc: fileEl.files && fileEl.files[0] ? fileEl.files[0].name : '',
        comment: commentEl.value.trim()
      };
      data.push(entry); saveDict(key,data); openDict(kind);
    };
    document.getElementById('dictClose').onclick = ()=>{ modal.classList.remove('open'); modal.setAttribute('aria-hidden','true'); };
  }

  function populateLookups(){
  const items = load();
  const catsProj = items.map(x=>x.category).filter(Boolean);
  const ownersProj = items.map(x=>x.owner).filter(Boolean);
  const respProj = items.map(x=>x.responsible).filter(Boolean);
  const vendorsProj = items.map(x=>x.vendor).filter(Boolean);
  const finProj = items.map(x=>x.fin_tools).filter(Boolean);

  const catsAll = Array.from(new Set([...catsProj, ...loadDict(DICT_KEYS.cats).map(x=>x.name)])).filter(Boolean).sort((a,b)=>a.localeCompare(b,'ru'));
  const ownersAll = Array.from(new Set([...ownersProj, ...loadDict(DICT_KEYS.owners).map(x=>x.name)])).filter(Boolean).sort((a,b)=>a.localeCompare(b,'ru'));
  const respAll = Array.from(new Set([...respProj, ...loadDict(DICT_KEYS.resp).map(x=>x.name)])).filter(Boolean).sort((a,b)=>a.localeCompare(b,'ru'));
  const vendorsAll = Array.from(new Set([...vendorsProj, ...loadDict(DICT_KEYS.vendors).map(x=>x.name)])).filter(Boolean).sort((a,b)=>a.localeCompare(b,'ru'));
  const finAll = Array.from(new Set([...finProj, ...loadDict(DICT_KEYS.fin).map(x=>x.name)])).filter(Boolean).sort((a,b)=>a.localeCompare(b,'ru'));

  const selCat = document.getElementById('mp_category');
  const selOwner = document.getElementById('mp_owner');
  const selResp = document.getElementById('mp_responsible');
  const selVendor = document.getElementById('mp_vendor');
  const selFin = document.getElementById('mp_fin_tools');

  if (selCat) selCat.innerHTML = '<option value=""></option>' + catsAll.map(v=>`<option value="${v}">${v}</option>`).join('');
  if (selOwner) selOwner.innerHTML = '<option value=""></option>' + ownersAll.map(v=>`<option value="${v}">${v}</option>`).join('');
  if (selResp) selResp.innerHTML = '<option value=""></option>' + respAll.map(v=>`<option value="${v}">${v}</option>`).join('');
  if (selVendor) selVendor.innerHTML = '<option value=""></option>' + vendorsAll.map(v=>`<option value="${v}">${v}</option>`).join('');
  if (selFin) selFin.innerHTML = '<option value=""></option>' + finAll.map(v=>`<option value="${v}">${v}</option>`).join('');
}


  function updateAttrLabel(){
    const toggle = document.getElementById('mp_attr_toggle');
    if (!toggle) return;
    const okc = document.getElementById('mp_attr_okc');
    const crit = document.getElementById('mp_attr_critical');
    const parts = [];
    if (okc && okc.checked) parts.push('ОКС Минстроя РФ');
    if (crit && crit.checked) parts.push('Особо важный объект');
    toggle.textContent = parts.length ? parts.join(' • ') : 'Нет атрибутов';
  }

  const datesToggle = document.getElementById('mp_dates_toggle');
  if (datesToggle){
    const body = document.getElementById('mp_dates_body');
    datesToggle.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
      if (!body) return;
      const opened = body.classList.toggle('open');
      datesToggle.textContent = opened ? 'Скрыть даты ▲' : 'Показать даты ▾';
    });
  }

  const attrToggle = document.getElementById('mp_attr_toggle');
  if (attrToggle){
    const body = document.getElementById('mp_attr_body');
    attrToggle.addEventListener('click', (e)=>{
      e.stopPropagation();
      if (!body) return;
      body.classList.toggle('open');
    });
    document.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
      if (body) body.classList.remove('open');
    });
    ['mp_attr_okc','mp_attr_critical'].forEach(id=>{
      const el = document.getElementById(id);
      if (el) el.addEventListener('change', updateAttrLabel);
    });
  }
  // Modal
  const modal=$('mpModal');
  function openModal(item){
    $('mpTitle').textContent = item ? 'Редактирование проекта' : 'Новый проект';
    $('mp_edit_id').value = item?.id || '';
    $('mp_name').value = item?.name || '';
    $('mp_code').value = item?.code || '';
    $('mp_status').value = item?.status || 'planned';
    $('mp_priority').value = item?.priority ?? 2;
    populateLookups();
    $('mp_owner').value = item?.owner || '';
    $('mp_category').value = item?.category || '';
    const cEl = document.getElementById('mp_classification'); if (cEl) cEl.value = item?.classification || '';
    const rEl = document.getElementById('mp_responsible'); if (rEl) rEl.value = item?.responsible || '';
    const vEl = document.getElementById('mp_vendor'); if (vEl) vEl.value = item?.vendor || '';

    // даты: план / прогноз / факт (совместимость со старыми полями start/due)
    const startPlan = item?.start_plan || item?.start || '';
    const endPlan = item?.end_plan || item?.due || '';
    const startForecast = item?.start_forecast || '';
    const endForecast = item?.end_forecast || '';
    const startFact = item?.start_fact || '';
    const endFact = item?.end_fact || '';
    const dBody = $('mp_dates_body');
    if (dBody){
      $('mp_start_plan').value = startPlan;
      $('mp_end_plan').value = endPlan;
      $('mp_start_forecast').value = startForecast;
      $('mp_end_forecast').value = endForecast;
      $('mp_start_fact').value = startFact;
      $('mp_end_fact').value = endFact;
    }

    // местоположение и атрибуты
    const locEl = $('mp_location'); if (locEl) locEl.value = item?.location || '';
    const okcEl = $('mp_attr_okc'); if (okcEl) okcEl.checked = !!item?.attr_okc;
    const critEl = $('mp_attr_critical'); if (critEl) critEl.checked = !!item?.attr_critical;

    // фин. инструменты
    const finEl = $('mp_fin_tools');
    if (finEl){
      finEl.value = item?.fin_tools || '';
    }
    updateAttrLabel();

    $('mp_budget_plan').value = item?.budget_plan ?? 0;
    $('mp_budget_spent').value = item?.budget_spent ?? 0;
    $('mp_progress').value = item?.progress ?? 0;
    $('mp_risk').value = item?.risk ?? 0;
    $('mp_tags').value = (item?.tags||[]).join(', ');
    $('mp_desc').value = item?.description || '';
    const elExec = document.getElementById('mp_exec'); if (elExec) elExec.value = item?.execution || '';
    $('mp_pet_type').value = item?.pet_type || '';
    populateParents(item?.parent_id||'');
    modal.classList.add('open'); modal.setAttribute('aria-hidden','false'); setTimeout(()=> $('mp_name').focus(), 0);
  }
  function closeModal(){ modal.classList.remove('open'); modal.setAttribute('aria-hidden','true'); }
  $('mpCancel').onclick = closeModal;

  function populateParents(selected){
    const sel = $('mp_parent');
    const items = load();
    sel.innerHTML = '<option value="">— нет —</option>' + items.map(p=>`<option value="${p.id}" ${p.id===selected?'selected':''}>${escapeHtml(p.name)} (${p.code||''})</option>`).join('');
  }

  $('mpSave').onclick = ()=>{
    const idExisting = $('mp_edit_id').value.trim();

    const startPlan = $('mp_start_plan').value||'';
    const endPlan = $('mp_end_plan').value||'';
    const startForecast = $('mp_start_forecast').value||'';
    const endForecast = $('mp_end_forecast').value||'';
    const startFact = $('mp_start_fact').value||'';
    const endFact = $('mp_end_fact').value||'';

    const loc = $('mp_location') ? $('mp_location').value.trim() : '';
    const attrOkc = $('mp_attr_okc') ? $('mp_attr_okc').checked : false;
    const attrCritical = $('mp_attr_critical') ? $('mp_attr_critical').checked : false;
    const finTools = $('mp_fin_tools') ? $('mp_fin_tools').value.trim() : '';

    const t = {
      id: idExisting || uid(),
      name: $('mp_name').value.trim()||'Без названия',
      code: $('mp_code').value.trim()||(('PRJ-'+Math.floor(Math.random()*9999)).toUpperCase()),
      description: $('mp_desc').value.trim(),
      execution: (document.getElementById('mp_exec')?.value || '').trim(),
      owner: $('mp_owner').value.trim(),
      responsible: (document.getElementById('mp_responsible')?.value || '').trim(),
      vendor: (document.getElementById('mp_vendor')?.value || '').trim(),
      category: $('mp_category').value.trim(),
      classification: (document.getElementById('mp_classification')?.value || '').trim(),
      status: $('mp_status').value,
      pet_type: $('mp_pet_type').value || '',
      parent_id: $('mp_parent').value || '',
      priority: +$('mp_priority').value||2,

      start_plan: startPlan,
      end_plan: endPlan,
      start_forecast: startForecast,
      end_forecast: endForecast,
      start_fact: startFact,
      end_fact: endFact,

      start: startPlan || today(),
      due: endPlan || endForecast || endFact || '',

      location: loc,
      attr_okc: attrOkc,
      attr_critical: attrCritical,
      fin_tools: finTools,

      budget_plan: +$('mp_budget_plan').value||0,
      budget_spent: +$('mp_budget_spent').value||0,
      progress: +$('mp_progress').value||0,
      risk: +$('mp_risk').value||0,
      tags: ($('mp_tags').value||'').split(',').map(s=>s.trim()).filter(Boolean),
      updated_at: nowISO(),
      archived:false
    };

    const addProg = +document.getElementById('mp_addProg').value || null;
    const addSpend = +document.getElementById('mp_addSpend').value || null;
    const addTasks = +document.getElementById('mp_addTasks').value || null;

    const arr = load();
    const prev = arr.find(x=>x.id===t.id);
    const metrics = prev?.metrics || {progress:[], spend:[], tasks_done:[]};
    if (addProg!=null) metrics.progress.push({t:today(), v:addProg});
    if (addSpend!=null) metrics.spend.push({t:today(), v:addSpend});
    if (addTasks!=null) metrics.tasks_done.push({t:today(), v:addTasks});
    t.metrics = metrics;

    let next;
    if (prev){ next = arr.map(x=> x.id===t.id ? {...prev, ...t} : x); }
    else { next = [t, ...arr]; }
    persist(next);
    closeModal();
    location.href = 'project_passport_offline.html?id='+encodeURIComponent(t.id);
  };

  function escapeHtml(s){ return (s??'').toString().replace(/[&<>"]/g, c=>({ '&':'&amp;','<':'&lt;','>':'&gt;','"':'&quot;' }[c])); }

  (()=>{const e=document.getElementById('btnNew'); if(e) e.onclick=()=>openModal();})();
  (()=>{const e=document.getElementById('mpNew'); if(e) e.onclick=()=>openModal();})();
 
  (()=>{ const e=document.getElementById('btnReports');
    if (e) e.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
      location.href = 'reports/projects_report.html';
    });
  })();


  
  (()=>{ const e=document.getElementById('btnInfographics');
    if (e) e.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
      location.href = 'projects_infographics.html';
    });
  })();

// ========== Charts helpers ==========
  function ensureLegend(el, html){
    let lg = el.querySelector('.legend');
    if (!lg){ lg = document.createElement('div'); lg.className='legend'; el.appendChild(lg); }
    lg.innerHTML = html;
  }
  function svgWithGradients(el){
    const w=el.clientWidth||300,h=el.clientHeight||220;
    el.innerHTML = `<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none"></svg>`;
    const svg = el.querySelector('svg');
    if (is3D()){
      const idG = 'g3d_'+Math.random().toString(36).slice(2,7);
      const idG2 = 'g3d2_'+Math.random().toString(36).slice(2,7);
      svg.insertAdjacentHTML('afterbegin', `<defs>
        <linearGradient id="${idG}" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(255,255,255,.45)"/>
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(0,0,0,.10)"/>
        </linearGradient>
        <linearGradient id="${idG2}" x1="0" y1="0" x2="0" y2="1">
          <stop offset="0%" stop-color="rgba(255,255,255,.35)"/>
          <stop offset="100%" stop-color="rgba(0,0,0,.08)"/>
        </linearGradient>
      </defs>`);
      return {svg, grads:[idG,idG2]};
    }
    return {svg, grads:[]};
  }

  function areaChart(el, data, color){
    const w = el.clientWidth || 300, h = el.clientHeight||96, p=8;
    const arr = data.map(x=> +x || 0);
    const max = Math.max(...arr, 1), min = Math.min(...arr, 0);
    const sx = (i)=> p + i*( (w-2*p)/(arr.length-1||1) );
    const sy = (v)=> h - p - ( (v-min) / (max-min || 1) )*(h-2*p);
    let d = `M ${p} ${h-p} `; arr.forEach((v,i)=> d += `L ${sx(i)} ${sy(v)} `); d += `L ${w-p} ${h-p} Z`;
    el.innerHTML = `<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="${d}" fill="rgba(34,197,94,.18)" stroke="${color}" stroke-width="2"/></svg>`;
  }
  function lineChart(el, data, color){
    const w=el.clientWidth||300,h=el.clientHeight||220,p=24;
    const arr = data.map(x=> +x || 0);
    const max = Math.max(...arr,1), min=Math.min(...arr,0);
    const sx = (i)=> p + i*( (w-2*p)/(arr.length-1||1) );
    const sy = (v)=> h - p - ( (v-min)/(max-min||1) )*(h-2*p);
    let d=`M ${sx(0)} ${sy(arr[0]||0)}`; for(let i=1;i<arr.length;i++) d+=` L ${sx(i)} ${sy(arr[i]||0)}`;
    el.innerHTML = `<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="${d}" fill="none" stroke="${color}" stroke-width="2"/></svg>`;
  }
  function lineChartTwo(el, a, b, ca, cb){
    const w=el.clientWidth||300,h=el.clientHeight||220,p=24;
    const A = a.map(x=> +x || 0), B = b.map(x=> +x || 0);
    const all = [...A,...B]; const max = Math.max(...all,1), min=Math.min(...all,0);
    const sx = (i)=> p + i*( (w-2*p)/(A.length-1||1) );
    const sy = (v)=> h - p - ( (v-min)/(max-min||1) )*(h-2*p);
    function path(data){ let d=`M ${sx(0)} ${sy(data[0]||0)}`; for(let i=1;i<data.length;i++) d+=` L ${sx(i)} ${sy(data[i]||0)}`; return d; }
    el.innerHTML = `<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="${path(A)}" fill="none" stroke="${ca}" stroke-width="2"/>
      <path d="${path(B)}" fill="none" stroke="${cb}" stroke-width="2"/>
    </svg>`;
  }
  function barChart(el, data, color){
    const w = el.clientWidth || 300, h = el.clientHeight||220, p=24;
    const arr = data.map(x=> +x || 0);
    const max = Math.max(...arr, 1);
    const bw = (w-2*p)/Math.max(1,arr.length) * 0.6;
    const gap = ((w-2*p)-bw*arr.length)/Math.max(1,arr.length-1);
    const {svg,grads} = svgWithGradients(el);
    arr.forEach((v,i)=>{
      const x = p + i*(bw+gap);
      const bh = (v/max)*(h-2*p);
      const y = h - p - bh;
      const fill = is3D()? `url(#${grads[i%2]})` : color;
      svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<rect x="${x}" y="${y}" width="${bw}" height="${bh}" fill="${fill}" stroke="${is3D()?'rgba(0,0,0,.1)':'none'}"/>`);
    });
  }
  function groupBarsTwo(el, a, b, ca, cb){
    const w=el.clientWidth||300, h=el.clientHeight||220, p=24;
    const A=a.map(x=>+x||0), B=b.map(x=>+x||0);
    const max = Math.max(...A, ...B, 1);
    const n=Math.max(A.length,B.length);
    const groupW = (w-2*p)/Math.max(1,n);
    const bw = groupW*0.36;
    const gapG = groupW*0.14;
    const {svg,grads} = svgWithGradients(el);
    for(let i=0;i<n;i++){
      const x0 = p + i*groupW + gapG;
      const bhA = (A[i]/max)*(h-2*p), yA=h-p-bhA;
      const bhB = (B[i]/max)*(h-2*p), yB=h-p-bhB;
      const fA = is3D()? `url(#${grads[0]})` : ca;
      const fB = is3D()? `url(#${grads[1]})` : cb;
      svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<rect x="${x0}" y="${yA}" width="${bw}" height="${bhA}" fill="${fA}" stroke="${is3D()?'rgba(0,0,0,.1)':'none'}"/>`);
      svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<rect x="${x0+bw+gapG}" y="${yB}" width="${bw}" height="${bhB}" fill="${fB}" stroke="${is3D()?'rgba(0,0,0,.1)':'none'}"/>`);
    }
  }
  function donutChart(el, values, colors, labels){
    const w = el.clientWidth || 300, h = el.clientHeight || 220, r = Math.min(w,h)/2 - 12, cx=w/2, cy=h/2;
    const vals = values.map(x=> +x || 0);
    const total = vals.reduce((s,x)=>s+x,0);
    if (total<=0){
      el.innerHTML = `<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none">
        <circle cx="${cx}" cy="${cy}" r="${r}" fill="none" stroke="#e5e7eb" stroke-width="10"/>
        <text x="${cx}" y="${cy}" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="middle" font-size="12" fill="currentColor">нет данных</text>
      </svg>`;
      if (labels) ensureLegend(el, labels);
      return;
    }
    let start = 0; let html = '';
    vals.forEach((v,i)=>{
      const a = (v/total)*Math.PI*2; const end = start + a;
      const x1 = cx + r*Math.cos(start), y1 = cy + r*Math.sin(start);
      const x2 = cx + r*Math.cos(end),   y2 = cy + r*Math.sin(end);
      const large = a>Math.PI ? 1 : 0;
      html += `<path d="M${cx} ${cy} L ${x1} ${y1} A ${r} ${r} 0 ${large} 1 ${x2} ${y2} Z" fill="${colors[i%colors.length]}" opacity="0.95"/>`;
      start = end;
    });
    const inner = getComputedStyle(document.body).getPropertyValue('--panel').trim() || '#ffffff';
    const brd = getComputedStyle(document.body).getPropertyValue('--brd').trim() || '#e5e7eb';
    el.innerHTML = `<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none">${html}
      <circle cx="${cx}" cy="${cy}" r="${r*0.58}" fill="${inner}" stroke="${brd}"/>
    </svg>`;
    if (labels) ensureLegend(el, labels);
  }
  function donutSingle(el, value, total, color){
    const v = Math.max(0, +value||0), T=Math.max(1, +total||1);
    donutChart(el, [v, Math.max(0,T-v)], [color, '#d1d5db']);
  }
  function deltaChart(el, plan, fact, mode='bar'){
    const P = plan.map(x=>+x||0), F=fact.map(x=>+x||0);
    const diff = F.map((v,i)=> v - (P[i]||0));
    if (mode==='line'){ lineChart(el, diff, '#22c55e'); return; }
    barChart(el, diff.map(x=>Math.abs(x)), '#3b82f6');
    ensureLegend(el, `<span style="display:inline-flex;gap:6px;align-items:center"><i style="width:10px;height:10px;background:#22c55e;display:inline-block;border-radius:2px"></i>Плюс/Минус (модуль)</span>`);
  }

  // Analytics helpers
  function monthsBack(n){
    const now = new Date(); const arr=[];
    for(let i=n-1;i>=0;i--) arr.push(new Date(now.getFullYear(), now.getMonth()-i,1));
    return arr;
  }
  const months12 = ()=> monthsBack(12);
  function ym(d){ return d.getFullYear()+'-'+String(d.getMonth()+1).padStart(2,'0'); }
  function yearRange(n){ const y=new Date().getFullYear(); const arr=[]; for(let i=n-1;i>=0;i--) arr.push(y-i); return arr; }

  function buildSeries(items){
    const months = months12(); const keys = months.map(ym);
    const mk = ()=> Object.fromEntries(keys.map(k=>[k,0]));
    const doneBy = mk(), pSum=mk(), pCnt=mk(), plan=mk(), fact=mk(), total=mk(), active=mk(), hold=mk();

    items.forEach(p=>{
      const upd = p.updated_at ? ym(new Date(p.updated_at)) : (p.start ? ym(new Date(p.start)) : keys[0]);
      if (total[upd]!=null) total[upd]+=1;
      if (p.status==='in_progress' && active[upd]!=null) active[upd]+=1;
      if (p.status==='on_hold' && hold[upd]!=null) hold[upd]+=1;

      if (p.status==='done' && p.due){ const m=ym(new Date(p.due)); if(doneBy[m]!=null) doneBy[m]+=1; }

      const prog = +p.progress || 0; if (pCnt[upd]!=null){ pCnt[upd]+=1; pSum[upd]+=prog; }

      const bp=+p.budget_plan||0;
      if (bp>0 && p.start && p.due){
        const ds=new Date(p.start), de=new Date(p.due);
        const n=Math.max(1,(de.getFullYear()-ds.getFullYear())*12+(de.getMonth()-ds.getMonth())+1);
        const per=Math.round(bp/n);
        for(let i=0;i<n;i++){
          const m=ym(new Date(ds.getFullYear(),ds.getMonth()+i,1)); if(plan[m]!=null) plan[m]+=per;
        }
      }
      if (+p.budget_spent>0 && p.start){
        const m=ym(new Date(p.start)); if(fact[m]!=null) fact[m]+= (+p.budget_spent||0);
      }
    });

    const keysArr = months.map(ym);
    const doneArr = keysArr.map(k=>doneBy[k]||0);
    for(let i=1;i<doneArr.length;i++) doneArr[i]+=doneArr[i-1];
    const avgProg = keysArr.map(k=> (pCnt[k]? Math.round((pSum[k]/pCnt[k])*10)/10 : 0) );

    return {
      keys: keysArr, months,
      series: {
        total: keysArr.map(k=> total[k]||0),
        active: keysArr.map(k=> active[k]||0),
        hold: keysArr.map(k=> hold[k]||0),
        done_cum: doneArr,
        progress_avg: avgProg,
        budget_plan_12m: keysArr.map(k=> plan[k]||0),
        budget_fact_12m: keysArr.map(k=> fact[k]||0)
      }
    };
  }

  // Indicators
  function monthLabel(d){ const mm=String(d.getMonth()+1).padStart(2,'0'); const yy=String(d.getFullYear()).slice(-2); return mm+'.'+yy; }
  function buildIndicators(items, metric='created', period='M'){
    let labels=[], data=[];
    if (period==='M'){
      const months = months12(); const map = new Map(months.map(d=>[ym(d),0]));
      if (metric==='created' || metric==='total'){
        items.forEach(p=>{ if(p.start){ const k=ym(new Date(p.start)); if(map.has(k)) map.set(k, map.get(k)+1); } });
      } else if (metric==='done'){
        items.forEach(p=>{ if(p.due){ const k=ym(new Date(p.due)); if(map.has(k)) map.set(k, map.get(k)+1); } });
      } else {
        items.forEach(p=>{ if(p.updated_at){ const k=ym(new Date(p.updated_at)); if(map.has(k) && p.status===metric) map.set(k, map.get(k)+1); } });
      }
      labels = months.map(monthLabel);
      data = months.map(d=> map.get(ym(d)) || 0);
    } else {
      const years = yearRange(5); const map = new Map(years.map(y=>[y,0]));
      if (metric==='created' || metric==='total'){
        items.forEach(p=>{ if(p.start){ const y=new Date(p.start).getFullYear(); if(map.has(y)) map.set(y, map.get(y)+1); } });
      } else if (metric==='done'){
        items.forEach(p=>{ if(p.due){ const y=new Date(p.due).getFullYear(); if(map.has(y)) map.set(y, map.get(y)+1); } });
      } else {
        items.forEach(p=>{ if(p.updated_at){ const y=new Date(p.updated_at).getFullYear(); if(map.has(y) && p.status===metric) map.set(y, map.get(y)+1); } });
      }
      labels = years.map(String);
      data = years.map(y=> map.get(y) || 0);
    }
    return {labels, data};
  }
  function renderIndicators(items){
    const metric = $('indMetric').value;
    const period = $('indPeriod').value;
    const order = $('indOrder').value;
    const ds = buildIndicators(items, metric, period);
    let idx = ds.labels.map((_,i)=>i);
    if (order==='asc' || order==='desc'){
      idx.sort((a,b)=> ds.data[a]-ds.data[b]);
      if (order==='desc') idx.reverse();
    }
    const labelsOrd = idx.map(i=> ds.labels[i]);
    const dataOrd = idx.map(i=> ds.data[i]);
    const host = $('chartIndicators');
    host.style.height = '220px';
    const mode = getMode();

    // Helpers: compute Progress & Risk same as in Паспорт проекта
    function __descendants(all, rootId){
      const res=[]; const stack=all.filter(x=>x.parent_id===rootId);
      while(stack.length){ const n=stack.pop(); res.push(n); stack.push(...all.filter(x=>x.parent_id===n.id)); }
      return res;
    }
    function calcProgressRisk(p, all){
      const desc = __descendants(all, p.id);
      const doneCount = desc.filter(x=>x.status==='done').length;
      const plan = +(p.budget_plan||0);
      const fact = +(p.budget_spent||0);
      const cashPct = plan>0 ? (fact/plan*100) : 0;
      const progress0 = desc.length ? (doneCount/Math.max(desc.length,1)*100) : cashPct;
      const progress = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, isFinite(progress0)?progress0:0));
      const undone = (desc.length||0) - doneCount;
      const risk0 = desc.length ? (undone/Math.max(desc.length,1)*100) : (plan>0 ? Math.max(0,(1 - (fact/plan))*100) : 0);
      const risk = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, isFinite(risk0)?risk0:0));
      return {progress, risk};
    }
        if (mode==='line') lineChart(host, dataOrd, '#10b981');
    else barChart(host, dataOrd, '#10b981');
    ensureLegend(host, labelsOrd.map(l=> `<span style="margin:0 6px;opacity:.9">${l}</span>`).join(''));
    const metricTitle = ({created:'Создано',done:'Завершено',total:'Всего',in_progress:'В работе',on_hold:'На паузе'})[metric]||metric;
    const periodTitle = (period==='M'?'Месяцы':'Годы');
    $('indLabel').textContent = `${metricTitle} • ${periodTitle}`;
  }

  function sendSummary(){
    const items = load();
    const payload = { total: items.length, in_progress: items.filter(i=>i.status==='in_progress').length, on_hold: items.filter(i=>i.status==='on_hold').length, done: items.filter(i=>i.status==='done').length };
    const b = buildSeries(items).series;
    localStorage.setItem('munart_dashboard_portfolio_v1', JSON.stringify({updatedAt: new Date().toISOString(), series: b, counters: payload}));
  }

  function render(){
    const items = load();
    const q = ($('search').value||'').toLowerCase().trim();
    const f = $('filter').value;
    const rows = items.filter(p=>{
      const okF = f==='all' ? true : p.status===f;
      const okQ = !q || [p.name,p.code,p.owner,p.category,(p.tags||[]).join(' '),(p.pet_type||'' )].join(' ').toLowerCase().includes(q);
      return okF && okQ;
    });
    const k = { total: items.length, active: items.filter(p=>p.status==='in_progress').length, hold: items.filter(p=>p.status==='on_hold').length, done: items.filter(p=>p.status==='done').length };
    $('kpiTotal').textContent = k.total; $('kpiActive').textContent = k.active; $('kpiHold').textContent = k.hold; $('kpiDone').textContent = k.done;

    const built = buildSeries(items).series;
    const mode = getMode();

    // Indicators
    renderIndicators(items);

    // KPI charts (enlarge donuts in ring mode)
    const sizeRing = (id, big)=>{ const el=$(id); if(!el) return; el.style.height = big? '200px':'96px'; };
    if (mode==='ring'){
      sizeRing('chartActive', true); sizeRing('chartHold', true); sizeRing('chartDone', true);
      donutSingle($('chartActive'), k.active, Math.max(k.total,1), '#22c55e');
      donutSingle($('chartHold'), k.hold, Math.max(k.total,1), '#a3e635');
      donutSingle($('chartDone'), k.done, Math.max(k.total,1), '#14b8a6');
      ensureLegend($('chartActive'), `${k.active} активных из ${k.total}`);
      ensureLegend($('chartHold'), `${k.hold} на паузе из ${k.total}`);
      ensureLegend($('chartDone'), `${k.done} завершено из ${k.total}`);
    } else {
      sizeRing('chartActive', false); sizeRing('chartHold', false); sizeRing('chartDone', false);
      if (mode==='bar'){
        barChart($('chartActive'), built.active, '#22c55e');
        barChart($('chartHold'), built.hold, '#a3e635');
        barChart($('chartDone'), built.done_cum, '#14b8a6');
      } else if (mode==='line'){
        lineChart($('chartActive'), built.active, '#22c55e');
        lineChart($('chartHold'), built.hold, '#a3e635');
        lineChart($('chartDone'), built.done_cum, '#14b8a6');
      } else {
        areaChart($('chartActive'), built.active, '#22c55e');
        areaChart($('chartHold'), built.hold, '#a3e635');
        areaChart($('chartDone'), built.done_cum, '#14b8a6');
      }
      ensureLegend($('chartActive'), 'Активные / 12м');
      ensureLegend($('chartHold'), 'На паузе / 12м');
      ensureLegend($('chartDone'), 'Кумулятивно завершено');
    }

    // Budget PF
    if (mode==='bar'){ groupBarsTwo($('chartBudgetPF'), built.budget_plan_12m, built.budget_fact_12m, '#22c55e', '#3b82f6'); }
    else { lineChartTwo($('chartBudgetPF'), built.budget_plan_12m, built.budget_fact_12m, '#22c55e', '#3b82f6'); }
    ensureLegend($('chartBudgetPF'), `<span style="display:inline-flex;gap:10px;align-items:center">
      <i style="width:10px;height:10px;background:#22c55e;display:inline-block;border-radius:2px"></i>План
      <i style="width:10px;height:10px;background:#3b82f6;display:inline-block;border-radius:2px;margin-left:10px"></i>Факт
    </span>`);

    // Donut statuses
    const planned = Math.max(0, (k.total - (k.active + k.hold + k.done)));
    const donutVals = [k.active||0, k.hold||0, k.done||0, planned||0];
    donutChart($('chartDonut'), donutVals, ['#22c55e','#f59e0b','#3b82f6','#a3a3a3'],
      `<span style="display:inline-flex;gap:10px;align-items:center">
        <i style="width:10px;height:10px;background:#22c55e;display:inline-block;border-radius:2px"></i>В работе
        <i style="width:10px;height:10px;background:#f59e0b;display:inline-block;border-radius:2px;margin-left:10px"></i>На паузе
        <i style="width:10px;height:10px;background:#3b82f6;display:inline-block;border-radius:2px;margin-left:10px"></i>Завершено
        <i style="width:10px;height:10px;background:#a3a3a3;display:inline-block;border-radius:2px;margin-left:10px"></i>Запланировано
      </span>`);

    // Done per month
    const inc = (()=>{ const d=built.done_cum.slice(); for(let i=d.length-1;i>0;i--) d[i]=Math.max(0,d[i]-d[i-1]); return d; })();
    if (mode==='line'){ lineChart($('chartBars'), inc, '#3b82f6'); } else { barChart($('chartBars'), inc, '#3b82f6'); }
    ensureLegend($('chartBars'), 'Завершено/мес');

    // Delta PF
    deltaChart($('chartDelta'), built.budget_plan_12m, built.budget_fact_12m, mode==='line' ? 'line' : 'bar');
    ensureLegend($('chartDelta'), 'Отклонение');

    // Top‑5 fact
    const top = [...items].sort((a,b)=>(+b.budget_spent||0) - (+a.budget_spent||0)).slice(0,5);
    $('budgetBars').innerHTML = top.map(p=>{
      const pct = Math.min(100, (+p.budget_spent||0) / Math.max(1,(+p.budget_plan||+p.budget_spent||1)) * 100);
      const rub = new Intl.NumberFormat('ru-RU').format(+p.budget_spent||0) + ' ₽';
      return `<div class="flex" style="justify-content:space-between"><div>${escapeHtml(p.name)}</div><div class="muted">${rub}</div></div>
              <div style="background:var(--chip);border:1px solid var(--brd);border-radius:999px;height:10px;overflow:hidden;margin:6px 0 10px">
                <i style="display:block;height:100%;width:${pct}%;background:${is3D()? 'linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.4), rgba(16,185,129,1))': '#10b981'}"></i>
              </div>`;
    }).join('');

    // Table
    const fmtDate = (d)=> d ? d : '—'; const fmtRub = (x)=> new Intl.NumberFormat('ru-RU').format(+x||0)+' ₽';
    const td = (s)=> `<td>${s}</td>`;
    const GROUP_KEY='mp_group_collapsed';
    let collapsed={}; try{ collapsed=JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(GROUP_KEY)||'{}'); }catch(e){ collapsed={}; }

    const groups = new Map();
    rows.forEach(p=>{
      const typ = p.pet_type || (p.parent_id ? 'Пет‑проект' : 'Основной');
      if (!groups.has(typ)) groups.set(typ, []);
      groups.get(typ).push(p);
    });

    const tbody = $('tbl').querySelector('tbody');
    let gidx = 0;
    let htmlRows = '';
    Array.from(groups.entries()).sort((a,b)=>a[0].localeCompare(b[0],'ru')).forEach(([typ, items])=>{
      const gid = 'g'+(gidx++);
      const isCollapsed = !!collapsed[gid];
      htmlRows += `<tr class="group-row${isCollapsed?' collapsed':''}" data-group="${gid}"><td colspan="9">${typ} <small>(${items.length})</small></td></tr>`;
      items.forEach(p=>{
        const status = ({planned:'Запланирован',in_progress:'В работе',on_hold:'На паузе',done:'Завершён'})[p.status] || p.status;
        const due = fmtDate(p.due);
        const bud = fmtRub(p.budget_spent);
        htmlRows += `<tr data-id="${p.id}" data-group="${gid}" class="row-link" style="${isCollapsed?'display:none;':''}">
          ${td(`<b>${escapeHtml(p.name||'')}</b>`)}
          ${td(escapeHtml(p.code||''))}
          ${td(escapeHtml(typ))}
          ${td(`<span class="chip">${status}</span>`)}
          ${(()=>{const pr=calcProgressRisk(p, items); return td((Math.round(pr.progress*10)/10)+"%");})()}
          ${(()=>{const pr=calcProgressRisk(p, items); return td((Math.round(pr.risk*10)/10)+"%");})()}
          ${td(bud)}
          ${td(due)}
          ${td(`<button class="action-btn" data-act="edit">Редактировать</button> <button class="action-btn action-del" data-act="del">Удалить</button>`)}
        </tr>`;
      });
    });
    tbody.innerHTML = htmlRows;

    tbody.querySelectorAll('.group-row').forEach(gr=>{
      gr.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
        const gid = gr.dataset.group;
        const willCollapse = !gr.classList.contains('collapsed');
        gr.classList.toggle('collapsed', willCollapse);
        tbody.querySelectorAll(`tr[data-group="${gid}"]`).forEach(r=>{
          if (r!==gr) r.style.display = willCollapse ? 'none' : '';
        });
        collapsed[gid] = willCollapse;
        try{ localStorage.setItem(GROUP_KEY, JSON.stringify(collapsed)); }catch(e){}
      });
    });

    tbody.querySelectorAll('tr[data-id]').forEach(tr=>{
      tr.addEventListener('click', (e)=>{
        const id = tr.getAttribute('data-id');
        const act = e.target.getAttribute('data-act');
        if (act==='edit' || act==='del') return;
        location.href = 'project_passport_offline.html?id='+encodeURIComponent(id);
      });
      tr.querySelectorAll('button[data-act]').forEach(btn=>{
        btn.addEventListener('click', (e)=>{
          e.stopPropagation();
          const id = tr.getAttribute('data-id');
          const items = load();
          const item = items.find(x=>x.id===id);
          const act = btn.getAttribute('data-act');
          if (act==='edit'){ openModal(item); }
          if (act==='del'){ if (confirm('Удалить проект?')){ persist(items.filter(x=>x.id!==id)); } }
        });
      });
    });

    // Row actions
    document.querySelectorAll('#tbl tbody tr').forEach(tr=>{
      tr.addEventListener('click', (e)=>{
        const id = tr.getAttribute('data-id');
        const act = e.target?.getAttribute?.('data-act');
        if (act==='edit' || act==='del' || e.target.tagName==='BUTTON') return;
        if (!id) return;
        location.href = 'project_passport_offline.html?id='+encodeURIComponent(id);
      });
      tr.querySelectorAll('button[data-act]').forEach(btn=> btn.addEventListener('click', (e)=>{
        e.stopPropagation();
        const id = tr.getAttribute('data-id');
        const items = load();
        const item = items.find(x=>x.id===id);
        const act = e.target.getAttribute('data-act');
        if (act==='edit'){ openModal(item); }
        if (act==='del'){ if(confirm('Удалить проект?')){ persist(items.filter(x=>x.id!==id)); } }
      }));
    });
  }

  // Resize handling
  let _rAf = null;
  function requestRerender(){ if (_rAf) cancelAnimationFrame(_rAf); _rAf = requestAnimationFrame(()=> render()); }
  window.addEventListener('resize', ()=>{ requestRerender(); });
  const ro = new ResizeObserver(()=> requestRerender());
  document.querySelectorAll('.chart').forEach(ch=> ro.observe(ch));

  // Search/filter and collapse
  document.getElementById('search').oninput = render; document.getElementById('filter').onchange = render;
  document.getElementById('btnCollapse').onclick = ()=> document.querySelector('.sidebar').classList.toggle('collapsed');

  // Indicators controls
  ['indMetric','indPeriod','indOrder'].forEach(id=> $(id).addEventListener('change', render));


  const btnCreate = document.getElementById('btnCreate');
  const createMenu = document.getElementById('createMenu');
  if (btnCreate && createMenu){
    btnCreate.addEventListener('click', (e)=>{ e.stopPropagation(); createMenu.classList.toggle('show'); });
    createMenu.querySelectorAll('button[data-act]').forEach(it=>{
      it.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
        const act = it.getAttribute('data-act');
        createMenu.classList.remove('show');
        if (act==='new') openModal();
        else if (act==='cats') openDict('cats');
        else if (act==='owners') openDict('owners');
        else if (act==='resp') openDict('resp');
        else if (act==='vendors') openDict('vendors');
        else if (act==='fin') openDict('fin');
      });
    });
    document.addEventListener('click', ()=> createMenu.classList.remove('show'));
  }

  render(); sendSummary();
})();</script>


  <div class="mp-modal" id="dictModal" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="mp-modal__content" style="max-width:820px">

  <script>
    (function(){
      var splash = document.getElementById('tasksSplash');
      if (!splash) return;
      function hideSplash(){
        splash.classList.add('splash-hidden');
        setTimeout(function(){
          if (splash && splash.parentNode){
            splash.parentNode.removeChild(splash);
          }
        }, 450);
      }
      var delay = 2500;
      if (document.readyState === 'complete' || document.readyState === 'interactive'){
        setTimeout(hideSplash, delay);
      } else {
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function(){
          setTimeout(hideSplash, delay);
        });
      }
    })();
  </script>

</body>

<script>
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
  // THEME
  const root = document.body;
  const saved = localStorage.getItem('munart_theme') || 'light';
  root.classList.toggle('theme-dark', saved==='dark');
  document.getElementById('btnTheme').onclick = () => {
    const dark = !root.classList.contains('theme-dark');
    root.classList.toggle('theme-dark', dark);
    localStorage.setItem('munart_theme', dark?'dark':'light');
  };

  // DATA
  const sections = [
    <!-- {key:'plan',       label:'План',          desc:'Календарь и маршрутные листы',         icon:'M4 12h16M4 6h16M4 18h10', color:'#3b82f6'}, -->
    {key:'routes',     label:'Маршруты',      desc:'Последовательность точек',             icon:'M4 6l8 6 8-6M4 18l8-6 8 6', color:'#22c55e'},
    {key:'objects',    label:'Объекты',       desc:'Список площадок и адресов',            icon:'M12 2l7 4v6c0 5-7 10-7 10S5 17 5 12V6l7-4z', color:'#f59e0b'},
    <!-- {key:'issues',     label:'Замечания',     desc:'Реестр отклонений',                    icon:'M12 9v4m0 4h.01M4 12a8 8 0 1 0 16 0 8 8 0 1 0-16 0z', color:'#ef4444'}, -->
    <!-- {key:'media',      label:'Фото/Видео',    desc:'Мультимедиа отчёты',                   icon:'M4 7h4l2-2h4l2 2h4v10H4z', color:'#0ea5e9'}, -->
    {key:'incidents',  label:'Инциденты',     desc:'НП, травмы, аварии',                   icon:'M12 9v2m0 4h.01M3 12l9-9 9 9-9 9-9-9z', color:'#ef4444'},
    <!-- {key:'approvals',  label:'Согласования',  desc:'Маршруты согласования',                icon:'M5 13l4 4L19 7', color:'#22c55e'}, -->
    {key:'reports',    label:'Отчёты',        desc:'PDF/Excel выгрузки',                   icon:'M8 7h8M8 11h8M8 15h6M5 5h14v14H5z', color:'#3b82f6'},
    <!-- {key:'metrics',    label:'Метрики',       desc:'KPI и дэшборды',                       icon:'M5 15l4-6 4 4 4-7', color:'#22c55e'}, -->
    <!-- {key:'settings',   label:'Настройки',     desc:'Параметры раздела',                    icon:'M12 8a4 4 0 100 8 4 4 0 000-8zM3 12h3m12 0h3M12 3v3m0 12v3', color:'#64748b'} -->
  ].map(s=>({...s, count: Math.floor(Math.random()*20)+1, progress: Math.floor(Math.random()*100)})); // demo
  <!-- const keep = new Set(['routes','objects','reports','incidents']); -->
  <!-- const sections = allSections.filter(s => keep.has(s.key)); -->
  // Elements
  const radial = document.getElementById('radial');
  const wires = document.getElementById('wires');
  const tip = document.getElementById('tip');
  const nodes = [];
  let activeIdx = 0;

  // Build nodes (+ progress markers)
  sections.forEach((s, idx)=>{
    const el = document.createElement('div'); el.className='hex'; el.dataset.key = s.key; el.setAttribute('tabindex', '0');
    el.innerHTML = '<div class="hex-shape"></div><div class="ringH"></div><div class="hex-inner">'+
      `<div class="iconWrap">
        <svg class="prog" viewBox="0 0 44 44" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle cx="22" cy="22" r="20" fill="none" stroke="var(--track)" stroke-width="4"></circle>
          <circle cx="22" cy="22" r="20" fill="none"
                  stroke="${s.color}" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-dasharray="${Math.PI*40}"
                  stroke-dashoffset="${(1 - s.progress/100) * Math.PI*40}"></circle>
        </svg>
        <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="${s.color}" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="${s.icon}"/>
        </svg>
      </div>`+
      `<div class="label">${s.label}</div><div class="desc">${s.desc}</div>`+
      `</div><div class="badge">${s.count}</div>`;
    el.addEventListener('click', ()=> openStub(s));
    el.addEventListener('mouseenter', (e)=> showTip(e, s));
    el.addEventListener('mousemove', (e)=> moveTip(e));
    el.addEventListener('mouseleave', hideTip);
    radial.appendChild(el);
    nodes.push(el);
    setTimeout(()=> el.classList.add('visible'), 40*idx);
  });

  // Layout (two arcs) + full wires from center

  function layout(){
    if(!nodes.length) return;
    const rect = radial.getBoundingClientRect();
    const cx = rect.width/2, cy = rect.height/2;
    const hexW = nodes[0].offsetWidth || 140, hexH = nodes[0].offsetHeight || 160;
    const r = Math.max(140, Math.min(rect.width, rect.height)/2 - Math.max(hexW, hexH)/2 - 8);

  // Углы: для <=4 — симметрично; иначе — старая дуговая раскладка
    let anglesDeg;
    if (nodes.length <= 4) {
    // порядок: левый верх, левый низ, правый верх, правый низ
      anglesDeg = [135, 225, -45, 45].slice(0, nodes.length);
    } else {
      const right = [-60, -30, 0, 30, 60];
      const left  = [120, 150, 180, 210, 240];
      anglesDeg = left.concat(right).slice(0, nodes.length);
    }
    const angles = anglesDeg.map(a=>a*Math.PI/180);

    wires.innerHTML='';
    nodes.forEach((el,i)=>{
      const a = angles[i];
      const x = cx + r * Math.cos(a);
      const y = cy + r * Math.sin(a);
      el.style.left = x + 'px';
      el.style.top  = y + 'px';

      const s = sections[i];
      const x2 = cx + (r - 10) * Math.cos(a);
      const y2 = cy + (r - 10) * Math.sin(a);
      wires.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend',
        `<line class="wire" x1="${cx}" y1="${cy}" x2="${x2}" y2="${y2}" stroke="${s.color}" opacity="0.85"></line>`+
        `<circle class="dot" cx="${x2}" cy="${y2}" r="4"></circle>`
      );
    });
  }
  window.addEventListener('resize', layout);
  setTimeout(layout, 0);
  setTimeout(layout, 150);

  // Tooltip
  function showTip(e, s){
    tip.style.display='block';
    tip.querySelector('.t').textContent = s.label + ' • ';
    tip.querySelector('.d').textContent = s.desc + ` — ${s.count} / прогресс ${s.progress}%`;
    moveTip(e);
  }
  function moveTip(e){
    const pad = 14;
    tip.style.left = (e.clientX + pad) + 'px';
    tip.style.top  = (e.clientY + pad) + 'px';
  }
  function hideTip(){ tip.style.display='none'; }

  // Keyboard
  function focusIdx(idx){
    nodes.forEach(n=>n.classList.remove('focused'));
    activeIdx = (idx + nodes.length) % nodes.length;
    nodes[activeIdx].classList.add('focused');
    nodes[activeIdx].focus({preventScroll:true});
  }
  focusIdx(0);
  document.addEventListener('keydown', (e)=>{
    if(document.getElementById('page-stub').style.display === 'block') return;
    if(['ArrowRight','ArrowDown'].includes(e.key)){ e.preventDefault(); focusIdx(activeIdx+1); }
    if(['ArrowLeft','ArrowUp'].includes(e.key)){ e.preventDefault(); focusIdx(activeIdx-1); }
    if(e.key==='Enter'){ e.preventDefault(); nodes[activeIdx].click(); }
    if(e.key==='Escape'){ e.preventDefault(); setMode('radial'); setView('rounds'); }
  });

  // Views & mode
  const sectionRounds = document.getElementById('page-rounds');
  const sectionList = document.getElementById('listMode');
  const btnRadial = document.getElementById('btnModeRadial');
  const btnList = document.getElementById('btnModeList');
  function setMode(mode){
    if(mode==='radial'){
      sectionRounds.style.display = 'block';
      sectionList.style.display = 'none';
      btnRadial.classList.add('active'); btnList.classList.remove('active');
      layout();
    } else {
      sectionRounds.style.display = 'none';
      sectionList.style.display = 'block';
      btnList.classList.add('active'); btnRadial.classList.remove('active');
    }
  }
  btnRadial.addEventListener('click', ()=> setMode('radial'));
  btnList.addEventListener('click', ()=> setMode('list'));

  // Build list
  const grid = document.getElementById('listGrid');
  grid.innerHTML = sections.map(s => `
    <div class="list-card">
      <div class="row">
        <svg class="ic" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="${s.color}" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="${s.icon}"/></svg>
        <div><div><b>${s.label}</b></div><div class="muted">${s.desc}</div></div>
        <div style="margin-left:auto" class="badge">${s.count}</div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:8px">
        <div style="height:6px; background:var(--track); border-radius:999px; overflow:hidden">
          <div style="width:${s.progress}%; height:100%; background:${s.color}"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:right; margin-top:8px"><button class="btn-ghost" data-open="${s.key}">Открыть</button></div>
    </div>`
  ).join('');
  grid.querySelectorAll('[data-open]').forEach(btn => btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const s = sections.find(x=>x.key===btn.getAttribute('data-open'));
    if(s) openStub(s);
  }));

  // Stub
  const stubTitle = document.getElementById('stubTitle');
  const stubDesc  = document.getElementById('stubDesc');
  const stubTable = document.getElementById('stubTable');
  const k1=document.getElementById('k1'), k2=document.getElementById('k2'), k3=document.getElementById('k3'), k4=document.getElementById('k4');

  function setView(which){
    document.getElementById('page-rounds').style.display = (which==='rounds')?'block':'none';
    document.getElementById('listMode').style.display   = (which==='list')?'block':'none';
    document.getElementById('page-stub').style.display   = (which==='stub')?'block':'none';
  }

  function openStub(s){
    setView('stub');
    stubTitle.textContent = s.label;
    stubDesc.textContent  = s.desc + ` — демо (прогресс: ${s.progress}%, элементов: ${s.count})`;
    const now = Date.now();
    const rows = Array.from({length:8}).map((_,i)=>{
      const st = ['draft','in_progress','blocked','done'][i%4];
      const dt = new Date(now - Math.floor(Math.random()*14)*86400000).toLocaleDateString('ru-RU');
      return `<tr><td style="padding:8px"><b>${s.label} #${100+i}</b></td><td style="padding:8px"><span class="badge">${st}</span></td><td style="padding:8px">${dt}</td></tr>`;
    }).join('');
    stubTable.innerHTML = rows;
    const t=8, inprog=(rows.match(/in_progress/g)||[]).length, blocked=(rows.match(/blocked/g)||[]).length, done=(rows.match(/done/g)||[]).length;
    k1.textContent=t; k2.textContent=inprog; k3.textContent=blocked; k4.textContent=done;
    history.replaceState({}, '', '#rounds/'+s.key);
  }
  document.getElementById('btnBack').addEventListener('click', ()=>{ setMode('radial'); setView('rounds'); history.replaceState({}, '', '#rounds'); });
  document.getElementById('centerBadge').addEventListener('click', ()=>{ setMode('radial'); setView('rounds'); });

  // Deep link
  if(location.hash.startsWith('#rounds/')){
    const key = location.hash.split('/')[1];
    const s = sections.find(x=>x.key===key);
    if(s) openStub(s);
  } else {
    setMode('radial'); // default
  }
});
</script>
</body>
</html>

 function applyLabels(on){ document.documentElement.classList.toggle('labels-hidden', !on); }

<script>
(function(){
  const $ = (id)=>document.getElementById(id);

  /* THEME */
  const root = document.documentElement;
  const THEME_KEY='theme-admin';
  const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem(THEME_KEY);
  if(savedTheme){ root.setAttribute('data-theme', savedTheme); }
  $('themeBtn').addEventListener('click', ()=>{
    const next = root.getAttribute('data-theme')==='dark' ? 'light' : 'dark';
    root.setAttribute('data-theme', next);
    localStorage.setItem(THEME_KEY, next);
    window.dispatchEvent(new StorageEvent('storage', { key: THEME_KEY, newValue: next }));
  });

  /* PREFS */
  const PREFS_KEY='munart_admin_prefs_v1';
  const prefs = Object.assign({
    grid:true, snap:true, route:'curve', defaultEdge:'L3', showLabels:true,
    ringW:4, nodeR:24, autosave:true, perf:false, accent:'#2563eb', maskSensitive:false
  }, JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(PREFS_KEY) || 'null') || {});
  function savePrefs(){ localStorage.setItem(PREFS_KEY, JSON.stringify(prefs)); applyPrefs(); }
  function applyPrefs(){
    $('gridRect').style.display = prefs.grid ? '' : 'none';
    document.documentElement.classList.toggle('labels-hidden', !prefs.showLabels);
    root.style.setProperty('--ring-w', prefs.ringW);
    root.style.setProperty('--node-r', prefs.nodeR);
    root.style.setProperty('--ring-r', prefs.nodeR + 4);
    root.style.setProperty('--primary', prefs.accent);
    draw();
  }
  window.addEventListener('storage', (e)=>{
    try{
      if(e.key===PREFS_KEY && e.newValue){ const np = JSON.parse(e.newValue); Object.assign(prefs, np); applyPrefs(); }
      if(e.key===THEME_KEY && e.newValue){ root.setAttribute('data-theme', e.newValue); }
    }catch(_){}
  });

  /* STORAGE (workspace) + миграция */
  const DATA_KEY='munart_workspace_v1';
  function getWorkspace(){ try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(DATA_KEY)||'null') || seed(); }catch(_){ return seed(); } }
  function setWorkspace(ws){ localStorage.setItem(DATA_KEY, JSON.stringify(ws)); }
  function normalizeWS(ws){
    ws = ws && typeof ws === 'object' ? ws : {};
    if (!Array.isArray(ws.nodes)) ws.nodes = [];
    if (!Array.isArray(ws.edges)) ws.edges = [];
    if (!ws.view) ws.view = { x:0, y:0, k:1 };
    return ws;
  }

  /* ОТДЕЛЬНО: snapshot ручной раскладки для «Пользовательского вида» */
  const USERLAYOUT_KEY = 'munart_user_layout_v1';
  function snapshotPositions(){
    return (state.nodes||[]).map(n=>({id:n.id,x:n.x,y:n.y}));
  }
  function saveUserLayout(){
    const snap = { positions: snapshotPositions(), view: {...state.view} };
    localStorage.setItem(USERLAYOUT_KEY, JSON.stringify(snap));
  }
  function loadUserLayout(){
    try{
      const j = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(USERLAYOUT_KEY) || 'null');
      if(!j || !Array.isArray(j.positions)) return false;
      const map = new Map(j.positions.map(p=>[p.id,p]));
      state.nodes.forEach(n=>{ const p = map.get(n.id); if(p){ n.x=p.x; n.y=p.y; } });
      if(j.view){ state.view = j.view; }
      draw(); save();
      return true;
    }catch(_){ return false; }
  }

  /* Состояние */
  const state = normalizeWS(getWorkspace()); setWorkspace(state);

  /* SVG / слои */
  const svg = $('svg'), vp = $('viewport');
  const edgesG = svg.querySelector('.edges'), labelsG = svg.querySelector('.labels'), nodesG = svg.querySelector('.nodes');

  /* Проекции */
  function project(p){ return { x: p.x*state.view.k + state.view.x, y: p.y*state.view.k + state.view.y }; }
  function unproject(p){ return { x: (p.x - state.view.x)/state.view.k, y: (p.y - state.view.y)/state.view.k }; }

  /* Утилиты */
  function nodeColorByStatus(n){ return n.status==='warn' ? 'var(--warn)' : (n.status==='down' ? 'var(--bad)' : 'var(--good)'); }
  function pathCurve(a,b){
    if(prefs.route==='straight') return `M ${a.x} ${a.y} L ${b.x} ${b.y}`;
    if(prefs.route==='orth'){
      const midX = (a.x + b.x)/2;
      return `M ${a.x} ${a.y} L ${midX} ${a.y} L ${midX} ${b.y} L ${b.x} ${b.y}`;
    }
    const dx=(b.x-a.x), k=0.35; const c1={x:a.x+dx*k,y:a.y}, c2={x:b.x-dx*k,y:b.y};
    return `M ${a.x} ${a.y} C ${c1.x} ${c1.y} ${c2.x} ${c2.y} ${b.x} ${b.y}`;
  }
  function edgeClass(e){
    const base = e.type==='L2' ? 'edge alt' : (e.type==='VPN' ? 'edge vpn' : (e.type==='DEP' ? 'edge dep' : 'edge'));
    if(e.status==='warn') return base + ' warn';
    if(e.status==='down') return base + ' bad';
    return base;
  }

  /* Рисование */
  function draw(){
    // edges
    edgesG.innerHTML=''; labelsG.innerHTML='';
    state.edges.forEach(e=>{
      const A = state.nodes.find(n=>n.id===e.s), B = state.nodes.find(n=>n.id===e.t);
      if(!A||!B) return;
      const ap = project(A), bp = project(B);
      const path = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','path');
      path.setAttribute('d', pathCurve(ap, bp)); path.setAttribute('class', edgeClass(e));
      if(!prefs.perf) path.setAttribute('filter','url(#glow)'); else path.removeAttribute('filter');
      path.dataset.id = e.id;
      edgesG.appendChild(path);
      if(prefs.showLabels && e.label){
        const tx = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','text');
        tx.setAttribute('class','edge-label'); tx.textContent = e.label;
        const mx = (ap.x + bp.x)/2, my = (ap.y + bp.y)/2; tx.setAttribute('x', mx); tx.setAttribute('y', my - 6);
        labelsG.appendChild(tx);
      }
    });

    // nodes
    nodesG.innerHTML='';
    state.nodes.forEach(n=>{
      const g = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','g');
      g.setAttribute('class','node'); g.dataset.id = n.id;
      const P = project(n); g.setAttribute('transform', `translate(${P.x},${P.y})`);
      if(n.cloud){
        // "облачко"
        const r = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','g');
        const path = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','path');
        path.setAttribute('d','M-58,2 C-72,-6 -74,-28 -58,-30 C-42,-30 -16,-32 0,-22 C18,-34 48,-26 50,-8 C74,-6 74,20 56,26 C48,40 18,46 0,38 C-18,46 -46,40 -58,18 Z');
        path.setAttribute('fill','color-mix(in oklab, var(--panel) 70%, var(--bg))');
        path.setAttribute('stroke','var(--ring)'); path.setAttribute('stroke-width','1.5');
        r.appendChild(path);
        const tx = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','text'); tx.textContent = n.label || n.id; tx.setAttribute('y','6'); r.appendChild(tx);
        g.appendChild(r);
      }else{
        // круг
        const ring = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','circle');
        ring.setAttribute('class','ring'); ring.setAttribute('r','var(--ring-r)'); ring.setAttribute('cx','0'); ring.setAttribute('cy','0');
        ring.setAttribute('stroke', nodeColorByStatus(n)); g.appendChild(ring);
        const c = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','circle');
        c.setAttribute('r','var(--node-r)'); c.setAttribute('cx','0'); c.setAttribute('cy','0'); g.appendChild(c);
        const tx = document.createElementNS('http://www.w3.org/2000/svg','text'); tx.textContent = n.label || n.id; tx.setAttribute('y','1'); g.appendChild(tx);
      }
      nodesG.appendChild(g);
    });
    sendSummary(); // no-op placeholder if встраивается
  }

  /* Панорамирование/зум */
  let isPanning=false, panStart=null;
  svg.addEventListener('mousedown', (e)=>{ if(e.target.closest('.node')) return; isPanning=true; panStart={x:e.clientX, y:e.clientY, ox:state.view.x, oy:state.view.y}; });
  window.addEventListener('mousemove', (e)=>{ if(!isPanning) return; state.view.x = panStart.ox + (e.clientX - panStart.x); state.view.y = panStart.oy + (e.clientY - panStart.y); draw(); });
  window.addEventListener('mouseup', ()=> isPanning=false);
  svg.addEventListener('wheel', (e)=>{
    e.preventDefault(); const scale = Math.exp(-e.deltaY * 0.0012);
    const pt = {x:e.offsetX, y:e.offsetY}; const before = unproject(pt);
    state.view.k = Math.min(2.5, Math.max(0.4, state.view.k * scale));
    const after = project(before); state.view.x += (pt.x - after.x); state.view.y += (pt.y - after.y); draw();
  }, {passive:false});
  $('resetView').addEventListener('click', ()=>{ state.view={x:0,y:0,k:1}; draw(); save(); });

  /* Перетаскивание узлов (теперь и облачка!) */
  let drag=null;
  nodesG.addEventListener('mousedown', (e)=>{
    const g = e.target.closest('.node'); if(!g) return;
    const id = g.dataset.id; const n = state.nodes.find(x=>x.id===id);
    if(!n) return; // убрали запрет для n.cloud
    drag = {n, start: unproject({x:e.clientX, y:e.clientY}), ox:n.x, oy:n.y};
    document.body.style.cursor='grabbing';
  });
  window.addEventListener('mousemove', (e)=>{
    if(!drag) return;
    const p = unproject({x:e.clientX, y:e.clientY});
    let nx = drag.ox + (p.x - drag.start.x), ny = drag.oy + (p.y - drag.start.y);
    if(prefs.snap){ const g = parseInt(getComputedStyle(root).getPropertyValue('--grid')) || 40; nx = Math.round(nx/g)*g; ny = Math.round(ny/g)*g; }
    drag.n.x = nx; drag.n.y = ny; draw();
  });
  window.addEventListener('mouseup', ()=>{
    if(drag){ save(); saveUserLayout(); } // любой перенос — это пользовательский вид
    drag=null; document.body.style.cursor='';
  });

  /* Выбор/инспектор — упрощённо */
  const f = { name: $('f_name'), type:$('f_type'), ip:$('f_ip'), os:$('f_os'), sla:$('f_sla'), owner:$('f_owner'), level:$('f_level'), status:$('f_status'), tags:$('f_tags'), note:$('f_note') };
  const selInfo = $('selInfo'); const inspectorNode = $('inspectorNode'); const inspectorEdge = $('inspectorEdge');
  let selected=null, selectedEdge=null;

  nodesG.addEventListener('click', (e)=>{
    const g = e.target.closest('.node'); if(!g) return;
	if (connectMode) return;
    const n = state.nodes.find(x=>x.id===g.dataset.id); if(!n) return;
    selectedEdge=null; inspectorEdge.style.display='none';
    selected=n; inspectorNode.style.display='grid'; reflectInspector();
  });

  function reflectInspector(){
    if(!selected){ selInfo.textContent='—'; return; }
    f.name.value = selected.label || selected.id || '';
    f.type.value = selected.type || '';
    f.ip.value   = selected.ip || ''; f.os.value   = selected.os || '';
    f.sla.value  = selected.sla||''; f.owner.value = selected.owner||'';
    f.level.value = selected.level || 1; f.status.value = selected.status || 'ok';
    f.tags.value = selected.tags || ''; f.note.value = selected.note || '';
    selInfo.textContent = `#${selected.id}`;
  }
  $('saveNode').addEventListener('click', ()=>{ if(!selected) return;
    selected.label=f.name.value.trim()||selected.label;
    selected.type=f.type.value||'';
    selected.ip=f.ip.value; selected.os=f.os.value; selected.sla=f.sla.value; selected.owner=f.owner.value;
    selected.level=+f.level.value||1; selected.status=f.status.value||'ok';
    selected.tags=f.tags.value; selected.note=f.note.value;
    draw(); save();
  });
  $('deleteNode').addEventListener('click', ()=>{
    if(!selected) return;
    state.edges = state.edges.filter(e=> e.s!==selected.id && e.t!==selected.id);
    state.nodes = state.nodes.filter(n=> n.id!==selected.id);
    selected=null; draw(); save();
  });

  /* Добавление и соединения */
  $('addNode').addEventListener('click', ()=>{
    const id='n'+Math.random().toString(36).slice(2,7);
    const center = unproject({x: svg.clientWidth/2, y: svg.clientHeight/2});
    const n={id, x:center.x + (Math.random()*120-60), y:center.y + (Math.random()*60-30), level:2, type:'server', label:id, status:'ok'};
    state.nodes.push(n); draw(); save(); saveUserLayout();
  });







// --- Режим создания связи (устойчивый) ---
const connectTip = $('connectTip');
let connectMode = false;
let sourceNodeId = null;

function clearFromHighlight(){
  nodesG.querySelectorAll('.node.from').forEach(el=>el.classList.remove('from'));
}
function toggleConnectMode(on){
  connectMode = !!on;
  $('connectBtn').setAttribute('aria-pressed', String(connectMode));
  connectTip.style.display = connectMode ? '' : 'none';
  if(!connectMode){ sourceNodeId = null; clearFromHighlight(); }
}

// безопасное добавление ребра: без дублей и самоссылающихся
function upsertEdge(s, t){
  if(!s || !t || s===t) return;
  const exists = state.edges.some(e => (e.s===s && e.t===t) || (e.s===t && e.t===s));
  if (exists) return;
  const id = 'e' + Math.random().toString(36).slice(2,7);
  const type  = ($('edgeType').value || prefs.defaultEdge || 'L3');
  const label = ($('edgeLabel').value || '').trim();
  state.edges.push({ id, s, t, type, label });
  draw(); save();
}

// клик по кнопке «Связь»
$('connectBtn').addEventListener('click', ()=> toggleConnectMode(!connectMode));

// клик по узлу в режиме связи
nodesG.addEventListener('click', (e)=>{
  if(!connectMode) return;
  const g = e.target.closest('.node'); if(!g) return;
  e.stopPropagation(); // не отдаём клик инспектору
  const id = g.dataset.id;

  // 1-й клик — запомнить источник и подсветить
  if(!sourceNodeId){
    sourceNodeId = id;
    clearFromHighlight();
    g.classList.add('from');
    return;
  }

  // 2-й клик — создать ребро (если ещё нет), выйти из режима
  upsertEdge(sourceNodeId, id);
  toggleConnectMode(false);
});








  /* Авто-раскладка и Пользовательский вид */
  $('autoLayout').addEventListener('click', ()=>{
    // перед авто — сохранить текущую ручную раскладку
    saveUserLayout();

    const groups = [1,2,3,4,5].map(lvl => state.nodes.filter(n=>!n.cloud && n.level===lvl));
    const leftPad=160, hgap=140, vstart=140, vgap=120;
    groups.forEach((g, idx)=>{
      const y = vstart + idx*vgap;
      g.forEach((n,i)=>{ n.x = leftPad + i*hgap; n.y = y; });
    });
    state.nodes.filter(n=>n.cloud).forEach((c,i)=>{ c.x = 720 + i*140; c.y = 60; });
    draw(); save();
  });

  $('userLayout').addEventListener('click', ()=>{
    if(!loadUserLayout()){
      // если ещё нет снапшота — создадим из текущего расположения
      saveUserLayout();
      alert('Пользовательский вид сохранён. Теперь вы можете переключаться между авто-раскладкой и этим видом.');
    }
  });

  /* Поиск */
  $('search').addEventListener('input', (e)=>{
    const q = e.target.value.trim().toLowerCase();
    nodesG.querySelectorAll('.node').forEach(g=>{
      const n = state.nodes.find(x=>x.id===g.dataset.id);
      const txt = ((n.label||'') + ' ' + (n.ip||'') + ' ' + (n.tags||'')).toLowerCase();
      const on = !q || txt.includes(q);
      g.style.opacity = on ? 1 : .25;
      g.style.pointerEvents = on ? '' : 'none';
    });
  });

  /* Экспорт/Импорт/PNG */
  $('exportBtn').addEventListener('click', ()=>{
    const blob = new Blob([JSON.stringify(state, null, 2)], {type:'application/json'});
    const a = document.createElement('a'); a.href = URL.createObjectURL(blob); a.download = 'munart_network.json'; a.click();
    setTimeout(()=>URL.revokeObjectURL(a.href), 4000);
  });
  $('importFile').addEventListener('change', (e)=>{
    const file = e.target.files[0]; if(!file) return;
    const fr = new FileReader();
    fr.onload = ()=>{
      try{
        const data = JSON.parse(fr.result);
        if(data.nodes && data.edges){ state.nodes=data.nodes; state.edges=data.edges; state.view=data.view || {x:0,y:0,k:1}; draw(); save(); saveUserLayout(); }
        else alert('Некорректный формат файла');
      }catch(err){ alert('Ошибка чтения файла: '+err.message); }
    };
    fr.readAsText(file);
  });
  $('exportPng').addEventListener('click', ()=>{
    const serializer = new XMLSerializer();
    const svgStr = serializer.serializeToString(svg);
    const img = new Image();
    img.onload = function(){
      const canvas = document.createElement('canvas');
      canvas.width = svg.clientWidth; canvas.height = svg.clientHeight;
      const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
      ctx.fillStyle = getComputedStyle(document.body).getPropertyValue('--bg'); ctx.fillRect(0,0,canvas.width,canvas.height);
      ctx.drawImage(img, 0, 0);
      const a = document.createElement('a'); a.download = 'munart_network.png'; a.href = canvas.toDataURL('image/png'); a.click();
    };
    img.src = 'data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,' + encodeURIComponent(svgStr);
  });

  /* Хелперы */
  function save(){ if(prefs.autosave) setWorkspace(state); }
  function sendSummary(){ /* можно отправлять summary наружу при встройке, опущено */ }

  /* Демо-данные */
  function seed(){
    return {
      nodes: [
        {id:'cs20', x:800, y:130, level:4, type:'network', label:'cs20', ip:'10.0.20.1', os:'', sla:'24/7', owner:'', status:'ok', tags:'core,gw', note:''},
        {id:'cloud4', x:700, y:60, level:5, label:'Level 4', cloud:true},
        {id:'cloud5', x:880, y:60, level:5, label:'Level 5', cloud:true},
        {id:'cs30', x:600, y:260, level:3, type:'server', label:'cs30', status:'ok', os:'Ubuntu 22.04'},
        {id:'cs51', x:760, y:260, level:3, type:'server', label:'cs51', status:'ok'},
        {id:'cs46', x:920, y:260, level:3, type:'server', label:'cs46', status:'ok'},
        {id:'cs52', x:1080,y:260, level:3, type:'app', label:'cs52', status:'warn'},
        {id:'cs76', x:200, y:380, level:2, type:'server', label:'cs76'},
        {id:'cs50', x:340, y:380, level:2, type:'db', label:'cs50'},
        {id:'cs23', x:480, y:380, level:2, type:'app', label:'cs23'},
        {id:'ded1', x:620, y:380, level:2, type:'service', label:'ded/1'},
        {id:'cs47', x:760, y:380, level:2, type:'server', label:'cs47'},
        {id:'cs36', x:900, y:380, level:2, type:'server', label:'cs36'},
        {id:'cs49', x:1040,y:380, level:2, type:'storage', label:'cs49'},
        {id:'cs22', x:1180,y:380, level:2, type:'app', label:'cs22'},
        {id:'cs71', x:1320,y:380, level:2, type:'server', label:'cs71'},
        {id:'cs29', x:1460,y:380, level:2, type:'server', label:'cs29'}
      ],
      edges: [
        {id:'e1', s:'cs20', t:'cs30', type:'L3', label:'1GbE'},
        {id:'e2', s:'cs20', t:'cs51', type:'L3', label:'1GbE'},
        {id:'e3', s:'cs20', t:'cs46', type:'L3', label:'1GbE'},
        {id:'e4', s:'cs20', t:'cs52', type:'L3', label:'HTTPS'},
        {id:'e5', s:'cs50', t:'cs23', type:'DEP', label:'depends'},
      ],
      view: {x:0,y:0,k:1}
    };
  }

  /* INIT */
  applyPrefs();
  draw();
  // При первом клике «Авто-раскладка» снимок сделается автоматически. Можно инициализировать вручную:
  if(!localStorage.getItem(USERLAYOUT_KEY)) saveUserLayout();

})();
</script>
</body>
</html>
===== END FILE: munart_ui\public\prototypes\networks_v5_userview.html =====

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_ui\public\prototypes\obezdy_offline.html (text) =====

<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#0f172a; --panel:#0b1220; --muted:#94a3b8; --text:#e2e8f0; --hub:#334155; --br:#1f2937;
    --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(2,6,23,.45);
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: light){
    :root{ --bg:#f7f8fb; --panel:#ffffff; --muted:#6b7280; --text:#0f172a; --hub:#94a3b8; --br:#e5e7eb; --shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(2,6,23,.1); }
  }
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  body{
    margin:0; font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Inter,Roboto,Arial;
    background:radial-gradient(1200px 700px at 10% -10%, rgba(99,102,241,.08), transparent), var(--bg);
    color:var(--text);
  }
  .wrap{display:flex; flex-direction:column;}
  .head{display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; padding:12px 18px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--br); background:var(--panel)}
  .title{font-weight:800; letter-spacing:.2px; font-size:18px}
  .muted{color:var(--muted); font-size:12px}
  .stage{position:relative; height:640px}
  svg{position:absolute; inset:0; width:100%; height:100%; shape-rendering:geometricPrecision}
  .label{font-size:16px; font-weight:700; pointer-events:none; letter-spacing:.2px}
  .badge{position:absolute; left:12px; top:12px; padding:6px 10px; border-radius:999px; border:1px solid var(--br); background:rgba(255,255,255,.04)}
  /* Узел-иконка увеличивается из центра */
  .node{transform-box:fill-box; transform-origin:center; transition:transform .18s ease}
  .node:hover{transform:scale(1.12)}
  /* Тонкая пульсация вокруг узла */
  .halo{fill:none; opacity:0}
  .node:hover .halo{animation:pulseHalo 1.8s ease-out infinite}
  @keyframes pulseHalo{
    0%   {stroke-width:0; opacity:.45; r:0}
    60%  {stroke-width:8; opacity:.12; r:36}
    100% {stroke-width:12; opacity:0; r:44}
  }
  /* Центр */
  .hubRing{fill:none; stroke:rgba(255,255,255,.35); stroke-width:2}
  .hubGlow{filter:url(#hubGlow)}
  .centerPulse{fill:none; opacity:0}
  .centerPulse.active{animation:centerPulse 2s ease-out infinite}
  @keyframes centerPulse{
    0%   {stroke-width:0; opacity:.35; r:0}
    70%  {stroke-width:14; opacity:.10; r:84}
    100% {stroke-width:20; opacity:0; r:100}
  }

  <div class="head">
    <div class="title">Объезды</div>
    <div class="muted">РАЗДЕЛ НАХОДИТСЯ В РАЗРАБОТКЕ</div>
  </div>

  <div class="stage">
    <div class="badge muted">Наведи/кликни по разделу</div>
    <svg id="svgel" aria-label="Схема объездов"></svg>

    <!-- Card sheet -->
    <div id="sheet" class="sheet" aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute; inset:0; display:none; align-items:stretch; justify-content:flex-end; backdrop-filter: blur(6px);">
      <div class="scrim" onclick="closeSheet()" style="position:absolute; inset:0;"></div>
      <div class="panel" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="ptitle"
           style="position:relative; margin-left:auto; width:min(540px, 100%); background:var(--panel); border-left:1px solid var(--br); box-shadow:var(--shadow); display:flex; flex-direction:column; height:100%;
