        </div>
        <div class="pbody" style="padding:16px 18px; overflow:auto; display:grid; gap:14px">
          <div id="psub" class="muted">Описание</div>
          <div class="card" id="pfeed" style="border:1px solid var(--br); border-radius:16px; padding:14px; background:rgba(255,255,255,.02)">Список последних событий / маршрутов / инцидентов (заготовка).</div>
          <div class="row" style="display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap">
            <button id="openBtn" class="btn" style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; padding:9px 12px; border-radius:12px; border:1px solid var(--br); background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(59,130,246,.18), rgba(59,130,246,.06)); color:var(--text); cursor:pointer; font-weight:700">Открыть раздел</button>
            <button class="btn" style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; padding:9px 12px; border-radius:12px; border:1px solid var(--br); background:rgba(255,255,255,.04); color:var(--text); cursor:pointer">Создать</button>
            <button class="btn" style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; padding:9px 12px; border-radius:12px; border:1px solid var(--br); background:rgba(255,255,255,.04); color:var(--text); cursor:pointer">Импорт</button>
            <button class="btn" style="display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; padding:9px 12px; border-radius:12px; border:1px solid var(--br); background:rgba(255,255,255,.04); color:var(--text); cursor:pointer">Экспорт</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
/* Разделы (цвет + ключ иконки) */
const sections = [
  { key:"reports",   label:"Отчёты",    icon:"clipboard", color:"#22c55e",
    desc:"Сводки и отчётность по объектам и маршрутам." },
  { key:"routes",    label:"Маршруты",  icon:"route",     color:"#60a5fa",
    desc:"Схемы объездов, последовательности визитов, GPS-треки." },
  { key:"events",    label:"События",   icon:"calendar",  color:"#f59e0b",
    desc:"Публикации и заметки, отмеченные по маршрутам и объектам." },
  { key:"incidents", label:"Инциденты", icon:"alert",     color:"#a78bfa",
    desc:"Регистрация нарушений, ЧС и несоответствий." },
  { key:"objects",   label:"Объекты",   icon:"building",  color:"#ef4444",
    desc:"Список площадок и адресов." },
];

/* Иконки (viewBox 0 0 24 24) */
const ICONS = {
  clipboard: ({g,color})=>{
    const r = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","rect");
    r.setAttribute("x","5"); r.setAttribute("y","4"); r.setAttribute("width","14"); r.setAttribute("height","16"); r.setAttribute("rx","2");
    r.setAttribute("fill","none"); r.setAttribute("stroke",color); r.setAttribute("stroke-width","2"); r.setAttribute("stroke-linejoin","round");
    g.appendChild(r);
    const t = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","path");
    t.setAttribute("d","M9 4v3h6V4"); t.setAttribute("fill","none"); t.setAttribute("stroke",color); t.setAttribute("stroke-width","2"); t.setAttribute("stroke-linecap","round");
    g.appendChild(t);
    const l1 = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","path");
    l1.setAttribute("d","M8 11h8M8 15h8"); l1.setAttribute("fill","none"); l1.setAttribute("stroke",color); l1.setAttribute("stroke-width","2"); l1.setAttribute("stroke-linecap","round");
    g.appendChild(l1);
  },
  route: ({g,color})=>{
    const p = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","path");
    p.setAttribute("d","M4 18c3 0 3-6 6-6s3 6 6 6 3-6 6-6");
    p.setAttribute("fill","none"); p.setAttribute("stroke",color); p.setAttribute("stroke-width","2"); p.setAttribute("stroke-linecap","round"); p.setAttribute("stroke-linejoin","round");
    g.appendChild(p);
    const a = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","circle");
    a.setAttribute("cx","4"); a.setAttribute("cy","18"); a.setAttribute("r","2"); a.setAttribute("fill",color);
    const b = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","circle");
    b.setAttribute("cx","22"); b.setAttribute("cy","12"); b.setAttribute("r","2"); b.setAttribute("fill",color);
    g.appendChild(a); g.appendChild(b);
  },
  calendar: ({g,color})=>{
    const r = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","rect");
    r.setAttribute("x","4"); r.setAttribute("y","5"); r.setAttribute("width","16"); r.setAttribute("height","15"); r.setAttribute("rx","2");
    r.setAttribute("fill","none"); r.setAttribute("stroke",color); r.setAttribute("stroke-width","2"); r.setAttribute("stroke-linejoin","round");
    g.appendChild(r);
    const l = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","path");
    l.setAttribute("d","M16 3v4M8 3v4M4 9h16"); l.setAttribute("fill","none"); l.setAttribute("stroke",color); l.setAttribute("stroke-width","2"); l.setAttribute("stroke-linecap","round");
    g.appendChild(l);
  },
  alert: ({g,color})=>{
    const tri = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","path");
    tri.setAttribute("d","M12 3L2 21h20L12 3z"); tri.setAttribute("fill","none"); tri.setAttribute("stroke",color); tri.setAttribute("stroke-width","2"); tri.setAttribute("stroke-linejoin","round");
    g.appendChild(tri);
    const ex1 = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","path");
    ex1.setAttribute("d","M12 9v5"); ex1.setAttribute("fill","none"); ex1.setAttribute("stroke",color); ex1.setAttribute("stroke-width","2"); ex1.setAttribute("stroke-linecap","round");
    const ex2 = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","circle");
    ex2.setAttribute("cx","12"); ex2.setAttribute("cy","17"); ex2.setAttribute("r","1.2"); ex2.setAttribute("fill",color);
    g.appendChild(ex1); g.appendChild(ex2);
  },
  building: ({g,color})=>{
    const body = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","rect");
    body.setAttribute("x","6"); body.setAttribute("y","6"); body.setAttribute("width","12"); body.setAttribute("height","14"); body.setAttribute("rx","1.8");
    body.setAttribute("fill","none"); body.setAttribute("stroke",color); body.setAttribute("stroke-width","2");
    g.appendChild(body);
    const win = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","path");
    win.setAttribute("d","M9 9h2v2H9zM13 9h2v2h-2zM9 13h2v2H9zM13 13h2v2h-2z");
    win.setAttribute("fill",color);
    g.appendChild(win);
    const door = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","rect");
    door.setAttribute("x","11"); door.setAttribute("y","16"); door.setAttribute("width","2"); door.setAttribute("height","4"); door.setAttribute("fill",color);
    g.appendChild(door);
  },
  /* Центральная тематическая картинка: рулевое колесо */
  wheel: ({g,color})=>{
    const circle = (cx,cy,r,opts={})=>{ const c=document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","circle"); c.setAttribute("cx",cx); c.setAttribute("cy",cy); c.setAttribute("r",r); for(const [k,v] of Object.entries(opts)) c.setAttribute(k,v); g.appendChild(c); return c; };
    circle(12,12,9,{fill:"none",stroke:color,"stroke-width":"2"});
    circle(12,12,5.5,{fill:"none",stroke:color,"stroke-width":"2"});
    circle(12,12,1.6,{fill:color});
    const spokes = [["M12 6v4"],["M18 12h-4"],["M6 12h4"]];
    for(const [d] of spokes){
      const p=document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","path");
      p.setAttribute("d",d); p.setAttribute("fill","none"); p.setAttribute("stroke",color); p.setAttribute("stroke-width","2"); p.setAttribute("stroke-linecap","round");
      g.appendChild(p);
    }
  }
};

const svg = document.getElementById('svgel');
const sheet = document.getElementById('sheet');
const HOVER_SCALE = 1.12;

function clear(el){ while(el.firstChild) el.removeChild(el.firstChild); }
function make(tag, attrs={}, parent=svg){ const el = document.createElementNS("http://www.w3.org/2000/svg", tag); for (const [k,v] of Object.entries(attrs)) el.setAttribute(k,v); parent.appendChild(el); return el; }

function lighten(hex, k){ // k in [0..1]
  const c = hex.replace('#','');
  const n = parseInt(c.length===3 ? c.split('').map(x=>x+x).join('') : c, 16);
  const r = (n>>16)&255, g=(n>>8)&255, b=n&255;
  const rn = Math.round(r + (255-r)*k), gn = Math.round(g + (255-g)*k), bn = Math.round(b + (255-b)*k);
  return `rgb(${rn},${gn},${bn})`;
}

function render(){
  clear(svg);
  const {width:W, height:H} = svg.getBoundingClientRect();
  const cx=W/2, cy=H/2;
  const orbit = Math.min(W,H)/2.6;
  const iconR = Math.min(W,H)/12; // радиус фонового круга иконки
  const hubR  = Math.min(W,H)/12;

  // defs: glow for center
  const defs=make('defs');
  const flt=make('filter',{id:'hubGlow',x:'-50%',y:'-50%',width:'200%',height:'200%'},defs);
  make('feGaussianBlur',{stdDeviation:'7',result:'blur'},flt);
  const feMerge=make('feMerge',{},flt); make('feMergeNode',{in:'blur'},feMerge); make('feMergeNode',{in:'SourceGraphic'},feMerge);
  const grad = make('radialGradient',{id:'hubGrad',cx:'50%',cy:'45%',r:'70%'},defs);
  const s1 = make('stop',{'offset':'0%','stop-color':'#a1aab8'},grad);
  const s2 = make('stop',{'offset':'100%','stop-color':'#4b5563'},grad);

  // center group
  const hubG=make('g',{});
  const pulse=make('circle',{cx,cy,r:hubR, class:'centerPulse'},hubG);
  const ring=make('circle',{cx,cy,r:hubR+8,class:'hubRing'},hubG);
  const hub=make('circle',{cx,cy,r:hubR,fill:'url(#hubGrad)',class:'hubGlow',stroke:'rgba(255,255,255,.18)','stroke-width':1.5},hubG);

  // inner thematic icon (steering wheel)
  const innerIcon = make('g',{},hubG);
  const innerScale = (hubR*0.70)/12;
  innerIcon.setAttribute('transform',`translate(${cx},${cy}) scale(${innerScale}) translate(-12,-12)`);
  ICONS.wheel({g:innerIcon, color:'#e5e7eb'});

  /* NODES (no edges) */
  sections.forEach((s,i)=>{
    const ang=(Math.PI*2*i/sections.length)-Math.PI/2;
    const px=cx+orbit*Math.cos(ang);
    const py=cy+orbit*Math.sin(ang);

    const node=make('g',{class:'node'});

    // пульс-ореол (перекрашиваем stroke под узел)
    const halo=make('circle',{cx:px,cy:py,r:0, class:'halo', stroke:s.color},node);

    // фон круга
    make('circle',{cx:px,cy:py,r:iconR,fill:s.color+'1F',stroke:s.color,'stroke-width':3},node);

    // иконка строго по центру
    const iconWrap = make('g',{},node);
    const inner = iconR*0.66;
    const scale = inner/12;
    iconWrap.setAttribute('transform',`translate(${px},${py}) scale(${scale}) translate(-12,-12)`);
    if (ICONS[s.icon]) ICONS[s.icon]({g:iconWrap, color:s.color});

    // подпись
    const label=make('text',{x:px,y:py+iconR+18,'text-anchor':'middle',class:'label',fill:s.color},node);
    label.textContent=s.label;

    // hover/leave
    node.addEventListener('mouseenter',()=>{
      const light = lighten(s.color, .45);
      s1.setAttribute('stop-color', light);
      s2.setAttribute('stop-color', s.color);
      ring.setAttribute('stroke', s.color);
      pulse.setAttribute('stroke', s.color);
      pulse.classList.add('active'); // запустить пульс центра
    });
    node.addEventListener('mouseleave',()=>{
      s1.setAttribute('stop-color', '#a1aab8');
      s2.setAttribute('stop-color', '#4b5563');
      ring.setAttribute('stroke', 'rgba(255,255,255,.35)');
      pulse.classList.remove('active');
    });

    node.addEventListener('click',()=>openSheet(s));
  });
}

function openSheet(s){
  document.getElementById('ptitle').textContent = s.label;
  document.getElementById('psub').textContent = s.desc || '';
  const btn = document.getElementById('openBtn');
  btn.style.borderColor = s.color;
  btn.style.background = `linear-gradient(180deg, ${s.color}2E, ${s.color}14)`;
  sheet.style.display='flex';
  requestAnimationFrame(()=>{ document.querySelector('.panel').style.transform='translateX(0)'; document.querySelector('.panel').style.opacity='1'; });
}
function closeSheet(){
  document.querySelector('.panel').style.transform='translateX(8px)'; document.querySelector('.panel').style.opacity='.0';
  setTimeout(()=>{ sheet.style.display='none'; },200);
}

const ro=new ResizeObserver(render); ro.observe(document.body);
render();
</script>
</body>
</html>
===== END FILE: munart_ui\public\prototypes\obezdy_offline.html =====

/* Универсальные правки для встроенных HTML, когда тема = dark */
:root[data-theme="dark"] {
  --embed-bg:        #0b1220;        /* фон страницы */
  --embed-panel:     rgba(2,6,23,.88);/* фон блоков/карточек */
  --embed-border:    #334155;         /* рамки */
  --embed-text:      #e5e7eb;         /* основной текст */
  --embed-muted:     #94a3b8;         /* вторичный текст */
}

/* фон страницы + общий текст */
:root[data-theme="dark"] body {
  background: var(--embed-bg) !important;
  color: var(--embed-text) !important;
}

<script>
(()=>{'use strict';
  // Theme support (light by default; respect '?theme=' or saved)
  const qs = new URLSearchParams(location.search);
  const prefTheme = qs.get('theme') || localStorage.getItem('munart_theme') || 'light';
  if (prefTheme === 'dark') document.body.classList.add('theme-dark'); else document.body.classList.remove('theme-dark');
  localStorage.setItem('munart_theme', prefTheme);

  const STORE='munart_projects_offline_light';
  const PID = new URLSearchParams(location.search).get('id')||'';
  const backTargets=['munart_projects_offline_light_auth__updated_v5.html','munart_projects_offline_light_auth.html'];

  const $ = (id)=> document.getElementById(id);
  const fmtRub = (x)=> new Intl.NumberFormat('ru-RU').format(+x||0)+' ₽';
  const fmtDate = (d)=> d ? d : '—';
  const nowISO = ()=> new Date().toISOString();
  const curUser = (()=>{ try{ const u=JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_current_user')||'{}'); return u.name||'Пользователь'; }catch(_){ return 'Пользователь'; }})();

  function load(){ try { return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(STORE))||[]; } catch(_){ return []; } }
  function saveAll(arr){ localStorage.setItem(STORE, JSON.stringify(arr)); }
  function uid(){ return 'p'+Math.random().toString(36).slice(2,8); }

  function getProject(){ return load().find(p=>p.id===PID); }
  function setProject(next){
    const arr=load().map(p=> p.id===next.id ? next : p);
    saveAll(arr);
  }

  function pushHistory(prj, event){
    prj.history = prj.history||[];
    prj.history.unshift({t: nowISO(), who: curUser, event});
    setProject(prj);
    renderHistory(prj);
  }

  // Header + overview
  function renderOverview(prj){
    $('pTitle').textContent = prj.name || 'Паспорт проекта';
  const tName = (prj.name && prj.name.trim()) ? prj.name.trim() : 'Без названия';
  const tType = prj.pet_type || prj.category || prj.type || '';
  const tEl = $('projInlineTitle'); if(tEl){ tEl.innerHTML = tType ? `${escapeHtml(tName)} <span class="chip">${escapeHtml(tType)}</span>` : escapeHtml(tName); }
    $('pSub').textContent = (prj.code? 'код '+prj.code+' • ' : '') + (prj.category||'') + (prj.owner? ' • '+prj.owner : '');

    const dictStatus={planned:'Запланирован',in_progress:'В работе',on_hold:'На паузе',done:'Завершён'};
    const children = load().filter(x=>x.parent_id===prj.id);

    const __all = load();
    function __descendants(rootId){
      const res=[]; const stack=__all.filter(x=>x.parent_id===rootId);
      while(stack.length){ const n=stack.pop(); res.push(n); stack.push(...__all.filter(x=>x.parent_id===n.id)); }
      return res;
    }
    const descendants = __descendants(prj.id);


    const doneCount = descendants.filter(x=>x.status==='done').length;
    const cashPct0 = (prj.budget_plan>0) ? (prj.budget_spent/prj.budget_plan*100) : 0;
    const progressAuto0 = descendants.length ? (doneCount/descendants.length*100) : cashPct0;
    const progressAuto = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, isFinite(progressAuto0)?progressAuto0:0));

    const undoneCount = (descendants.length||0) - doneCount;
    const riskAuto0 = descendants.length ? (undoneCount/descendants.length*100) : ((prj.budget_plan>0) ? Math.max(0,(1 - (prj.budget_spent/prj.budget_plan))*100) : 0);
    const riskAuto = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, isFinite(riskAuto0)?riskAuto0:0));

        $('kvMain').innerHTML = `      <div><b>Описание</b></div><div><div class="collapsible">${escapeHtml(prj.description||'')}</div><div class="collapsible-toggle">Развернуть</div></div>
      <div><b>Классификация</b></div><div>${escapeHtml(prj.classification||'—')}</div>
      <div><b>Выполнение, %</b></div><div><div class="collapsible">${escapeHtml(prj.execution||'')}</div><div class="collapsible-toggle">Развернуть</div></div>
      <div><b>Владелец</b></div><div>${escapeHtml(prj.owner||'—')}</div>
      <div><b>Руководитель</b></div><div>${escapeHtml(prj.responsible||'—')}</div>
      <div><b>Ответственный</b></div><div>${escapeHtml(prj.accountable||prj.responsible||'—')}</div>
      <div><b>Подрядчик</b></div><div>${escapeHtml(prj.vendor||'—')}</div>
      <div><b>Категория</b></div><div>${escapeHtml(prj.category||'—')}</div>
      <div><b>Местоположение</b></div><div>${escapeHtml(prj.location||'—')}</div>
      <div><b>Атрибуты объекта</b></div><div>${
        (()=>{
          const parts = [];
          if (prj.attr_okc) parts.push('Объект является ОКС под контролем Минстроя РФ');
          if (prj.attr_critical) parts.push('Объект является особо важным');
          return parts.length ? parts.map(escapeHtml).join('<br>') : '—';
        })()
      }</div>
      <div><b>Финансовые инструменты</b></div><div>${escapeHtml(prj.fin_tools||'—')}</div>
`;

    // quick edit init
    $('f_status').value = prj.status||'planned';
    const vcEl = $('f_viz_classifier'); if (vcEl) vcEl.value = prj.viz_classifier || '';
    $('f_progress').value = (Math.round(progressAuto*10)/10);
    const fRiskEl = $('f_risk'); if (fRiskEl) fRiskEl.value = (Math.round(riskAuto*10)/10);
    
    const startPlan = prj.start_plan || prj.start || '';
    const endPlan = prj.end_plan || prj.due || '';
    const startForecast = prj.start_forecast || '';
    const endForecast = prj.end_forecast || '';
    const startFact = prj.start_fact || '';
    const endFact = prj.end_fact || '';

    const bodyDates = $('pf_dates_body');
    if (bodyDates){
      const s1 = $('f_start_plan'); if (s1) s1.value = startPlan;
      const e1 = $('f_end_plan'); if (e1) e1.value = endPlan;
      const s2 = $('f_start_forecast'); if (s2) s2.value = startForecast;
      const e2 = $('f_end_forecast'); if (e2) e2.value = endForecast;
      const s3 = $('f_start_fact'); if (s3) s3.value = startFact;
      const e3 = $('f_end_fact'); if (e3) e3.value = endFact;
    }

    // Инициализация экономики
    const ecoDefaults = {plan:0, allocated:0, contracted:0, paid:0};
    const ecoState = Object.assign({fb:{},kb:{},mb:{},vb:{}}, prj.economy||{});
    ['fb','kb','mb','vb'].forEach(key=>{
      ecoState[key] = Object.assign({}, ecoDefaults, ecoState[key]||{});
    });
    document.querySelectorAll('input.eco').forEach(inp=>{
      const src = inp.getAttribute('data-src');
      const field = inp.getAttribute('data-field');
      const row = ecoState[src] || ecoDefaults;
      inp.value = row[field] ?? 0;
    });
    const ecoCommentEl = $('eco_comment'); if (ecoCommentEl) ecoCommentEl.value = prj.economy_comment||'';

    function recomputeFromEconomy(){
      const ecoRows = {fb:{...ecoDefaults},kb:{...ecoDefaults},mb:{...ecoDefaults},vb:{...ecoDefaults}};
      let planTotal = 0, paidTotal = 0;

      document.querySelectorAll('input.eco').forEach(inp=>{
        const src = inp.getAttribute('data-src');
        const field = inp.getAttribute('data-field');
        const v = +inp.value||0;
        if (!ecoRows[src]) ecoRows[src] = {...ecoDefaults};
        ecoRows[src][field] = v;
        if (field==='plan') planTotal += v;
        if (field==='paid') paidTotal += v;
      });

      const hasDesc = descendants && descendants.length>0;
      let prog = 0, risk = 0;
      if (hasDesc){
        const done = descendants.filter(x=>x.status==='done').length;
        prog = descendants.length ? (done/descendants.length*100) : 0;
        risk = descendants.length ? ((descendants.length - done)/descendants.length*100) : 0;
      } else {
        prog = (planTotal>0 && isFinite(paidTotal/planTotal)) ? (paidTotal/planTotal*100) : 0;
        risk = (planTotal>0 && isFinite(paidTotal/planTotal)) ? Math.max(0,(1 - paidTotal/planTotal)*100) : 0;
      }
      $('f_progress').value = (Math.round(prog*10)/10);
      const riskEl = $('f_risk'); if (riskEl) riskEl.value = (Math.round(risk*10)/10);

      // KPI
      const cashPct = (planTotal>0 && isFinite(paidTotal/planTotal)) ? (paidTotal/planTotal*100) : 0;
      const cashRounded = Math.round(cashPct*10)/10;
      const diff = cashRounded - (+$('f_progress').value||0);

      const totalPlanEl = $('eco_total_plan'); if (totalPlanEl) totalPlanEl.value = planTotal;
      const totalPaidEl = $('eco_total_paid'); if (totalPaidEl) totalPaidEl.value = paidTotal;
      const cashEl = $('eco_cash_pct'); if (cashEl) cashEl.value = cashRounded;
      const diffEl = $('eco_cash_vs_progress'); if (diffEl) diffEl.value = Math.round(diff*10)/10;

      // Подсветка рисков по строкам
      document.querySelectorAll('input.eco').forEach(inp=>{
        inp.classList.remove('eco-warning','eco-error');
      });
      Object.entries(ecoRows).forEach(([src,row])=>{
        const plan = row.plan||0, allocated=row.allocated||0, contracted=row.contracted||0, paid=row.paid||0;
        if (allocated < plan){
          const cell = document.querySelector(`input.eco[data-src="${src}"][data-field="allocated"]`);
          if (cell) cell.classList.add('eco-warning');
        }
        if (paid > contracted){
          const cell = document.querySelector(`input.eco[data-src="${src}"][data-field="paid"]`);
          if (cell) cell.classList.add('eco-error');
        }
      });
    }

    recomputeFromEconomy();
    document.querySelectorAll('input.eco').forEach(inp=>{
      inp.addEventListener('input', recomputeFromEconomy);
    });

    // Сворачивание длинных текстов
    document.querySelectorAll('#kvMain .collapsible-toggle').forEach(btn=>{
      btn.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
        const box = btn.previousElementSibling;
        if (!box) return;
        const expanded = box.classList.toggle('expanded');
        btn.textContent = expanded ? 'Свернуть' : 'Развернуть';
      });
    });
('input', ()=>{computeCash(); computeProgress(); computeRisk();});

    // children list with focus-on-branch
    $('childrenBox').innerHTML = children.length ? (
      '<ul style="margin:0;padding-left:16px">'+children.map(c=>`<li><a href="#" data-focus="${c.id}">${escapeHtml(c.name)}</a> <span class="code">${escapeHtml(c.code||'')}</span></li>`).join('')+'</ul>'
    ) : 'Контрольных точек нет';
    document.querySelectorAll('[data-focus]').forEach(a=> a.addEventListener('click', (e)=>{ e.preventDefault(); focusNode(a.getAttribute('data-focus')); }));
  }

  // Materials
  function renderFiles(prj){
    const tbody = $('tblFiles').querySelector('tbody');
    const items = (prj.attachments||[]);
    tbody.innerHTML = items.length ? items.map(a=>`
      <tr>
        <td>${escapeHtml(a.name)}</td>
        <td>${escapeHtml(a.type||'')}</td>
        <td>${(a.size||0)} Б</td>
        <td>${escapeHtml(a.who||'')}</td>
        <td>${a.t.slice(0,19).replace('T',' ')}</td>
        <td><a download="${escapeHtml(a.name)}" href="${a.data}" class="btn-ghost">Скачать</a>
            <button data-id="${a.id}" class="btn-ghost del">Удалить</button></td>
      </tr>`).join('') : `<tr><td colspan="6"><small>Материалов нет</small></td></tr>`;
    tbody.querySelectorAll('button.del').forEach(b=> b.onclick = ()=>{
      const id=b.getAttribute('data-id');
      prj.attachments = (prj.attachments||[]).filter(x=>x.id!==id);
      setProject(prj);
      renderFiles(prj);
      pushHistory(prj, 'Удалён материал');
    });
  }

  // History
  function renderHistory(prj){
    const tbody = $('tblHistory').querySelector('tbody');
    const arr = prj.history||[];
    tbody.innerHTML = arr.length ? arr.map(h=> `<tr><td>${h.t.slice(0,19).replace('T',' ')}</td><td>${escapeHtml(h.who)}</td><td>${escapeHtml(h.event)}</td></tr>`).join('')
      : `<tr><td colspan="3"><small>История изменений появится здесь</small></td></tr>`;
  }

  // ===== Tree view state & helpers =====
const stage = $('treeStage');
const canvas = $('treeCanvas');
const overlay = $('treeOverlay');
const mini = document.getElementById('miniMap');

let view = {x:0, y:0, k:1};          // pan/zoom
let compact = false;
let nodePos = {};                    // id -> {x,y} in scene coords

// UI state
let filterMode = 'all';              // all | active | overdue
let showCritical = false;
let searchQuery = '';

// Collapse state (persist per user)
const COLLAPSE_KEY = 'munart_tree_collapsed';
const collapsed = new Set((()=>{ try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(COLLAPSE_KEY)||'[]')||[]; }catch(_){ return []; }})());

function saveCollapsed(){
  try{ localStorage.setItem(COLLAPSE_KEY, JSON.stringify(Array.from(collapsed))); }catch(_){}
}

function applyView(){
  stage.style.transform = `translate(${view.x}px, ${view.y}px) scale(${view.k})`;
  renderMiniMapViewport();
}
function resetView(){ view={x:0,y:0,k:1}; applyView(); }

// Zoom with wheel
stage.parentElement.addEventListener('wheel', (e)=>{
  e.preventDefault();
  const delta = -Math.sign(e.deltaY) * 0.1;
  const k0 = view.k;
  const k1 = Math.min(3, Math.max(0.5, k0*(1+delta)));
  const rect = stage.getBoundingClientRect();
  const cx = e.clientX - rect.left;
  const cy = e.clientY - rect.top;
  view.x = cx - (cx - view.x) * (k1/k0);
  view.y = cy - (cy - view.y) * (k1/k0);
  view.k = k1;
  applyView();
}, {passive:false});

// Pan with mouse
let dragging=false, sx=0, sy=0, ox=0, oy=0;
stage.parentElement.addEventListener('mousedown', (e)=>{ dragging=true; sx=e.clientX; sy=e.clientY; ox=view.x; oy=view.y; });
window.addEventListener('mousemove', (e)=>{ if(!dragging) return; view.x = ox + (e.clientX - sx); view.y = oy + (e.clientY - sy); applyView(); });
window.addEventListener('mouseup', ()=> dragging=false);

// Controls
const chipCompact = document.getElementById('chipCompact');
if (chipCompact) chipCompact.onclick = ()=>{ compact = !compact; chipCompact.classList.toggle('active', compact); drawTree(getProject()); };

const chipCritical = document.getElementById('chipCritical');
if (chipCritical) chipCritical.onclick = ()=>{ showCritical = !showCritical; chipCritical.classList.toggle('active', showCritical); drawTree(getProject()); };

const chipReset = document.getElementById('chipReset');
if (chipReset) chipReset.onclick = ()=> resetView();

const filterEl = document.getElementById('treeFilter');
if (filterEl) filterEl.addEventListener('change', ()=>{ filterMode = filterEl.value || 'all'; drawTree(getProject()); });

const searchEl = document.getElementById('treeSearch');
if (searchEl){
  searchEl.addEventListener('input', ()=>{ searchQuery = (searchEl.value||'').trim(); drawTree(getProject()); });
  searchEl.addEventListener('keydown', (e)=>{
    if (e.key === 'Enter'){
      e.preventDefault();
      const q = (searchEl.value||'').trim();
      if (!q) return;
      const hit = findFirstMatchId(q);
      if (hit) focusNode(hit);
    }
    if (e.key === 'Escape'){
      searchEl.value=''; searchQuery=''; drawTree(getProject());
    }
  });
}

function focusNode(id){
  const pt = nodePos[id]; if (!pt) return;
  const wrap = document.querySelector('.canvasWrap');
  const cx = wrap.clientWidth/2, cy = wrap.clientHeight/2;
  view.x = cx - pt.x*view.k;
  view.y = cy - pt.y*view.k;
  applyView();
  const el = overlay.querySelector(`[data-id="${id}"]`);
  if (el){ el.classList.add('match'); setTimeout(()=> el.classList.remove('match'), 900); }
}

// ---- Minimap helpers ----
let _miniScene = {W:0,H:0,ox:0,oy:0,s:1,mw:220,mh:160};
function renderMiniMap(scene, nodes, edges){
  if (!mini) return;
  const dpr = Math.max(1, window.devicePixelRatio||1);
  const mw = mini.clientWidth || 220;
  const mh = mini.clientHeight || 160;
  mini.width = Math.floor(mw*dpr);
  mini.height = Math.floor(mh*dpr);
  const ctx = mini.getContext('2d');
  ctx.setTransform(dpr,0,0,dpr,0,0);
  ctx.clearRect(0,0,mw,mh);

  const W = scene.W || 1;
  const H = scene.H || 1;
  const s = Math.min(mw / W, mh / H);
  const ox = (mw - W*s) / 2;
  const oy = (mh - H*s) / 2;
  _miniScene = {W,H,ox,oy,s,mw,mh};

  // edges
  ctx.lineWidth = 1;
  ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(148,163,184,.35)';
  edges.forEach(([a,b])=>{
    const pa = nodes.get(a), pb = nodes.get(b);
    if (!pa || !pb) return;
    ctx.beginPath();
    ctx.moveTo(ox + pa.x*s, oy + pa.y*s);
    ctx.lineTo(ox + pb.x*s, oy + pb.y*s);
    ctx.stroke();
  });

  // nodes
  nodes.forEach((p)=>{
    ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(226,232,240,.85)';
    ctx.fillRect(ox + (p.x-2)*s, oy + (p.y-2)*s, 4*s, 4*s);
  });

  renderMiniMapViewport();
}

function renderMiniMapViewport(){
  if (!mini) return;
  const ctx = mini.getContext('2d');
  if (!ctx) return;
  const {W,H,ox,oy,s,mw,mh} = _miniScene;
  if (!W || !H) return;

  // clear only overlay by redrawing minimap on drawTree; here just draw viewport rectangle
  // To avoid "ghosting", we clear the whole and rely on drawTree to repaint. If minimap exists but not repainted yet, skip.
  // (Viewport will be drawn after renderMiniMap.)
  // NOTE: When applyView is called often, this keeps it lightweight.
  // We'll draw a semi-transparent overlay rectangle to "refresh" previous viewport.
  ctx.save();
  ctx.setTransform(Math.max(1, window.devicePixelRatio||1),0,0,Math.max(1, window.devicePixelRatio||1),0,0);
  // Draw a subtle veil (very light) to soften previous viewport frames without full redraw
  ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(2,6,23,.06)';
  ctx.fillRect(0,0,mw,mh);

  const wrap = document.querySelector('.canvasWrap');
  const vx = (-view.x) / view.k;
  const vy = (-view.y) / view.k;
  const vw = wrap.clientWidth / view.k;
  const vh = wrap.clientHeight / view.k;

  ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(59,130,246,.9)';
  ctx.lineWidth = 2;
  ctx.strokeRect(ox + vx*s, oy + vy*s, vw*s, vh*s);
  ctx.restore();
}

if (mini){
  mini.addEventListener('click', (e)=>{
    const rect = mini.getBoundingClientRect();
    const mx = e.clientX - rect.left;
    const my = e.clientY - rect.top;
    const {W,H,ox,oy,s} = _miniScene;
    const sx = (mx - ox) / s;
    const sy = (my - oy) / s;

    const wrap = document.querySelector('.canvasWrap');
    const cx = wrap.clientWidth/2, cy = wrap.clientHeight/2;
    view.x = cx - sx*view.k;
    view.y = cy - sy*view.k;
    applyView();
  });
}

// Helper: find first match among rendered nodes
function findFirstMatchId(q){
  const qq = (q||'').toLowerCase();
  const prj0 = getProject(); if (!prj0) return null;
  const all = load();
  const els = Array.from(overlay.querySelectorAll('.branchCard'));
  for (const el of els){
    const id = el.getAttribute('data-id');
    const p = (prj0.id===id) ? prj0 : all.find(x=>x.id===id);
    if (p && (p.name||'').toLowerCase().includes(qq)) return p.id;
  }
  const hit = all.find(x=> (x.name||'').toLowerCase().includes(qq));
  return hit ? hit.id : null;
}

// ===== Drawing =====
  function drawTree(prj){
  nodePos = {};
  const today = new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10);
  const isOverdue = (p)=> !!(p && p.due && p.due < today && p.status!=='done');
  const isActive  = (p)=> !!(p && (p.status||'') !== 'done');

  const iconFor = (p)=>{
    const t = (p && (p.pet_type||p.type||'')) ? (p.pet_type||p.type) : '';
    const s = (t||'').toLowerCase();
    if (s.includes('инфра') || s.includes('оборуд') || s.includes('тех')) return '⚙️';
    if (s.includes('исслед') || s.includes('аналит') || s.includes('док')) return '📄';
    return '⛏️';
  };

  const wrap = document.querySelector('.canvasWrap');
  const dpr = Math.max(1, window.devicePixelRatio||1);

  // Reset overlay
  overlay.innerHTML = '';

  const all = load();
  const childrenOf = (id)=> all.filter(p=>p.parent_id===id);

  // ---- Build hierarchy (respect collapse) ----
  function build(id, depth){
    const data = (id===prj.id) ? prj : all.find(x=>x.id===id);
    const isCollapsed = collapsed.has(id) && depth>0;
    const kids = isCollapsed ? [] : childrenOf(id).map(ch=>build(ch.id, depth+1));
    return { id, data, depth, kids, h:0, x:0, y:0, __collapsed:isCollapsed };
  }
  let root = build(prj.id, 0);

  // ---- Filter / prune (keep ancestors if any descendant matches) ----
  function keepSelf(n){
    const p = n.data||{};
    if (filterMode==='active') return isActive(p);
    if (filterMode==='overdue') return isOverdue(p);
    return true;
  }
  function prune(n){
    const kids = (n.kids||[]).map(prune).filter(Boolean);
    const keep = (n.depth===0) || keepSelf(n) || kids.length>0;
    if (!keep) return null;
    n.kids = kids;
    return n;
  }
  root = prune(root) || root;

  // ---- Empty state ----
  if (!root.kids.length){
    const W0 = wrap.clientWidth, H0 = wrap.clientHeight;
    canvas.width = Math.floor(W0*dpr); canvas.height = Math.floor(H0*dpr);
    canvas.style.width = W0+'px'; canvas.style.height = H0+'px';
    overlay.style.width = W0+'px'; overlay.style.height = H0+'px';
    stage.style.width = W0+'px'; stage.style.height = H0+'px';
    const ctx0 = canvas.getContext('2d'); ctx0.setTransform(dpr,0,0,dpr,0,0);
    ctx0.clearRect(0,0,W0,H0);
    ctx0.fillStyle = 'rgba(255,255,255,.65)';
    ctx0.font = '12px system-ui, sans-serif';
    ctx0.textAlign = 'center';
    ctx0.fillText('Нет элементов по выбранному фильтру', W0*0.5, H0*0.5);
    renderMiniMap({W:W0,H:H0}, new Map(), []);
    return;
  }

  // ---- Layout constants ----
  const cardWMain = compact ? 240 : 300;
  const cardWSub  = compact ? 210 : 240;
  const cardHMain = compact ? 64  : 86;
  const cardHSub  = compact ? 56  : 72;
  const vGap = compact ? 18 : 26;
  const hGap = compact ? 80 : 110;
  const padX = 36;
  const padY = 30;

  function nodeCardW(n){
    if (n.depth===0) return cardWMain;
    return (n.depth===1) ? cardWMain : cardWSub;
  }
  function nodeCardH(n){
    if (n.depth===0) return cardHMain;
    return (n.depth===1) ? cardHMain : cardHSub;
  }

  // ---- Measure subtree heights (tidy tree) ----
  function measure(n){
    const selfH = nodeCardH(n);
    if (!n.kids.length){ n.h = selfH; return n.h; }
    let sum = 0;
    n.kids.forEach(k=>{ sum += measure(k); });
    const kidsH = sum + vGap*(n.kids.length-1);
    n.h = Math.max(selfH, kidsH);
    return n.h;
  }
  measure(root);

  // ---- Assign positions ----
  let maxX = 0, maxY = 0;
  function assign(n, x, yTop){
    const centerY = yTop + n.h/2;
    n.x = x;
    n.y = centerY;
    maxX = Math.max(maxX, x + nodeCardW(n));
    maxY = Math.max(maxY, yTop + n.h);

    if (!n.kids.length) return;

    const blockH = n.kids.reduce((a,k)=>a+k.h,0) + vGap*(n.kids.length-1);
    let cyTop = centerY - blockH/2;

    n.kids.forEach((k)=>{
      assign(k, x + nodeCardW(n) + hGap, cyTop);
      cyTop += k.h + vGap;
    });
  }
  assign(root, padX, padY);

  // ---- Resize stage/canvas to scene ----
  const W = Math.max(wrap.clientWidth, Math.ceil(maxX + padX));
  const H = Math.max(wrap.clientHeight, Math.ceil(maxY + padY));

  stage.style.width = W+'px';
  stage.style.height = H+'px';

  canvas.width = Math.floor(W*dpr); canvas.height = Math.floor(H*dpr);
  canvas.style.width = W+'px'; canvas.style.height = H+'px';

  overlay.style.width = W+'px';
  overlay.style.height = H+'px';

  const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
  ctx.setTransform(dpr,0,0,dpr,0,0);
  ctx.clearRect(0,0,W,H);

  // ---- Critical path (heuristic) ----
  const criticalEdges = new Set();
  if (showCritical){
    function scoreNode(p){
      const ov = isOverdue(p) ? 8 : 0;
      const act = isActive(p) ? 2 : 0;
      return ov + act + 1;
    }
    function best(n){
      if (!n.kids.length) return {score: scoreNode(n.data||{}), path:[n]};
      let bestChild = {score:-1, path:[]};
      for (const k of n.kids){
        const r = best(k);
        if (r.score > bestChild.score) bestChild = r;
      }
      return {score: scoreNode(n.data||{}) + bestChild.score, path:[n, ...bestChild.path]};
    }
    const path = best(root).path;
    for (let i=0;i<path.length-1;i++){
      criticalEdges.add(path[i].id + '->' + path[i+1].id);
    }
  }

  // ---- Collect nodes/edges for minimap ----
  const miniNodes = new Map();
  const miniEdges = [];

  // ---- Draw connectors ----
  function drawEdge(from, to){
    const key = from.id + '->' + to.id;
    const critical = criticalEdges.has(key);

    const fromW = nodeCardW(from);
    const x1 = from.x + fromW;
    const y1 = from.y;
    const x2 = to.x;
    const y2 = to.y;

    const c = Math.max(40, (x2 - x1) * 0.45);
    ctx.beginPath();
    ctx.moveTo(x1, y1);
    ctx.bezierCurveTo(x1 + c, y1, x2 - c, y2, x2, y2);

    ctx.strokeStyle = critical ? 'rgba(59,130,246,.95)' : 'rgba(148,163,184,.42)';
    ctx.lineWidth = critical ? 3.5 : 2;
    ctx.setLineDash(critical ? [6,6] : []);
    ctx.stroke();
    ctx.setLineDash([]);

    // anchor dots
    ctx.beginPath();
    ctx.arc(x1, y1, 3.2, 0, Math.PI*2);
    ctx.arc(x2, y2, 3.2, 0, Math.PI*2);
    ctx.fillStyle = critical ? 'rgba(59,130,246,.95)' : 'rgba(147,197,253,.9)';
    ctx.fill();

    miniEdges.push([from.id, to.id]);
  }

  function walkEdges(n){
    n.kids.forEach(k=>{
      drawEdge(n, k);
      walkEdges(k);
    });
  }
  walkEdges(root);

  // ---- Cards ----
  const matches = new Set();
  if (searchQuery){
    const q = searchQuery.toLowerCase();
    (function collect(n){
      const p = n.data||{};
      if ((p.name||'').toLowerCase().includes(q) || (p.code||'').toLowerCase().includes(q)) matches.add(n.id);
      n.kids.forEach(collect);
    })(root);
  }

  function injectNodeCard(n){
    const p = n.data || {};
    nodePos[p.id] = {x: n.x, y: n.y};
    miniNodes.set(p.id, {x:n.x, y:n.y});

    const card = document.createElement('div');
    const depth = n.depth;
    const cls = (depth===0 || depth===1) ? 'branchCard main' : 'branchCard sub';
    card.className = cls + (compact ? ' compact' : '');
    if (matches.has(p.id)) card.classList.add('match');
    card.setAttribute('data-id', p.id);

    const due = p.due ? p.due : '—';
    const st = ({'planned':'Запланирован','in_progress':'В работе','on_hold':'На паузе','done':'Завершён'})[p.status] || (p.status||'');
    const prog = (+p.progress||0);
    const ico = (depth===0) ? '' : iconFor(p);

    const hasKids = (childrenOf(p.id).length>0); // original children count (before prune/collapse)
    const isCollapsed = collapsed.has(p.id) && depth>0;
    const toggleLabel = isCollapsed ? '▶' : '▼';

    const head = (depth===0)
      ? `<div class="nodeHead"><div class="nodeTitle">${escapeHtml(p.name||'Проект')}</div></div>`
      : `<div class="nodeHead"><span class="nodeIcon" title="${escapeHtml(p.pet_type||'')}">${ico}</span><div class="nodeTitle">${escapeHtml(p.name||'')}</div>${hasKids ? `<button class="nodeToggle" title="Свернуть/развернуть">${toggleLabel}</button>` : ''}</div>`;

    const body = (depth===0)
      ? `<div class="code">${escapeHtml(p.code||'')}</div><small>${escapeHtml(st)} • ${prog}% • Срок: ${escapeHtml(due)}</small>`
      : (depth===1)
        ? `<div class="code">${escapeHtml(p.code||'')}</div><small>${escapeHtml(st)} • ${prog}% • Срок: ${escapeHtml(due)}</small>`
        : `<small>${escapeHtml(p.code||'')} • ${prog}% • ${escapeHtml(due)}</small>`;

    card.innerHTML = head + body;

    card.style.left = n.x + 'px';
    card.style.top  = (n.y - nodeCardH(n)/2) + 'px';

    // toggle collapse
    const btn = card.querySelector('.nodeToggle');
    if (btn){
      btn.addEventListener('click', (ev)=>{
        ev.stopPropagation();
        const id = p.id;
        if (collapsed.has(id)) collapsed.delete(id); else collapsed.add(id);
        saveCollapsed();
        drawTree(getProject());
      });
    }

    // navigation (card click)
    card.addEventListener('click', (ev)=>{
      ev.stopPropagation();
      location.href = 'project_passport_offline.html?id='+encodeURIComponent(p.id);
    });

    overlay.appendChild(card);
  }

  function walkCards(n){
    injectNodeCard(n);
    n.kids.forEach(walkCards);
  }
  walkCards(root);

  // ---- Subtle left guide line ----
  ctx.beginPath();
  ctx.moveTo(padX - 18, padY - 10);
  ctx.lineTo(padX - 18, H - padY + 10);
  const lg = ctx.createLinearGradient(padX-18, padY-10, padX-18, H-padY+10);
  lg.addColorStop(0, 'rgba(56,189,248,.85)');
  lg.addColorStop(1, 'rgba(249,115,22,.65)');
  ctx.strokeStyle = lg;
  ctx.lineWidth = 6;
  ctx.lineCap = 'round';
  ctx.stroke();

  // ---- Minimap ----
  renderMiniMap({W,H}, miniNodes, miniEdges);
}

// Utils
  function escapeHtml(s){ return (s??'').toString().replace(/[&<>"]/g, c=>({ '&':'&amp;','<':'&lt;','>':'&gt;','\"':'&quot;' }[c])); }

  // Wire tabs
  document.querySelectorAll('.tab').forEach(t=> t.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
    const id = t.getAttribute('data-tab');
    document.querySelectorAll('.tab').forEach(n=> n.classList.remove('active'));
    t.classList.add('active');
    document.querySelectorAll('.tabpage').forEach(p=> p.classList.remove('active'));
    $('tab-'+id).classList.add('active');
    if (id==='tree'){ drawTree(getProject()); }
  }));

  // Back behavior
  $('btnBack').onclick = ()=>{
    if (document.referrer && document.referrer!==location.href){ history.back(); return; }
    for(let i=0;i<backTargets.length;i++){ try{ location.href = backTargets[i]; return; }catch(_){ } }
  };

  // Edit quick save
  $('btnSaveQuick').onclick = ()=>{
    const prj = getProject(); if(!prj) return;
    const before = JSON.parse(JSON.stringify(prj));
    prj.status = $('f_status').value;
    prj.viz_classifier = $('f_viz_classifier') ? $('f_viz_classifier').value : '';
    prj.progress = +$('f_progress').value||0;

    const s1 = $('f_start_plan') ? $('f_start_plan').value : '';
    const e1 = $('f_end_plan') ? $('f_end_plan').value : '';
    const s2 = $('f_start_forecast') ? $('f_start_forecast').value : '';
    const e2 = $('f_end_forecast') ? $('f_end_forecast').value : '';
    const s3 = $('f_start_fact') ? $('f_start_fact').value : '';
    const e3 = $('f_end_fact') ? $('f_end_fact').value : '';

    prj.start_plan = s1;
    prj.end_plan = e1;
    prj.start_forecast = s2;
    prj.end_forecast = e2;
    prj.start_fact = s3;
    prj.end_fact = e3;

    prj.start = prj.start_plan || prj.start || '';
    prj.due = prj.end_plan || prj.end_forecast || prj.end_fact || prj.due || '';

    // считываем экономику из таблицы
    const eco = {fb:{},kb:{},mb:{},vb:{}};
    document.querySelectorAll('input.eco').forEach(inp=>{
      const src = inp.getAttribute('data-src');
      const field = inp.getAttribute('data-field');
      if (!eco[src]) eco[src] = {};
      eco[src][field] = +inp.value||0;
    });
    prj.economy = eco;

    // агрегированные значения для совместимости
    let planTotal = 0, factTotal = 0;
    Object.values(eco).forEach(row=>{
      if (!row) return;
      planTotal += +row.plan||0;
      factTotal += +row.paid||0;
    });
    prj.budget_plan = planTotal;
    prj.budget_spent = factTotal;

    // комментарий по экономике
    const ecoCommentEl = $('eco_comment');
    if (ecoCommentEl) prj.economy_comment = ecoCommentEl.value||'';

    prj.updated_at = new Date().toISOString();
    setProject(prj);
    renderOverview(prj);
    let ch=[];
    if (before.status!==prj.status) ch.push('статус → '+prj.status);
    if ((before.viz_classifier||'') !== (prj.viz_classifier||'')) ch.push('визуализация → '+(prj.viz_classifier||'—'));
    if (before.progress!==prj.progress) ch.push('прогресс → '+prj.progress+'%');
    if (before.budget_plan!==prj.budget_plan) ch.push('план → '+prj.budget_plan);
    if (before.budget_spent!==prj.budget_spent) ch.push('факт → '+prj.budget_spent);
    if (before.due!==prj.due) ch.push('срок → '+prj.due);
    pushHistory(prj, 'Изменения: '+(ch.join(', ')||'без изменений'));
  };

  const pfToggle = $('pf_dates_toggle');
  if (pfToggle){
    const body = $('pf_dates_body');
    pfToggle.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
      if (!body) return;
      const opened = body.classList.toggle('open');
      pfToggle.textContent = opened ? 'Скрыть даты ▲' : 'Показать даты ▾';
    });
  }

  // Materials add
  $('btnAddFiles').onclick = ()=>{
    const files = $('fileInput').files; if (!files || !files.length) return;
    const prj = getProject(); prj.attachments = prj.attachments||[];
    let left = files.length;
    Array.from(files).forEach(f=>{
      const rd = new FileReader();
      rd.onload = ()=>{
        prj.attachments.push({id:'a'+Math.random().toString(36).slice(2,8), name:f.name, type:f.type, size:f.size, data: rd.result, t: new Date().toISOString(), who: curUser});
        left--; if (left===0){
          setProject(prj); renderFiles(prj); pushHistory(prj, 'Добавлены материалы: '+files.length+' файл(а)');
          $('fileInput').value='';
        }
      };
      rd.readAsDataURL(f);
    });
  };

  // Edit
  $('btnEdit').onclick = ()=>{
    if (document.referrer){ history.back(); return; }
    alert('Редактирование доступно со списка проектов (кнопка Редактировать).');
  };

  // New child modal
  const modal=$('newChildModal');
  const openNewChild = ()=>{ modal.classList.add('open'); modal.setAttribute('aria-hidden','false'); $('nc_name').focus(); };
  const btnHeader = document.getElementById('btnNewChild'); if(btnHeader) btnHeader.onclick = openNewChild;
  const btnTabs = document.getElementById('btnNewChildTabs'); if(btnTabs) btnTabs.onclick = openNewChild;
  const btnFab = document.getElementById('fabNewChild'); if(btnFab) btnFab.onclick = openNewChild;
  $('nc_cancel').onclick = ()=> { modal.classList.remove('open'); modal.setAttribute('aria-hidden','true'); };
  $('nc_save').onclick = ()=>{
    const prj = getProject(); if(!prj) return;
    const arr = load();
    const item = {
      id: uid(),
      name: $('nc_name').value.trim() || 'Контрольная точка',
      code: $('nc_code').value.trim() || ('SUB-'+Math.floor(Math.random()*9000+1000)),
      pet_type: $('nc_pet').value,
      status: $('nc_status').value,
      start: new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10),
      due: $('nc_due').value || '',
      budget_plan: +$('nc_bp').value || 0,
      budget_spent: 0,
      owner: prj.owner||'',
      category: prj.category||'',
      priority: 2,
      progress: 0,
      risk: 10,
      tags: [],
      description: '',
      parent_id: prj.id,
      updated_at: new Date().toISOString()
    };
    arr.unshift(item); saveAll(arr);
    modal.classList.remove('open'); modal.setAttribute('aria-hidden','true');
    pushHistory(prj, 'Создан пет‑проект: '+item.name);
    renderOverview(getProject());
    drawTree(getProject());
  };

  // Init
  const prj = getProject();
  if (!prj){ alert('Проект не найден'); }
  else {
    renderOverview(prj);
    renderFiles(prj);
    renderHistory(prj);
    drawTree(prj);
  }

  // Resize -> redraw (keeping view transform)
  new ResizeObserver(()=> drawTree(getProject())).observe(document.querySelector('.canvasWrap'));

})();</script>
</body>
</html>
===== END FILE: munart_ui\public\prototypes\project_passport_offline.html =====

<script>
(()=>{'use strict';
  const STORE='munart_projects_offline_light';

  const $ = (id)=>document.getElementById(id);
  const esc = (s)=>{
    const str = (s??'').toString();
    let out = '';
    for (let i=0;i<str.length;i++){
      const ch = str[i];
      if (ch==='&') out += '&amp;';
      else if (ch==='<') out += '&lt;';
      else if (ch==='>') out += '&gt;';
      else if (ch==='"') out += '&quot;';
      else out += ch;
    }
    return out;
  };
  const fmtInt = (n)=>{
    if (!isFinite(n)) return '0';
    const v = Math.round(Number(n));
    try{
      // Use ru-RU to get spaces as thousand separators in most browsers
      return new Intl.NumberFormat('ru-RU').format(v).split('\u00A0').join(' ');
    }catch(e){
      // Fallback: manual grouping
      const s = String(Math.abs(v));
      let out = '';
      for (let i=0;i<s.length;i++){
        const idx = s.length - i;
        out = s[idx-1] + out;
        if (i%3===2 && idx-1>0) out = ' ' + out;
      }
      return (v<0?'-':'') + out;
    }
  };
  const fmtPct = (x)=> (isFinite(x)? (Math.round(x*10)/10).toString().replace('.',',')+'%' : '0%');
  const toISO = (d)=> new Date(d).toISOString().slice(0,10);

  function loadProjects(){
    try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(STORE) || '[]') || []; }catch(e){ return []; }
  }

  function uniq(arr){
    return Array.from(new Set(arr.filter(Boolean))).sort((a,b)=>a.localeCompare(b,'ru'));
  }

  function statusLabel(s){
    return ({planned:'Запланирован', in_progress:'В работе', on_hold:'На паузе', done:'Завершён'})[s] || (s||'—');
  }

  function parseDate(s){
    if (!s) return null;
    const d = new Date(s);
    return isNaN(+d) ? null : d;
  }

  function inRange(d, from, to){
    if (!d) return true;
    if (from && d < from) return false;
    if (to && d > to) return false;
    return true;
  }

  function getSelectedMulti(sel){
    return Array.from(sel.selectedOptions).map(o=>o.value);
  }

  function ensureLegend(el, items){
    let lg = el.querySelector('.legend');
    if (!lg){ lg=document.createElement('div'); lg.className='legend'; el.appendChild(lg); }
    lg.innerHTML = items.map(it=>`<span><i style="background:${it.c}"></i>${esc(it.l)}</span>`).join('');
  }

  function palette(i){
    // deterministic soft-ish colors without external libs
    const hues = [210, 140, 30, 280, 0, 190, 110, 330, 250, 60, 160, 20];
    const h = hues[i % hues.length];
    return `hsl(${h} 70% 55%)`;
  }

  function donutChart(host, pairs){
    const w = host.clientWidth||640, h = host.clientHeight||360;
    const r = Math.min(w,h)/2 - 26;
    const cx=w/2, cy=h/2;
    const total = pairs.reduce((s,p)=>s+(+p.v||0),0);
    host.innerHTML = `<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none"></svg>`;
    const svg = host.querySelector('svg');

    if (total<=0){
      svg.innerHTML = `<circle cx="${cx}" cy="${cy}" r="${r}" fill="none" stroke="#e5e7eb" stroke-width="18"/>
        <text x="${cx}" y="${cy}" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="middle" font-size="12" fill="currentColor">нет данных</text>`;
      ensureLegend(host, pairs.map((p,i)=>({l:p.l,c:palette(i)})));
      return;
    }

    let start = -Math.PI/2;
    const items = [];
    pairs.forEach((p,i)=>{
      const v = +p.v||0;
      if (v<=0) return;
      const a = (v/total)*Math.PI*2;
      const end = start + a;
      const x1 = cx + r*Math.cos(start), y1 = cy + r*Math.sin(start);
      const x2 = cx + r*Math.cos(end), y2 = cy + r*Math.sin(end);
      const large = a > Math.PI ? 1 : 0;
      const c = palette(i);
      const d = `M ${cx} ${cy} L ${x1} ${y1} A ${r} ${r} 0 ${large} 1 ${x2} ${y2} Z`;
      svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<path d="${d}" fill="${c}" opacity=".92"></path>`);
      start = end;
      items.push({l:p.l, c});
    });

    // hole
    const r2 = r*0.62;
    svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<circle cx="${cx}" cy="${cy}" r="${r2}" fill="var(--panel)"></circle>`);
    svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<text x="${cx}" y="${cy-4}" text-anchor="middle" font-size="20" font-weight="800" fill="currentColor">${fmtInt(total)}</text>`);
    svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<text x="${cx}" y="${cy+18}" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" fill="currentColor" opacity=".75">суммарно</text>`);

    ensureLegend(host, items);
  }

  function barsChart(host, pairs, topN){
    const w = host.clientWidth||640, h = host.clientHeight||360;
    const p = 36;
    const data = pairs.slice().sort((a,b)=>(+b.v||0)-(+a.v||0)).slice(0, topN);
    const max = Math.max(...data.map(x=>+x.v||0), 1);
    host.innerHTML = `<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none"></svg>`;
    const svg = host.querySelector('svg');

    const n = Math.max(1,data.length);
    const bw = (w-2*p)/n * 0.66;
    const gap = ((w-2*p)-bw*n)/Math.max(1,n-1);

    const items=[];

    data.forEach((d,i)=>{
      const v = +d.v||0;
      const bh = (v/max)*(h-2*p);
      const x = p + i*(bw+gap);
      const y = h - p - bh;
      const c = palette(i);
      svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<rect x="${x}" y="${y}" width="${bw}" height="${bh}" rx="8" fill="${c}" opacity=".92"></rect>`);
      // value
      svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<text x="${x + bw/2}" y="${y-8}" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="currentColor" opacity=".8">${fmtInt(v)}</text>`);
      // label (trim)
      const lab = (d.l||'—').toString();
      const lab2 = lab.length>14 ? lab.slice(0,13)+'…' : lab;
      svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<text x="${x + bw/2}" y="${h-12}" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="currentColor" opacity=".75">${esc(lab2)}</text>`);

      items.push({l:lab, c});
    });

    ensureLegend(host, items);
  }

  function lineChart(host, points){
    const w = host.clientWidth||640, h = host.clientHeight||360;
    const p = 44;
    const arr = points.map(x=>+x.v||0);
    const max = Math.max(...arr,1), min = Math.min(...arr,0);
    const n = Math.max(1, points.length);

    const sx = (i)=> p + i*((w-2*p)/Math.max(1,n-1));
    const sy = (v)=> h - p - ((v-min)/(max-min||1))*(h-2*p);

    let d = `M ${sx(0)} ${sy(arr[0]||0)}`;
    for (let i=1;i<n;i++) d += ` L ${sx(i)} ${sy(arr[i]||0)}`;

    host.innerHTML = `<svg viewBox="0 0 ${w} ${h}" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="${d}" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"></path>
      <path d="${d} L ${sx(n-1)} ${h-p} L ${sx(0)} ${h-p} Z" fill="color-mix(in oklab,var(--accent) 18%, transparent)"></path>
    </svg>`;
    const svg = host.querySelector('svg');

    // points and x labels
    points.forEach((pt,i)=>{
      const x=sx(i), y=sy(+pt.v||0);
      svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<circle cx="${x}" cy="${y}" r="4.5" fill="var(--accent)"></circle>`);
      const lab = (pt.l||'').toString();
      svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<text x="${x}" y="${h-18}" text-anchor="middle" font-size="11" fill="currentColor" opacity=".75">${esc(lab)}</text>`);
    });

    // y labels (min/max)
    svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<text x="${14}" y="${p}" font-size="11" fill="currentColor" opacity=".65">${fmtInt(max)}</text>`);
    svg.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', `<text x="${14}" y="${h-p+4}" font-size="11" fill="currentColor" opacity=".65">${fmtInt(min)}</text>`);

    // legend stub
    ensureLegend(host, [{l:'Динамика', c:'var(--accent)'}]);
  }

  function build(){
    const all = loadProjects();
    $('dataHint').textContent = `${all.length} проектов`;

    // Fill dictionaries
    const classifications = uniq(all.map(x=>x.classification));
    const responsibles = uniq(all.map(x=>x.responsible));
    const owners = uniq(all.map(x=>x.owner));

    const cSel = $('classification');
    if (cSel && cSel.options.length<=1){
      cSel.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', classifications.map(v=>`<option value="${esc(v)}">${esc(v)}</option>`).join(''));
    }

    const rSel = $('responsible');
    if (rSel && rSel.options.length<=1){
      rSel.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', responsibles.map(v=>`<option value="${esc(v)}">${esc(v)}</option>`).join(''));
    }

    const oSel = $('owner');
    if (oSel && oSel.options.length<=1){
      oSel.insertAdjacentHTML('beforeend', owners.map(v=>`<option value="${esc(v)}">${esc(v)}</option>`).join(''));
    }

    // Read filters
    const scope = $('scope').value;
    const statuses = getSelectedMulti($('status'));
    const cls = $('classification').value;
    const resp = $('responsible').value;
    const owner = $('owner').value;
    const from = parseDate($('dateFrom').value);
    const to = parseDate($('dateTo').value);
    const topN = +$('topN').value || 8;

    // Apply filters
    let items = all.slice();

    if (scope==='main') items = items.filter(x=>!x.parent_id);
    else if (scope==='pet') items = items.filter(x=>!!x.parent_id);

    if (statuses.length) items = items.filter(x=>statuses.includes(x.status));

    if (cls && cls!=='__all__') items = items.filter(x=>(x.classification||'')===cls);
    if (resp && resp!=='__all__') items = items.filter(x=>(x.responsible||'')===resp);
    if (owner && owner!=='__all__') items = items.filter(x=>(x.owner||'')===owner);

    // Date range uses start_plan if available, else start
    items = items.filter(x=>{
      const d = parseDate(x.start_plan || x.start);
      return inRange(d, from, to);
    });

    $('fltCount').textContent = `в выборке: ${items.length}`;

    // KPIs
    const n = items.length;
    const done = items.filter(x=>x.status==='done').length;
    const undone = n - done;
    const factSum = items.reduce((s,x)=>s+(+x.budget_spent||0),0);
    const planSum = items.reduce((s,x)=>s+(+x.budget_plan||0),0);

    $('kpiN').textContent = fmtInt(n);
    $('kpiN2').textContent = n ? `доля от базы: ${fmtPct(n/Math.max(all.length,1)*100)}` : '—';
    $('kpiDone').textContent = fmtInt(done);
    $('kpiDone2').textContent = n ? `завершено: ${fmtPct(done/Math.max(n,1)*100)}` : '—';
    $('kpiUndone').textContent = fmtInt(undone);
    $('kpiUndone2').textContent = n ? `не завершено: ${fmtPct(undone/Math.max(n,1)*100)}` : '—';
    $('kpiFact').textContent = fmtInt(factSum);
    $('kpiFact2').textContent = planSum ? `план: ${fmtInt(planSum)}` : 'план: 0';

    // Active tags
    const tags = [];
    if (scope==='main') tags.push('Материнские');
    if (scope==='pet') tags.push('Пет‑проекты');
    if (cls && cls!=='__all__') tags.push(`Класс: ${cls}`);
    if (resp && resp!=='__all__') tags.push(`Ответств.: ${resp}`);
    if (owner && owner!=='__all__') tags.push(`Владелец: ${owner}`);
    if ($('dateFrom').value) tags.push(`с ${$('dateFrom').value}`);
    if ($('dateTo').value) tags.push(`по ${$('dateTo').value}`);
    const stLabels = statuses.map(statusLabel);
    if (stLabels.length && stLabels.length<4) tags.push(`Статусы: ${stLabels.join(', ')}`);
    $('activeTags').innerHTML = tags.map(t=>`<span class="pill">${esc(t)}</span>`).join('') || `<span class="muted">Фильтры не заданы (используется база/дефолт).</span>`;

    // Metric + grouping
    const metric = $('metric').value;
    const groupBy = $('groupBy').value;
    const chartPref = $('chartType').value;

    function metricValueForGroup(groupItems){
      if (metric==='count') return groupItems.length;
      if (metric==='budget_fact_sum') return groupItems.reduce((s,x)=>s+(+x.budget_spent||0),0);
      if (metric==='budget_plan_sum') return groupItems.reduce((s,x)=>s+(+x.budget_plan||0),0);
      if (metric==='undone_pct'){
        const N = groupItems.length;
        const d = groupItems.filter(x=>x.status==='done').length;
        return N ? ((N-d)/N*100) : 0;
      }
      if (metric==='done_pct'){
        const N = groupItems.length;
        const d = groupItems.filter(x=>x.status==='done').length;
        return N ? (d/N*100) : 0;
      }
      return groupItems.length;
    }

    function groupKeyLabel(x){
      if (groupBy==='status') return {k:(x.status||'—'), l:statusLabel(x.status)};
      if (groupBy==='classification') return {k:(x.classification||'—'), l:(x.classification||'—')};
      if (groupBy==='responsible') return {k:(x.responsible||'—'), l:(x.responsible||'—')};
      if (groupBy==='owner') return {k:(x.owner||'—'), l:(x.owner||'—')};
      return {k:'—', l:'—'};
    }

    // Build aggregated pairs or time points
    let title = '';
    const outMeta = [];

    const metricLabel = ({
      count:'Количество проектов',
      undone_pct:'Процент невыполненных',
      done_pct:'Процент завершённых',
      budget_fact_sum:'Сумма бюджета (факт)',
      budget_plan_sum:'Сумма бюджета (план)'
    })[metric] || metric;

    const groupLabel = ({
      status:'по статусам',
      classification:'по классификациям',
      responsible:'по ответственным',
      owner:'по владельцам',
      month_created:'по месяцам создания'
    })[groupBy] || groupBy;

    title = `${metricLabel} ${groupLabel}`;
    $('outTitle').textContent = title;

    outMeta.push(`метрика: ${metricLabel}`);
    outMeta.push(`группировка: ${groupLabel}`);
    $('outMeta').textContent = outMeta.join(' • ');

    const chartHost = $('chart');
    chartHost.innerHTML = '';

    // Decide chart type (auto)
    let chartType = chartPref;
    if (chartType==='auto'){
      if (groupBy==='month_created') chartType = 'line';
      else if (metric==='undone_pct' || metric==='done_pct') chartType = 'bars';
      else if (groupBy==='status') chartType = 'donut';
      else chartType = 'bars';
    }

    if (groupBy==='month_created'){
      // create points by month from created_at/updated_at/start_plan/start
      const buckets = new Map();
      items.forEach(x=>{
        const d = parseDate(x.created_at) || parseDate(x.updated_at) || parseDate(x.start_plan) || parseDate(x.start) || null;
        if (!d) return;
        const key = d.getFullYear()+'-'+String(d.getMonth()+1).padStart(2,'0');
        if (!buckets.has(key)) buckets.set(key, []);
        buckets.get(key).push(x);
      });
      const keys = Array.from(buckets.keys()).sort();
      const points = keys.map(k=>{
        const gi = buckets.get(k);
        return { l:k.slice(2).replace('-','.'), v: metricValueForGroup(gi) };
      });
      // If metric is percent in time points: fine
      lineChart(chartHost, points);
      return;
    }

    const groups = new Map();
    items.forEach(x=>{
      const gl = groupKeyLabel(x);
      if (!groups.has(gl.k)) groups.set(gl.k, {label: gl.l, arr: []});
      groups.get(gl.k).arr.push(x);
    });

    const pairs = Array.from(groups.values()).map((g)=>({ l:g.label, v: metricValueForGroup(g.arr) }));

    if (chartType==='donut'){
      // Donut expects absolute parts; if metric is percent, donut becomes misleading.
      // For percent metrics, fallback to bars automatically.
      if (metric==='undone_pct' || metric==='done_pct'){
        barsChart(chartHost, pairs, topN);
      } else {
        donutChart(chartHost, pairs);
      }
    } else if (chartType==='line'){
      // line needs ordering; we can approximate by sorting labels alpha
      const pts = pairs.slice().sort((a,b)=>(a.l||'').localeCompare(b.l||'', 'ru')).map(p=>({l:p.l, v:p.v}));
      lineChart(chartHost, pts);
    } else {
      barsChart(chartHost, pairs, topN);
    }
  }

  // Theme toggle
  function applyTheme(){
    const key='munart_theme';
    const saved = localStorage.getItem(key) || 'light';
    document.body.classList.toggle('theme-dark', saved==='dark');
    document.body.classList.toggle('theme-light', saved!=='dark');
  }
  $('btnTheme').addEventListener('click', ()=>{
    const key='munart_theme';
    const cur = localStorage.getItem(key) || 'light';
    localStorage.setItem(key, cur==='dark' ? 'light' : 'dark');
    applyTheme();
  });

  $('btnBack').addEventListener('click', ()=> history.back());
  $('btnBuild').addEventListener('click', build);
  // Secondary build button (in left panel)
  const b2 = $('btnBuild2');
  if (b2) b2.addEventListener('click', build);

  // Auto-rebuild on any parameter change (so user doesn't have to hunt for a button)
  const autoIds = ['metric','groupBy','chartType','status','classification','responsible','owner','dateFrom','dateTo','scope','topN'];
  autoIds.forEach(id=>{
    const el = $(id);
    if (!el) return;
    el.addEventListener('change', ()=>{ build(); });
    // for date inputs, also react on input
    el.addEventListener('input', ()=>{ build(); });
  });


  // Auto-run: fill lists and build once
  applyTheme();
  // Warm up selects and defaults
  const all = loadProjects();
  $('dataHint').textContent = `${all.length} проектов`;
  // Try set date range to last 12 months if not set
  const now = new Date();
  const from = new Date(now); from.setMonth(from.getMonth()-12);
  if (!$('dateFrom').value) $('dateFrom').value = toISO(from);
  if (!$('dateTo').value) $('dateTo').value = toISO(now);

  // initial build
  build();

  // Empty-state hint (no stored projects)
  if (!all || all.length===0){
    $('outTitle').textContent = 'Нет данных для построения';
    $('outMeta').textContent = 'В localStorage пока нет проектов. Откройте страницу «Проекты», создайте хотя бы 1 проект и вернитесь сюда.';
    const ch = $('chart');
    ch.innerHTML = `<div class="note" style="padding:18px;text-align:center">
      <div style="font-weight:800;font-size:16px;margin-bottom:6px">Проекты не найдены</div>
      <div>Система читает данные из <b>localStorage</b> (ключ: <b>${STORE}</b>).</div>
      <div style="margin-top:8px">Если вы запускаете страницу впервые — перейдите в «Проекты», сохраните данные и повторите.</div>
      <div style="margin-top:12px;display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap">
        <button class="btn" onclick="history.back()">← Назад</button>
        <button class="btn primary" onclick="location.reload()">Обновить</button>
      </div>
    </div>`;
  }



  // Tabs logic
  document.querySelectorAll('.tab').forEach(t=>{
    t.addEventListener('click',()=>{
      document.querySelectorAll('.tab').forEach(x=>x.classList.remove('active'));
      document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content').forEach(x=>x.classList.remove('active'));
      t.classList.add('active');
      const panel = document.getElementById('tab-'+t.dataset.tab);
      panel.classList.add('active');

      // When showing the map, force recalculation of canvas size and center on the city
      if(t.dataset.tab==='viz'){
        setTimeout(()=>{
          try{ window.__artemMapApi && window.__artemMapApi.home(); }catch(e){}
        }, 0);
      }
    });
  });

  
  // Artem map (OSM SHP export): pan/zoom + hover highlight (canvas, no external deps)
