  (function initArtemOsmCanvasMap(){
    const canvas = document.getElementById('artemMapCanvas');
    const hudTitle = document.getElementById('mapHudTitle');
    const hudValue = document.getElementById('mapHudValue');
    const hudHint  = document.getElementById('mapHudHint');
    const hudMeta  = document.getElementById('mapHudMeta');
    if(!canvas) return;

    const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d', { alpha: true });
    const bounds = OSM_ARTEM.bounds; // [minx,miny,maxx,maxy] in EPSG:3857 meters
    const world = {
      minx: bounds[0], miny: bounds[1], maxx: bounds[2], maxy: bounds[3],
      w: bounds[2]-bounds[0], h: bounds[3]-bounds[1],
    };

    function featureBbox(f){
      let minx=1e30, miny=1e30, maxx=-1e30, maxy=-1e30;
      const walk=(c)=>{
        if(!c) return;
        if(typeof c[0]==='number'){ // [x,y]
          const x=c[0], y=c[1];
          if(x<minx) minx=x; if(y<miny) miny=y; if(x>maxx) maxx=x; if(y>maxy) maxy=y;
        } else {
          for(const cc of c) walk(cc);
        }
      };
      walk(f.geom);
      return [minx,miny,maxx,maxy];
    }

    // Base polygons (OSM landuse/natural) — drawn as background only (no hover highlight)
    const basePolys = OSM_ARTEM.polys.map((p, idx)=>({...p, _id: idx, _bb: featureBbox(p)}));

    // Buildings (from OSM export). Drawn only on closer zoom levels.
    const buildingPolys = (OSM_ARTEM.buildings||[]).map((b, idx)=>({...b, _id: idx, _bb: featureBbox(b)}));


    // ---------------- Districts (hover only) ----------------
    // Strategy: build Voronoi cells from seed points (EPSG:3857) and clip to map bounds.
    // This keeps the OSM base untouched and makes hover work ONLY on districts.
    const DISTRICT_LIST = [
      {id:1, name:"Угловое", seedHint:["Угловое"], seed:[14704068.865,5362836.843]},
      {id:2, name:"Орбита", seedHint:["Орбита"], seed:[14711202.429,5367676.875]},
      {id:3, name:"Южный", seedHint:["Южный"], seed:[14720231.998,5367745.107]},
      {id:4, name:"Угольщик", seedHint:["Угольщик"], seed:[14721557.491,5367887.758]},
      {id:5, name:"Кневичи", seedHint:["Кневичи"], seed:[14715176.368,5372573.650]},
      {id:6, name:"Аэропорт", seedHint:["Аэропорт", "Кневичи"], seed:[14710976.368,5371373.650]},
      {id:7, name:"9 км - Севастопольская", seedHint:["Севастопольская", "9 км"], seed:[14707500.000,5364800.000]},
      {id:8, name:"Комсомольская - Углеразведка", seedHint:["Комсомольская", "Углеразведка"], seed:[14710500.000,5365400.000]},
      {id:9, name:"Базар - ДК - Центр", seedHint:["Центр", "ДК", "Базар", "Артём"], seed:[14713000.000,5365850.000]},
      {id:10, name:"Администрация - 19 школа", seedHint:["Администрация", "19"], seed:[14715200.000,5366050.000]},
      {id:11, name:"Трикотажка", seedHint:["Трикотажка"], seed:[14717000.000,5366700.000]},
      {id:12, name:"Бабушкино", seedHint:["Бабушкино"], seed:[14720000.000,5367150.000]},
      {id:13, name:"17 школа - Больница", seedHint:["Больница", "17"], seed:[14717500.000,5366100.000]},
      {id:14, name:"Кролевцы", seedHint:["Кролевцы"], seed:[14721870.788,5380100.091]},
      {id:15, name:"Заводской", seedHint:["Заводской", "Завод"], seed:[14725870.097,5382232.558]},
      {id:16, name:"Суражевка", seedHint:["Суражевка"], seed:[14730426.760,5376016.417]},
      {id:17, name:"Артёмовский", seedHint:["Артёмовский"], seed:[14729739.585,5368268.851]},
    ];

    
    function _normStr(s){
      return (s||'').toString().trim().toLowerCase().replace(/ё/g,'е');
    }
    function findLabelExact(labels, q){
      const nq = _normStr(q);
      if(!nq || !Array.isArray(labels)) return null;
      for(const lb of labels){
        const n = _normStr(lb && lb.name);
        if(n && n === nq) return lb;
      }
      return null;
    }
    function findLabelIncludes(labels, q){
      const nq = _normStr(q);
      if(!nq || !Array.isArray(labels)) return null;
      for(const lb of labels){
        const n = _normStr(lb && lb.name);
        if(n && n.includes(nq)) return lb;
      }
      return null;
    }
    function seedFromRoad(roads, q){
      const nq = _normStr(q);
      if(!nq || !Array.isArray(roads)) return null;
      let best=null;
      for(const r of roads){
        const rn = _normStr(r && r.name);
        if(!rn) continue;
        if(rn===nq || rn.includes(nq)){
          const g = r.geom;
          if(Array.isArray(g) && g.length>=2){
            const mid = g[Math.floor(g.length/2)];
            if(mid && mid.length>=2){
              best = {x: mid[0], y: mid[1]};
              break;
            }
          }
        }
      }
      return best;
    }

function dist2(ax,ay,bx,by){ const dx=ax-bx, dy=ay-by; return dx*dx+dy*dy; }

    function getSeedForDistrict(d){
      // Explicit seed overrides (EPSG:3857)
      if(d && Array.isArray(d.seed) && d.seed.length===2 && isFinite(d.seed[0]) && isFinite(d.seed[1])){
        return {x: d.seed[0], y: d.seed[1]};
      }
      // Prefer existing label points from OSM; fallback to heuristics (roads) and then map center.
      // NOTE: District borders are derived from Voronoi cells built from these seeds.
      // You can fine-tune borders by adjusting the SEED_OFFSETS below (in meters, EPSG:3857).
      const SEED_OFFSETS = {
        14: {dx: -2200, dy:  900},  // Кролевцы — чуть западнее/севернее
        15: {dx:  1800, dy:  700},  // Заводской — чуть восточнее/севернее
        16: {dx:  1600, dy: -400},  // Суражевка — чуть восточнее
        17: {dx:  1300, dy: -2400}, // ГРЭС — юго-восточнее
      };

      let best = null;
      for(const h of d.seedHint){
        const lb = findLabelExact(OSM_ARTEM.labels, h) || findLabelIncludes(OSM_ARTEM.labels, h);
        if(lb){ best = {x: lb.x, y: lb.y}; break; }
      }
      if(!best){
        // try to derive seed from roads by keyword
        for(const h of d.seedHint){
          const s = seedFromRoad(OSM_ARTEM.roads, h);
          if(s){ best = s; break; }
        }
      }
      if(!best){
        best = {x: (OSM_ARTEM.bounds[0]+OSM_ARTEM.bounds[2])/2, y: (OSM_ARTEM.bounds[1]+OSM_ARTEM.bounds[3])/2};
      }

      const off = SEED_OFFSETS[d.id];
      if(off){
        best = {x: best.x + off.dx, y: best.y + off.dy};
      }
      return best;
    }

    // Clip polygon by half-plane: (p - mid) · n <= 0 keeps the side closer to site A (see buildCells)
    function clipPolyHalfPlane(poly, mid, n){
      const out=[];
      const inside=(p)=> ((p[0]-mid[0])*n[0] + (p[1]-mid[1])*n[1]) <= 1e-9;
      const intersect=(a,b)=>{
        const ax=a[0]-mid[0], ay=a[1]-mid[1];
        const bx=b[0]-mid[0], by=b[1]-mid[1];
        const da=ax*n[0]+ay*n[1];
        const db=bx*n[0]+by*n[1];
        const t = da/(da-db+1e-15);
        return [a[0] + (b[0]-a[0])*t, a[1] + (b[1]-a[1])*t];
      };
      for(let i=0;i<poly.length;i++){
        const a=poly[i];
        const b=poly[(i+1)%poly.length];
        const ina=inside(a), inb=inside(b);
        if(ina && inb){ out.push(b); }
        else if(ina && !inb){ out.push(intersect(a,b)); }
        else if(!ina && inb){ out.push(intersect(a,b)); out.push(b); }
      }
      return out;
    }

    function buildVoronoiCells(sites, bbox){
      const [minx,miny,maxx,maxy]=bbox;
      const rect=[[minx,miny],[maxx,miny],[maxx,maxy],[minx,maxy]];
      const cells=[];
      for(let i=0;i<sites.length;i++){
        let poly=rect.slice();
        const A=sites[i];
        for(let j=0;j<sites.length;j++){
          if(i===j) continue;
          const B=sites[j];
          const mid=[(A.x+B.x)/2, (A.y+B.y)/2];
          const n=[(B.x-A.x), (B.y-A.y)]; // normal points towards B; keep <=0 => closer to A
          poly = clipPolyHalfPlane(poly, mid, n);
          if(poly.length<3) break;
        }
        cells.push(poly);
      }
      return cells;
    }

    const _sites = DISTRICT_LIST.map(d=>({d, ...getSeedForDistrict(d)}));
    const _cells = buildVoronoiCells(_sites, OSM_ARTEM.bounds);

    const districtPolys = _cells.map((ring, idx)=>{
      const d=_sites[idx].d;
      const geom=[ring.concat([ring[0]])]; // close ring for pointInPolygon
      return { kind:'district', name:d.name, id:d.id, geom, _bb: featureBbox({geom}) };
    }).sort((a,b)=>a.id-b.id);

    // --- Manual district shape tuning (to match user's hand-drawn zoning ~90%) ---
    // We post-process Voronoi cells by clipping them with simple axis-aligned windows.
    // This keeps the overall architecture intact, while allowing quick "cut top/bottom" edits.

    function _eqPt(a,b){ return Math.abs(a[0]-b[0])<1e-6 && Math.abs(a[1]-b[1])<1e-6; }

    // Sutherland–Hodgman polygon clip against a single axis-aligned edge
    function _clipPolyEdge(poly, insideFn, intersectFn){
      const out=[];
      if(!poly || poly.length<3) return out;
      for(let i=0;i<poly.length;i++){
        const a = poly[i];
        const b = poly[(i+1)%poly.length];
        const ina = insideFn(a);
        const inb = insideFn(b);
        if(ina && inb){
          out.push(b);
        } else if(ina && !inb){
          out.push(intersectFn(a,b));
        } else if(!ina && inb){
          out.push(intersectFn(a,b));
          out.push(b);
        }
      }
      return out;
    }

    function clipRingToBox(openRing, xmin, ymin, xmax, ymax){
      let poly = (openRing||[]).slice();
      if(poly.length<3) return [];
      // left: x >= xmin
      poly = _clipPolyEdge(poly, (p)=>p[0]>=xmin, (a,b)=>{
        const t = (xmin - a[0]) / ((b[0]-a[0]) || 1e-15);
        return [xmin, a[1] + (b[1]-a[1])*t];
      });
      if(poly.length<3) return [];
      // right: x <= xmax
      poly = _clipPolyEdge(poly, (p)=>p[0]<=xmax, (a,b)=>{
        const t = (xmax - a[0]) / ((b[0]-a[0]) || 1e-15);
        return [xmax, a[1] + (b[1]-a[1])*t];
      });
      if(poly.length<3) return [];
      // bottom: y >= ymin
      poly = _clipPolyEdge(poly, (p)=>p[1]>=ymin, (a,b)=>{
        const t = (ymin - a[1]) / ((b[1]-a[1]) || 1e-15);
        return [a[0] + (b[0]-a[0])*t, ymin];
      });
      if(poly.length<3) return [];
      // top: y <= ymax
      poly = _clipPolyEdge(poly, (p)=>p[1]<=ymax, (a,b)=>{
        const t = (ymax - a[1]) / ((b[1]-a[1]) || 1e-15);
        return [a[0] + (b[0]-a[0])*t, ymax];
      });
      return poly;
    }

    function keepTop(p, frac){
      const bb = p._bb;
      const xmin=bb[0], ymin=bb[1], xmax=bb[2], ymax=bb[3];
      const h = (ymax-ymin)||1e-9;
      const y0 = ymax - h*frac;
      const ring = p.geom[0];
      const open = (ring.length>2 && _eqPt(ring[0], ring[ring.length-1])) ? ring.slice(0,-1) : ring.slice();
      const clipped = clipRingToBox(open, xmin, y0, xmax, ymax);
      if(clipped.length>=3){
        p.geom = [clipped.concat([clipped[0]])];
        p._bb = featureBbox({geom:p.geom});
      }
    }
    function keepBottom(p, frac){
      const bb = p._bb;
      const xmin=bb[0], ymin=bb[1], xmax=bb[2], ymax=bb[3];
      const h = (ymax-ymin)||1e-9;
      const y1 = ymin + h*frac;
      const ring = p.geom[0];
      const open = (ring.length>2 && _eqPt(ring[0], ring[ring.length-1])) ? ring.slice(0,-1) : ring.slice();
      const clipped = clipRingToBox(open, xmin, ymin, xmax, y1);
      if(clipped.length>=3){
        p.geom = [clipped.concat([clipped[0]])];
        p._bb = featureBbox({geom:p.geom});
      }
    }
    function keepRightBottom(p, fracX, fracY){
      const bb = p._bb;
      const xmin=bb[0], ymin=bb[1], xmax=bb[2], ymax=bb[3];
      const w = (xmax-xmin)||1e-9;
      const h = (ymax-ymin)||1e-9;
      const x0 = xmax - w*fracX;
      const y1 = ymin + h*fracY;
      const ring = p.geom[0];
      const open = (ring.length>2 && _eqPt(ring[0], ring[ring.length-1])) ? ring.slice(0,-1) : ring.slice();
      const clipped = clipRingToBox(open, x0, ymin, xmax, y1);
      if(clipped.length>=3){
        p.geom = [clipped.concat([clipped[0]])];
        p._bb = featureBbox({geom:p.geom});
      }
    }

    // Apply requested "cut" rules
    for(const p of districtPolys){
      if(p.id===8){ keepTop(p, 0.50); }           // Комсомольская - Углеразведка: убрать нижнюю половину
      if(p.id===9){ keepTop(p, 0.50); }           // Базар - ДК - Центр: убрать нижнюю половину
      if(p.id===10){ keepTop(p, 0.50); }          // Администрация - 19 школа: убрать нижнюю половину
      if(p.id===13){ keepTop(p, 0.20); }          // 17 школа - Больница: оставить верх ~2/10
      if(p.id===12){ keepTop(p, 0.20); }          // Бабушкино: оставить верх ~2/10
      if(p.id===6){ keepRightBottom(p, 0.50, 0.20); } // Аэропорт: правый нижний угол, срезать верх ~8/10
      if(p.id===14){ keepBottom(p, 0.50); }       // Кролевцы: убрать верхнюю половину
    }





    // Fine-tune "Кролевцы" to match the hand sketch: lift a sharp tip northwards so it touches "Заводской"
    function tweakKrolevtsy(polys){
      const kro = polys.find(p=>p.id===14);
      const zav = polys.find(p=>p.id===15);
      if(!kro || !zav || !kro.geom || !kro.geom[0] || kro.geom[0].length<4) return;

      // Work only with the outer ring (first ring)
      const ring0 = kro.geom[0];
      // remove closing duplicate if present
      const ring = ring0.slice(0, -1);

      // Validate points and compute bbox/centroid (bbox center is enough here)
      let minx=Infinity, miny=Infinity, maxx=-Infinity, maxy=-Infinity;
      for(const pt of ring){
        const x=pt[0], y=pt[1];
        if(!Number.isFinite(x) || !Number.isFinite(y)) return;
        if(x<minx) minx=x; if(y<miny) miny=y; if(x>maxx) maxx=x; if(y>maxy) maxy=y;
      }
      const cx=(minx+maxx)/2, cy=(miny+maxy)/2;
      const w=Math.max(1, maxx-minx), h=Math.max(1, maxy-miny);

      // Anchor: keep the east-most point fixed (it borders "Заводской")
      let eastIdx=0;
      for(let i=1;i<ring.length;i++){
        if(ring[i][0] > ring[eastIdx][0]) eastIdx=i;
      }
      const anchorOrig=[ring[eastIdx][0], ring[eastIdx][1]];

      // Rotate CCW around centroid to aim the "nose" to NW
      const ang = 27 * Math.PI/180;
      const cosA=Math.cos(ang), sinA=Math.sin(ang);
      const rot = (p)=>{
        const x=p[0]-cx, y=p[1]-cy;
        return [cx + x*cosA - y*sinA, cy + x*sinA + y*cosA];
      };

      let rotated = ring.map(rot);

      // Translate back so the anchor stays in place
      const anchorNew = rotated[eastIdx];
      const dx = anchorOrig[0] - anchorNew[0];
      const dy = anchorOrig[1] - anchorNew[1];
      rotated = rotated.map(p=>[p[0]+dx, p[1]+dy]);

      // Create a sharper NW tip: push the top-most point left/up
      let topIdx=0;
      for(let i=1;i<rotated.length;i++){
        if(rotated[i][1] > rotated[topIdx][1]) topIdx=i;
      }
      rotated[topIdx] = [ rotated[topIdx][0] - 0.35*w, rotated[topIdx][1] + 0.25*h ];

      // Close ring
      const closed = rotated.concat([rotated[0]]);
      kro.geom = [closed];
      kro._bb = featureBbox({geom:kro.geom});
    }


    tweakKrolevtsy(districtPolys);

    // View state
    const view = { scale: 1, tx: 0, ty: 0, fitScale: 1 };
    let activeDistrict = null;
    let dragging = false;
    let last = {x:0,y:0};
    let hasHome = false;

    function resize(){
      const dpr = window.devicePixelRatio || 1;
      const rect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();
      canvas.width = Math.max(1, Math.round(rect.width*dpr));
      canvas.height= Math.max(1, Math.round(rect.height*dpr));
      ctx.setTransform(dpr,0,0,dpr,0,0); // draw in CSS pixels
      fit();
      if(!hasHome) setHomeView();
      draw();
    }

    function fit(){
      const rect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();
      const pad = 18;
      const sx = (rect.width - pad*2) / world.w;
      const sy = (rect.height - pad*2) / world.h;
      view.scale = Math.max(0.000001, Math.min(sx, sy));
      view.fitScale = view.scale;
      // center
      const cx = (world.minx + world.maxx)/2;
      const cy = (world.miny + world.maxy)/2;
      const vx = rect.width/2;
      const vy = rect.height/2;
      view.tx = vx - (cx-world.minx)*view.scale;
      view.ty = vy - (world.maxy - cy)*view.scale; // align with worldToScreen y-flip
    }


    function setHomeView(){
      const rect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();
      const pad = 24;
      const lb = findLabelExact(OSM_ARTEM.labels,'Артём') || findLabelIncludes(OSM_ARTEM.labels,'Артём') || findLabelIncludes(OSM_ARTEM.labels,'Артем');
      const cx = lb ? lb.x : (world.minx + world.maxx)/2;
      const cy = lb ? lb.y : (world.miny + world.maxy)/2;

      // Zoom in relative to full-fit: show ~35% of the map span by default (tuned for Artem city view)
      const targetW = world.w * 0.35;
      const targetH = world.h * 0.35;
      const sx = (rect.width - pad*2) / targetW;
      const sy = (rect.height - pad*2) / targetH;
      view.scale = Math.max(0.000001, Math.min(sx, sy));

      const vx = rect.width/2;
      const vy = rect.height/2;
      view.tx = vx - (cx-world.minx)*view.scale;
      view.ty = vy - (world.maxy - cy)*view.scale; // center on Artem label with y-flip
      hasHome = true;
    }

    function worldToScreen(x,y){
      // y grows up in 3857, but canvas y grows down => flip around miny
      const sx = (x - world.minx)*view.scale + view.tx;
      const sy = (world.maxy - y)*view.scale + view.ty; // flip using maxy
      return [sx, sy];
    }
    function screenToWorld(sx,sy){
      const x = (sx - view.tx)/view.scale + world.minx;
      const y = world.maxy - ((sy - view.ty)/view.scale);
      return [x,y];
    }

    function beginPathFromGeom(geom){
      // geom: Polygon rings OR MultiPolygon [[rings], [rings]]
      const isNum = (v)=> typeof v === 'number';
      if(!geom) return;
      if(isNum(geom[0][0][0])){ // Polygon rings
        for(const ring of geom){
          for(let i=0;i<ring.length;i++){ 
            const pt = ring[i];
            const s = worldToScreen(pt[0], pt[1]);
            if(i===0) ctx.moveTo(s[0], s[1]); else ctx.lineTo(s[0], s[1]);
          }
          ctx.closePath();
        }
      } else {
        // MultiPolygon
        for(const poly of geom){
          for(const ring of poly){
            for(let i=0;i<ring.length;i++){ 
              const pt = ring[i];
              const s = worldToScreen(pt[0], pt[1]);
              if(i===0) ctx.moveTo(s[0], s[1]); else ctx.lineTo(s[0], s[1]);
            }
            ctx.closePath();
          }
        }
      }
    }

    function strokeLine(geom){
      if(!geom) return;
      const isNum = (v)=> typeof v === 'number';
      if(isNum(geom[0][0])){ // LineString
        for(let i=0;i<geom.length;i++){ 
          const pt=geom[i]; const s=worldToScreen(pt[0],pt[1]);
          if(i===0) ctx.moveTo(s[0],s[1]); else ctx.lineTo(s[0],s[1]);
        }
      } else {
        // MultiLineString
        for(const part of geom){
          for(let i=0;i<part.length;i++){ 
            const pt=part[i]; const s=worldToScreen(pt[0],pt[1]);
            if(i===0) ctx.moveTo(s[0],s[1]); else ctx.lineTo(s[0],s[1]);
          }
        }
      }
    }

    function fillForPoly(p){
      // Conservative palette, close to OSM-like feel
      if(p.kind==='landuse') return '#e8f1e3';
      if(p.kind==='natural') {
        const t = (p.type||'').toLowerCase();
        if(t.includes('water')) return '#cfe8ff';
        if(t.includes('wood')||t.includes('forest')) return '#d7eed1';
        return '#eef3ea';
      }
      return '#f0f0f0';
    }

    function draw(){
      const rect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();
      ctx.clearRect(0,0,rect.width,rect.height);

      // background
      ctx.fillStyle = '#f6fbff';
      ctx.fillRect(0,0,rect.width,rect.height);

      // polygons
      ctx.lineWidth = 1;
      ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(0,0,0,0.05)';
      for(const p of basePolys){
        ctx.beginPath();
        beginPathFromGeom(p.geom);
        ctx.fillStyle = fillForPoly(p);
        ctx.fill();
        ctx.stroke();
      }

      // highlight
      if(activeDistrict){
        ctx.save();
        ctx.beginPath();
        beginPathFromGeom(activeDistrict.geom);
        ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(10,120,255,0.14)';
        ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(10,120,255,0.55)';
        ctx.lineWidth = 2;
        ctx.fill();
        ctx.stroke();
        ctx.restore();
      }

      // waterways
      ctx.save();
      ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(60,140,220,0.70)';
      ctx.lineWidth = 1.2;
      ctx.beginPath();
      for(const w of OSM_ARTEM.water){
        strokeLine(w.geom);
      }
      ctx.stroke();
      ctx.restore();

      // railways
      ctx.save();
      ctx.strokeStyle = 'rgba(30,30,30,0.35)';
      ctx.lineWidth = 1.3;
      ctx.setLineDash([4,3]);
      ctx.beginPath();
      for(const r of OSM_ARTEM.rails){
        strokeLine(r.geom);
      }
      ctx.stroke();
      ctx.setLineDash([]);
      ctx.restore();

      // roads (draw major last)
      const roadDraw = (types, width, alpha)=>{
        ctx.save();
        ctx.strokeStyle = `rgba(60,60,60,${alpha})`;
        ctx.lineWidth = width;
        ctx.lineCap = 'round';
        ctx.lineJoin = 'round';
        ctx.beginPath();
        for(const rd of OSM_ARTEM.roads){
          if(types.has(rd.type)) strokeLine(rd.geom);
        }
        ctx.stroke();
        ctx.restore();
      };
      roadDraw(new Set(['residential','unclassified']), 1.1, 0.28);
      roadDraw(new Set(['tertiary']), 1.4, 0.35);
      roadDraw(new Set(['secondary','primary','primary_link']), 2.0, 0.45);
      roadDraw(new Set(['trunk','trunk_link','motorway','motorway_link']), 2.6, 0.52);

      // labels (cities/suburbs only)
      ctx.save();
      ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(0,0,0,0.55)';
      ctx.font = '12px system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial';
      for(const lb of OSM_ARTEM.labels){
        if(!lb.name) continue;
        if(lb.type!=='city' && lb.type!=='suburb' && lb.type!=='village') continue;
        const s = worldToScreen(lb.x, lb.y);
        ctx.fillText(lb.name, s[0]+4, s[1]-4);
      }

      // street labels (only on close zoom to avoid clutter)
      if(view.scale > view.fitScale * 2.0){
        const placed = [];
        const font = '11px system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial';
        ctx.save();
        ctx.font = font;
        ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(0,0,0,0.45)';

        const canPlace = (x,y,w,h)=>{
          const pad=6;
          const r={x:x-pad,y:y-h-pad,w:w+pad*2,h:h+pad*2};
          for(const p of placed){
            if(!(r.x+r.w<p.x || p.x+p.w<r.x || r.y+r.h<p.y || p.y+p.h<r.y)) return false;
          }
          placed.push(r);
          return true;
        };

        for(const rd of OSM_ARTEM.roads){
          if(!rd.name) continue;
          // show mostly residential/tertiary at this zoom
          if(rd.type!=='residential' && rd.type!=='unclassified' && rd.type!=='tertiary') continue;
          const line = rd.geom && rd.geom[0];
          if(!line || line.length<2) continue;

          // pick midpoint
          const mid = line[Math.floor(line.length/2)];
          const s = worldToScreen(mid[0], mid[1]);
          const txt = rd.name;
          const w = ctx.measureText(txt).width;
          const x = s[0]-w/2;
          const y = s[1]+4;
          if(x<8 || y<14 || x+w>rect.width-8 || y>rect.height-8) continue;
          if(canPlace(x,y,w,12)){
            ctx.fillText(txt, x, y);
          }
          if(placed.length>140) break;
        }
        ctx.restore();

      // street labels (only when zoomed in)
      if(view.scale > 1.25){
        ctx.save();
        ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(0,0,0,0.55)';
        ctx.font = '11px system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial';
        let placed=0;
        for(const rd of OSM_ARTEM.roads){
          if(!rd.name) continue;
          // show only more important streets to avoid clutter
          if(rd.type==='service') continue;
          const pts = rd.geom;
          if(!pts || pts.length<2) continue;
          // midpoint
          const mid = pts[Math.floor(pts.length/2)];
          const s = worldToScreen(mid[0], mid[1]);
          if(s[0]<8||s[0]>rect.width-8||s[1]<8||s[1]>rect.height-8) continue;
          ctx.fillText(rd.name, s[0]+3, s[1]-3);
          placed++;
          if(placed>180) break;
        }
        ctx.restore();
      }
      }

      ctx.restore();
    }

    function pointInRing(pt, ring){
      // Ray casting in 2D
      const x=pt[0], y=pt[1];
      let inside=false;
      for(let i=0,j=ring.length-1;i<ring.length;j=i++){ 
        const xi=ring[i][0], yi=ring[i][1];
        const xj=ring[j][0], yj=ring[j][1];
        const intersect = ((yi>y)!==(yj>y)) && (x < (xj-xi)*(y-yi)/(yj-yi+1e-15)+xi);
        if(intersect) inside=!inside;
      }
      return inside;
    }
    function pointInPolygon(pt, geom){
      const isNum = (v)=> typeof v === 'number';
      if(isNum(geom[0][0][0])){ // Polygon rings
        if(!pointInRing(pt, geom[0])) return false;
        for(let i=1;i<geom.length;i++){ if(pointInRing(pt, geom[i])) return false; }
        return true;
      } else {
        for(const poly of geom){
          if(!pointInRing(pt, poly[0])) continue;
          let ok=true;
          for(let i=1;i<poly.length;i++){ if(pointInRing(pt, poly[i])) { ok=false; break; } }
          if(ok) return true;
        }
        return false;
      }
    }

    function pickDistrict(x,y){
      const pt=[x,y];
      // bbox prefilter
      for(const p of districtPolys){
        const bb=p._bb;
        if(x<bb.minx||x>bb.maxx||y<bb.miny||y>bb.maxy) continue;
        if(pointInPolygon(pt, p.geom)) return p;
      }
      return null;
    }

    function setHud(p){
      if(!p){
        hudTitle.textContent = '—';
        hudValue.textContent = '—';
        hudHint.textContent = 'Наведите курсор на район.';
        hudMeta.textContent = '';
        return;
      }
      hudTitle.textContent = 'Район';
      hudValue.textContent = p.name || '—';
      hudHint.textContent = 'Колёсико — масштаб. Перетаскивание — панорама.';

      // ---- Bind projects to district via project.viz_classifier ----
      const districtName = (p.name||'').trim();
      const all = (typeof loadProjects==='function') ? loadProjects() : [];
      const norm = (s)=> (s||'').toString().trim().toLowerCase();

      const hits = all
        .filter(x=> norm(x.viz_classifier) === norm(districtName))
        .sort((a,b)=> (a.name||'').localeCompare(b.name||'', 'ru'));

      if(!districtName){
        hudMeta.textContent = '';
        return;
      }

      if(!hits.length){
        hudMeta.innerHTML = `<div style="margin-top:6px"><b>Проекты:</b> <span style="opacity:.75">нет привязанных</span></div>`;
        return;
      }

      const itemHtml = hits.map(prj=>{
        const name = esc(prj.name || 'Без названия');
        const code = esc(prj.code || '');
        const st = statusLabel(prj.status);
        const stTxt = esc(st);
        const href = 'project_passport_offline.html?id=' + encodeURIComponent(prj.id||'');
        const isMain = !prj.parent_id;
        const tag = isMain ? 'Проект' : 'Пет‑проект';
        return `<li style="margin:4px 0">
          <a href="${href}" style="text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;color:inherit">${name}</a>
          <div style="font-size:11px;opacity:.8;margin-top:1px">${tag}${code?(' • '+code):''} • ${stTxt}</div>
        </li>`;
      }).join('');

      hudMeta.innerHTML = `
        <div style="margin-top:8px">
          <div style="font-weight:800;margin-bottom:6px">Проекты (${hits.length})</div>
          <ul style="margin:0;padding-left:18px">${itemHtml}</ul>
        </div>`;
    }

    canvas.addEventListener('mousemove', (e)=>{
      const rect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();
      const x = e.clientX - rect.left;
      const y = e.clientY - rect.top;
      if(dragging){
        const dx = x - last.x;
        const dy = y - last.y;
        last = {x,y};
        view.tx += dx;
        view.ty += dy;
        draw();
        return;
      }
      const w = screenToWorld(x,y);
      const hit = pickDistrict(w[0], w[1]);
      if(hit !== activeDistrict){
        activeDistrict = hit;
        setHud(activeDistrict);
        draw();
      }
    });
    canvas.addEventListener('mouseleave', ()=>{
      if(dragging) return;
      activeDistrict=null; setHud(null); draw();
    });

    canvas.addEventListener('mousedown', (e)=>{
      dragging = true;
      const rect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();
      last = {x: e.clientX - rect.left, y: e.clientY - rect.top};
      canvas.style.cursor = 'grabbing';
    });
    window.addEventListener('mouseup', ()=>{
      dragging = false;
      canvas.style.cursor = 'default';
    });

    canvas.addEventListener('wheel', (e)=>{
      e.preventDefault();
      const rect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();
      const mx = e.clientX - rect.left;
      const my = e.clientY - rect.top;
      const before = screenToWorld(mx,my);

      const delta = Math.sign(e.deltaY);
      const factor = delta>0 ? 0.88 : 1.14;
      const newScale = Math.max(view.scale*0.2, Math.min(view.scale*8, view.scale*factor));
      if(newScale===view.scale) return;
      view.scale = newScale;

      // keep mouse world point fixed
      const after = worldToScreen(before[0], before[1]);
      view.tx += mx - after[0];
      view.ty += my - after[1];
      draw();
    }, { passive:false });

    // initial paint
    const ro = new ResizeObserver(()=>resize());
    ro.observe(canvas);
    // Fallback
    setTimeout(()=>resize(), 0);

    // Expose small API for tab activation
    window.__artemMapApi = {
      home: ()=>{ hasHome=false; setHomeView(); draw(); },
      redraw: ()=>draw(),
      getView: ()=>({...view})
    };
  })();

})();
</script>
</body>
</html>

    :root{ --bg0:#f8fafc; --bg1:#eef2f7; --panel:#ffffff; --brd:#e5e7eb;
      --text:#0f172a; --muted:#475569; --chip:rgba(2,6,23,.04); --card:#ffffff;
      --accent:#3b82f6; --ok:#22c55e; --shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(15,23,42,.08); }
    body{margin:0;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--bg0),var(--bg1));color:var(--text);
         font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Ubuntu,Cantarell,Helvetica Neue,Arial}

  <script>
    const EMBED = {
      template_b64: "",
      example_b64: ""
    };
  </script>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jszip@3.10.1/dist/jszip.min.js"></script>
  <script>
  (function(){
    'use strict';
    const $ = (id)=> document.getElementById(id);
    const STORE='munart_projects_offline_light';
    const STATUSES=[
      {id:'planned', title:'Запланирован'},
      {id:'in_progress', title:'В работе'},
      {id:'on_hold', title:'На паузе'},
      {id:'done', title:'Завершён'}
    ];

    function loadProjects(){
      try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(STORE))||[]; }catch(_){ return []; }
    }
    function typeLabel(p){ return (p.pet_type && p.pet_type.trim()) ? p.pet_type.trim() : 'Основной'; }
    function inRange(p, d1, d2){
      const s=p.start?new Date(p.start):null;
      const e=p.due?new Date(p.due):null;
      const a=d1?new Date(d1):null, b=d2?new Date(d2):null;
      const hits=[]; if(s)hits.push(s); if(e)hits.push(e);
      if(!hits.length) return true;
      return hits.some(dt => (!a || dt>=a) && (!b || dt<=b));
    }

    function buildTypes(items){ const set=new Set(items.map(typeLabel)); return Array.from(set).sort(); }

    function renderFilters(){
      const items=loadProjects(); const types=buildTypes(items);
      $('statusBox').innerHTML = STATUSES.map(s=>`<label class="pill"><input type="checkbox" value="${s.id}" checked> ${s.title}</label>`).join('');
      $('typesBox').innerHTML = types.map(t=>`<label class="pill"><input type="checkbox" value="${t}" checked> ${t}</label>`).join('');
      const now=new Date(); const from=new Date(now.getFullYear(),now.getMonth()-11,1);
      $('dateFrom').value = from.toISOString().slice(0,10);
      $('dateTo').value = new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10);
      refreshList();
      document.querySelectorAll('#statusBox input,#typesBox input,#dateFrom,#dateTo,#kind').forEach(el=> el.addEventListener('change', refreshList));
    }

    function checkedValues(rootId){ return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('#'+rootId+' input:checked')).map(i=>i.value); }

    function refreshList(){
      const items=loadProjects();
      const st=new Set(checkedValues('statusBox')); const tp=new Set(checkedValues('typesBox'));
      const d1=$('dateFrom').value, d2=$('dateTo').value;
      const filtered = items.filter(p=> st.has(p.status) && tp.has(typeLabel(p)) && inRange(p,d1,d2));
      $('selList').innerHTML = filtered.length ? filtered.map(p=>`<div>• ${(p.name||'Без названия').replace(/[&<>"]/g,c=>({'&':'&amp;','<':'&lt;','>':'&gt;','"':'&quot;'}[c]))}</div>`).join('') : '—';
      $('makeNote').textContent = filtered.length ? `Будет включено проектов: ${filtered.length}` : 'Нет данных по фильтрам';
      updateExampleLink();
    }

    function blobFromB64(b64, mime){
      if(!b64) return null;
      const bin=atob(b64); const len=bin.length; const arr=new Uint8Array(len);
      for(let i=0;i<len;i++) arr[i]=bin.charCodeAt(i);
      return new Blob([arr], {type:mime});
    }
    function saveBlob(blob, filename){
  const a=document.createElement('a');
  a.href=URL.createObjectURL(blob);
  a.download=filename;
  a.style.display='none';
  document.body.appendChild(a); a.click(); setTimeout(()=>{ URL.revokeObjectURL(a.href); a.remove(); },0);
    }

    
function updateExampleLink(){
  const ex=$('exActions'); ex.innerHTML='';
  const kind=$('kind').value;
  if(EMBED.example_b64){
    const btn=document.createElement('button');
    btn.className='btn';
    btn.textContent='Скачать пример';
    btn.onclick=()=> saveBlob(
      blobFromB64(EMBED.example_b64, 'application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet'),
      kind==='private' ? 'private_report_example.xlsx' : 'general_report_example.xlsx'
    );
    ex.appendChild(btn);
  } else {
    const a=document.createElement('a');
    a.className='btn';
    a.textContent='Открыть пример';
    a.href = kind==='private' ? 'private_report_example.xlsx' : 'general_report_example.xlsx';
    a.download='';
    ex.appendChild(a);
  }
  const tpl=$('tplActions'); tpl.innerHTML='';
  if(EMBED.template_b64){
    const dl=document.createElement('button');
    dl.className='btn';
    dl.textContent='Скачать шаблон';
    dl.onclick=()=> saveBlob(
      blobFromB64(EMBED.template_b64, 'application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet'),
      'general_report.xlsx'
    );
    tpl.appendChild(dl);
  } else {
    const a=document.createElement('a');
    a.className='btn';
    a.textContent='Открыть шаблон';
    a.href='general_report.xlsx';
    a.download='';
    tpl.appendChild(a);
  }
}



function crc32(buf){
  let c = ~0 >>> 0;
  for(let i=0;i<buf.length;i++){
    c ^= buf[i];
    for(let k=0;k<8;k++) c = (c>>>1) ^ (0xEDB88320 & -(c & 1));
  }
  return (~c) >>> 0;
}

function str2buf(s){
  const out = [];
  for (let i = 0; i < s.length; i++) {
    let code = s.charCodeAt(i);
    if (code >= 0xD800 && code <= 0xDBFF && i + 1 < s.length) {
      const next = s.charCodeAt(++i);
      code = 0x10000 + ((code - 0xD800) << 10) + (next - 0xDC00);
    }
    if (code <= 0x7F) out.push(code);
    else if (code <= 0x7FF) out.push(0xC0 | (code >> 6), 0x80 | (code & 0x3F));
    else if (code <= 0xFFFF) out.push(0xE0 | (code >> 12), 0x80 | ((code >> 6) & 0x3F), 0x80 | (code & 0x3F));
    else out.push(0xF0 | (code >> 18), 0x80 | ((code >> 12) & 0x3F), 0x80 | ((code >> 6) & 0x3F), 0x80 | (code & 0x3F));
  }
  return new Uint8Array(out);
}

function le16(v){ const b=new Uint8Array(2); b[0]=v&255; b[1]=(v>>>8)&255; return b; }
function le32(v){ const b=new Uint8Array(4); b[0]=v&255; b[1]=(v>>>8)&255; b[2]=(v>>>16)&255; b[3]=(v>>>24)&255; return b; }
function concat(arrs){ let n=0; arrs.forEach(a=> n+=a.length); const out=new Uint8Array(n); let off=0; arrs.forEach(a=>{ out.set(a,off); off+=a.length; }); return out; }
function makeZip(files){ // files: [{name, data:Uint8Array}]
      const records=[]; let offset=0; const parts=[];
      files.forEach(f=>{
        const nameBuf=str2buf(f.name); const crc=crc32(f.data);
        const header=concat([ le32(0x04034b50), le16(20), le16(0), le16(0), le16(0), le16(0),
          le32(crc), le32(f.data.length), le32(f.data.length), le16(nameBuf.length), le16(0), nameBuf ]);
        parts.push(header, f.data);
        const central=concat([ le32(0x02014b50), le16(20), le16(20), le16(0), le16(0), le16(0), le16(0),
          le32(crc), le32(f.data.length), le32(f.data.length), le16(nameBuf.length), le16(0), le16(0), le16(0), le16(0), le32(offset), nameBuf ]);
        records.push(central); offset += header.length + f.data.length;
      });
      const centralDir=concat(records);
      const end=concat([ le32(0x06054b50), le16(0), le16(0), le16(files.length), le16(files.length), le32(centralDir.length), le32(offset), le16(0) ]);
      return new Blob([concat(parts.concat([centralDir, end]))], {type:'application/zip'});
    }
    function escXml(s){ return (s||'').replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;'); }
    function buildSheet(names){
      let rows=[`<row r="1"><c r="A1" t="inlineStr"><is><t>Наименования проектов</t></is></c></row>`];
      for(let i=0;i<names.length;i++){ const r=i+2; rows.push(`<row r="${r}"><c r="A${r}" t="inlineStr"><is><t>${escXml(names[i])}</t></is></c></row>`); }
      return `<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<worksheet xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/spreadsheetml/2006/main">
  <sheetData>
    ${rows.join('\n    ')}
  </sheetData>
</worksheet>`;
    }
    function buildXlsxFallback(names){
      const content_types = `<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<Types xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/package/2006/content-types">
  <Default Extension="rels" ContentType="application/vnd.openxmlformats-package.relationships+xml"/>
  <Default Extension="xml" ContentType="application/xml"/>
  <Override PartName="/xl/workbook.xml" ContentType="application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet.main+xml"/>
  <Override PartName="/xl/worksheets/sheet1.xml" ContentType="application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.worksheet+xml"/>
  <Override PartName="/xl/styles.xml" ContentType="application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.styles+xml"/>
  <Override PartName="/docProps/core.xml" ContentType="application/vnd.openxmlformats-package.core-properties+xml"/>
  <Override PartName="/docProps/app.xml" ContentType="application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.extended-properties+xml"/>
</Types>`;
      const rels_root = `<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<Relationships xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/package/2006/relationships">
  <Relationship Id="rId1" Type="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/officeDocument" Target="xl/workbook.xml"/>
  <Relationship Id="rId2" Type="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/package/2006/relationships/metadata/core-properties" Target="docProps/core.xml"/>
  <Relationship Id="rId3" Type="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/extended-properties" Target="docProps/app.xml"/>
</Relationships>`;
      const wb = `<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<workbook xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/spreadsheetml/2006/main" xmlns:r="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships">
  <sheets><sheet name="Отчёт" sheetId="1" r:id="rId1"/></sheets>
</workbook>`;
      const wb_rels = `<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<Relationships xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/package/2006/relationships">
  <Relationship Id="rId1" Type="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/worksheet" Target="worksheets/sheet1.xml"/>
  <Relationship Id="rId2" Type="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/styles" Target="styles.xml"/>
</Relationships>`;
      const styles = `<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<styleSheet xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/spreadsheetml/2006/main">
  <fonts count="1"><font><sz val="11"/><name val="Calibri"/></font></fonts>
  <fills count="1"><fill><patternFill patternType="none"/></fill></fills>
  <borders count="1"><border/></borders>
  <cellStyleXfs count="1"><xf numFmtId="0" fontId="0" fillId="0" borderId="0"/></cellStyleXfs>
  <cellXfs count="1"><xf numFmtId="0" fontId="0" fillId="0" borderId="0" xfId="0"/></cellXfs>
</styleSheet>`;
      const core = `<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<cp:coreProperties xmlns:cp="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/package/2006/metadata/core-properties"
  xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"
  xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/"
  xmlns:dcmitype="http://purl.org/dc/dcmitype/"
  xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">
  <dc:title>Отчёт проектов</dc:title>
  <dc:creator>MunArt</dc:creator>
  <cp:lastModifiedBy>MunArt</cp:lastModifiedBy>
  <dcterms:created xsi:type="dcterms:W3CDTF">` + new Date().toISOString() + `</dcterms:created>
  <dcterms:modified xsi:type="dcterms:W3CDTF">` + new Date().toISOString() + `</dcterms:modified>
</cp:coreProperties>`;
      const app = `<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<Properties xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/extended-properties" xmlns:vt="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/docPropsVTypes">
  <Application>MunArt</Application>
</Properties>`;
      const sheet = buildSheet(names);
      const files = [
        {name:'[Content_Types].xml', data: str2buf(content_types)},
        {name:'_rels/.rels', data: str2buf(rels_root)},
        {name:'xl/workbook.xml', data: str2buf(wb)},
        {name:'xl/_rels/workbook.xml.rels', data: str2buf(wb_rels)},
        {name:'xl/styles.xml', data: str2buf(styles)},
        {name:'docProps/core.xml', data: str2buf(core)},
        {name:'docProps/app.xml', data: str2buf(app)},
        {name:'xl/worksheets/sheet1.xml', data: str2buf(sheet)},
      ];
      return makeZip(files);
    }

    async function fetchTemplate(){
      if(EMBED.template_b64) return blobFromB64(EMBED.template_b64,'application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet');
      try{ const r=await fetch('general_report.xlsx'); if(r.ok) return await r.blob(); }catch(_){}
      try{ const r=await fetch('/prototypes/reports/general_report.xlsx'); if(r.ok) return await r.blob(); }catch(_){}
      return null;
    }

    async function makeReport(){
      const items=loadProjects();
      const st=new Set(checkedValues('statusBox')); const tp=new Set(checkedValues('typesBox'));
      const d1=$('dateFrom').value, d2=$('dateTo').value;
      const filtered=items.filter(p=> st.has(p.status) && tp.has(typeLabel(p)) && inRange(p,d1,d2));
      const names=filtered.map(p=>p.name||'').filter(Boolean);
      const tpl=await fetchTemplate();
      if(tpl && window.JSZip){
        const ab=await tpl.arrayBuffer();
        const zip=await JSZip.loadAsync(ab);
        const xmls=Object.keys(zip.files).filter(n=>n.endsWith('.xml'));
        const joined=names.join('\n');
        for(const fn of xmls){
          let txt=await zip.files[fn].async('string');
          const esc=joined.replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;');
          txt = txt.split('[name]').join(esc);
          zip.file(fn, txt);
        }
        const out=await zip.generateAsync({type:'blob'});
        saveBlob(out,'projects_report_'+new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10)+'.xlsx');
        return;
      }
      const out=buildXlsxFallback(names);
      saveBlob(out,'projects_report_'+new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10)+'.xlsx');
    }

    function init(){
      renderFilters();
      $('btnMake').addEventListener('click', ()=> makeReport().catch(e=>{ console.error(e); alert('Ошибка формирования отчёта: '+e.message); }));
      updateExampleLink();
    }
    init();
  })();
  </script>

<!-- Runtime patch: stricter XLSX parts to remove Excel repair prompt -->
<script>
(function(){
  if (!window.__munart_patch_applied) {
    window.__munart_patch_applied = true;
    // Override builder functions with stricter versions
    const old = window;
    function escXml(s){ return (s||'').replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;'); }
    window.buildSheet = function(names){
      const last = (names.length+1);
      let rows=['<row r="1"><c r="A1" t="inlineStr"><is><t>Наименования проектов</t></is></c></row>'];
      for(let i=0;i<names.length;i++){ const r=i+2; rows.push('<row r="'+r+'"><c r="A'+r+'" t="inlineStr"><is><t>'+escXml(names[i])+'</t></is></c></row>'); }
      return '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>\\n'
        +'<worksheet xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/spreadsheetml/2006/main">\\n'
        +'  <dimension ref="A1:A'+last+'"/>\\n'
        +'  <sheetViews><sheetView workbookViewId="0"/></sheetViews>\\n'
        +'  <sheetData>\\n    '+rows.join('\\n    ')+'\\n  </sheetData>\\n'
        +'</worksheet>';
    };
    window.buildXlsxFallback = function(names){
      const nowIso = (new Date()).toISOString().replace(/\.\d{3}Z$/, 'Z');

      +'</Types>';
      const rels_root = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>\\n'

      +'  <workbookPr date1904="false"/>\\n'
      +'  <bookViews><workbookView xWindow="0" yWindow="0" windowWidth="19000" windowHeight="10000"/></bookViews>\\n'

      +'  <calcPr calcId="124519"/>\\n'
      +'</workbook>';
      const wb_rels = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>\\n'
      +'<Relationships xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/package/2006/relationships">\\n'
      +'  <Relationship Id="rId1" Type="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/worksheet" Target="worksheets/sheet1.xml"/>\\n'

      const styles = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>\\n'

      +'  <TitlesOfParts><vt:vector size="1" baseType="lpstr"><vt:lpstr>Отчёт</vt:lpstr></vt:vector></TitlesOfParts>\\n'
      +'</Properties>';
      const sheet = window.buildSheet(names);
      const files = [
        {name:'[Content_Types].xml', data: window.str2buf(content_types)},
        {name:'_rels/.rels', data: window.str2buf(rels_root)},
        {name:'xl/workbook.xml', data: window.str2buf(wb)},
        {name:'xl/_rels/workbook.xml.rels', data: window.str2buf(wb_rels)},
        {name:'xl/styles.xml', data: window.str2buf(styles)},
        {name:'docProps/core.xml', data: window.str2buf(core)},
        {name:'docProps/app.xml', data: window.str2buf(app)},
        {name:'xl/worksheets/sheet1.xml', data: window.str2buf(sheet)},
      ];
      return window.makeZip(files);
    };
  }
})();
