<!-- Patch: row-per-name insertion using JSZip; no UI changes -->
<script>
(function(){
  // Attach high-priority capture listener to override original handler
  const btn = document.getElementById('btnMake');
  if (!btn) return;
  btn.addEventListener('click', function(ev){
    try { ev.preventDefault(); ev.stopImmediatePropagation(); ev.stopPropagation(); } catch(_) {}
    generateReportRows().catch(err=>{ console.error(err); alert('Ошибка формирования отчёта: '+err.message); });
  }, true); // capture

  function getCheckedValues(rootId){
    return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('#'+rootId+' input:checked')).map(i=>i.value);
  }
  function loadProjects(){
    try { return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_projects_offline_light')) || []; } catch(_) { return []; }
  }
  function typeLabel(p){ return (p.pet_type && p.pet_type.trim()) ? p.pet_type.trim() : 'Основной'; }
  function inRange(p, d1, d2){
    const s=p.start?new Date(p.start):null, e=p.due?new Date(p.due):null;
    const a=d1?new Date(d1):null, b=d2?new Date(d2):null;
    const hits=[]; if(s)hits.push(s); if(e)hits.push(e);
    if(!hits.length) return true; return hits.some(dt => (!a || dt>=a) && (!b || dt<=b));
  }
  function escXml(s){ return (s||'').replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;'); }

  async function fetchTemplateBlob(){
    if (window.EMBED && EMBED.template_b64) {
      const bin = atob(EMBED.template_b64); const arr = new Uint8Array(bin.length);
      for (let i=0;i<bin.length;i++) arr[i]=bin.charCodeAt(i);
      return new Blob([arr], {type:'application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet'});
    }
    try{ const r=await fetch('general_report.xlsx'); if(r.ok) return await r.blob(); }catch(_){}
    try{ const r=await fetch('/prototypes/reports/general_report.xlsx'); if(r.ok) return await r.blob(); }catch(_){}
    throw new Error('Шаблон general_report.xlsx не найден');
  }

  
function transformSheetRows(xml, names){
  // Locate a template row containing [name]
  const rowRe = /<row[^>]*>[\s\S]*?\[name\][\s\S]*?<\/row>/i;
  const m = rowRe.exec(xml);
  if (!m) return xml;

  const baseRowXml = m[0];
  const rMatch = /<row[^>]*\br="(\d+)"/.exec(baseRowXml);
  const baseR = rMatch ? parseInt(rMatch[1],10) : 1;

  function buildRow(tpl, r, name, num){
    let row = tpl.replace(/(\s|^)r="\d+"/, (mm)=> mm.replace(/\d+/, String(r)));
    row = row.replace(/ r="([A-Z]+)\d+"/g, (mm, col)=> ' r="'+col+r+'"');
    row = row.replace(/\[name\]/g, escXml(name||''));
    row = row.replace(/\[numeric\]/g, String(num));
    return row;
  }

  const rowsXml = names.map((n,i)=> buildRow(baseRowXml, baseR+i, n, i+1)).join('');

  const before = xml.slice(0, m.index);
  const after = xml.slice(m.index + m[0].length);

  // Shift subsequent rows down by delta (if any)
  const delta = names.length - 1;
  let afterShifted = after;
  if (delta !== 0){
    afterShifted = after.replace(/<row[^>]*r="(\d+)"[^>]*>[\s\S]*?<\/row>/g, function(row){
      const mm = /<row[^>]*\br="(\d+)"/.exec(row);
      if (!mm) return row;
      const oldr = parseInt(mm[1],10);
      if (oldr <= baseR) return row;
      const newr = oldr + delta;
      let out = row.replace(/(\s|^)r="\d+"/, (m)=> m.replace(/\d+/, String(newr)));
      out = out.replace(/ r="([A-Z]+)\d+"/g, (m, col)=> ' r="'+col+newr+'"');
      return out;
    });
  }

  let combined = before + rowsXml + afterShifted;

  // Update sheet dimension (A1:COLROW)
  combined = combined.replace(/<dimension[^>]*ref="([A-Z]+\d+):([A-Z]+)(\d+)"[^>]*\/>/,
    function(m, a1, col2, row2){
      const n = String(parseInt(row2,10) + delta);
      return m.replace(col2+row2, col2+n);
    });

  // drop merges to prevent Excel repair on template-specific merges
  combined = combined.replace(/<mergeCells[\s\S]*?<\/mergeCells>/, '');
  return combined;
}
async 
function generateReportRows(){
    return (async function(){
      const items = loadProjects();
      const st = new Set(getCheckedValues('statusBox'));
      const tp = new Set(getCheckedValues('typesBox'));
      const d1 = document.getElementById('dateFrom').value;
      const d2 = document.getElementById('dateTo').value;
      const filtered = items.filter(p=> st.has(p.status) && tp.has(typeLabel(p)) && inRange(p,d1,d2));
      const names = filtered.map(p=>p.name||'').filter(Boolean);
      if (!names.length) { alert('Нет данных по фильтрам'); return; }

      const tpl = await fetchTemplateBlob();
      const ab = await tpl.arrayBuffer();
      const zip = await JSZip.loadAsync(ab);

      // 1) Parse sharedStrings just once
      let sst = [];
      if (zip.files['xl/sharedStrings.xml']){
        const xml = await zip.files['xl/sharedStrings.xml'].async('string');
        const blocks = xml.match(/<si[\s\S]*?<\/si>/g) || [];
        for (const si of blocks){
          let t = si.replace(/<[^>]+>/g,''); t = t.replace(/\s+/g,' ').trim();
          sst.push(t);
        }
      }

      function escXml(s){ return (s||'').replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;'); }

      function transformSheetRowsShared(sheetXml, sst, names){
        const nameIdx = sst.indexOf('[name]');
        const numIdx  = sst.indexOf('[numeric]');
        const rowRe = /<row[^>]*>[\s\S]*?<\/row>/g;
        let m, base=null, baseR=null;
        while ((m = rowRe.exec(sheetXml))){
          const row = m[0];
          const hasNameShared = nameIdx>=0 && new RegExp(`<c[^>]*t="s"[^>]*>[\\s\\S]*?<v>\\s*${nameIdx}\\s*<\\/v>[\\s\\S]*?<\\/c>`,'i').test(row);
          if (hasNameShared){ base = row; const rMatch = /<row[^>]*\\sr="(\\d+)"/.exec(row); baseR = rMatch ? parseInt(rMatch[1],10) : 10; break; }
        }
        if (!base) return sheetXml;

        function updateRowIndex(row, newR){
          let out = row.replace(/(\\s|^)r="\\d+"/, m=> m.replace(/\\d+/, String(newR)));
          out = out.replace(/ r="([A-Z]+)\\d+"/g, (mm, col)=> ' r="'+col+newR+'"');
          return out;
        }
        

function replaceTokenCells(row, newR, valName, valNum){
  const mcol = row.match(/ r="([A-Z]+)\d+"/);
  const col = mcol ? mcol[1] : 'A';
  if (typeof nameIdx === 'number' && nameIdx >= 0){
    const reName = new RegExp(`<c[^>]*t="s"[^>]*>[\\s\\S]*?<v>\\s*${nameIdx}\\s*<\\/v>[\\s\\S]*?<\\/c>`, 'i');
    row = row.replace(reName, `<c r="${col}${newR}" t="inlineStr"><is><t>${escXml(valName)}</t></is></c>`);
  }
  if (typeof numIdx === 'number' && numIdx >= 0){
    const reNum = new RegExp(`<c[^>]*t="s"[^>]*>[\\s\\S]*?<v>\\s*${numIdx}\\s*<\\/v>[\\s\\S]*?<\\/c>`, 'i');
    row = row.replace(reNum, `<c r="${col}${newR}"><v>${valNum}</v></c>`);
  }
  row = row.replace(/\[name\]/g, escXml(valName));
  row = row.replace(/\[numeric\]/g, String(valNum));
  return row;
}



        const copies = names.map((n,i)=>{
          const r = baseR + i;
          let row = updateRowIndex(base, r);
          row = replaceTokenCells(row, r, n, i+1);
          return row;
        }).join('');

        const before = sheetXml.substring(0, sheetXml.indexOf(base));
        const afterStart = sheetXml.indexOf(base) + base.length;
        const after = sheetXml.substring(afterStart);

        const delta = names.length - 1;
        let afterShifted = after.replace(/<row[^>]*r="(\\d+)"[^>]*>[\\s\\S]*?<\\/row>/g, function(row){
          const mm = /<row[^>]*\\sr="(\\d+)"/.exec(row); if (!mm) return row;
          const oldr = parseInt(mm[1],10);
          if (oldr <= baseR) return row;
          const newr = oldr + delta;
          let out = row.replace(/(\\s|^)r="\\d+"/, t=> t.replace(/\\d+/, String(newr)));
          out = out.replace(/ r="([A-Z]+)\\d+"/g, (t, col)=> ' r="'+col+newr+'"');
          return out;
        });

        let combined = before + copies + afterShifted;
        const dimRe = new RegExp('<dimension[^>]*ref="([A-Z]+\\d+):([A-Z]+)(\\d+)"[^>]*/>');
        combined = combined.replace(dimRe, function(m, a1, col2, row2){
          const n = String(parseInt(row2,10) + (names.length-1)); return m.replace(col2+row2, col2+n);
        });
        combined = combined.replace(/<mergeCell ref="([A-Z]+)(\\d+):([A-Z]+)(\\d+)"\\/>/g, function(m, c1,r1,c2,r2){
          const nr1 = parseInt(r1,10) > baseR ? parseInt(r1,10) + (names.length-1) : parseInt(r1,10);
          const nr2 = parseInt(r2,10) > baseR ? parseInt(r2,10) + (names.length-1) : parseInt(r2,10);
          return `<mergeCell ref="${c1}${nr1}:${c2}${nr2}"/>`;
        });
        return combined;
      }

      const sheets = Object.keys(zip.files).filter(n=>/^xl\\/worksheets\\/sheet\\d+\\.xml$/.test(n));
      let touched = false;
      for (const fn of sheets){
        let xml = await zip.files[fn].async('string');
        const newXml = transformSheetRowsShared(xml, sst, names);
        if (newXml !== xml){ zip.file(fn, newXml); touched = true; }
      }
      if (!touched){
        // fallback to inline tokens just in case
        for (const fn of sheets){
          let xml = await zip.files[fn].async('string');
          if (xml.includes('[name]')){
            xml = transformSheetRows(xml, names);
            zip.file(fn, xml);
            touched = true;
          }
        }
      }

      const out = await zip.generateAsync({type:'blob'});
      const a=document.createElement('a'); a.href=URL.createObjectURL(blob);
      a.download='projects_report_'+new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10)+'.xlsx'; a.style.display='none';
      document.body.appendChild(a); a.click(); setTimeout(()=>{URL.revokeObjectURL(a.href); a.remove();},0);
    })();
}

})();
</script>


<!-- Hardening: ensure generation always produces a file -->
<script>
(function(){
  const btn = document.getElementById('btnMake');
  if (!btn) return;
  // Replace all previous handlers by cloning
  const clone = btn.cloneNode(true);
  btn.parentNode.replaceChild(clone, btn);
  clone.addEventListener('click', function(e){
    e.preventDefault();
    e.stopPropagation();
    runReport().catch(err=>{ console.error(err); alert('Не удалось сформировать отчёт: '+err.message); });
  });

  function el(id){return document.getElementById(id);}
  function getChecked(root){return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('#'+root+' input:checked')).map(x=>x.value);}
  function typeLabel(p){ return (p.pet_type && p.pet_type.trim()) ? p.pet_type.trim() : 'Основной'; }
  function inRange(p, d1, d2){
    const s=p.start?new Date(p.start):null, e=p.due?new Date(p.due):null;
    const a=d1?new Date(d1):null, b=d2?new Date(d2):null;
    const hits=[]; if(s)hits.push(s); if(e)hits.push(e);
    if(!hits.length) return true; return hits.some(dt => (!a || dt>=a) && (!b || dt<=b));
  }
  function loadProjects(){ try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_projects_offline_light'))||[]; }catch(_){ return []; } }
  function escXml(s){ return (s||'').replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;'); }

  async function runReport(){
    const items = loadProjects();
    const st = new Set(getChecked('statusBox'));
    const tp = new Set(getChecked('typesBox'));
    const d1 = el('dateFrom').value, d2 = el('dateTo').value;
    const filtered = items.filter(p=> st.has(p.status) && tp.has(typeLabel(p)) && inRange(p,d1,d2));
    const names = filtered.map(p=>p.name||'').filter(Boolean);
    if (!names.length) throw new Error('Нет данных по выбранным фильтрам');

    async function ensureJSZip(){
      if (window.JSZip) return;
      await new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        const s=document.createElement('script');
        s.src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jszip@3.10.1/dist/jszip.min.js';
        s.onload=resolve; s.onerror=()=>reject(new Error('JSZip недоступен'));
        document.head.appendChild(s);
      });
    }

    // 1) Try template path with JSZip
    try{
      await ensureJSZip();
      const tpl = await (async ()=>{
        if (window.EMBED && EMBED.template_b64){
          const b=atob(EMBED.template_b64); const u=new Uint8Array(b.length); for(let i=0;i<b.length;i++) u[i]=b.charCodeAt(i);
          return new Blob([u],{type:'application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet'});
        }
        try{ const r=await fetch('general_report.xlsx'); if(r.ok) return await r.blob(); }catch(_){}
        try{ const r=await fetch('/prototypes/reports/general_report.xlsx'); if(r.ok) return await r.blob(); }catch(_){}
        throw new Error('Шаблон general_report.xlsx не найден');
      })();

      const ab = await tpl.arrayBuffer();
      const zip = await JSZip.loadAsync(ab);

      // For every sheet containing [name] row — duplicate it
      const sheets = Object.keys(zip.files).filter(n=>/^xl\/worksheets\/sheet\d+\.xml$/.test(n));
      for (const fn of sheets){
        let xml = await zip.files[fn].async('string');
        if (!xml.includes('[name]')) continue;
        const rowRe = /<row[^>]*>[\s\S]*?\[name\][\s\S]*?<\/row>/i;
        const m = rowRe.exec(xml);
        if (!m) continue;
        const baseRow = m[0];
        const rMatch = /<row[^>]*\sr="(\d+)"/.exec(baseRow);
        const baseR = rMatch ? parseInt(rMatch[1],10) : 10;
        const rows = names.map((n,i)=>{
          const r = baseR + i;
          let row = baseRow.replace(/(\s|^)r="\d+"/, m=> m.replace(/\d+/, String(r)));
          row = row.replace(/ r="([A-Z]+)\d+"/g, (mm, col)=> ' r="'+col+r+'"');
          row = row.replace(/\[name\]/g, escXml(n));
          row = row.replace(/\[numeric\]/g, String(i+1));
          return row;
        }).join('');
        const before = xml.slice(0, m.index);
        const after = xml.slice(m.index + m[0].length);
        const delta = names.length - 1;
        let afterShifted = after;
        if (delta !== 0){
          afterShifted = after.replace(/<row[^>]*r="(\d+)"[^>]*>[\s\S]*?<\/row>/g, function(row){
            const mm = /<row[^>]*\sr="(\d+)"/.exec(row); if (!mm) return row;
            const oldr = parseInt(mm[1],10);
            if (oldr <= baseR) return row;
            const newr = oldr + delta;
            let out = row.replace(/(\s|^)r="\d+"/, t=> t.replace(/\d+/, String(newr)));
            out = out.replace(/ r="([A-Z]+)\d+"/g, (t, col)=> ' r="'+col+newr+'"');
            return out;
          });
        }
        let combined = before + rows + afterShifted;
        combined = combined.replace(/<dimension[^>]*ref="([A-Z]+\d+):([A-Z]+)(\d+)"[^>]*\/>/,
          function(m, a1, col2, row2){ const n = String(parseInt(row2,10) + (names.length-1)); return m.replace(col2+row2, col2+n); }
        );
        zip.file(fn, combined);
      }

      const out = await zip.generateAsync({type:'blob'});
      const a=document.createElement('a'); a.href=URL.createObjectURL(blob);
      a.download='projects_report_'+new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10)+'.xlsx'; a.style.display='none';
      document.body.appendChild(a); a.click(); setTimeout(()=>{URL.revokeObjectURL(a.href); a.remove();},0);
      return;
    }catch(err){
      console.warn('Template path failed, fallback:', err);
      // 2) Fallback: minimal XLSX (names column) — чтобы всегда хоть что-то скачать
      if (typeof buildXlsxFallback === 'function'){
        const blob = buildXlsxFallback(names);
        const a=document.createElement('a'); a.href=URL.createObjectURL(blob);
        a.download='projects_report_'+new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10)+'.xlsx'; a.style.display='none';
        document.body.appendChild(a); a.click(); setTimeout(()=>{URL.revokeObjectURL(a.href); a.remove();},0);
        return;
      }
      throw err;
    }
  }
})();
</script>


<script>
// Override runReport to ensure [numeric] becomes 1..N for each created row.
(function(){
  // guard to run once
  if (window.__projects_report_patch_v9__) return; 
  window.__projects_report_patch_v9__ = true;

  function escXml(s){ return (s||'').replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;'); }

  async function ensureJSZip(){
    if (window.JSZip) return;
    await new Promise((resolve,reject)=>{
      const s=document.createElement('script');
      s.src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jszip@3.10.1/dist/jszip.min.js';
      s.onload=resolve; s.onerror=()=>reject(new Error('JSZip недоступен'));
      document.head.appendChild(s);
    });
  }
  async function getTemplateBlob(){
    if (window.EMBED && EMBED.template_b64){
      const b=atob(EMBED.template_b64); const u=new Uint8Array(b.length);
      for(let i=0;i<b.length;i++) u[i]=b.charCodeAt(i);
      return new Blob([u], {type:'application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet'});
    }
    try{ const r=await fetch('general_report.xlsx'); if(r.ok) return await r.blob(); }catch(_){}
    try{ const r=await fetch('/prototypes/reports/general_report.xlsx'); if(r.ok) return await r.blob(); }catch(_){}
    throw new Error('Шаблон general_report.xlsx не найден');
  }
  function parseSharedStrings(xml){
    const out = []; const blocks = xml.match(/<si[\s\S]*?<\/si>/g) || [];
    for (const si of blocks){
      let t = si.replace(/<[^>]+>/g,''); t = t.replace(/\s+/g,' ').trim();
      out.push(t);
    }
    return out;
  }
  function duplicateWithTokens(sheetXml, names, sst){
    const nameIdx = (Array.isArray(sst)? sst.indexOf('[name]') : -1);
    const numIdx  = (Array.isArray(sst)? sst.indexOf('[numeric]') : -1);

    // Locate a base row by shared string id or by inline [name]
    const rowRe = /<row[^>]*>[\s\S]*?<\/row>/g;
    let base=null, baseR= null;
    for (const m of sheetXml.matchAll(rowRe)){
      const row = m[0];
      const hasNameShared = nameIdx>=0 && new RegExp(`<c[^>]*t="s"[^>]*>[\\s\\S]*?<v>\\s*${nameIdx}\\s*<\\/v>[\\s\\S]*?<\\/c>`,'i').test(row);
      const hasNameInline = /\[name\]/i.test(row);
      if (hasNameShared || hasNameInline){
        base = row; 
        const rMatch = /<row[^>]*\sr="(\d+)"/.exec(row); baseR = rMatch? parseInt(rMatch[1],10) : 10;
        break;
      }
    }
    if (!base) return sheetXml;

    function updateRowIndex(row, newR){
      let out = row.replace(/(\s|^)r="\d+"/, m=> m.replace(/\d+/, String(newR)));
      out = out.replace(/ r="([A-Z]+)\d+"/g, (mm, col)=> ' r="'+col+newR+'"');
      return out;
    }
    function replaceTokenCells(row, newR, valName, valNum){
      let out = row;
      // Replace shared-string [name] cell to inline string
      if (nameIdx>=0){
        const reCell = new RegExp(`<c([^>]*)t="s"([^>]*)r="([A-Z]+)\d+"([^>]*)>[\\s\\S]*?<v>\\s*${nameIdx}\\s*<\\/v>[\\s\\S]*?<\\/c>`, 'i');
        out = out.replace(reCell, (m, a1,a2,col)=> `<c r="${col}${newR}" t="inlineStr"><is><t>${escXml(valName)}</t></is></c>`);
      }
      // Replace shared-string [numeric] cell to plain number
      if (numIdx>=0){
        const reNum = new RegExp(`<c([^>]*)t="s"([^>]*)r="([A-Z]+)\d+"([^>]*)>[\\s\\S]*?<v>\\s*${numIdx}\\s*<\\/v>[\\s\\S]*?<\\/c>`, 'i');
        out = out.replace(reNum, (m, a1,a2,col)=> `<c r="${col}${newR}"><v>${valNum}</v></c>`);
      }
      // Inline fallbacks
      out = out.replace(/\[name\]/g, escXml(valName));
      out = out.replace(/\[numeric\]/g, String(valNum));
      return out;
    }

    const copies = names.map((n,i)=>{
      const r = baseR + i;
      let row = updateRowIndex(base, r);
      row = replaceTokenCells(row, r, n, i+1);
      return row;
    }).join('');

    const before = sheetXml.substring(0, sheetXml.indexOf(base));
    const afterStart = sheetXml.indexOf(base) + base.length;
    const after = sheetXml.substring(afterStart);

    const delta = names.length - 1;
    let afterShifted = after.replace(/<row[^>]*r="(\d+)"[^>]*>[\s\S]*?<\/row>/g, function(row){
      const mm = /<row[^>]*\sr="(\d+)"/.exec(row); if (!mm) return row;
      const oldr = parseInt(mm[1],10);
      if (oldr <= baseR) return row;
      const newr = oldr + delta;
      let out = row.replace(/(\s|^)r="\d+"/, t=> t.replace(/\d+/, String(newr)));
      out = out.replace(/ r="([A-Z]+)\d+"/g, (t, col)=> ' r="'+col+newr+'"');
      return out;
    });

    let combined = before + copies + afterShifted;
    combined = combined.replace(/<dimension[^>]*ref="([A-Z]+\d+):([A-Z]+)(\d+)"[^>]*\/>/,
      function(m, a1, col2, row2){ const n = String(parseInt(row2,10) + (names.length-1)); return m.replace(col2+row2, col2+n); }
    );
    combined = combined.replace(/<mergeCell ref="([A-Z]+)(\d+):([A-Z]+)(\d+)"\/>/g, function(m, c1,r1,c2,r2){
      const nr1 = parseInt(r1,10) > baseR ? parseInt(r1,10) + (names.length-1) : parseInt(r1,10);
      const nr2 = parseInt(r2,10) > baseR ? parseInt(r2,10) + (names.length-1) : parseInt(r2,10);
      return `<mergeCell ref="${c1}${nr1}:${c2}${nr2}"/>`;
    });
    return combined;
  }

  // Redefine runReport used by the page
  window.runReport = async function runReport(){
    const getChecked = (window.getChecked || window.getCheckedValues || ((root)=> Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('#'+root+' input:checked')).map(x=>x.value)));
    const typeLabel = (window.typeLabel || (p=> (p && p.pet_type && p.pet_type.trim()) ? p.pet_type.trim() : 'Основной'));
    const inRange = (window.inRange || ((p, d1, d2)=> true));
    const items = (window.loadProjects? window.loadProjects() : []);
    const st = new Set(getChecked('statusBox'));
    const tp = new Set(getChecked('typesBox'));
    const d1 = document.getElementById('dateFrom')?.value;
    const d2 = document.getElementById('dateTo')?.value;
    const filtered = (items||[]).filter(p=> st.has(p.status) && tp.has(typeLabel(p)) && inRange(p,d1,d2));
    const names = filtered.map(p=>p.name||'').filter(Boolean);
    if (!names.length) throw new Error('Нет данных по выбранным фильтрам');

    await ensureJSZip();
    const tpl = await getTemplateBlob();
    const ab = await tpl.arrayBuffer();
    const zip = await JSZip.loadAsync(ab);

    let sst = [];
    if (zip.files['xl/sharedStrings.xml']){
      const shared = await zip.files['xl/sharedStrings.xml'].async('string');
      sst = parseSharedStrings(shared);
    }
    const sheets = Object.keys(zip.files).filter(n=>/^xl\/worksheets\/sheet\d+\.xml$/.test(n));
    let touched=false;
    for (const fn of sheets){
      let xml = await zip.files[fn].async('string');
      const newXml = duplicateWithTokens(xml, names, sst);
      if (newXml !== xml){ zip.file(fn, newXml); touched = true; }
    }
    if (!touched) throw new Error('В шаблоне не найден маркер [name]');

    const out = await zip.generateAsync({type:'blob'});
    const a=document.createElement('a'); a.href=URL.createObjectURL(blob);
    a.download='projects_report_'+new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10)+'.xlsx'; a.style.display='none';
    document.body.appendChild(a); a.click(); setTimeout(()=>{URL.revokeObjectURL(a.href); a.remove();},0);
  };
})();
</script>



<!-- Report Builder v13: right-side UI, fixed XLSX, no templates -->
<style>
  .rb-card{ margin-top: 12px; }
  .rb-row{ display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center; padding:6px 8px; border:1px dashed var(--brd,#e5e7eb); border-radius:10px; margin-bottom:6px; cursor:grab; background:var(--chip,rgba(2,6,23,.04)); }
  .rb-row .drag{ font-weight:600; user-select:none; }
  .rb-row input[type="text"]{ width:180px; }
  .rb-cols{ max-width: 980px; }
  .rb-preview{ max-height: 380px; overflow:auto; border:1px solid var(--brd,#e5e7eb); border-radius:10px; }
  .rb-actions{ display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center; }
  .rb-muted{ opacity: .7; font-size: 12px;}
  .rb-table{ border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; font-size: 12px; }
  .rb-table th, .rb-table td{ border:1px solid #9993; padding:4px 6px; white-space:nowrap; }
</style>
<script>
(function(){
  const STORE_COLS = 'munart_report_columns_v1';
  const BTN_ID = 'btnMake';
  function $(id){ return document.getElementById(id); }
  function qa(sel){ return Array.from(document.querySelectorAll(sel)); }
  function esc(t){ return String(t).replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;'); }

  function loadProjects(){
    try{ return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('munart_projects_offline_light'))||[]; }catch(_){ return []; }
  }
  function typeLabel(p){ return (p && p.pet_type && p.pet_type.trim()) ? p.pet_type.trim() : 'Основной'; }
  function inRange(p, d1, d2){
    const s=p.start?new Date(p.start):null, e=p.due?new Date(p.due):null;
    const a=d1?new Date(d1):null, b=d2?new Date(d2):null;
    const hits=[]; if(s)hits.push(s); if(e)hits.push(e);
    if(!hits.length) return true; return hits.some(dt => (!a || dt>=a) && (!b || dt<=b));
  }
    function getFiltered(){
    const items = loadProjects();
    const stInputs = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('#statusBox input:checked'));
    const tpInputs = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('#typesBox input:checked'));
    const st = new Set(stInputs.map(x=>x.value));
    const tp = new Set(tpInputs.map(x=>x.value));
    const d1 = document.getElementById('dateFrom')?document.getElementById('dateFrom').value:null;
    const d2 = document.getElementById('dateTo')?document.getElementById('dateTo').value:null;
    return items.filter(p=> {
      const statusOk = st.size===0 ? true : st.has(p.status);
      const typeOk = tp.size===0 ? true : tp.has((p && p.pet_type && p.pet_type.trim()) ? p.pet_type.trim() : 'Основной');
      return statusOk && typeOk && inRange(p,d1,d2);
    });
  }  function toIso(d){
    if(!d) return '';
    try{ const dt=new Date(d); if(isNaN(dt)) return String(d); return dt.toISOString().slice(0,10); }catch(_){ return String(d||''); }
  }

  // Column registry (default)
  const DEFAULT_COLS = [
    {key:'num',       title:'№',             visible:true,  isNumeric:true,  compute:(p,i)=> i+1},
    {key:'beginning', title:'Начало работ',  visible:true,  compute:(p)=> toIso(p.start)},
    {key:'executor',  title:'Исполнитель',   visible:true,  compute:(p)=> p.executor||p.manager||''},
    {key:'name',      title:'Наименование',  visible:true,  compute:(p)=> p.name||''},
    {key:'contractor',title:'Подрядчик',     visible:true,  compute:(p)=> p.contractor||''},
    {key:'completion',title:'Завершение работ',visible:true, compute:(p)=> toIso(p.due)},
    {key:'amount',    title:'Сумма контракта',visible:true, compute:(p)=> (p.amount==null?'':String(p.amount))},
  ];
  function loadCols(){
    try{
      const raw = localStorage.getItem(STORE_COLS);
      if (!raw) return DEFAULT_COLS.map(x=>({...x}));
      const saved = JSON.parse(raw);
      const byKey = Object.fromEntries(DEFAULT_COLS.map(c=>[c.key,c]));
      const list = [];
      for(const s of saved){ if (byKey[s.key]) list.push({...byKey[s.key], ...s}); }
      for(const d of DEFAULT_COLS){ if (!list.find(x=>x.key===d.key)) list.push({...d}); }
      return list;
    }catch(_){ return DEFAULT_COLS.map(x=>({...x})); }
  }
  function saveCols(cols){ localStorage.setItem(STORE_COLS, JSON.stringify(cols)); }
  function currentCols(){ return loadCols().filter(c=>c.visible); }

  // Right-side replacement: remove "Пример отчёта"/"Шаблон" and insert builder
  function ensureRightBuilder(){
    const ex = document.getElementById('exActions');
    const tpl = document.getElementById('tplActions');
    let hostCard = null;
    if (ex && ex.closest('.card')) hostCard = ex.closest('.card');
    else if (tpl && tpl.closest('.card')) hostCard = tpl.closest('.card');
    if (!hostCard) return null;
    hostCard.innerHTML = `
      <div class="field">
        <label>Конструктор отчёта</label>
        <div class="rb-cols" id="rb-cols"></div>
        <div class="rb-actions">
          <button id="rb-reset" class="btn ghost">Сбросить</button>
          <span class="rb-muted">Перетаскивайте строки. Снимите галочку — чтобы скрыть столбец. Заголовок можно переименовать.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="field">
        <label>Предпросмотр</label>
        <div class="rb-preview"><table class="rb-table"><thead id="rb-th"></thead><tbody id="rb-tb"></tbody></table></div>
      </div>`;
    return hostCard;
  }

  function renderBuilder(){
    const root = ensureRightBuilder();
    if (!root) return;
    const cols = loadCols();
    const host = document.getElementById('rb-cols'); host.innerHTML = '';
    cols.forEach(col=>{
      const row = document.createElement('div');
      row.className = 'rb-row';
      row.draggable = true;
      row.dataset.key = col.key;
      row.innerHTML = '<span class="drag">⋮⋮</span>' +
                      '<input type="checkbox" class="rb-vis" '+(col.visible?'checked':'')+'>' +
                      '<input type="text" class="rb-title" value="'+esc(col.title).replace(/&amp;quot;/g,'&quot;')+'" placeholder="Заголовок">' +
                      '<span class="rb-muted">'+col.key+'</span>';
      host.appendChild(row);
    });

    // Drag handlers
    host.addEventListener('dragstart', e=>{
      const r = e.target.closest('.rb-row'); if(!r) return;
      e.dataTransfer.setData('text/plain', r.dataset.key);
      r.classList.add('dragging');
    });
    host.addEventListener('dragend', e=>{
      const r = e.target.closest('.rb-row'); if(r) r.classList.remove('dragging');
      persistFromUI(); renderPreview();
    });
    host.addEventListener('dragover', e=>{
      e.preventDefault();
      const dragging = host.querySelector('.rb-row.dragging');
      if (!dragging) return;
      const rows = Array.from(host.querySelectorAll('.rb-row:not(.dragging)'));
      let after = null;
      for(const el of rows){
        const rect = el.getBoundingClientRect();
        if (e.clientY < rect.top + rect.height/2){ after = el; break; }
      }
      if (after) host.insertBefore(dragging, after); else host.appendChild(dragging);
    });

    // IO handlers
    host.addEventListener('change', e=>{
      if (e.target.classList.contains('rb-vis') || e.target.classList.contains('rb-title')){ persistFromUI(); renderPreview(); }
    });
    host.addEventListener('input', e=>{ if (e.target.classList.contains('rb-title')){ persistFromUI(); renderPreview(); } });
    const resetBtn = document.getElementById('rb-reset'); if (resetBtn) resetBtn.addEventListener('click', ()=>{ saveCols(DEFAULT_COLS); renderBuilder(); renderPreview(); });

    renderPreview();
  }

  function persistFromUI(){
    const list = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('#rb-cols .rb-row')).map(row => {
      const key = row.dataset.key;
      const visible = row.querySelector('.rb-vis').checked;
      const title = row.querySelector('.rb-title').value || '';
      const base = Object.assign({}, DEFAULT_COLS.find(c=>c.key===key));
      return Object.assign(base, {visible, title});
    });
    saveCols(list);
  }

  function renderPreview(){
    const cols = currentCols();
    const th = document.getElementById('rb-th'); const tb = document.getElementById('rb-tb'); if (!th || !tb) return;
    th.innerHTML = '<tr>' + cols.map(c=> '<th>'+esc(c.title)+'</th>').join('') + '</tr>';
    const data = getFiltered();
    const rows = data.slice(0, 50).map((p,i)=>{
      return '<tr>' + cols.map(c=> {
        const base = DEFAULT_COLS.find(d=>d.key===c.key);
        const val = base.compute(p, i);
        return '<td>'+esc(val)+'</td>';
      }).join('') + '</tr>';
    }).join('');
    tb.innerHTML = rows || '<tr><td colspan="'+cols.length+'">Нет данных по фильтрам</td></tr>';
  }

  // XLSX builder with correct sharedStrings counts
  async function ensureJSZip(){
    if (window.JSZip) return;
    await new Promise((resolve,reject)=>{
      const s=document.createElement('script'); s.src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/jszip@3.10.1/dist/jszip.min.js';
      s.onload=resolve; s.onerror=()=>reject(new Error('JSZip недоступен')); document.head.appendChild(s);
    });
  }
  function buildXlsx(headers, rows, numericCols){
    const zip = new JSZip();
    const sst = []; const sstMap = new Map(); let sstCount = 0;
    function addS(s){
      const t = String(s==null?'':s);
      if (!sstMap.has(t)){ sstMap.set(t, sst.length); sst.push(t); }
      sstCount += 1; return sstMap.get(t);
    }
    function escxml(t){ return String(t).replace(/&/g,'&amp;').replace(/</g,'&lt;').replace(/>/g,'&gt;'); }
    function sstXml(){
      const items = sst.map(txt => '<si><t>'+escxml(txt)+'</t></si>').join('');
      return '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>\n'+
             '<sst xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/spreadsheetml/2006/main" count="'+sstCount+'" uniqueCount="'+sst.length+'">'+items+'</sst>';
    }
    function colLetter(idx){ let n = idx+1, s=''; while(n>0){ const r=(n-1)%26; s=String.fromCharCode(65+r)+s; n=Math.floor((n-1)/26); } return s; }
    function cellRef(c,r){ return colLetter(c)+(r+1); }

    const headerCells = headers.map((h,c)=> '<c r="'+cellRef(c,0)+'" t="s"><v>'+addS(h)+'</v></c>').join('');
    let sheetData = '<row r="1">'+headerCells+'</row>';

    rows.forEach((row, ri)=>{
      const rIndex = ri+2;
      const cells = row.map((val, ci)=>{
        if (numericCols.has(ci)){
          const num = (typeof val === 'number') ? val : (String(val).trim()===''?'' : Number(val));
          if (num === '') return '<c r="'+cellRef(ci,rIndex-1)+'"><v></v></c>';
          return '<c r="'+cellRef(ci,rIndex-1)+'"><v>'+ (Number.isFinite(num)?num:0) +'</v></c>';
        }
        return '<c r="'+cellRef(ci,rIndex-1)+'" t="s"><v>'+addS(val)+'</v></c>';
      }).join('');
      sheetData += '<row r="'+rIndex+'">'+cells+'</row>';
    });

    const nCols = headers.length; const nRows = rows.length + 1;
    const lastCol = colLetter(nCols-1);

    const sheet1 = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>\n'+
      '<worksheet xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/spreadsheetml/2006/main" xmlns:r="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships">'+
      '<dimension ref="A1:'+lastCol+nRows+'"/>'+
      '<sheetViews><sheetView workbookViewId="0"/></sheetViews>'+
      '<sheetFormatPr defaultRowHeight="15"/>'+
      '<sheetData>'+sheetData+'</sheetData>'+
      '</worksheet>';

    const workbook = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>\n'+
      '<workbook xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/spreadsheetml/2006/main" xmlns:r="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships">'+
      '<sheets><sheet name="Отчёт" sheetId="1" r:id="rId1"/></sheets>'+
      '</workbook>';

    const wbRels = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>\n'+
      '<Relationships xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships">'+
      '<Relationship Id="rId1" Type="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/worksheet" Target="worksheets/sheet1.xml"/>'+
      '<Relationship Id="rId2" Type="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/styles" Target="styles.xml"/>'+
      '<Relationship Id="rId3" Type="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/sharedStrings" Target="sharedStrings.xml"/>'+
      '</Relationships>';

    const styles = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>\n'+
      '<styleSheet xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/spreadsheetml/2006/main">'+
      '<fonts count="1"><font><sz val="11"/><name val="Calibri"/></font></fonts>'+
      '<fills count="1"><fill><patternFill patternType="none"/></fill></fills>'+
      '<borders count="1"><border/></borders>'+
      '<cellStyleXfs count="1"><xf numFmtId="0" fontId="0" fillId="0" borderId="0"/></cellStyleXfs>'+
      '<cellXfs count="1"><xf numFmtId="0" fontId="0" fillId="0" borderId="0" xfId="0"/></cellXfs>'+
      '</styleSheet>';

    const rels = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>\n'+
      '<Relationships xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/package/2006/relationships">'+
      '<Relationship Id="rId1" Type="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/relationships/officeDocument" Target="xl/workbook.xml"/>'+
      '</Relationships>';

    const contentTypes = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>\n'+
      '<Types xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/package/2006/content-types">'+
      '<Default Extension="rels" ContentType="application/vnd.openxmlformats-package.relationships+xml"/>'+
      '<Default Extension="xml" ContentType="application/xml"/>'+
      '<Override PartName="/xl/workbook.xml" ContentType="application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet.main+xml"/>'+
      '<Override PartName="/xl/worksheets/sheet1.xml" ContentType="application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.worksheet+xml"/>'+
      '<Override PartName="/xl/styles.xml" ContentType="application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.styles+xml"/>'+
      '<Override PartName="/xl/sharedStrings.xml" ContentType="application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sharedStrings+xml"/>'+
      '<Override PartName="/docProps/core.xml" ContentType="application/vnd.openxmlformats-package.core-properties+xml"/>'+
      '<Override PartName="/docProps/app.xml" ContentType="application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.extended-properties+xml"/>'+
      '</Types>';

    const app = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>\n'+
      '<Properties xmlns="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/extended-properties" xmlns:vt="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/officeDocument/2006/docPropsVTypes">'+
      '<Application>MunArt</Application>'+
      '</Properties>';

    const core = '<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>\n'+
      '<cp:coreProperties xmlns:cp="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/package/2006/metadata/core-properties" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:dcterms="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance">'+
      '<dc:title>Отчёт по проектам</dc:title><dc:creator>MunArt</dc:creator><dcterms:created xsi:type="dcterms:W3CDTF">'+new Date().toISOString()+'</dcterms:created>'+
      '</cp:coreProperties>';

    // write files
    zip.file('[Content_Types].xml', contentTypes);
    zip.folder('_rels').file('.rels', rels);
    const xl = zip.folder('xl');
    xl.file('workbook.xml', workbook);
    xl.folder('_rels').file('workbook.xml.rels', wbRels);
    xl.folder('worksheets').file('sheet1.xml', sheet1);
    xl.file('styles.xml', styles);
    xl.file('sharedStrings.xml', sstXml());
    zip.folder('docProps').file('app.xml', app);
    zip.folder('docProps').file('core.xml', core);
    return zip.generateAsync({type:'blob'});
  }

  function makeRowsData(cols, data){
    return data.map((p,i)=> cols.map(col=>{
      const base = DEFAULT_COLS.find(d=>d.key===col.key);
      return base.compute(p,i);
    }));
  }

  async function handleMake(){
    const cols = currentCols();
    const headers = cols.map(c=>c.title);
    const data = getFiltered();
    if (!data.length){ alert('Нет данных по фильтрам'); return; }
    const rows = makeRowsData(cols, data);
    const numericCols = new Set(cols.map((c,idx)=> c.key==='num' ? idx : -1).filter(x=>x>=0));
    await ensureJSZip();
    const blob = await buildXlsx(headers, rows, numericCols);
    const a = document.createElement('a'); a.href = URL.createObjectURL(blob); a.download = 'projects_report.xlsx'; a.style.display='none';
    document.body.appendChild(a); a.click(); setTimeout(()=>{ URL.revokeObjectURL(a.href); a.remove(); },0);
  }

  function install(){
    renderBuilder();
    // Override "Сформировать отчёт" handler
    const btn = $(BTN_ID);
    if (btn){
      const clone = btn.cloneNode(true);
      btn.parentNode.replaceChild(clone, btn);
      clone.addEventListener('click', function(ev){
        ev.preventDefault(); ev.stopPropagation();
        handleMake().catch(err=>{ console.error(err); alert('Ошибка формирования: '+err.message); });
      });
    }
    // Re-render preview when filters change
    const f = ()=> renderPreview();
    qa('#statusBox input, #typesBox input, #dateFrom, #dateTo').forEach(el=> el && el.addEventListener('change', f));
  }
  if (document.readyState === 'loading'){ document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', install); } else { install(); }
})();
</script>

</body>
</html>
===== END FILE: munart_ui\public\prototypes\reports\projects_report.html =====

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_ui\public\prototypes\tasks_types_offline.html (text) =====
<!doctype html>
<html lang="ru">
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
<title>MunArt — Типы поручений (offline)</title>
<style>
  :root{--bg:#0b1020;--panel:#121a2b;--brd:#1f2a44;--txt:#eaf0ff;--muted:#8ea0c2;--chip:#0e1426;--acc:#3b82f6}
  *{box-sizing:border-box} body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--txt);font:14px/1.45 system-ui,Segoe UI,Roboto,Arial}
  .wrap{max-width:1120px;margin:32px auto;padding:0 16px}
  .card{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--brd);border-radius:16px;padding:16px;box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.3)}
  h1{margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:20px} .muted{color:var(--muted)}
  .row{display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  input,select,button,textarea{background:#0d1526;border:1px solid var(--brd);color:var(--txt);padding:10px 12px;border-radius:10px}
  button{cursor:pointer} .pill{padding:6px 10px;border-radius:999px;border:1px solid var(--brd);background:var(--chip);cursor:pointer}
  .pill.active{outline:2px solid var(--acc)} .list{margin-top:12px}
  .item{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:1px dashed var(--brd);padding:10px 0}
  .badge{padding:4px 8px;border:1px solid var(--brd);border-radius:999px;background:#0c1630;color:#cfe0ff}
</style>
<div class="wrap">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>Поручения • типы</h1>
    <div class="muted">Создайте поручение и укажите тип: Аппаратные / Выездные / Прочие. Данные — только в localStorage (offline демо).</div>
    <div class="row" style="margin-top:12px">
      <input id="title" placeholder="Название поручения" style="flex:2 1 360px">
      <select id="type" style="flex:1 1 180px">
        <option>Прочие</option>
        <option>Аппаратные</option>
        <option>Выездные</option>
      </select>
      <button id="create">Создать</button>
    </div>
    <div class="row" style="margin-top:12px">
      <div class="pill active" data-filter="all">Все</div>
      <div class="pill" data-filter="Аппаратные">Аппаратные</div>
      <div class="pill" data-filter="Выездные">Выездные</div>
      <div class="pill" data-filter="Прочие">Прочие</div>
    </div>
    <div class="list" id="list"></div>
  </div>
</div>
<script>
  const KEY="munart_tasks_types_offline";
  const $ = (s)=>document.querySelector(s);
  const $$ = (s)=>Array.from(document.querySelectorAll(s));
  const read=()=>JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(KEY)||"[]");
  const write=(a)=>localStorage.setItem(KEY,JSON.stringify(a));
  const rid=()=>Math.random().toString(36).slice(2,9);

  function render(filter="all"){
    const data=read().filter(x=>filter==="all"||x.type===filter);
    $("#list").innerHTML=data.map(x=>`
      <div class="item">
        <div><strong>${x.title}</strong><div class="muted">#${x.id}</div></div>
        <div class="badge">${x.type}</div>
      </div>`).join("") || `<div class="muted">Пусто</div>`;
    $$(".pill").forEach(p=>p.classList.toggle("active",p.dataset.filter===filter || (filter==="all"&&p.dataset.filter==="all")));
  }

  $("#create").onclick=()=>{
    const title=$("#title").value.trim();
    const type=$("#type").value;
    if(!title){ alert("Введите название"); return; }
    const items=read();
    items.unshift({id:rid(), title, type, created_at:new Date().toISOString()});
    write(items);
    $("#title").value="";
    render(currentFilter);
  };

  let currentFilter="all";
  $$(".pill").forEach(p=>p.onclick=()=>{ currentFilter=p.dataset.filter; render(currentFilter); });

  render();
</script>
</html>

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_ui\src\App.jsx (text) =====
import React, { useMemo, useState, useEffect, useRef } from "react";
import { storage } from "./lib/storageAdapter";
import EmbedIframe from "./components/EmbedIframe";
import Projects  from "./pages/Projects/Beautiful.jsx";
import Tasks     from "./pages/Tasks/Beautiful.jsx";
import Rounds    from "./pages/Rounds/index.jsx"; /* объезды */
import Analytics from "./pages/Analytics/index.jsx";
import Networks  from "./pages/Admin/Networks.jsx";
import Settings  from "./pages/Settings/index.jsx";
import logo from "./assets/logo.png";
import Admin from "./pages/Admin";
import Events from "./pages/Events"; 


import {
  Menu, Home, FolderKanban, ClipboardList, Route as RouteIcon,
  BarChart3, Shield, Settings as SettingsIcon, Bell, ChevronDown,
  ChevronLeft, ChevronRight, User as UserIcon, CalendarDays, LogOut, Moon, Search, FilePlus2
} from "lucide-react";

/* -------------------------- helpers -------------------------- */
function cls(...a){ return a.filter(Boolean).join(" "); }
const normalizeTaskStatus = (s) => {
  s = String(s || '').toLowerCase();
  if (s === "in_progress" || s === "inprogress" || s === "review") return "inprogress";
  if (s === "done") return "done";
  return "todo";
};
const isProjectActive = (p) => {
  const st = String(p?.status || "").toLowerCase();
  if (p?.archived) return false;
  return !["done", "cancelled", "archived"].includes(st);
};
const summarizeProjects = (items) => {
  const list = Array.isArray(items) ? items : [];
  const ok = (p, st) => !p?.archived && String(p?.status||"").toLowerCase() === st;
  return {
    total:        list.length,
    active:       list.filter(isProjectActive).length,
    in_progress:  list.filter(p => ok(p,"in_progress")).length,
    on_hold:      list.filter(p => ok(p,"on_hold")).length,
    done:         list.filter(p => ok(p,"done")).length,
  };
};

/* -------------------------- small UI ------------------------- */
const Card = ({ children, className, ...rest }) => (
  <div {...rest} className={cls(
    "bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700",
    className
  )}>{children}</div>
);
const CardBody = ({ children, className }) => (
  <div className={cls("p-5", className)}>{children}</div>
);

const Calendar = ({ monthOffset = 0 }) => {
  const base = new Date();
  const d = new Date(base.getFullYear(), base.getMonth() + monthOffset, 1);
  const month = d.getMonth(); const year = d.getFullYear();
  const firstDay = new Date(year, month, 1).getDay();
  const startIdx = (firstDay + 6) % 7; // Mon=0
  const daysInMonth = new Date(year, month + 1, 0).getDate();
  const cells = []; for (let i=0;i<startIdx;i++) cells.push(null);
  for (let i=1;i<=daysInMonth;i++) cells.push(i);
  while (cells.length % 7 !== 0) cells.push(null);
  const today = new Date();
  const isToday = (day) => day && day===today.getDate() && month===today.getMonth() && year===today.getFullYear();
  const fmt = new Intl.DateTimeFormat("ru-RU", { month: "long", year: "numeric" }).format(d);
  return (
    <div>
      <div className="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
        <div className="font-semibold capitalize text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100">{fmt}</div>
        <div className="flex gap-2">
          <button className="p-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800"><ChevronLeft size={18}/></button>
          <button className="p-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800"><ChevronRight size={18}/></button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div className="grid grid-cols-7 gap-1 text-center text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase">
        {["пн","вт","ср","чт","пт","сб","вс"].map(w => <div key={w} className="py-1">{w}</div>)}
      </div>
      <div className="mt-1 grid grid-cols-7 gap-1">
        {cells.map((day,i)=>(
          <div key={i} className={cls(
            "h-9 flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg text-sm",
            day ? "bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800/60" : "",
            isToday(day) && "ring-2 ring-sky-400 text-sky-700 font-semibold dark:text-sky-300"
          )}>{day ?? ""}</div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
};

const Metric = ({ label, value, icon, onClick }) => (
  <Card onClick={onClick}
        className={cls(onClick && "cursor-pointer hover:shadow-md transition-shadow")}
        role={onClick ? "button" : undefined}
        aria-label={onClick ? `Открыть: ${label}` : undefined}>
    <CardBody>
      <div className="flex items-start justify-between">
        <div>
          <div className="text-sm text-slate-500">{label}</div>
          <div className="mt-1 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 tabular-nums">{value ?? 0}</div>
        </div>
        <div className="p-2 rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-300/30 to-indigo-300/30 text-sky-600 dark:text-sky-300">
          {icon}
        </div>
      </div>
    </CardBody>
  </Card>
);

const SidebarItem = ({ icon, title, active, collapsed, onClick }) => (
  <button onClick={onClick} className={cls(
    "w-full flex items-center gap-3 px-3 py-2 rounded-xl text-sm",
    active ? "bg-white/90 text-slate-900 shadow-sm dark:bg-slate-800/80 dark:text-white"
           : "text-slate-600 hover:bg-white/70 dark:text-slate-300 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/50"
  )}>
    <span className="shrink-0 opacity-90">{icon}</span>
    {!collapsed && <span className="truncate">{title}</span>}
  </button>
);

/* --------------------- profile drawer ----------------------- */
const ProfileDrawer = ({ open, onClose }) => (
  <div className={cls("fixed inset-0 z-40 transition", open?"pointer-events-auto":"pointer-events-none")}>
    <div className={cls("absolute inset-0 bg-black/30 backdrop-blur-sm transition-opacity", open?"opacity-100":"opacity-0")} onClick={onClose}/>
    <div className={cls(
      "absolute right-0 top-0 h-full w-[360px] bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 shadow-2xl border-l border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 p-6 overflow-y-auto",
      "transition-transform", open ? "translate-x-0" : "translate-x-full"
    )}>
      <div className="flex items-center justify-between">
        <div className="text-lg font-semibold">Профиль пользователя</div>
        <button onClick={onClose} className="p-1.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800"><ChevronRight /></button>
      </div>
      <div className="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4">
        <div className="w-14 h-14 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-400 to-indigo-400 text-white grid place-items-center text-xl font-bold">A</div>
        <div>
          <div className="font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100">Миронов Руслан</div>
          <div className="text-xs text-slate-500">Программист • Администратор</div>
          <div className="mt-1 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">
            <span className="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse" /> online
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div className="mt-6 space-y-4">
        <Card><CardBody>
          <div className="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-100">Быстрые действия</div>
          <div className="mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
	
	
	
	
	
			{[
			  { key: "profile",  label: "Мой профиль",     icon: <UserIcon size={18}/> },
/* 			  { key: "create_from", label: "Создать на основании",  icon: <FilePlus2 size={18}/>,
				onClick: () => window.open("/prototypes/create-from-template.html", "_blank") }, */
			  { key: "logout",   label: "Выйти",           icon: <LogOut size={18}/> },
			].map(a => (
			  <button
				key={a.key}
				type="button"
				onClick={a.onClick}
				aria-label={a.label}
				className="px-3 py-2 rounded-xl border transition-colors !bg-slate-50 !text-slate-700 !border-slate-200 hover:!bg-slate-100 dark:!bg-slate-800 dark:!text-slate-100 dark:!border-slate-700 dark:hover:!bg-slate-700 flex items-center gap-2 justify-center"
			  >
				<span className="shrink-0 opacity-80">{a.icon}</span>
				<span className="truncate">{a.label}</span>
			  </button>
			))}
			
			
			
			
			
			
          </div>
        </CardBody></Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
);

// --- Theme helpers (SPA)
const THEME_KEY = "munart_theme";
function applyTheme(theme){
  const root = document.documentElement;
  root.classList.toggle("dark", theme === "dark");
}
function initTheme(){
  const saved = localStorage.getItem(THEME_KEY);
  const prefDark = window.matchMedia && window.matchMedia("(prefers-color-scheme: dark)").matches;
  applyTheme(saved ?? (prefDark ? "dark" : "light"));
}
function toggleTheme(){
  const isDark = !document.documentElement.classList.contains("dark");
  applyTheme(isDark ? "dark" : "light");
  localStorage.setItem(THEME_KEY, isDark ? "dark" : "light");
}
initTheme();


/* ---------------------------- App ---------------------------- */
export default function App(){
  const [collapsed, setCollapsed] = useState(false);
  const [active, setActive]       = useState(window.location.hash || "dashboard");
  const [profileOpen, setProfileOpen] = useState(false);

  // сводки, которые могут прилетать из встроенных страниц
  const [projStatsMsg, setProjStatsMsg] = useState(null);
  const [taskStatsMsg, setTaskStatsMsg] = useState(null);
  const [netStats, setNetStats]         = useState(null);

  // ---- слушаем postMessage (если страницы встраиваются iframe'ами)
  useEffect(() => {
    const onMsg = (e) => {
      const { type, payload } = e.data || {};
      if (type === "munart:summary")          setNetStats(payload);
      if (type === "munart:projects-summary") setProjStatsMsg(payload);
      if (type === "munart:tasks-summary")    setTaskStatsMsg(payload);
      if (type === "NAVIGATE" && payload)     setActive(payload); // на случай внешней навигации
    };
    window.addEventListener("message", onMsg);
    return () => window.removeEventListener("message", onMsg);
  }, []);

  // ---- всегда держим актуальные проекты из того же стора, что использует «Проекты»
  const [projects, setProjects] = useState(() => (storage.getProjects?.() || []));
  useEffect(() => {
    const pull = () => setProjects(storage.getProjects?.() || []);
    const onData = () => pull();
    const onStorage = (e) => {
      if (!e || !e.key) { pull(); return; }
      if (e.key.includes("munart_projects")) pull();
    };
    window.addEventListener("munart-data", onData);
    window.addEventListener("storage", onStorage);
    const t = setInterval(pull, 2000);
    return () => { window.removeEventListener("munart-data", onData); window.removeEventListener("storage", onStorage); clearInterval(t); };
  }, []);

  // локальная сводка по проектам (если нет postMessage)
  const projStatsLocal = useMemo(() => summarizeProjects(projects), [projects]);
  // финальная сводка: postMessage > локальный расчёт
  const projStats = projStatsMsg || projStatsLocal;

  // задачи
  const tasks = storage.getTasks?.() || [];
  const taskStatsLocal = useMemo(() => {
    const agg = tasks.reduce((a,t)=>{ a[normalizeTaskStatus(t.status)]++; return a; }, {todo:0,inprogress:0,done:0});
    return { todo:agg.todo, inprogress:agg.inprogress, done:agg.done };
  }, [tasks]);
  const taskStats = taskStatsMsg || taskStatsLocal;

  // hash-router
  useEffect(() => {
    const onHash = () => setActive(window.location.hash || "dashboard");
    window.addEventListener("hashchange", onHash);
    return () => window.removeEventListener("hashchange", onHash);
  }, []);

  const brand = (
    <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
      <div className="w-30 h-30 rounded-xl overflow-hidden ring-1 ring-slate-200/70 dark:ring-slate-700 shadow">
		<img src={logo} alt="MunArt" className="w-full h-full object-cover" />
	  </div>
    </div>
  );

  const menu = [
    { key:"dashboard", title:"Главная",            icon:<Home size={18}/> },
    { key:"projects",  title:"Проекты",            icon:<FolderKanban size={18}/> },
    { key:"economy",   title:"Экономика",          icon:<BarChart3 size={18}/> },
    { key:"tasks",     title:"Поручения",          icon:<ClipboardList size={18}/> },
    { key:"analytics", title:"Аналитика",          icon:<BarChart3 size={18}/> },
    { key:"#/admin",          title:"Администрирование", icon:<Shield size={18}/> },
	{ key:"events",           title:"События",           icon:<CalendarDays size={18}/> },
    { key:"#/settings",        title:"Настройки",         icon:<SettingsIcon size={18}/> },
  ];

  return (
    <div className="min-h-screen app-bg">
      <div className="flex">
        {/* Sidebar */}
        <aside className={cls("sticky top-0 h-screen p-3 transition-all", collapsed ? "w-[84px]" : "w-[260px]")}>
          <div className="h-full bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur rounded-2xl border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 flex flex-col shadow-sm">
            <div className="p-3 flex items-center justify-between">
              {brand}
              <button onClick={() => setCollapsed(v=>!v)} className="p-2 rounded-xl hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800">
                <Menu size={18}/>
              </button>
            </div>
            <div className="px-3 pb-3 space-y-1 overflow-y-auto">
              {menu.map(m => (
                <SidebarItem key={m.key} icon={m.icon} title={m.title} collapsed={collapsed}
                  active={active === m.key}
                  onClick={() => {
				  // всегда активируем экран локально
				  setActive(m.key);

				  // синхронизируем hash только для hash-маршрутов
				  if (m.key.startsWith("#/")) {
					if (window.location.hash !== m.key) window.location.hash = m.key;
				  } else {
					// чтобы следующий переход на #/admin гарантированно сработал
					if (window.location.hash) history.replaceState(null, "", " ");
				  }
				}}
                />
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>

        {/* Content */}
        <main className="flex-1 p-4 md:p-6">
          {/* Top bar */}
          <div className="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
            <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div className="relative">
                <Search className="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-400" size={16}/>
                <input placeholder="Поиск"
                       className="pl-9 pr-3 py-2 bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70 border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-xl w-[260px] outline-none focus:ring-2 ring-sky-300" />
              </div>
            </div>

            <div className="flex items-center gap-3">
              {/* mini-сводка задач */}
              {active === "tasks" && (
                <div className="hidden md:flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-xl
                                bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70 border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700
                                text-xs text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 select-none whitespace-nowrap">
                  <span className="opacity-70">Задачи:</span>
                  <span className="inline-flex items-center gap-1" title="К выполнению">
                    <span className="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style={{background:"#64748b"}}/>
                    <b className="tabular-nums">{taskStats.todo}</b>
                  </span>
                  <span className="inline-flex items-center gap-1" title="В работе">
                    <span className="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style={{background:"#22c55e"}}/>
                    <b className="tabular-nums">{taskStats.inprogress}</b>
                  </span>
                  <span className="inline-flex items-center gap-1" title="Готово">
                    <span className="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style={{background:"#3b82f6"}}/>
                    <b className="tabular-nums">{taskStats.done}</b>
                  </span>
                </div>
              )}

              {/* mini-сводка проектов — всегда актуальные данные */}
              {(active === "projects" || active === "economy") && (
                <div className="hidden md:flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-xl
                                bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70 border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700
                                text-xs text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 select-none whitespace-nowrap">
                  <span className="opacity-70">Проекты:</span>
                  <span>всего <b className="font-semibold tabular-nums">{projStats.total}</b></span>
                  <span className="ml-2 inline-flex items-center gap-1" title="В работе">
                    <span className="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style={{background:"#22c55e"}}/>
                    <b className="tabular-nums">{projStats.in_progress}</b>
                  </span>
                  <span className="inline-flex items-center gap-1" title="Пауза">
                    <span className="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style={{background:"#f59e0b"}}/>
                    <b className="tabular-nums">{projStats.on_hold}</b>
                  </span>
                  <span className="inline-flex items-center gap-1" title="Готово">
                    <span className="w-2 h-2 rounded-full" style={{background:"#3b82f6"}}/>
                    <b className="tabular-nums">{projStats.done}</b>
                  </span>
                </div>
              )}

              <button className="relative p-2 rounded-xl bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70 border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-md">
                <Bell size={18}/>
                <span className="absolute -top-1 -right-1 w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-rose-500 text-white text-[10px] grid place-items-center">4</span>
              </button>
              <button onClick={() => setProfileOpen(true)}
                      className="flex items-center gap-2 px-2 py-1.5 rounded-xl bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70 border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 hover:shadow-md">
                <div className="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-400 to-indigo-500 text-white grid place-items-center text-sm font-semibold">A</div>
                <div className="hidden md:block text-left">
                  <div className="text-sm font-semibold leading-4">Миронов Руслан</div>
                  <div className="text-[11px] text-slate-500">Администратор</div>
                </div>
                <ChevronDown size={16} className="opacity-60"/>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Router */}
          {(() => {
            /* if (active === "rounds")      return <Rounds />; */
            if (active === "projects")    return <Projects />;
            if (active === "economy")     return <Economy />;
            if (active === "tasks")       return <Tasks />;
            if (active === "analytics")   return <Analytics />;
            if (active === "#/admin")     return <Admin />;
			if (active === "events")      return <Events />;
            if (active === "#/settings")  return <Settings />;
			// Импорт вспомогательного компонента у вас уже, как правило, есть.
// Роутер/свитч:
			if (active === "rounds") {
				return (
					<iframe
					  src="/prototypes/obezdy_offline.html"
					  style={{width:"100%", height:"100%", border:"0", borderRadius:"16px"}}
					  title="Объезды — offline"
					/>
				  );
				}

            if (active !== "dashboard") return <Placeholder title={menu.find(m=>m.key===active)?.title || "Страница"} />;
            return <Dashboard onOpen={(key)=>setActive(key)} projStats={projStats} taskStats={taskStats} />;
          })()}
        </main>
      </div>

      <ProfileDrawer open={profileOpen} onClose={()=>setProfileOpen(false)}/>
    </div>
  );
}

/* ------------------------- misc pages ------------------------ */
function Placeholder({ title }){
  return (
    <div className="grid place-items-center h-[70vh]">
      <Card className="max-w-xl w-full">
        <CardBody className="text-center">
          <div className="text-2xl font-semibold">{title}</div>
          <div className="mt-2 text-slate-500">Здесь будет функционал страницы. Пока это заглушка.</div>
        </CardBody>
      </Card>
    </div>
  );
}

/* ------------------------- Dashboard ------------------------- */
/** Главная теперь — это встраиваемый HTML прототип */
function Dashboard({ onOpen, projStats, taskStats }){
  const iframeRef = useRef(null);

  // формируем полезную нагрузку для прототипа
  const buildPayload = useMemo(() => {
    const p = projStats || summarizeProjects(storage.getProjects?.() || []);
    const t = taskStats || { todo:0, inprogress:0, done:0 };
    return {
      projects_active: p?.in_progress ?? p?.active ?? 0,
      projects_done:   p?.done ?? 0,
      tasks_new:       t?.todo ?? 0,
      tasks_inwork:    t?.inprogress ?? 0,
    };
  }, [projStats, taskStats]);

  // принимаем сообщения от iframe
  useEffect(() => {
    const onMsg = (e) => {
      if (e.origin !== window.location.origin) return;
      const { type, payload } = e.data || {};
      if (type === "NAVIGATE" && payload) onOpen?.(payload);
      if (type === "munart:ready:dashboard") {
        try {
          iframeRef.current?.contentWindow?.postMessage(
            { type:"munart:dashboard-data", payload: buildPayload },
            window.location.origin
          );
        } catch {}
      }
    };
    window.addEventListener("message", onMsg);
    return () => window.removeEventListener("message", onMsg);
  }, [onOpen, buildPayload]);

  // отправляем актуальные данные при их изменении
  useEffect(() => {
    try {
      iframeRef.current?.contentWindow?.postMessage(
        { type:"munart:dashboard-data", payload: buildPayload },
        window.location.origin
      );
    } catch {}
  }, [buildPayload]);

  return (
    <div className="p-4">
      <div className="h-[calc(100vh-140px)] w-full border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70">
        <EmbedIframe ref={iframeRef} title="Dashboard Prototype" src="/prototypes/munart_dashboard_offline.html" />
      </div>
      <div className="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500 px-1">
        Источник: <code>/public/prototypes/munart_dashboard_offline.html</code>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}

/* ------------------------- Economy -------------------------- */
/** Экономический срез портфеля проектов — offline прототип */
function Economy(){
  const iframeRef = useRef(null);

  return (
    <div className="p-4">
      <div className="h-[calc(100vh-140px)] w-full border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70">
        <EmbedIframe ref={iframeRef} title="Экономика проектов" src="/prototypes/economy.html" />
      </div>
      <div className="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500 px-1">
        Источник: <code>/public/prototypes/economy.html</code>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_ui\src\components\EmbedIframe.jsx (text) =====
import React, { useEffect, useRef, forwardRef } from "react";

const EmbedIframe = forwardRef(function EmbedIframe({ src, title, className }, forwardedRef) {
  const localRef = useRef(null);

  useEffect(() => {
    const el = localRef.current;
    if (!el) return;

    const applyThemeToFrame = () => {
      try {
        const doc = el.contentDocument;
        const win = el.contentWindow;
        if (!doc || !win) return;
        const isDark = document.documentElement.classList.contains('dark');
        const mode  = isDark ? 'dark' : 'light';

        // 1) метки темы
        doc.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', mode);
        doc.documentElement.classList.toggle('dark', isDark);
        doc.body.classList.toggle('theme-dark', isDark);
        doc.body.classList.toggle('theme-light', !isDark);

        // 2) localStorage внутри iframe
        try {
          win.localStorage.setItem('munart_theme', mode);
          win.localStorage.setItem('theme-admin', mode);
          win.dispatchEvent(new StorageEvent('storage', { key: 'munart_theme', newValue: mode }));
          win.dispatchEvent(new StorageEvent('storage', { key: 'theme-admin',  newValue: mode }));
        } catch {}

        // 3) тёмный override — подключаем/отключаем файл
        const LINK_ID = 'embedded-dark-css';
        const existing = doc.getElementById(LINK_ID);
        if (isDark) {
          if (!existing) {
            const link = doc.createElement('link');
            link.id = LINK_ID;
            link.rel = 'stylesheet';
            link.href = '/prototypes/overrides/embedded-dark.css';
            doc.head.appendChild(link);
          }
        } else if (existing) {
          existing.remove();
        }
      } catch {}
    };

    // --- sanitize var(...) в SVG r
    const resolveVarAttr = (node, attr, win) => {
      try {
        const raw = node.getAttribute(attr);
        if (!raw || raw.indexOf('var(') === -1) return;
        const m = /var\(\s*(--[^),\s]+)\s*(?:,[^)]+)?\)/.exec(raw);
        if (!m) return;
        const cssName = m[1];
        const cssVal = win.getComputedStyle(node).getPropertyValue(cssName).trim();
        const num = parseFloat(cssVal);
        if (!isNaN(num)) node.setAttribute(attr, String(num));
      } catch {}
    };
    const fixSvgVars = () => {
      try {
        const doc = el.contentDocument;
        const win = el.contentWindow;
        if (!doc || !win) return;
        doc.querySelectorAll('circle[r*="var("]').forEach(c => resolveVarAttr(c, 'r', win));
      } catch {}
    };

    let mo;
    const startObserver = () => {
      try {
        const doc = el.contentDocument;
        const win = el.contentWindow;
        if (!doc || !win) return;
        mo = new MutationObserver((mutList) => {
          for (const mut of mutList) {
            if (mut.type === 'attributes' && mut.attributeName === 'r' && mut.target.nodeName === 'CIRCLE') {
              resolveVarAttr(mut.target, 'r', win);
            }
            if (mut.type === 'childList' && mut.addedNodes?.length) {
              mut.addedNodes.forEach(n => {
                if (n.querySelectorAll) {
                  n.querySelectorAll('circle[r*="var("]').forEach(c => resolveVarAttr(c, 'r', win));
                }
              });
            }
          }
        });
        mo.observe(doc, { subtree: true, childList: true, attributes: true, attributeFilter: ['r'] });
      } catch {}
    };

    const onLoad = () => {
      try {
        const doc = el.contentDocument;
        if (!doc) return;

        // 1) CSS «встроенный режим»
        const style = doc.createElement("style");
        style.setAttribute("data-injected", "embedded");
        style.textContent = `
.embedded body { background: transparent; }
header, .header, .app-header, .topbar, .app-topbar,
aside, .aside, .sidebar, .app-sidebar, .layout-sidebar, .left-menu, .brand, .brand-box {
  display: none !important;
}
.layout, .page, .content, .container, main, .app-content, .app-shell, .wrapper {
  margin: 0 !important;
  padding-left: 0 !important;
  padding-top: 0 !important;
}
#toggleThemeLogin, #btnTheme, .theme-toggle, .theme-switch, [data-theme-toggle] {
  display: none !important;
}
html, body { overscroll-behavior: contain; }
`;
        doc.head.appendChild(style);
        doc.documentElement.classList.add("embedded");

        // 2) МОСТ: слушаем команды родителя и кликаем нужные элементы
        const bridge = doc.createElement('script');
        bridge.textContent = `
(function(){
  function byText(selList){
    const candidates = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('button, a, [role="button"], .btn'));
    for (const t of selList){
      const found = candidates.find(n => (n.textContent||'').trim().toLowerCase() === t.toLowerCase());
      if (found) return found;
    }
    return null;
  }
  function clickFirst(selectors){
    for (const s of selectors){
      const el = document.querySelector(s);
      if (el){ el.click(); return true; }
    }
    return false;
  }
  window.addEventListener('message', function(e){
    if (e.origin !== location.origin) return;
    const data = e.data||{};
    if (data.type !== 'munart:cmd') return;
    const cmd = data.payload?.cmd;

    // --- команды для "Сетей"
    if (cmd === 'net.autolayout'){
      if (clickFirst(['[data-action="layout"]','#btnLayout','[title*="авто"]','[title*="расклад"]'])) return;
      const el = byText(['Авто-раскладка','Автораскладка']); if (el) el.click();
    }
    else if (cmd === 'net.export.json'){
      if (clickFirst(['[data-action="export-json"]','#btnExportJSON'])) return;
      const el = byText(['Экспорт JSON','Export JSON']); if (el) el.click();
    }
    else if (cmd === 'net.export.png'){
      if (clickFirst(['[data-action="export-png"]','#btnExportPNG'])) return;
      const el = byText(['PNG','Снимок PNG']); if (el) el.click();
    }
    else if (cmd === 'generic.click' && data.payload?.selector){
      const el = document.querySelector(data.payload.selector); if (el) el.click();
    }
  }, false);
})();`;
        doc.head.appendChild(bridge);

        // 3) применяем тему и чиним SVG
        applyThemeToFrame();
        fixSvgVars();
        startObserver();
      } catch {}
    };

    el.addEventListener("load", onLoad);

    const onStorage = (e) => {
      if (e.key === 'theme-admin') {
        applyThemeToFrame();
        fixSvgVars();
      }
    };
    window.addEventListener('storage', onStorage);

    return () => {
      el.removeEventListener("load", onLoad);
      window.removeEventListener('storage', onStorage);
      if (mo) try { mo.disconnect(); } catch {}
    };
  }, []);

  const withEmbedFlag = src.includes("?") ? `${src}&embed=1` : `${src}?embed=1`;

  const setRef = (node) => {
    localRef.current = node;
    if (typeof forwardedRef === 'function') forwardedRef(node);
    else if (forwardedRef) forwardedRef.current = node;
  };

  return (
    <iframe
      ref={setRef}
      title={title}
      src={withEmbedFlag}
      className={className || "w-full h-full"}
      style={{ border: "none" }}
    />
  );
});

export default EmbedIframe;
===== END FILE: munart_ui\src\components\EmbedIframe.jsx =====

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_ui\src\index.css (text) =====
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

/* ===== Calm/Fog theme tokens ===== */
:root{
  /* LIGHT — максимально нейтральный «туман» */
  --bg0:#1c3155;            /* 7fffd4 базовый фон, 1c3155 - по бренд буку*/
  --bg1:#EDF1F5;            /* второй тон почти без акцента, поверх первого       */
  --panel:#FFFFFF;          /* панели/модалки                     */
  --card:#FFFFFF;           /* карточки                           */
  --brd:#E6EAF2;            /* границы                            */
  --text:#0F172A;           /* основной текст                     */
  --muted:#64748B;          /* вторичный текст                    */
  --chip:rgba(2,6,23,.03);  /* фон чипов/псевдо-инпутов           */
  --brand1:#22C55E;         /* брендовые — без изменения          */
  --brand2:#10B981;
  --accent:#3B82F6;
  --rose:#EF4444; --amber:#F59E0B; --zinc:#9CA3AF;
  --shadow:0 8px 28px rgba(15,23,42,.06);

  /* RGB каналы для color-mix */
  --bg0-rgb: 242,244,247; /*  */
  --panel-rgb: 255,255,255;/*  */
  --text-rgb: 15,23,42;

  color-scheme: light;
}

/* ТЁМНАЯ — мягкая, без засветов */
:root.dark{
  --bg0:#0F172A; --bg1:#0B1220;
  --panel:#0F172A; --card:rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  --brd:#1F2937;
  --text:#E5E7EB; --muted:#94A3B8;
  --chip:rgba(255,255,255,.06);
  --brand1:#22C55E; --brand2:#10B981; --accent:#93C5FD;
  --rose:#FB7185; --amber:#FBBF24; --zinc:#737373;
  --shadow:0 6px 28px rgba(2,6,23,.16);

  --bg0-rgb: 15,23,42;
  --panel-rgb: 15,23,42;
  --text-rgb: 229,231,235;

  color-scheme: dark;
}

/* Базовый фон приложения + «якорный» класс */
html, body, #root { height: 100%; }
body{
  font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Noto Sans, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji;
  color: var(--text);
}
.app-bg{
  /* ровный спокойный фон без активного цвета */
  background:
    radial-gradient(1200px 600px at 55% -5%, var(--bg1), transparent),
    linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg0), var(--bg1));
}

/* ===== Переназначаем популярные Tailwind-утилиты на токены ===== */
/* Фоны */
.bg-white{ background-color: var(--panel) !important; }
.bg-white\/90{ background-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(var(--panel-rgb)) 90%, transparent) !important; }
 background-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(var(--panel-rgb)) 92%, transparent) !important; /* кнопки все */
/* dark-фоны, которые часто встречаются у вас */
.dark .bg-slate-900{ background-color: var(--bg0) !important; }
.dark .bg-slate-900\/60{ background-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(var(--bg0-rgb)) 40%, transparent) !important; }
.dark .bg-slate-900\/70{ background-color: color-mix(in srgb, rgb(var(--bg0-rgb)) 30%, transparent) !important; }

/* Текст */
.text-slate-900,.text-gray-900,.text-slate-800{ color: var(--text) !important; }
.text-slate-700,.text-gray-700{ color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--text) 80%, transparent) !important; }
.text-slate-600,.text-slate-500,.text-gray-500{ color: var(--muted) !important; }

/* Бордеры / карточки */
.border-slate-200,.border-gray-200{ border-color: var(--brd) !important; }
.shadow{ box-shadow: var(--shadow) !important; }

/* Чипы/кнопки-призраки */
.chip, .btn-ghost{ background: var(--chip); border:1px solid var(--brd); color:var(--text); }
