===== BEGIN FILE: munart_ui\src\lib\storageAdapter.js (text) =====
// munart_ui/src/lib/storageAdapter.js
const WK = 'munart_workspace_v1';
const PF = 'munart_admin_prefs_v1';

export const storage = {
  // что было
  DEFAULT_PREFS: { grid: true, showLabels: true, defaultEdge: 'L3', maskSensitive: false },

  getWorkspace() {
    try {
      const raw = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(WK) || 'null');
      const ws = (raw && typeof raw === 'object') ? raw : {};
      if (!Array.isArray(ws.nodes)) ws.nodes = [];
      if (!Array.isArray(ws.edges)) ws.edges = [];
      if (!ws.view) ws.view = { x: 0, y: 0, k: 1 };
      localStorage.setItem(WK, JSON.stringify(ws));
      return ws;
    } catch {
      return { nodes: [], edges: [], view: { x: 0, y: 0, k: 1 } };
    }
  },

  setWorkspace(data) {
    localStorage.setItem(WK, JSON.stringify(data));
  },

  getPrefs() {
    try {
      const cur = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(PF) || 'null') || {};
      return { ...this.DEFAULT_PREFS, ...cur };
    } catch {
      return { ...this.DEFAULT_PREFS };
    }
  },

  setPrefs(patch) {
    const merged = { ...this.getPrefs(), ...patch };
    localStorage.setItem(PF, JSON.stringify(merged));
    return merged;
  },

  // оставим, но не будем ими больше автоматически подменять пустые массивы
  DEFAULT_PROJECTS: [
    { id: 'p-core', name: 'Core infra', owner: 'Ops', budget: 1200, status: 'active' },
    { id: 'p-erp',  name: 'ERP rollout', owner: 'IT',  budget: 3400, status: 'active' },
    { id: 'p-ml',   name: 'ML PoC',      owner: 'R&D', budget:  800, status: 'archived' },
  ],
  DEFAULT_TASKS: [
    { id: 't-1', title: 'Согласовать ТЗ', projectId: 'p-core', assignee: 'PM',  status: 'todo',       due: '2025-11-01' },
    { id: 't-2', title: 'План миграции',  projectId: 'p-core', assignee: 'Ops', status: 'in_progress', due: '2025-11-10' },
    { id: 't-3', title: 'Подготовка ERP', projectId: 'p-erp',  assignee: 'IT',  status: 'done',       due: '2025-10-21' },
  ],

  rid() {
    return Math.random().toString(36).slice(2, 10);
  },

  // ← ключевые две функции

  getProjects() {
    const K = 'munart_projects_v1';
    try {
      const arr = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(K) || 'null');
      if (Array.isArray(arr)) return arr;
    } catch (e) {
      // игнор
    }
    // если хранилище было пустым или битым — кладём ПУСТОЙ массив
    const empty = [];
    localStorage.setItem(K, JSON.stringify(empty));
    return empty;
  },

  setProjects(list) {
    localStorage.setItem('munart_projects_v1', JSON.stringify(list));
    window.dispatchEvent(new Event('munart-data'));
    return list;
  },

  getTasks() {
    const K = 'munart_tasks_v1';
    try {
      const arr = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(K) || 'null');
      if (Array.isArray(arr)) return arr;
    } catch (e) {
      // игнор
    }
    // ПУСТО, а не демо
    const empty = [];
    localStorage.setItem(K, JSON.stringify(empty));
    return empty;
  },

  setTasks(list) {
    localStorage.setItem('munart_tasks_v1', JSON.stringify(list));
    window.dispatchEvent(new Event('munart-data'));
    return list;
  },
};
===== END FILE: munart_ui\src\lib\storageAdapter.js =====

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_ui\src\main.jsx (text) =====
// src/main.jsx
import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom/client'
import App from './App.jsx'
import './index.css'

// --- NEW: централизованная функция применения темы
function applyTheme(next) {
  const t = next || localStorage.getItem('theme-admin') || 'light';
  const root = document.documentElement;
  root.setAttribute('data-theme', t);
  root.classList.toggle('dark', t === 'dark');
}
applyTheme();

// --- NEW: реагируем на смену темы из "Настроек" и из других вкладок
window.addEventListener('storage', (e) => {
  if (e.key === 'theme-admin') applyTheme(e.newValue);
});

ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root')).render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
  </React.StrictMode>
)
===== END FILE: munart_ui\src\main.jsx =====

import React, { useState } from "react";
import EmbedIframe from "../../components/EmbedIframe";

export default function Admin(){
  const tabs = [
    {key:"panel",  title:"Панель управления", src:"/prototypes/Master_admin.html"},
    {key:"nets",   title:"Сети",               src:"/prototypes/networks_v5_userview.html"},
    {key:"history",title:"История",            src:"/prototypes/History.html"},
  ];
  const [active, setActive] = useState("panel");
  const cur = tabs.find(t => t.key === active);

  return (
    <div className="p-4">
      <div className="mb-3 flex gap-2">
        {tabs.map(t => (
          <button key={t.key}
            className={
			  "px-3 py-1.5 rounded-xl border transition-colors " +
			  (t.key===active
				? "bg-sky-50 text-sky-800 border-sky-200 ring-2 ring-sky-300 " +
				  "dark:bg-slate-800/60 dark:text-sky-200 dark:border-slate-600 dark:ring-slate-600/40"
				: "bg-white/90 text-slate-700 border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50 " +
				  "dark:bg-slate-900/70 dark:text-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/70"
			  )
			}
			onClick={() => setActive(t.key)}>
            {t.title}
          </button>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div className="h-[calc(100vh-180px)] w-full border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70">
        <EmbedIframe title={"Admin: " + cur.title} src={cur.src} />
      </div>
      <div className="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500 px-1">Источник: <code>{cur.src}</code></div>
    </div>
  );
}

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_ui\src\pages\Analytics\index.jsx (text) =====
import React, { useRef, useEffect, useState } from "react";

const TABS = [
  { id: "slice",  title: "Срез" },
  { id: "deep",   title: "Глубокий анализ" },
  { id: "anoms", title: "Аномалии" },  // если в офлайне нет экспорта, ниже создадим секцию-заглушку
];

export default function Analytics() {
  const [tab, setTab] = useState("slice");
  const iframeRef = useRef(null);

  // при смене вкладки — сообщаем во фрейм без перезагрузки
  useEffect(() => {
    const win = iframeRef.current?.contentWindow;
    if (!win) return;
    win.postMessage({ type: "analytics:setTab", tab }, "*");
  }, [tab]);

  return (
    <div className="p-4">
	<div className="mb-3 flex gap-2">
	  {TABS.map(t => (
		<button
		  key={t.id}
		  onClick={() => setTab(t.id)}
		  className={
			"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-xl border transition-colors " +
			(tab === t.id
			  ? "bg-sky-50 text-sky-800 border-sky-200 ring-2 ring-sky-300 " +
				"dark:bg-slate-800/60 dark:text-sky-200 dark:border-slate-600 dark:ring-slate-600/40"
			  : "bg-white/90 text-slate-700 border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50 " +
				"dark:bg-slate-900/70 dark:text-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/70"
			)
		  }
		>
		  {t.title}
		</button>
	  ))}
	</div>

      {/* Сам iframe: прячем внутренние (красные) вкладки режимом embed=1 */}
      <div className="h-[calc(100vh-180px)] w-full border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70">
        <iframe
		  ref={iframeRef}
		  title="Analytics offline"
		  src={`/prototypes/analytics_offline_v2.html?embed=1&tab=${tab}`}
		  style={{ width: "100%", height: "100%", border: 0 }}
		/>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
===== END FILE: munart_ui\src\pages\Analytics\index.jsx =====

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_ui\src\pages\Events\index.jsx (text) =====
import React, { useEffect, useMemo, useState } from "react";
import {
  Plus, Star, StarOff, Trash2, Edit3, Save, X, Search
} from "lucide-react";

/** Ключи хранилища */
const LS_POSTS = "munart_events_posts_v1";
const LS_NOTES = "munart_notes_v1";
const LS_EOD   = "munart_event_of_day_id_v1"; // id «События дня»

/** Утилиты */
const nowISO = () => new Date().toISOString();
const fmt = (s) => new Date(s).toLocaleString();

/** Заглушки палитры/классов в стиле приложения */
const card = "bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70 border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl shadow-sm";
const btnBase =
  "inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2 rounded-xl border transition-colors";
const btnSoft =
  `${btnBase} bg-slate-50 text-slate-700 border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700 dark:hover:bg-slate-700`;
const btnPrimary =
  `${btnBase} bg-sky-600 text-white border-sky-700 hover:bg-sky-700 dark:bg-sky-600/90 dark:hover:bg-sky-600`;
const tabCls = (active) =>
  "px-3 py-1.5 rounded-xl border transition-colors " +
  (active
    ? "bg-sky-50 text-sky-800 border-sky-200 ring-2 ring-sky-300 dark:bg-slate-800/60 dark:text-sky-200 dark:border-slate-600 dark:ring-slate-600/40"
    : "bg-white/90 text-slate-700 border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-900/70 dark:text-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/70");

export default function Events() {
  const [tab, setTab] = useState("pubs"); // pubs | notes

  // --- Publications
  const [posts, setPosts] = useState(() => {
    try { return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(LS_POSTS) || "[]"); }
    catch { return []; }
  });
  const [eventOfDayId, setEventOfDayId] = useState(() => localStorage.getItem(LS_EOD) || "");
  const [q, setQ] = useState("");
  const [onlyEod, setOnlyEod] = useState(false);

  // форма публикации/редакции
  const emptyPost = { id:"", title:"", body:"", tags:"", createdAt: nowISO(), eod:false };
  const [draft, setDraft] = useState(emptyPost);
  const [editId, setEditId] = useState("");

  useEffect(()=> localStorage.setItem(LS_POSTS, JSON.stringify(posts)), [posts]);
  useEffect(()=> {
    if (eventOfDayId) localStorage.setItem(LS_EOD, eventOfDayId);
    else localStorage.removeItem(LS_EOD);
  }, [eventOfDayId]);

  const filtered = useMemo(() => {
    const needle = q.trim().toLowerCase();
    return posts
      .filter(p => (!onlyEod || p.id === eventOfDayId))
      .filter(p => !needle ||
        p.title.toLowerCase().includes(needle) ||
        p.body.toLowerCase().includes(needle) ||
        (p.tags||"").toLowerCase().includes(needle))
      .sort((a,b)=> (b.createdAt||"").localeCompare(a.createdAt||""));
  }, [posts, q, onlyEod, eventOfDayId]);

  const savePost = () => {
    const t = draft.title.trim();
    if (!t) return;
    const id = editId || `post_${Date.now()}`;
    const eod = draft.eod || false;

    // если ставим «Событие дня» при сохранении — сбросить у остальных
    let next = posts.filter(p => p.id !== id);
    next = [
      ...next,
      { ...draft, id, createdAt: editId ? draft.createdAt : nowISO(), eod }
    ];
    if (eod) setEventOfDayId(id);
    setPosts(next);
    setDraft(emptyPost);
    setEditId("");
  };

  const removePost = (id) => {
    const next = posts.filter(p => p.id !== id);
    if (eventOfDayId === id) setEventOfDayId("");
    setPosts(next);
  };

  const startEdit = (p) => {
    setEditId(p.id);
    setDraft({ ...p });
  };

  const cancelEdit = () => { setEditId(""); setDraft(emptyPost); };

  const toggleEod = (p) => {
    const id = p.id;
    const newId = (eventOfDayId === id) ? "" : id;
    setEventOfDayId(newId);
    setPosts(posts.map(x => x.id === id ? { ...x, eod: newId === id } : { ...x, eod:false }));
  };

  // --- Notes
  const [notes, setNotes] = useState(() => {
    try { return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(LS_NOTES) || "[]"); }
    catch { return []; }
  });
  const [noteText, setNoteText] = useState("");
  const [noteQ, setNoteQ] = useState("");

  useEffect(()=> localStorage.setItem(LS_NOTES, JSON.stringify(notes)), [notes]);

  const addNote = () => {
    const v = noteText.trim();
    if (!v) return;
    setNotes([{ id:`note_${Date.now()}`, text:v, createdAt: nowISO() }, ...notes]);
    setNoteText("");
  };
  const delNote = (id) => setNotes(notes.filter(n => n.id !== id));
  const notesFiltered = useMemo(() => {
    const needle = noteQ.trim().toLowerCase();
    return notes
      .filter(n => !needle || n.text.toLowerCase().includes(needle))
      .sort((a,b)=> (b.createdAt||"").localeCompare(a.createdAt||""));
  }, [notes, noteQ]);

  return (
    <div className="p-4 space-y-3">
      {/* Tabs */}
      <div className="flex gap-2">
        <button className={tabCls(tab==="pubs")} onClick={()=>setTab("pubs")}>Публикации</button>
        <button className={tabCls(tab==="notes")} onClick={()=>setTab("notes")}>Заметки</button>
      </div>

      {/* === Публикации === */}
      {tab==="pubs" && (
        <div className={`p-4 ${card}`}>
          {/* Форма */}
          <div className="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div className="space-y-3">
              <div>
                <div className="text-sm mb-1">Заголовок</div>
                <input
                  className="w-full px-3 py-2 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                  placeholder="Например: Запуск нового проекта"
                  value={draft.title}
                  onChange={e=>setDraft({...draft, title:e.target.value})}
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <div className="text-sm mb-1">Текст публикации</div>
                <textarea
                  rows={6}
                  className="w-full px-3 py-2 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                  placeholder="Краткое описание события…"
                  value={draft.body}
                  onChange={e=>setDraft({...draft, body:e.target.value})}
                />
              </div>
              <div className="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <div>
                  <div className="text-sm mb-1">Теги (через запятую)</div>
                  <input
                    className="w-full px-3 py-2 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                    placeholder="#релиз, #финансы"
                    value={draft.tags}
                    onChange={e=>setDraft({...draft, tags:e.target.value})}
                  />
                </div>
                <label className="flex items-center gap-2 mt-6">
                  <input type="checkbox" checked={!!draft.eod}
                         onChange={e=>setDraft({...draft, eod:e.target.checked})}/>
                  <span className="font-medium">Событие дня</span>
                </label>
              </div>

              <div className="flex gap-2">
                <button className={btnPrimary} onClick={savePost}>
                  {editId ? <><Save size={16}/> Сохранить</> : <><Plus size={16}/> Опубликовать</>}
                </button>
                {editId && (
                  <button className={btnSoft} onClick={cancelEdit}><X size={16}/> Отмена</button>
                )}
              </div>
            </div>

            {/* Поиск/фильтр */}
            <div className="space-y-3">
              <div className="text-sm mb-1">Поиск и фильтр</div>
              <div className="flex gap-2">
                <div className="flex-1 relative">
                  <Search size={16} className="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 opacity-60"/>
                  <input
                    className="w-full pl-9 pr-3 py-2 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                    placeholder="Найти по заголовку, тексту или тегам…"
                    value={q}
                    onChange={e=>setQ(e.target.value)}
                  />
                </div>
                <label className={`${btnSoft} cursor-pointer`}>
                  <input type="checkbox" className="mr-2"
                         checked={onlyEod} onChange={e=>setOnlyEod(e.target.checked)}/>
                  Только «Событие дня»
                </label>
              </div>

              {/* Плашка текущего Event of Day */}
              <div className="text-xs text-slate-500">
                Текущий «Событие дня»: {eventOfDayId ? <span className="text-sky-600">{eventOfDayId}</span> : "— не назначено"}
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Лента */}
          <div className="mt-5 space-y-3">
            {filtered.length === 0 && (
              <div className="text-sm text-slate-500">Публикаций нет.</div>
            )}
            {filtered.map(p => (
              <article key={p.id} className="p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200/70 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white/70 dark:bg-slate-900/50">
                <div className="flex items-start gap-3 justify-between">
                  <div>
                    <div className="text-lg font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">
                      {p.title}
                      {p.id === eventOfDayId && (
                        <span className="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 border border-amber-200">
                          Событие дня
                        </span>
                      )}
                    </div>
                    <div className="text-xs text-slate-500">{fmt(p.createdAt)}</div>
                  </div>
                  <div className="flex gap-1">
                    <button className={btnSoft} title="Сделать событием дня" onClick={()=>toggleEod(p)}>
                      {p.id === eventOfDayId ? <><Star size={16}/> Снять</> : <><StarOff size={16}/> Назначить</>}
                    </button>
                    <button className={btnSoft} onClick={()=>startEdit(p)}><Edit3 size={16}/> Править</button>
                    <button className={btnSoft} onClick={()=>removePost(p.id)}><Trash2 size={16}/> Удалить</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
                {p.tags && (
                  <div className="mt-2 flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                    {p.tags.split(",").map((t,i)=>(
                      <span key={i} className="text-xs px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 border border-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 dark:text-slate-300 dark:border-slate-700">
                        #{t.trim()}
                      </span>
                    ))}
                  </div>
                )}
                {p.body && <p className="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-200 whitespace-pre-wrap">{p.body}</p>}
              </article>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      )}

      {/* === Заметки === */}
      {tab==="notes" && (
        <div className={`p-4 ${card}`}>
          <div className="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
            <div className="md:col-span-2">
              <div className="text-sm mb-1">Новая заметка</div>
              <textarea
                rows={4}
                className="w-full px-3 py-2 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                placeholder="Быстрый захват мысли…"
                value={noteText}
                onChange={e=>setNoteText(e.target.value)}
              />
              <div className="mt-2">
                <button className={btnPrimary} onClick={addNote}><Plus size={16}/> Добавить</button>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div className="text-sm mb-1">Поиск</div>
              <div className="relative">
                <Search size={16} className="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 opacity-60"/>
                <input
                  className="w-full pl-9 pr-3 py-2 rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                  placeholder="Фильтр заметок…"
                  value={noteQ}
                  onChange={e=>setNoteQ(e.target.value)}
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div className="mt-4 grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
            {notesFiltered.map(n=>(
              <div key={n.id} className="p-3 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white/70 dark:bg-slate-900/50">
                <div className="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-1">{fmt(n.createdAt)}</div>
                <div className="text-sm whitespace-pre-wrap">{n.text}</div>
                <div className="mt-2 flex justify-end">
                  <button className={btnSoft} onClick={()=>delNote(n.id)}><Trash2 size={16}/> Удалить</button>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
            {notesFiltered.length===0 && (
              <div className="text-sm text-slate-500">Заметок нет.</div>
            )}
          </div>
        </div>
      )}
    </div>
  );
}
===== END FILE: munart_ui\src\pages\Events\index.jsx =====

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_ui\src\pages\Projects\Beautiful.jsx (text) =====
import React from "react";
import EmbedIframe from "../../components/EmbedIframe";

export default function Projects(){
  return (
    <div className="p-4">
      <div className="h-[calc(100vh-140px)] w-full border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70">
        <EmbedIframe title="Projects Prototype" src="/prototypes/munart_projects_offline_light_auth.html" />
      </div>
      <div className="mt-2 text-xs text-slate-500 px-1">
        Источник: <code>/public/prototypes/munart_projects_offline_light_auth.html</code>.

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_ui\src\pages\Projects\index.jsx (text) =====
import React, { useMemo, useState } from 'react';
import { storage } from '../../lib/storageAdapter';

export default function Projects(){
  const [items, setItems] = useState(storage.getProjects());
  const [form, setForm]   = useState({ name:'', owner:'', budget:'' });

  const add = () => {
    if(!form.name.trim()) return;
    const p = {
      id: storage.rid(),
      name: form.name.trim(),
      owner: form.owner || '—',
      budget: Number(form.budget || 0),
      status: 'active'
    };
    const next = [...items, p];
    setItems(storage.setProjects(next));
    setForm({ name:'', owner:'', budget:'' });
  };

  const toggle = (id) => {
    const next = items.map(p => p.id === id
      ? { ...p, status: p.status === 'active' ? 'archived' : 'active' }
      : p
    );
    setItems(storage.setProjects(next));
  };

  const total = useMemo(
    () => items.reduce((s,p)=> s + (p.budget||0), 0),
    [items]
  );

  return (
    <div className="p-4">
      <div className="max-w-4xl bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70 border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5">
        <div className="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100">Проекты</h2>
          <div className="text-sm text-slate-500">
            Итого бюджет: <b className="tabular-nums">{total.toLocaleString('ru-RU')}</b> ₽
          </div>
        </div>

        <div className="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <input
            className="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 w-56"
            placeholder="Название"
            value={form.name}
            onChange={e=>setForm({...form, name:e.target.value})}
          />
          <input
            className="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 w-40"
            placeholder="Владелец"
            value={form.owner}
            onChange={e=>setForm({...form, owner:e.target.value})}
          />
          <input
            type="number"
            className="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 w-36"
            placeholder="Бюджет"
            value={form.budget}
            onChange={e=>setForm({...form, budget:e.target.value})}
          />
          <button onClick={add} className="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-sky-600 hover:bg-sky-700 text-white">
            Добавить
          </button>
        </div>

        <div className="overflow-x-auto">
          <table className="w-full text-sm">
            <thead className="text-left text-slate-500">
              <tr>
                <th className="p-2">Проект</th>
                <th className="p-2">Владелец</th>
                <th className="p-2">Бюджет</th>
                <th className="p-2">Статус</th>
                <th className="p-2"></th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              {items.map(p=>(
                <tr key={p.id} className="border-t border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700">
                  <td className="p-2">{p.name}</td>
                  <td className="p-2">{p.owner}</td>
                  <td className="p-2 tabular-nums">{(p.budget||0).toLocaleString('ru-RU')}</td>
                  <td className="p-2">
                    <span className={p.status==='active' ? 'text-emerald-600' : 'text-slate-400'}>
                      {p.status}
                    </span>
                  </td>
                  <td className="p-2">
                    <button onClick={()=>toggle(p.id)} className="px-2 py-1 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800">
                      {p.status==='active' ? 'Архив' : 'Активировать'}
                    </button>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              ))}
              {!items.length && (
                <tr>
                  <td className="p-2 text-slate-500" colSpan={5}>Пока пусто</td>
                </tr>
              )}
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
===== END FILE: munart_ui\src\pages\Projects\index.jsx =====

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_ui\src\pages\Settings\index.jsx (text) =====
// src/pages/Settings/index.jsx
import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react";
import { storage } from "../../lib/storageAdapter"; // для вкладки "Сети"

export default function Settings(){
  // --- вкладки
  const [tab, setTab] = useState("interface");

  // --- Уведомления (заготовка)
  const [notif, setNotif] = useState(() => {
    try { return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("munart_notif_v1") || "{}"); }
    catch { return {}; }
  });
  useEffect(()=>localStorage.setItem("munart_notif_v1", JSON.stringify(notif)), [notif]);

  // --- Интерфейс
  const [ui, setUi] = useState(() => {
    try { return JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("munart_ui_v1") || "{}"); }
    catch { return {}; }
  });
  useEffect(()=>localStorage.setItem("munart_ui_v1", JSON.stringify(ui)), [ui]);

  // применяем тему при входе
  useEffect(() => {
    const theme = ui.theme ?? localStorage.getItem("munart_theme") ?? "system";
    applyTheme(theme);
  // eslint-disable-next-line react-hooks/exhaustive-deps
  }, []);

  const applyTheme = (theme) => {
    if (theme === "dark" || theme === "light") {
      document.documentElement.classList.toggle("dark", theme === "dark");
      localStorage.setItem("munart_theme", theme);
    } else {
      // system
      document.documentElement.classList.toggle("dark", window.matchMedia("(prefers-color-scheme: dark)").matches);
      localStorage.removeItem("munart_theme");
    }
    // оповестим все iframes/вкладки
    window.dispatchEvent(new StorageEvent("storage", { key: "munart_theme", newValue: theme }));
  };

  // --- Сети (оставляем ваши prefs)
  const [netPrefs, setNetPrefs] = useState(storage.getPrefs());
  const saveNet = (patch) => {
    const np = storage.setPrefs({ ...netPrefs, ...patch });
    setNetPrefs(np);
    window.dispatchEvent(new StorageEvent("storage", { key: "munart_admin_prefs_v1", newValue: JSON.stringify(np) }));
  };

  return (
    <div className="p-4">
      <div className="mb-3 flex gap-2">
        {[
          {k:"interface", t:"Интерфейс"},
          {k:"notifications", t:"Уведомления"},
          {k:"network", t:"Сети"},
        ].map(x=>(
		<button
		  key={x.k}
		  onClick={() => setTab(x.k)}
		  className={
			"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-xl border transition-colors " +
			(tab===x.k
			  ? "bg-sky-50 text-sky-800 border-sky-200 ring-2 ring-sky-300 " +
				"dark:bg-slate-800/60 dark:text-sky-200 dark:border-slate-600 dark:ring-slate-600/40"
			  : "bg-white/90 text-slate-700 border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50 " +
				"dark:bg-slate-900/70 dark:text-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/70"
			)
		  }
		>
		  {x.t}
		</button>

        ))}
      </div>

      {/* === Вкладка: Интерфейс === */}
      {tab==="interface" && (
        <div className="max-w-3xl bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70 border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5">
          <h2 className="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Интерфейс</h2>

          <div className="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <div>
              <div className="text-sm mb-2">Тема</div>
              <select
                className="w-full px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                value={ui.theme ?? "system"}
                onChange={e => { setUi({...ui, theme: e.target.value}); applyTheme(e.target.value); }}
              >
                <option value="system">Авто</option>
                <option value="light">Светлая</option>
                <option value="dark">Тёмная</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div>
              <div className="text-sm mb-2">Плотность</div>
              <select
                className="w-full px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                value={ui.density ?? "normal"}
                onChange={e => setUi({...ui, density: e.target.value})}
              >
                <option value="compact">Компактная</option>
                <option value="normal">Обычная</option>
                <option value="comfortable">Комфорт</option>
              </select>
            </div>

            <div>
              <div className="text-sm mb-2">Стиль графиков</div>
              <select
                className="w-full px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                value={ui.charts ?? "vivid"}
                onChange={e => setUi({...ui, charts: e.target.value})}
              >
                <option value="vivid">Яркий (градиенты)</option>
                <option value="classic">Классический</option>
                <option value="mono">Моно</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div className="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4">
            <label className="flex items-center gap-2">
              <input type="checkbox" checked={!!ui.anim} onChange={e=>setUi({...ui, anim:e.target.checked})}/>
              Анимации
            </label>
            <label className="flex items-center gap-2">
              <input type="checkbox" checked={ui.legends ?? true} onChange={e=>setUi({...ui, legends:e.target.checked})}/>
              Показывать легенды на графиках
            </label>
            <label className="flex items-center gap-2">
              <input type="checkbox" checked={ui.compactCards ?? false} onChange={e=>setUi({...ui, compactCards:e.target.checked})}/>
              Компактные карточки
            </label>
          </div>

          <div className="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">Хранится: <code>munart_ui_v1</code>, тема — <code>munart_theme</code>.</div>
        </div>
      )}

      {/* === Вкладка: Уведомления === */}
      {tab==="notifications" && (
        <div className="max-w-3xl bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70 border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5">
          <h2 className="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Уведомления</h2>

          <div className="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-2">Каналы</div>
          <div className="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <label className="flex items-center gap-2">
              <input type="checkbox" checked={!!notif.email?.on}
                     onChange={e=>setNotif({...notif, email:{...(notif.email||{}), on:e.target.checked}})}/>
              Email
            </label>
            <label className="flex items-center gap-2">
              <input type="checkbox" checked={!!notif.telegram?.on}
                     onChange={e=>setNotif({...notif, telegram:{...(notif.telegram||{}), on:e.target.checked}})}/>
              Telegram
            </label>
            <label className="flex items-center gap-2">
              <input type="checkbox" checked={!!notif.inapp?.on}
                     onChange={e=>setNotif({...notif, inapp:{...(notif.inapp||{}), on:e.target.checked}})}/>
              Встроенные
            </label>
          </div>

          <div className="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-4">
            <input className="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                   placeholder="Email-адрес" value={notif.email?.addr||""}
                   onChange={e=>setNotif({...notif, email:{...(notif.email||{}), addr:e.target.value}})} />
            <input className="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                   placeholder="Telegram chat id" value={notif.telegram?.chatId||""}
                   onChange={e=>setNotif({...notif, telegram:{...(notif.telegram||{}), chatId:e.target.value}})} />
          </div>

          <div className="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-5 mb-2">Триггеры</div>
          <div className="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
            <label className="flex items-center gap-2">
              <input type="checkbox" checked={!!notif.assignments}
                     onChange={e=>setNotif({...notif, assignments:e.target.checked})}/>
              По назначениям
            </label>
            <label className="flex items-center gap-2">
              <input type="checkbox" checked={!!notif.deadlines}
                     onChange={e=>setNotif({...notif, deadlines:e.target.checked})}/>
              По дедлайнам
            </label>
            <label className="flex items-center gap-2">
              <input type="checkbox" checked={!!notif.statuses}
                     onChange={e=>setNotif({...notif, statuses:e.target.checked})}/>
              По изменениям статусов
            </label>
          </div>

          <div className="mt-5">
            <label className="inline-flex items-center gap-2">
              <input type="checkbox" checked={!!notif.enabled}
                     onChange={e=>setNotif({...notif, enabled:e.target.checked})}/>
              <span className="font-semibold">Активировать</span>
              <span className="text-slate-500 text-sm">(заготовка; отправка пока не подключена)</span>
            </label>
          </div>

          <div className="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">Хранится: <code>munart_notif_v1</code></div>
        </div>
      )}

      {/* === Вкладка: Сети (как было, только вынесено на отдельную вкладку) === */}
      {tab==="network" && (
        <div className="max-w-xl bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70 border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5">
          <h2 className="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Сети</h2>

          <label className="mt-1 flex items-center gap-2">
            <input type="checkbox" checked={netPrefs.grid} onChange={e=>saveNet({grid:e.target.checked})}/>
            Сетка (grid)
          </label>

          <label className="mt-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <input type="checkbox" checked={netPrefs.showLabels} onChange={e=>saveNet({showLabels:e.target.checked})}/>
            Показывать метки связей
          </label>

          <label className="mt-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <input type="checkbox" checked={netPrefs.maskSensitive} onChange={e=>saveNet({maskSensitive:e.target.checked})}/>
            Маскировать чувствительные поля
          </label>

          <label className="mt-3 block">
            <div className="mb-1">Тип связи по умолчанию</div>
            <select className="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                    value={netPrefs.defaultEdge} onChange={e=>saveNet({defaultEdge:e.target.value})}>
              <option value="L3">L3</option>
              <option value="L2">L2</option>
              <option value="VPN">VPN</option>
              <option value="DEP">Dependency</option>
            </select>
          </label>

          <div className="mt-3 text-xs text-slate-500">
            Сохраняется в localStorage: <code>munart_admin_prefs_v1</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      )}
    </div>
  );
}

import EmbedIframe from "../../components/EmbedIframe";

    <div className="p-4">

===== BEGIN FILE: munart_ui\src\pages\Tasks\index.jsx (text) =====
import React, { useMemo, useState } from 'react';
import { storage } from '../../lib/storageAdapter';

const COLUMNS = [
  { key:'todo',       title:'К выполнению' },
  { key:'inprogress', title:'В работе' },
  { key:'done',       title:'Готово' }
];

export default function Tasks(){
  const [projects] = useState(storage.getProjects());
  const [tasks, setTasks] = useState(storage.getTasks());
  const [form, setForm] = useState({ title:'', projectId: projects[0]?.id || '', assignee:'', due:'' });

  const add = ()=>{
    if(!form.title.trim()) return;
    const t = { id: storage.rid(), title: form.title.trim(), projectId: form.projectId, assignee: form.assignee||'—', status:'todo', due: form.due||null };
    const next = [...tasks, t];
    setTasks(storage.setTasks(next));
    setForm({ title:'', projectId: projects[0]?.id || '', assignee:'', due:'' });
  };
  const move = (id, status)=>{
    const next = tasks.map(t=> t.id===id ? { ...t, status } : t);
    setTasks(storage.setTasks(next));
  };

  const byCol = useMemo(()=>({
    todo: tasks.filter(t=>t.status==='todo'),
    inprogress: tasks.filter(t=>t.status==='inprogress'),
    done: tasks.filter(t=>t.status==='done')
  }),[tasks]);

  // --- Фактический прогресс (done / all) ---
  const total = tasks.length||1;
  const doneN = byCol.done.length;
  const progressPct = Math.round(100*doneN/total);

  return (
    <div className="p-4">
      <div className="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div className="bg-white/90 dark:bg-slate-900/70 border border-slate-200/60 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-2xl shadow-sm p-5">
          <h2 className="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-3">Поручения</h2>

          {/* Прогресс */}
          <div className="mb-4">
            <div className="text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-1">
              Выполнено: <b>{doneN}</b> из {total} ({progressPct}%)
            </div>
            <div className="h-2 rounded bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-800 overflow-hidden">
              <div className="h-2 bg-emerald-500" style={{width:`${progressPct}%`}}/>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* форма */}
          <div className="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
            <input className="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 w-64"
                   placeholder="Задача" value={form.title} onChange={e=>setForm({ ...form, title:e.target.value})}/>
            <select className="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                    value={form.projectId} onChange={e=>setForm({ ...form, projectId:e.target.value})}>
              {projects.map(p=><option key={p.id} value={p.id}>{p.name}</option>)}
            </select>
            <input className="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 w-40"
                   placeholder="Исполнитель" value={form.assignee} onChange={e=>setForm({ ...form, assignee:e.target.value})}/>
            <input type="date" className="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
                   value={form.due} onChange={e=>setForm({ ...form, due:e.target.value})}/>
            <button onClick={add}
                    className="px-3 py-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-900 text-white dark:bg-white dark:text-slate-900 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
              Добавить
            </button>
          </div>

          {/* Канбан */}
          <div className="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-3">
            {COLUMNS.map(col=>(
              <div key={col.key} className="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 p-3">
                <div className="font-medium mb-2">{col.title}</div>
                <div className="space-y-2">
                  {byCol[col.key].map(t=>(
                    <div key={t.id} className="border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg p-3 bg-white/80 dark:bg-slate-900/70">
                      <div className="text-sm font-medium">{t.title}</div>
                      <div className="text-xs text-slate-500">Проект: {projects.find(p=>p.id===t.projectId)?.name||'—'}</div>
                      <div className="flex gap-1 mt-2">
                        {COLUMNS.map(s=> s.key!==col.key &&
                          <button key={s.key} onClick={()=>move(t.id, s.key)}
                                  className="px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">
                            {'→ ' + s.title}
                          </button>
                        )}
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  ))}
                  {!byCol[col.key].length && <div className="text-xs text-slate-400">Пусто</div>}
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
===== END FILE: munart_ui\src\pages\Tasks\index.jsx =====

  plugins: [],
